nārāyaṇaṃ namaskṛtya naraṃ caiva narottamam
devīṃ sarasvatīṃ caiva tato jayam udīrayet Maṅg1
dvaipāyanauṣṭhapuṭaniḥsṛtam aprameyaṃ puṇyaṃ pavitram atha pāpaharaṃ śubhaṃ ca
yo bhārataṃ samadhigacchati vācyamānaṃ kiṃ tasya puṣkarajalair abhiṣecanena Maṅg2
namo vyāsāya gurave sarvajñāya maharṣaye
pārāśaryāya śāntāya namo nārāyaṇāya te Maṅg2alt
kṛtābhiṣekaṃ tanayam rājñaḥ pārīkṣitasya ha
draṣṭum abhyāyayuḥ prītyā śaunakādyā maharṣayaḥ 001.001
tān āgatān sa rājarṣiḥ pādyārghyādibhir arcitān
sukhopaviṣṭān viśrāntān kṛtasaṃpraśnasatkathān 001.002
tatkathābhiḥ kṛtāhlādaḥ praṇipatya kṛtāñjaliḥ
śatānīko 'tha papraccha nārāyaṇakathāṃ parām 001.003
yam āśritya jagannātham mama pūrvapitāmahāḥ
vipakṣāpahṛtaṃ rājyam avāpuḥ puruṣottamāḥ 001.004
drauṇibrahmāstranirdagdho mama yena pitāmahaḥ
parīkṣit prāṇasaṃyogaṃ devadevena lambhitaḥ 001.005
tasya devasya māhātmyaṃ devarṣisiddhamanujaiḥ
śrutaṃ subahuśo mayā stutasyāśeṣajanmanaḥ 001.006
kaḥ stotum īśas tam ajaṃ yasyaitat sacarācaram
avyayasyāprameyasya brahmāṇḍam udare śayam 001.007
rudraḥ krodhodbhavo yasya prasādāc ca pitāmahaḥ
tasya devasya kaḥ śaktaḥ pravaktuṃ vā vibhūtayaḥ 001.008
so 'ham icchāmi devasya tasya sarvātmanaḥ prabhoḥ
śrotum ārādhanaṃ yena nistareyaṃ bhavārṇavam 001.009
kenopāyena mantrair vā rahasyaiḥ paricaryayā
dānair vratopavāsair vā japyair homair athāpi vā 001.010
ārādhitaḥ samastānāṃ kleśānāṃ hānido hariḥ
śakyaḥ samārādhayituṃ tan naḥ śaṃsata sattamāḥ 001.011
vidyānām api sā vidyā śrutānām api tac chrutam
rahasyānāṃ rahasyaṃ tad yena viṣṇuḥ prasīdati 001.012
mantrāṇāṃ paramo mantro vratānāṃ tan mahāvratam
upoṣitaṃ hi tac chreṣṭhaṃ yena tuṣyati keśavaḥ 001.013
sā jihvā yā hariṃ stauti tac cittaṃ yat tadarpaṇam
tāv eva kevalau ślāghyau yau tatpūjākarau karau 001.014
sujanma deham atyantaṃ tad evāśeṣajanmasu
yad eva pulakodbhāsi viṣṇor nāmābhikīrtanāt 001.015
sā hānis tan mahac chidraṃ sā cāndhajaḍamūkatā
yan muhūrtaṃ kṣaṇaṃ vāpi vāsudevo na cintyate 001.016
nūnaṃ tat kaṇṭhaśālūkam athavā pratijihvikā
rogo vānyo na sā jihvā yā na vakti harer guṇān 001.017
santy anekā bilās tadvac śrotram apy alpamedhasām
dattvāvadhānaṃ yac chabde vinaiva harisaṃstutim 001.018
dharmārthakāmasaṃprāptau puruṣāṇāṃ viceṣṭitam
janmany aviphalā saikā yā govindāśrayā kriyā 001.019
durgasaṃsārakāntāram apāram abhidhāvatām
ekaḥ kṛṣṇanamaskāro muktitīrasya deśikaḥ 001.020
sarvaratnamayo meruḥ sarvāścaryamayaṃ nabhaḥ
sarvatīrthamayī gaṅgā sarvadevamayo hariḥ 001.021
evam ādiguṇo bhogaḥ kṛṣṇasyādbhutakarmaṇaḥ
śruto me bahuśo siddhaiḥ gīyamānas tathāparaiḥ 001.022
so 'ham icchāmi taṃ devaṃ sarvalokaparāyaṇam
nārāyaṇam aśeṣasya jagato hṛdy avasthitam 001.023
ārādhayitum īśānam anantam amitaujasam
śaṃkaraṃ jagataḥ prāṇaṃ smṛtamātrāghahāriṇam 001.024
tan mamādya muniśreṣṭhāḥ prasādayitum icchataḥ
upadeśapradānena prasādaṃ kartum arhata 001.025
tasyaitad vacanaṃ śrutvā bhaktim udvahato hareḥ
paritoṣaṃ paraṃ jagmur munayaḥ sarva eva te 001.026
sarve ca te muniśreṣṭhā bhṛguśreṣṭhaṃ ca śaunakam
yathārthaṃ bhagavaṃs tasmai kathyatām ity acodayan 001.027
sarvajñānanidhiḥ sphītas tvam atra bhṛgunandana
trailokyasarvasaṃdeha- tamodīpas tapodhana 001.028
evam ukto munivaraiḥ prītyā tasya ca bhūpateḥ
bhaktyā ca devadevasya pravaṇīkṛtamānasaḥ 001.029
kṛtvottarīyaparyaṅkaṃ śithilaṃ bhagavān atha
pratyuvāca mahābhāgaḥ śaunakas taṃ mahīpatim 001.030
yat pṛcchasi mahīpāla kṛṣṇasyārādhanaṃ prati
vratopavāsajapyādi tad ihaikamanāḥ śṛṇu 001.031
anādimat paraṃ brahma sarvaheyavivarjitam
vyāpi yat sarvabhūteṣu sthitaṃ sadasataḥ param 001.032
pradhānapuṃsor ajayor yataḥ kṣobhaḥ pravartate
nityayor vyāpinoś caiva jagadādau mahātmanoḥ 001.033
tatkṣobhakatvād brahmāṇḍa- sṛṣṭihetur nirañjanaḥ
ahetur api sarvātmanaḥ jāyate parameśvaraḥ 001.034
pradhānapuruṣatvaṃ ca tathaiveśvaralīlayā
samupaiti tataś caiva brahmatvaṃ chandataḥ prabhuḥ 001.035
tataḥ sthitau pālayitā viṣṇutvaṃ jagataḥ kṣaye
rudratvaṃ ca jagannāthaḥ svecchayā kurute 'vyayaḥ 001.036
tad ekam akṣaraṃ dhāma paraṃ sadasator mahat
bhedābhedasvarūpasthaṃ praṇipatya paraṃ padam 001.037
pravakṣyāmi yathā pūrvaṃ matpitrā kathitaṃ mama
tasyāpi kila tatpitrā tasmai cāha kilośanāḥ 001.038
tenāpi bhṛgum ārādhya prāptam ārādhanaṃ hareḥ
sakāśād brahmaṇaḥ prāptaṃ bhṛguṇāpi mahātmanā 001.039
marīcimiśraiś ca purā param etan maharṣibhiḥ
prāptaṃ sakāśād devasya brahmaṇo vyaktajanmanaḥ 001.040
yogaṃ brahmā paraṃ prāha maharṣīṇāṃ yadā prabhuḥ
samastavṛttisaṃrodhāt kaivalyapratipādakam 001.041
tadā jagatpatir brahmā praṇipatya maharṣibhiḥ
sarvaiḥ kilokto bhagavān ātmayoniḥ prajāhitam 001.042
yo yogo bhavatā prokto manovṛttinirodhajaḥ
prāptuṃ śakyaḥ sa tv anekaiḥ janmabhir jagataḥ pate 001.043
viṣayā durjayā nR̥ṇām indriyākarṣaṇāḥ prabho
vṛttayaś cetasaś cāpi capalā cātidurdharāḥ 001.044
rāgādayaḥ kathaṃ jetuṃ śakyā varṣaśatair api
na yogayogyaṃ hi mano bhavaty ebhir anirjitaiḥ 001.045
alpāyuṣaś ca puruṣā brahman kṛtayuge 'py amī
tretāyāṃ dvāpare caiva kimu prāpte kalau yuge 001.046
bhagavaṃs tvam upāyajñaḥ prasanno vaktum arhasi
anāyāsena yenemam uttarema bhavārṇavam 001.047
duḥkhāmbumagnāḥ puruṣāḥ prāpya brahma mahāplavam
uttareyur bhavāmbhodhiṃ tathā tvam anucintaya 001.048
evam uktas tadā brahmā kriyāyogaṃ mahātmanām
teṣām ṛṣīṇām ācaṣṭa narāṇāṃ hitakāmyayā 001.049
ārādhayata viśveśam nārāyaṇam atandritāḥ
bāhyālambanasāpekṣās tam ajaṃ jagataḥ patim 001.050
ijyāpūjānamaskāra- śuśrūṣābhir aharniśam
vratopavāsair vividhair brāhmaṇānāṃ ca tarpaṇaiḥ 001.051
tais taiś cābhimataiḥ kāmair ye ca cetasi tuṣṭidāḥ
aparicchedyamāhātmyam ārādhayata keśavam 001.052
tanniṣṭhās tadgatadhiyas tatkarmāṇas tadāśrayāḥ
taddṛṣṭayas tanmanasaḥ sarvasmin sa iti sthitaḥ 001.053
samastāny atha karmāṇi tatra sarvātmanātmani
saṃnyasyadhvaṃ sa vaḥ kartā samastāvaraṇakṣayam 001.054
etat tad akṣaraṃ brahma pradhānapuruṣāv ubhau
yato yasmin yathā cobhau sarvavyāpiny avasthitau 001.055
paraḥ parāṇāṃ paramaḥ sa ekaḥ puruṣottamaḥ
yasyābhinnam idaṃ sarvam yac ceṅgaṃ yac ca neṅgati 001.056
tam ārādhya jagannāthaṃ mokṣakāraṇam avyaktam
acintyam aparigraham kriyāyogena mucyate 001.057
iti te brahmaṇaḥ śrutvā rahasyam ṛṣisattamāḥ
narāṇām upakārāya yogaśāstrāṇi cakrire
kriyāyogaparāṇīha muktikāryāṇy anekaśaḥ 001.058
ārādhyate jagannātho yadanuṣṭhānatatparaiḥ
paramātmā hṛṣīkeśaḥ sarveśaḥ sarvabhāvanaḥ 001.059
tāni te nṛpaśārdūla sarvapāpaharāṇy aham
vakṣyāmi śrūyatām anyad rahasyam idam uttamam 001.060
saṃsārārṇavamagnānāṃ viṣayākrāntacetasām
uttāram icchatāṃ tasmād bhṛśaṃ yan nāntarair api
viṣṇupotaṃ vinā nānyat kiṃcid asti parāyaṇam 001.061
uttiṣṭhaṃś cintaya hariṃ vrajaṃś cintaya keśavam
bhuñjaṃś cintaya govindam svapaṃś cintaya mādhavam 001.062
evam ekāgracittas tvaṃ saṃśrito madhusūdanam
janmamṛtyujarāgrāhaṃ saṃsārāmbhas tariṣyasi 001.063
anantam īḍyaṃ puruṣaṃ purāṇaṃ jagadvidhātāram ajaṃ janitryam
samāśritā ye harim īśitāraṃ teṣāṃ bhavo nāsti hi muktibhājām 001.064
śrūyatāṃ kuruśārdūla saṃvādo 'yam anuttamaḥ
ambarīṣasya rājarṣeḥ saha devena cakriṇā 002.001
ambarīṣo mahīpālaḥ pālayann eva medinīm
udvigna eva dvandvāntam abhīpsuḥ puruṣarṣabhaḥ 002.002
devadevāt sa govindād abhīpsur dvandvasaṃkṣayam
tapas tepe nirāhāro gṛṇan brahma sanātanam 002.003
tasya kālena mahatā bhaktim udvahataḥ parām
tutoṣa bhagavān viṣṇuḥ sarvalokapatiḥ prabhuḥ 002.004
sa rūpam aindram āsthāya tam uvāca mahīpatim
meghagambhīranirghoṣo vāraṇendragatis tadā 002.005
rājarṣe vada yat kāryaṃ tava cetasy avasthitam
varado 'ham anuprāpto varaṃ varaya suvrata 002.006
evam uktas tato rājā vilokya ca puraṃdaraṃ
pratyuvācārghyam udyamya svāgataṃ te 'stv iti prabho 002.007
nāham ārādhayāmi tvāṃ tava baddho 'yam añjaliḥ
varārthināṃ tvaṃ varadaḥ prayacchābhimatān varān 002.008
varārthāya tvayānyaiś ca kriyate nṛpate tapaḥ
sa kim arthaṃ tvam asmatto na gṛhṇāsy abhivāṃchitam 002.009
na varārtham ayaṃ yatnas tvatto devapate mama
viṣṇor ārādhanārthāya viddhi māṃ tvaṃ kṛtodyamam 002.010
ahaṃ hi sarvadevānāṃ trailokyasya tatheśvaraḥ
pālayanti mamaivājñām ādityādyāḥ sadā surāḥ 002.011
ādityā vasavo rudrā nāsatyau marutāṃ gaṇāḥ
prajānāṃ patayaḥ sādhyā viśvedevā maharṣayaḥ 002.012
kurvanty ete mamaivājñāṃ siddhagandharvapannagāḥ
matto hi ko 'nyo varadaḥ pratigṛhṇīṣva vāñchitam 002.013
tvam indraḥ satyam evaitad devas tribhuvaneśvaraḥ
tvayāpi prāptam aiśvaryaṃ yatas taṃ toṣayāmy aham 002.014
trailokyaṃ tava deveśa vaśe yasya mahātmanaḥ 002.015,*(1)
saptodare śayā lokās tam īśaṃ toṣayāmy aham 002.015
yasya tvam amaraiḥ sarvaiḥ samavetāḥ sureśvara
dehaprāpto 'ntarastho vai taṃ namāmi janārdanam 002.016
nimeṣo brahmaṇo rātrir unmeṣo yasya vāsaraḥ
tam īḍyam īśam ajaraṃ praṇato 'smi janārdanam 002.017
yo hartā jagato devaḥ kartā pālāyitā ca yaḥ
trayasyāsya ca yo yonis taṃ viṣṇuṃ toṣayāmy aham 002.018
hiraṇyakaśipuḥ pūrvaṃ hiraṇyākṣaś ca te ripuḥ
tavānukampayā yena hatau daityau nato 'smi tam 002.019
balināpahṛtaṃ śakra dattaṃ yena purā tava
trailokyarājyaṃ taṃ baddhvā taṃ namāmi janārdanam 002.020
prasīda śakra gaccha tvam aham apy atra saṃsthitaḥ
tapas tapsye jagannāthaṃ draṣṭuṃ nārāyaṇaṃ harim 002.021
evam uktas tatas tena śakrarūpī janārdanaḥ
punar apy āha taṃ kopāt pārthivaṃ tapasi sthitam 002.022
yadi madvacanād adya na bhavāṃs tyakṣyate tapaḥ
vajraṃ te prahariṣyāmi budhyasvaitad yadīcchasi 002.023
nāpy alpam aparādhaṃ te karomi tridaśeśvara
tathāpi vadhayogyaṃ māṃ manyase cet kṣipāyudham 002.024
śrūyate kila govinde bhaktim udvahatāṃ nṛṇām
saṃsārārṇāvabhītānāṃ tridaśāḥ paripanthinaḥ 002.025
tāpaso 'haṃ kva niḥsaṅgaḥ kva ca kopas tavedṛśaḥ
vijñātam etad govinda- bhaktivighnopapāditam 002.026
bhavanti bahavo vighnā nare śreyaḥparāyaṇe
govindabhaktyabhyadhikaṃ śreyaś cānyan na vidyate 002.027
sa tvaṃ prahara vā mā vā mayi vajraṃ puraṃdara
nāham utsṛjya govindam anyam ārādhayāmi bhoḥ 002.028
na cāpi vajraṃ vajrī vā tvaṃ ca nānye surāsurāḥ
śaktā nihantum īśāne hṛdayasthe janārdane 002.029
kiṃ ca no bahunoktena nāhaṃ vakṣyāmy ataḥ paraṃ
yathepsitaṃ kuruṣva tvaṃ kariṣye 'ham abhīpsitam 002.030
evam uktvā surapatiṃ pārthivaḥ sa punas tapaḥ
cacāra maunam āsthāya tenātuṣyata keśavaḥ 002.031
saṃdarśayām āsa tataḥ svaṃ vapuḥ kaiṭabhārdanaḥ
caturbhujam udārāṅgaṃ śaṅkhacakragadādharam 002.032
kirīṭasragdharaṃ spaṣṭaṃ nīlotpaladalacchavim
airāvataś ca garuḍas tatkṣaṇāt samadṛśyata 002.033
sa ca rājavaro devaṃ pītavāsasam acyutam
vilokya bhaktiśirasā sahasaiva mahīṃ yayau 002.034
pratyuvāca ca bhūpālaḥ praṇipatya kṛtāñjaliḥ
romāñcitatanuḥ stotram padmanābhaṃ tato 'stuvat 002.035
ādideva jayājeya jaya sargādikāraka
jayāspaṣṭaprakāśāṇḍa bṛhanmūrte jayākṣara 002.036
jaya sarvagatācintya jaya janmajarāpaha
jaya vyāpiñ jayābheda sarvabhūteṣv avasthita 002.037
jaya yajñapate nātha havyakavyāśanāvyaya
jaya vijñātasiddhānta māyāmohaka keśava 002.038
lokasthityartham anagha varāha jaya bhūdhara
nṛsiṃha jaya devāri- vakṣaḥsthalavidāraṇa 002.039
devānām aribhītānām ārtināśana vāmana
jaya krāntasamastorvī- nabhaḥsvarlokabhāvana 002.040
jitaṃ te jagatām īśa jitaṃ te sarva sarvada 002.*(2)
jitaṃ te sarvabhūteśa yogidhyeya namo 'stu te 002.041
namo 'stv avyapadeśyāya namaḥ sūkṣmasvarūpiṇe
namas trimūrtaye tubhyaṃ viśvamūrte namo 'stu te 002.042
brahmādyaiś cintyate rūpaṃ yat tat sadasataḥ paraṃ
viśeṣair aviśeṣyāya tasmai tubhyaṃ namo namaḥ 002.043
puruṣākhyaṃ tato rūpaṃ nirguṇaṃ guṇabhoktṛ ca
prakṛteḥ parataḥ sūkṣmaṃ tan namasyāmi te hare 002.044
avyaktādiviśeṣāntam atisūkṣmatamaṃ mahat
prākṛtaṃ tava tad rūpaṃ tasmai deva namāmy aham 002.045
rūpair nānāvidhair yaś ca tadrūpāntaragocaram
līlayā vyavahāras te tasmai devātmane namaḥ 002.046
prasīda viṣṇo govinda śaṅkhacakragadādhara
dharādharāravindākṣa vāsudeva maheśvara 002.047
itthaṃ stuto jagannāthaḥ proktavān iti keśavaḥ
ambarīṣaṃ pṛthivīśaṃ jagat saṃnādayan girā 002.048
ambarīṣa prasanno 'smi bhaktyā stotreṇa cānagha
varaṃ vṛṇīṣva dharmajña yat te manasi vartate 002.049
eṣa eva varaḥ ślāghyo yad dṛṣṭo 'si jagatpate
tvaddarśanam apuṇyānāṃ svapneṣv api hi durlabham 002.050
bālyāt prabhṛti yā deva tvayi bhaktir mamācyuta
vetti tāṃ bhagavān eva hṛdisthaḥ sarvadehinām 002.051
tvatprasādān mameśāna rājyam avyāhataṃ bhuvi
kośadaṇḍau tathātīva śarīrārogyam uttamam 002.052
striyo 'nnapānasāmarthyā hāniḥ svalpāpi nāsti me
balaṃ nāgasahasrasya dhārayāmy arisūdana 002.053
saṃtatir nibhṛtā bhṛtyā sānurāgāś ca me janāḥ
dharmahāniś ca deveśa na hi me pālane bhuvaḥ 002.054
yad yad icchāmy ahaṃ tat tat sarvam asti jagatpate
etenaivānumānena prasanno bhagavān iti 002.055
jñātaṃ mayā hi govinde nāprasanne vibhūtayaḥ
evaṃ sarvasukhāhlāda- madhyastho 'pi ca keśava 002.056
punarāvṛttiduḥkhānāṃ trāsād udvignamānasaḥ
mayi prasādābhimukhaṃ manas te yadi keśava
tan mām agādhe saṃsāre magnam uddhartum arhasi 002.057
sukhāni tāni naivānte yeṣāṃ duḥkhaṃ na tat sukham
yad ante duḥkham āgāmi kiṃpākasyaiva bhakṣaṇam 002.058
sa prasādaṃ kuru guro jagatām tvaṃ janārdana
jñānadānena yenemāṃ vāgurān nistaremahi 002.059
ity uktas tasya govindaḥ kathayām āsa yogavit
yogaṃ nirbījam atyanta- duḥkhasaṃyogabheṣajam 002.060
upadiṣṭe tato yoge praṇipatyācyutaṃ nṛpaḥ
punaḥ prāha mahābāhur vinayāvanataḥ sthitaḥ 002.061
devadeva tvayā yogo yaḥ prokto madhusūdana
naiṣa prāpyo mayā nānyair mānavair ajitendriyaiḥ 002.062
viṣayā durjayāḥ puṃbhir indriyākarṣiṇaḥ sadā
indriyāṇāṃ jayaṃ teṣu kaḥ śaktānāṃ kariṣyati 002.063
ahaṃ mameti cākhyāti durjayaṃ cañcalaṃ manaḥ
rāgādayaḥ kathaṃ jetuṃ śakyā janmāntarair api 002.064
so 'ham icchāmi deveśa tvatprasādād anirjitaiḥ
rāgādibhir amartyatvaṃ prāptuṃ prakṣīṇakalmaṣaḥ 002.065
yady evaṃ muktikāmas tvaṃ naranātha śṛṇuṣva tat
kriyāyogaṃ samastānāṃ kleśānāṃ hānikārakam 002.066
manmanā bhava madbhakto madyājī māṃ namaskuru
mām evaiṣyasi yuktvaivam ātmānaṃ matparāyaṇaḥ 002.067
madbhāvanā madyajanā madbhaktā matparāyaṇāḥ
mama pūjāparāś caiva mayi yānti layaṃ narāḥ 002.068
sarvabhūteṣu māṃ paśya samavasthitam īśvaram
kartāsi kena vairatvaṃ evaṃ doṣān prahāsyasi 002.069
jaṅgamājaṅgame jñāte mayy ātmani tathā tava
rāgalobhādināśena bhavitrī kṛtakṛtyatā 002.070
bhaktyātipravaṇasyāpi cañcalatvān mano yadi
mayy anāsādavad bhūpa kuru madrūpiṇīṃ tanum 002.071
suvarṇarajatādyais tvaṃ śailamṛddārulekhajām
pūjāmaharhair vividhaiḥ saṃpūjaya ca pārthiva 002.072
tasyāṃ cittaṃ samāveśya tyājayānyān vyapāśrayān
pūjitā saiva te bhaktyā dhyātā caivopakāriṇī 002.073
gacchaṃs tiṣṭhan svapan bhuñjaṃs tām evāgre ca pṛṣṭhataḥ
upary adhas tathā pārśve cintayāntas tathātmanaḥ 002.074
snānais tīrthodakair hṛdyaiḥ puṣpagandhānulepanaiḥ
vāsobhir bhūṣaṇair bhakṣyair gītavādyair manoharaiḥ 002.075
yac ca yac ca nṛpeṣṭaṃ te kiṃcid bhojyādi tena tām
bhaktinamro naraśreṣṭha prīṇayārcāṃ kṛtāṃ mama 002.076
rāgeṇākṛṣyate ceto gandharvābhimukhaṃ yadi
mayi buddhiṃ samāveśya gāyethā mama tāṃ kathām 002.077
kathāyāṃ ramate ceto yadi tatbhāvanā mama
śrotavyā prītiyuktena avatāreṣu yā kathā 002.078
evaṃ mayy arpitamanāś cetaso ye vyapāśrayāḥ
heyās tān akhilān bhūpa parityakṣyasy abhīr bhava 002.079
akṣīṇarāgadoṣo 'pi matkriyā paramaḥ param
padam āpsyasi mā bhais tvaṃ mayy arpitamanā bhava 002.080
mayi saṃnyasya sarvaṃ tvam ātmānaṃ yat tavāsti ca
madarthaṃ kuru karmāṇi mā ca dharmavyatikramam 002.081
rājyaṃ kuru naraśreṣṭha nivedya pṛthivīṃ mama
tadvyāghātaparā ye ca jahi tān avanīpate 002.082
etenaivopadeśena vyākhyātam akhilaṃ tava
kriyāyogaṃ samāsthāya mayy arpitamanā bhava 002.083
maddhitāya jagannātha kriyāyogāśritaṃ mama
vistareṇedam ākhyāhi prasannas tvaṃ hi duḥkhahā 002.084
tvām ṛtena hi no vaktuṃ samartho 'nyo jagadguro
guhyam etat pavitraṃ ca tad ācakṣya prasīda me 002.085
ākhyāsyaty etad akhilaṃ vasiṣṭhas te purohitaḥ
matprasādād avikalaṃ sa ca vetsyaty aśeṣataḥ 002.086
ity uktvāntardadhe devaḥ sarvalokeśvaro hariḥ
sa ca rājā vanād bhūyo nijam abhyāgamat puram 002.087
rājyasthas tu mahīpālaḥ praṇipatya purohitam
vasiṣṭhaṃ paripapraccha viṣṇor ārādhanaṃ prati 003.001
devadevena bhagavann ādiṣṭo 'si mahātmanā
kriyāyogāśritaṃ sarvaṃ vyākhyāsyati bhavān kila 003.002
sa tvāṃ pṛcchāmy ahaṃ sarvaṃ kriyāyogena keśavam
saṃtoṣayitum īśānaṃ yathā śakṣyāmi tad vada 003.003
devaprasādād akhilā mamāpi smṛtir āgatā
jñānam etad aśeṣaṃ te kathayāmi nibodha tat 003.004
bhaktimān abhavad daityo hiraṇyakaśipoḥ sutaḥ
nārāyaṇe mahāprajñaḥ sarvalokaparāyaṇe
sa papraccha bhṛguśreṣṭhaṃ śukram ātmapurohitam 003.005
bhagavan nṛsiṃharūpasya viṣṇos tātaṃ jighāṃsataḥ
dṛṣṭaṃ dehe mayā sarvaṃ trailokyaṃ bhūrbhuvādikam 003.006
brahmā prajāpatiś cendro rudraiḥ paśupatiḥ saha
vasavo 'ṣṭau tathādityā dvādaśāhaḥkṣapā mahī 003.007
diśo nabhas tārakaughaṃ nakṣatragrahasaṃkulam
aśvinau marutaḥ sādhyā viśvedevās tatha rṣayaḥ 003.008
varṣācalās tathā nadyaḥ sapta sapta kulācalāḥ
samudrāḥ sapta ṛtavaḥ kāntārāṇi vanāni ca
nagaragrāmatarubhiḥ samāvetaṃ ca bhūtalam 003.009
etac cānyac ca yat kiṃcid devarṣipitṛmānavam
satiryagūrdhvapātālaṃ tasya dṛṣṭaṃ tanau mayā 003.010
so 'haṃ tam ajaraṃ devaṃ duṣṭadaityanivarhaṇam
ārādhayitum icchāmi bhagavaṃs tvadanujñayā 003.011
anugrāhyo 'smi yadi te mamāyaṃ bhaktimān iti
tan mamopadiśādya tvaṃ mahad ārādhanaṃ hareḥ 003.012
anugrāhyo 'si devasya nūnam avyaktajanmanaḥ
ārādhanāya daityendra yat te tatpravaṇaṃ manaḥ 003.013
yadi devapatiṃ viṣṇum ārādhayitum icchasi
bhagavantam anādyantaṃ bhava bhāgavato 'sura 003.014
na hy abhāgavatair viṣṇur jñātuṃ stotuṃ ca tattvataḥ
draṣṭuṃ vā śakyate martyaiḥ praveṣṭuṃ kuta eva hi 003.015
janmabhir bahubhiḥ pūtā narās tadgatacetasaḥ
bhavanti vai bhāgavatās te viṣṇuṃ praviśanti ca 003.016
anekajanmasaṃsāra- cite pāpasamuccaye
nākṣīṇe jāyate puṃsāṃ govindābhimukhī matiḥ 003.017
pradveṣaṃ yāti govinde dvijān vedāṃś ca nindati
yo naras taṃ vijānīyād asurāṃśasamudbhavam 003.018
pāṣaṇḍeṣu ratiḥ puṃsāṃ hetuvādānukūlatā
jāyate viṣṇumāyāmbhaḥ- patitānāṃ durātmanām 003.019
yadā pāpakṣayaḥ puṃsāṃ tadā vedadvijātiṣu
viṣṇau ca yajñapuruṣe śraddhā bhavati te yathā 003.020
yadā svalpāvaśeṣas tu narāṇāṃ pāpasaṃcayaḥ
bhavanti te bhāgavatās tadā daityapate narāḥ 003.021
bhrāmyatām atra saṃsāre narāṇāṃ karmadurgame
hastāvalambado hy eko bhaktiprīto janārdanaḥ 003.022
sa tvaṃ bhāgavato bhūtvā sarvapāpaharaṃ harim
ārādhaya paraṃ bhaktyā prītim eṣyati keśavaḥ 003.023
kiṃlakṣaṇā bhāgavatā bhavanti puruṣā guro
yac ca bhāgavataiḥ kāryaṃ tan me kathaya bhārgava 003.024
karmaṇā manasā vācā prāṇināṃ yo na hiṃsakaḥ
bhāvabhaktaś ca govinde daitya bhāgavato hi saḥ 003.025
yo brāhmaṇāṃś ca vedāṃś ca nityam envānumaṃsyati
na ca drogdhā paraṃ vāde daitya bhāgavato hi saḥ 003.026
sarvān devān hariṃ vetti sarvalokāṃś ca keśavam
tebhyaś ca nānyam ātmānaṃ daitya bhāgavato hi saḥ 003.027
devaṃ manuṣyam anyaṃ vā paśupakṣipipīlikān
tarupāṣāṇakaṣṭhādi bhūmyambhogaganaṃ diśaḥ 003.028
ātmānaṃ vāpi deveśān nātiriktaṃ janārdanāt
yo bhajeta vijānīṣva taṃ vai bhāgavataṃ naram 003.029
sarvaṃ bhagavato bhāvo yad bhūtaṃ bhavasaṃsthitam
iti yo vai vijānāti sa tu bhāgavato naraḥ 003.030
bhavabhītiṃ haraty eṣa bhaktibhāvena bhāvitaḥ
bhagavān iti bhāvo yaḥ sa tu bhāgavato naraḥ 003.031
bhāvaṃ na kurute yas tu sarvabhūteṣu pāpakam
karmaṇā manasā vācā sa tu bhāgavato naraḥ 003.032
bāhyārthanirapekṣo yo bhakto bhagavataḥ kriyām
bhāvena niṣpādayati jñeyo bhāgavatas tu saḥ 003.033
nārayo yasya na snigdhā na codāsī na vṛttayaḥ
paśyataḥ sarvam evedaṃ viṣṇuṃ bhāgavato hi saḥ 003.034
sutapteneha tapasā yajñair vā bahudakṣiṇaiḥ
tāṃ gatiṃ na narā yānti yāṃ vai bhāgavatā gatāḥ 003.035
yogacyutair bhāgavatair devarājaḥ śatakratuḥ
arvāṅ nirīkṣyate yajñī kimu ye yogapāragāḥ 003.036
yajñaniṣpattaye vedā yajño yajñapateḥ kṛte
tattoṣaṇāya bhāvena tasmād bhāgavato bhava 003.037
yena sarvātmanā viṣṇau bhaktyā bhāvo niveśitaḥ
daityeśvara kṛtārthatvāc ślāghyo bhāgavato hi saḥ 003.038
api naḥ sa kule dhanyo jāyate kulapāvanaḥ
bhagavān bhaktibhāvena yena viṣṇur upāsitaḥ 003.039
yaḥ kārayati devārcāṃ hṛdayālambanaṃ hareḥ
sa naro viṣṇusālokyam upaiti dhūtakalmaṣaḥ 003.040
yaś ca devālayaṃ bhaktyā viṣṇoḥ kārayati svayam
sa saptapuruṣāṃl lokān viṣṇor nayati mānavaḥ 003.041
yāvanty abdāni devārcā hares tiṣṭhati mandire
tāvadvarṣasahasrāṇi viṣṇuloke sa modate 003.042
devārcā lakṣaṇopetā tadgṛhaṃ satataṃ divi
niṣkāmaṃ ca mano yasya sa yāty akṣarasātmyatām 003.043
puṣpāṇy atisugandhīni manojñāni ca yaḥ pumān
prayacchati hṛṣīkeśe tadbhāvagatamānasaḥ 003.044
dhūpāṃś ca vividhāṃs tāṃs tān gandhāḍhyaṃ cānulepanam
dīpāvalyupahārāṃś ca yac cābhīṣṭam athātmanaḥ 003.045
naraḥ so 'nudinaṃ yajñaṃ karoty ārādhanaṃ hareḥ
yajñeśo bhagavān viṣṇur makhair api hi toṣyate 003.046
bahūpakaraṇā yajñā nānāsaṃbhāravistarāḥ
prāpyante te dhanayutair manuṣyair nālpasaṃcayaiḥ 003.047
bhaktyā ca puruṣaiḥ pūjā kṛtā dūrvāṅkurair api
harer dadāti hi phalaṃ sarvayajñaiḥ sudurlabham 003.048
yāni puṣpāṇi hṛdyāni dhūpagandhānulepanam
dayitaṃ bhūṣaṇaṃ yac ca ye ca kauśeyavāsasī 003.049
yāni cābhyavahārāṇi bhakṣyāṇi ca phalāni ca
prayaccha tāni govinde bhavethāś caiva tanmanāḥ 003.050
ādyantaṃ yajñapuruṣaṃ yathāśaktyā prasādaya
ārādhya yāti taṃ devaṃ tasminn eva naro layam 003.051
puṇyais tīrthodakair gandhair madhunā sarpiṣā tathā
kṣīreṇa snāpayed īśam acyutaṃ jagataḥ patim 003.052
dadhikṣīrahradān puṇyāṃs tato lokān madhucyutaḥ
prayāsyasy asuraśreṣṭha nirvṛtiṃ cāpi śāśvatīm 003.053
stotrair gītais tathā vādyair brāhmaṇānāṃ ca tarpaṇaiḥ
manasaś caikatāyogād ārādhaya janārdanam 003.054
ārādhya taṃ videhānāṃ puruṣāḥ saptasaptatiḥ
haihayāḥ pañcapañcāśad amṛtatvam upāgatāḥ 003.055
sa tvam ebhiḥ prakārais tam upavāsaiś ca keśavam
toṣayādyo hi tuṣṭo 'sau viṣṇur dvandvapraśāntidaḥ 003.056
upavāsair hṛṣīkeśaḥ kathaṃ tuṣyati bhārgava
parihārāṃs tathācakṣva ye tyājyāś copavāsinām 004.001
yad yat kāryaṃ yathā caiva keśavārādhane naraiḥ
tat sarvaṃ vistarād brahman yathāvad vaktum arhasi 004.002
smṛtaḥ saṃpūjito dhūpa- puṣpādyair dayitair hariḥ
bhoginām upakārāya kiṃ punaś copavāsinām 004.003
upāvṛttas tu pāpebhyo yas tu vāso guṇaiḥ saha
upavāsaḥ sa vijñeyaḥ sarvabhogavivarjitaḥ 004.004
ekarātraṃ dvirātraṃ vā trirātram athavāparam
upavāsī hariṃ yas tu bhaktyā dhyāyati mānavaḥ 004.005
tannāmajāpī tatkarma- ratis tadgatamānasaḥ
niṣkāmo daitya sa brahma param āpnoty asaṃśayam 004.006
yaṃ ca kāmam abhidhyāyan keśavārpitamānasaḥ
upoṣyati tam āpnoti prasanne garuḍadhvaje 004.007
kathyate ca purā vipraḥ pulastyo brahmavādinā
dālbhyena pṛṣṭo 'kathayad yathaitad arisūdana 004.008
brāhmaṇaiḥ kṣatriyair vaiśyaiḥ śūdraiḥ strībhis tathā mune
saṃsāragartapaṅkasthaiḥ sugatiḥ prāpyate katham 004.009
anārādhya jagannāthaṃ sarvadhātāram acyutam
nirvyalīkena cittena kaḥ prayāsyati sadgatim 004.010
viṣayagrāhi vai yasya na cittaṃ keśavārpitam
sa kathaṃ pāpapaṅkāṅkī naro yāsyati sadgatim 004.011
yadi saṃsāraduḥkhārtaḥ sugatiṃ gantum icchasi
tadārādhaya sarveśaṃ jagaddhātāram acyutam 004.012
puṣpaiḥ sugandhair hṛdyaiś ca dhūpaiḥ sāgarucandanaiḥ
vāsobhir bhūṣaṇair bhakṣyair upavāsaparāyaṇaḥ 004.013
yadi saṃsāranirvedād abhivāñchasi sadgatim
tadārādhaya govindaṃ yac ceṣṭaṃ tava cetasi 004.014
puṣpāṇi yadi te na syuḥ śastaṃ pādapapallavaiḥ
dūrvāṅkurair api brahmaṃs tadabhāve 'rcayācyutam 004.015
sugandhipuṣpadīpādyair yaḥ kuryāt keśavālaye
sarvatīrthaphalaṃ tasya saṃbhavet keśavārcayā
sabāhyābhyantaraṃ yas tu mārjayed acyutālayam
sabāhyābhyantaraṃ tasya kāyo niṣkalmaṣo bhavet 004.*(3)
puṣpapatrāmbubhir dhūpair yathāvibhavam acyutaḥ
pūjitas tuṣṭim atulāṃ bhaktyāyāty ekacetasām 004.016
yaḥ sadāyatane viṣṇoḥ kurute mārjanakriyām
sa pāṃsubhūmer dehāc ca sarvapāpaṃ vyapohati 004.017
yāvantyaḥ pāṃsukaṇikā mārjyante keśavālaye
dināni divi tāvanti tiṣṭhaty astamalo naraḥ 004.018
ahany ahani yat pāpaṃ kurute dvijasattama
gocarmamātraṃ saṃmārjya hanti tat keśavālaye 004.019
yaś copalepanaṃ kuryād viṣṇor āyatane naraḥ
so 'pi lokaṃ samāsādya modate ca śatakratoḥ 004.020
mṛdā dhātuvikārair vā varṇakair gomayena vā
upalepanakṛd yāti vimānaṃ maṇicitritam 004.021
udakābhyukṣaṇaṃ viṣṇor yaḥ karoti tathā gṛhe
so 'pi gacchati yatrāste bhagavān yādasāṃ patiḥ 004.022
puṣpaprakaram atyarthaṃ sugandhaṃ keśavālaye
upalipte naro dattvā na durgatim avāpnuyāt 004.023
vimānam atividyoti sarvaratnamayaṃ divi
samāpnoti naro dattvā dīpakaṃ keśavālaye 004.024
yas tu saṃvatsaraṃ pūrṇaṃ tilapātraprado naraḥ
dhvajaṃ tu viṣṇave dadyāt samam etat phalaṃ dvija 004.025
vidhunvan hanti vātena dātur ajñānataḥ kṛtam
pāpaṃ ketur gṛhe viṣṇor divārātram asaṃśayam 004.026
gītavādyādibhir devaṃ ya upāste janārdanam
gāndharvair gītanṛtyaiḥ sa vimānastho niṣevyate 004.027
jātismaratvaṃ medhāṃ ca tathaivoparame smṛtim
prāpnoti viṣṇvāyatane puṇyākhyānakathākaraḥ 004.028
upoṣitaḥ pūjito vā dṛṣṭo vā namito 'pi vā
pradambha harate (?) pāpaṃ ko na seved dhariṃ tataḥ
vedavādakriyāyajña- snānatīrthaphalaṃ param
aṣṭāṅgapraṇipātena praṇipatya hariṃ labhet
pragamya hṛdā śirasā pādapadme mahītale
niṣkalmaṣo bhavet sadyo na nāṭī pādapāṃsunā
ekasya kṛṣṇasya krājataḥ praṇāmo daśāśvamedhāvabhṛthena tulyaḥ
daśāśvamedhaiḥ punar eti janma kṛṣṇapraṇāmī na punarbhavāya 004.*(4)
evaṃ deveśvaro bhaktyā yena viṣṇur upāsitaḥ
sa prāpnoti gatiṃ ślāghyāṃ yāṃ yām icchati cetasā 004.029
devatvaṃ manujaiḥ kaiścid gandharvatvaṃ tathāparaiḥ
vidyādharatvam aparair ārādhyāptaṃ janārdanam 004.030
śakraḥ kratuśateneśam ārādhya garuḍadhvajam
devendratvaṃ gatas tasmān nānyaḥ pūjyatamaḥ kvacit 004.031
devebhyo 'pi hi pūjyas tu svagurur brahmacāriṇaḥ
tasyāpi yajñapuruṣo viṣṇuḥ pūjyo dvijottama 004.032
striyaś ca bhartāram ṛte pūjyam anyan na daivatam
bhartur gṛhasthasya sataḥ pūjyo yajñapatir hariḥ 004.033
vaikhānasānām ārādhyas tapobhir madhusūdanaḥ
dhyeyaḥ parivrājakānāṃ vāsudevo mahātmanām 004.034
evaṃ sarvāśramāṇāṃ hi vāsudevaḥ parāyaṇam
sarveṣāṃ caiva varṇānāṃ tam ārādhyāpnuyād gatim 004.035
śṛṇuṣva gadataḥ kāmyām upavāsāṃs tathāparān
tat tam āśritya yān kāmān kurvītepsitam ātmanaḥ 004.036
ekādaśyāṃ śuklapakṣe phālgune māsi yo naraḥ
japet kṛṣṇeti devasya nāma bhaktyā punaḥpunaḥ 004.037
devārcane cāṣṭaśataṃ kṛtvaitat tu japec chuciḥ
prātaḥ prasthānakāle ca utthāne skhalite kṣute 004.038
pāṣaṇḍapatitāṃś caiva tathaivāntyāvasāyinaḥ
nālapeta tathā kṛṣṇam arcayec chraddhayānvitaḥ
idaṃ codāharet kṛṣṇe manaḥ saṃdhāya tatparaḥ 004.039
kṛṣṇa kṛṣṇa kṛpālus tvam agatīnāṃ gatir bhava
saṃsārāntarnimagnānāṃ prasīda madhusūdana 004.040
evaṃ prasādyopāvāsaṃ kṛtvā niyatamānasaḥ
pūrvāhna eva cānyedyur gavyaṃ saṃprāsya vai sakṛt
snāto 'rcayitvā kṛṣṇeti punar nāma prakīrtayet 004.041
vāridhārātrayaṃ caiva vikṣiped devapādayoḥ
caitravaiśākhayoś caiva tadvaj jyeṣṭhe tu pūjayet 004.042
martyaloke gatiṃ śreṣṭhāṃ dālbhya prāpnoti vai naraḥ
utkrāntikāle kṛṣṇasya smaraṇaṃ ca tathāpnute 004.043
āṣāḍhe śrāvaṇe caiva māse bhādrapade tathā
tathaivāśvayuje devam anena vidhinā naraḥ 004.044
upoṣya saṃpūjya tathā keśaveti ca kīrtayet
gomūtraprāśanāt pūrvaṃ svargalokagatiṃ vrajet 004.045
ārādhitasya jagatām īśvarasyāvyāyātmanaḥ
utkrāntikāle smaraṇaṃ keśavasya tathāpnuyāt 004.046
kṣīrasya prāśanaṃ yas tu vidhiṃ cemaṃ yathoditam
kārttikādi yathānyāyaṃ kuryān māsacatuṣṭayam 004.047
tenaiva vidhinā brahman viṣṇor nāma prakīrtayet
sa yāti viṣṇusālokyaṃ viṣṇuṃ smarati ca kṣaye 004.048
pratimāsaṃ dvijātibhyo dadyād dānaṃ yathecchayā
cāturmāsye ca saṃpūrṇe puṇyaṃ śravaṇakīrtanam 004.049
kathāṃ vā vāsudevasya tadgītīr vāpi kārayet
evam etāṃ gatiṃ śreṣṭhāṃ devanāmānukīrtanāt 004.050
kathitaṃ pāraṇaṃ yat te kārṣṇaṃ māsacatuṣṭayam
ādhipatyaṃ tathā bhogāṃs tena prāpnoti mānuṣān 004.051
dvitīyena tathā bhogān aindrān prāpnoti mānavaḥ
viṣṇor lokaṃ tṛtīyena pāraṇena tathāpnuyāt 004.052
evam etat samākhyātaṃ gatiprāpakam uttamam
vidhānaṃ dvijaśārdūla kṛṣṇatuṣṭipradaṃ nṛṇām 004.053
sugatidvādaśīm etāṃ śraddadhānas tu yo naraḥ
upoṣya ca tathā nārī prāpnoti trividhāṃ gatim 004.054
eṣā dhanyā pāpaharā tithir nityam upāsitā
ārādhanāya śiṣṭaiṣā devadevasya cakriṇaḥ 004.055
pañcadaśyāṃ ca śuklasya phālgunasyaiva sattama
pāṣaṇḍapatitāṃś caiva tathaivāntyāvasāyinaḥ 005.001
nāstikān bhinnavṛttīṃś ca pāpinaś cāpy anālapan
nārāyaṇe gatamanāḥ puruṣo niyatendriyaḥ 005.002
tiṣṭhan vrajan praskhalite kṣute vāpi janārdanam
kīrtayet tatkriyākāle saptakṛtvaḥ prakīrtayet 005.003
lakṣmyā samanvitaṃ devam arcayec ca janārdanam
saṃdhyāvyuparame cendu- svarūpaṃ harim īśvaram 005.004
rātriṃ ca lakṣmīṃ saṃcintya samyag arghyena pūjayet
naktaṃ ca bhuñjīta naras tailakṣāravivarjitam 005.005
tathaiva caitravaiśākha- jyeṣṭheṣu munisattama
arcayīta yathāproktaṃ prāpte prāpte tu taddine 005.006
niṣpāditaṃ bhaved ekam pāraṇaṃ dālbhya bhaktitaḥ
dvitīyaṃ cāpi vakṣyāmi pāraṇaṃ dvijasattama 005.007
āṣāḍhe śrāvaṇe māsi prāpte bhādrapade tathā
tathaivāśvayuje 'bhyarcya śrīdharaṃ ca śriyā saha 005.008
samyak candramase dattvā bhuñjītārghyaṃ yathāvidhi
dvitīyam etad ākhyātaṃ tṛtīyaṃ pāraṇaṃ śṛṇu 005.009
kārttikādiṣu māseṣu tathaivābhyarcya keśavam
bhūtyā samanvitaṃ dadyāc śaśāṅkāyārhanaṃ niśi 005.010
bhuñjīta ca tathā proktaṃ tṛtīyam iti pāraṇam
pratipūjāsu dadyāc ca brāhmaṇebhyaś ca dakṣiṇām 005.011
pratimāsaṃ ca vakṣyāmi prāśanaṃ kāyaśodhanam
caturaḥ prathamān māsān pañcagavyam udāhṛtam 005.012
kuśodakaṃ tathaivānyad uktaṃ māsacatuṣṭayam
sūryāṃśutaptaṃ tadvac ca jalaṃ māsacatuṣṭayam 005.013
gītavādyādikaṃ pāṭhyaṃ tathā kṛṣṇasya vā kathān
kāriyīta ca devasya pāraṇe pāraṇe gate 005.014
evaṃ saṃpūjya vidhivat sapatnīkaṃ janārdanam
nāpnotīṣtaviyogādīn pumān yoṣid athāpi vā 005.015
janārdanaṃ salakṣmīkam arcayet prathamaṃ tataḥ
saśrīkaṃ śrīdharaṃ bhaktyā tṛtīye bhūtikeśavau 005.016
yāvanty etadvidhānena pāraṇenārcati prabhum
tāvanti janmāny asukhaṃ nāpnotīṣṭaviyogajam 005.017
devasya ca prasādena maraṇe prāpya tatsmṛtim 005.018,*(6)
kule satāṃ sphītadhane bhogabhuj jāyate naraḥ 005.018
nāriṃ prāpnoti na vyādhiṃ narakaṃ ca na paśyati
durgamaṃ yamamārgaṃ ca nekṣate dvijasattama 005.*(5)
śrotum icchāmy ahaṃ tāta yamamārgaṃ sudurgamam
yathā sukhena saṃyānti mānavās tad vadasva me 005.019
pratimāsaṃ tu nāmāni kṛṣṇasyaitāni dvādaśa
kṛtopavāsaḥ susnātaḥ pūjayitvā janārdanam
uccārayan naro 'bhyeti susukhenaiva tatpatham 005.020
tato viprāya vai dadyād udakumbhaṃ sadakṣiṇaṃ
upānadvastrayugmaṃ ca chattraṃ kanakam eva ca 005.021
yad vai māsagataṃ nāma tatprītiś cāpi saṃvadet
saṃvatsarānte 'py athavā pratimāsaṃ dvijān budhaḥ
vācayed udakumbhādyair dānaiḥ sarvān anukramāt 005.022
keśavaṃ mārgaśīrṣe tu pauṣe nārāyaṇaṃ tathā
mādhavaṃ māghamāse tu govindaṃ phālgune tathā 005.023
viṣṇuṃ caitre 'tha vaiśākhe tathaiva madhusūdanam
jyeṣṭhe trivikramaṃ devam āṣāḍhe vāmanaṃ tathā 005.024
śrāvaṇe śrīdharaṃ caiva hṛṣīkeśeti cāparam
nāma bhādrapade māsi gīyate puṇyakāṅkṣibhiḥ 005.025
padmanābhaṃ cāśvayuje dāmodaram ataḥ param
kārttike devadeveśaṃ stuvaṃs tarati durgatim 005.026
iha vai svasthatāṃ prāpya maraṇe smaraṇaṃ tataḥ
yāmyakleśam asaṃprāpya svargaloke mahīyate 005.027
tato mānuṣyam āsādya nirātaṅko gatajvaraḥ
dhanadhānyavati sphīte janma sādhukule 'rhati 005.028
upavāsavratānīha keśavārādhanaṃ prati
mamācakṣva mahābhāga paraṃ kautūhalaṃ hi me 006.001
kāmān yān yān naro bhakto manasecchati keśavāt
vratopavāsanāt prītas tāṃs tān viṣṇuḥ prayacchati 006.002
ratnaparvatam āruhya yathā ratnaṃ mahāmune
sattvānurūpam adatte tathā kṛtsnān manorathān 006.003
mārgaśīrṣaṃ tu yo māsam ekabhaktena yaḥ kṣapet
kurvan vai viṣṇuśuśrūṣāṃ sa deśe jāyate śubhe 006.004
pauṣamāsaṃ tathā dālbhya ekabhaktena yaḥ kṣapet
śuśrūṣaṇaparaḥ śaurer na rogī sa ca jāyate 006.005
māghamāsaṃ dvijaśreṣṭha ekabhaktena yaḥ kṣapet
viṣṇuśuśrūṣaṇaparaḥ sa kule jāyate satām 006.006
kṣapayed ekabhaktena śuśrūṣur yaś ca phālgunam
saubhāgyaṃ svajanānāṃ sa sarveṣām eti sonnatim 006.007
caitraṃ viṣṇuparo māsam ekabhaktena yaḥ kṣapet
suvarṇamaṇimuktāḍhyaṃ sa gārhasthyam avāpnuyāt 006.008
yaḥ kṣaped ekabhaktena vaiśākhaṃ pūjayan harim
naro vā yadi vā nārī jñātīnāṃ śreṣṭhatāṃ vrajet 006.009
kṛṣṇārpitamanā jyeṣṭham ekabhaktena yaḥ kṣapet
aiśvaryam atulaṃ śreṣṭhaṃ pumān strī vābhijāyate 006.010
āṣāḍham ekabhaktena yo nayed viṣṇutanmanāḥ
bahudhānyo bahudhano bahuputraś ca jāyate 006.011
kṣapayed ekabhaktena śrāvaṇaṃ viṣṇutatparaḥ
dhanadhānyahiraṇyāḍhye kule sa jñātivardhanaḥ 006.012
ekāhāro bhādrapadaṃ yaś ca kṛṣṇaparāyaṇaḥ
dhanāḍhyaṃ sphītam acalam aiśvaryaṃ pratipadyate 006.013
nayaṃś cāśvayujaṃ viṣṇuṃ pūjayed ekabhojanaḥ
dhanavān vāhanāḍhyaś ca bahuputraś ca jāyate 006.014
kārttike caikadā bhuṅkte yaś ca viṣṇuparo naraḥ
śūraś ca kṛtavidyaś ca bahuputraś ca jāyate 006.015
yas tu saṃvatsaraṃ pūrṇam ekabhakto bhaven naraḥ
ahiṃsaḥ sarvabhūteṣu vāsudevaparāyaṇaḥ 006.016
namo 'stu vāsudevāyety ahaś cāṣṭaśataṃ japet
atirātrasya yajñasya tataḥ phalam avāpnuyāt 006.017
daśa varṣasahasrāṇi svargaloke mahīyate
tatkṣayād iha cāgatya māhātmyaṃ pratipadyate 006.018
brāhmaṇaḥ kṣatriyo vaiśyaḥ strī śūdro vā yathoditān
upavāsān imān kurvan phalāny etāny avāpnuyāt 006.019
jagatpatiṃ jagadyoniṃ jaganniṣṭhaṃ jagadgurum
jayaṃ śaraṇam abhyetya na janaiḥ śocyate janaḥ 006.020
yasya nāmni smṛte martyaḥ samutkrānter anantaram
prāpnoti śāśvataṃ sthānaṃ tataḥ pūjyataro hi saḥ 006.021
nādir na madhyaṃ naivānto yasya devasya vidyate
anāditvād amadhyatvād anantatvāc ca so 'vyayaḥ 006.022
parāparaṃ sukṛtavatāṃ parāṃ gatiṃ svayaṃbhuvaṃ prabhavan nidhānam avyayam
sanātanaṃ yad amṛtam acyutaṃ dhruvaṃ praviśya taṃ harim amaratvam aśnute 006.023
śṛṇu dālbhya paraṃ kāmyaṃ vrataṃ saṃtatidaṃ nṛṇām
yam upoṣya na vicchedaḥ pitṛpiṇḍasya jāyate 007.001
kṛṣṇāṣṭamyāṃ caitramāse snāto niyatamānasaḥ
kṛṣṇam abhyarcya pūjāṃ ca devakyāḥ kurute tu yaḥ 007.002
nirāhāro japan nāma kṛṣṇasya jagataḥ pateḥ
upaviṣṭo japasnāna- kṣutapraskhalitādiṣu 007.003
pūjāyāṃ cāpi kṛṣṇasya sapta vārān prakīrtayet
pāṣaṇḍino vikarmasthān nālapec caiva nāstikān 007.004
prabhāte tu punaḥ snāto dattvā viprāya dakṣiṇām
bhuñjīta kṛtapūjas tu kṛṣṇasyaiva jagatpateḥ 007.005
vaiśākhajyeṣṭhayoś caiva pāraṇaṃ hi trimāsikam
upoṣya devadeveśaṃ ghṛtena snāpayed dharim 007.006
āṣāḍhe śrāvaṇe caiva māse bhādrapade tathā
upoṣite dvitīyaṃ vai pāraṇaṃ pūrvavat tu tat 007.007
tathaivāśvayujaṃ cādiṃ kṛtvā māsatrayaṃ budhaḥ
upoṣya snāpayed devaṃ haviṣā pāraṇe gate 007.008
pauṣe māghe phālgune ca naras tadvad upoṣitaḥ
caturthe pāraṇe pūrṇe ghṛtena snāpayed dharim 007.009
evaṃ kṛtopavāsasya puruṣasya tathā striyaḥ
na saṃtateḥ paricchedaḥ kadācid abhijāyate 007.010
kṛṣṇāṣṭamīm imāṃ yas tu naro yoṣid athāpi vā
upoṣyatīha sāhlādaṃ nṛloke prāpya nirvṛttim 007.011
putrapautrasamṛddhiṃ ca mṛtaḥ svarge mahīyate
ity etat kathitaṃ dālbhya mayā kṛṣṇāṣṭaṃīvratam 007.012
prāvṛṭkāle tu niyamāñ śṛṇu kāmyān imān mama 007.013
prāvṛṭkāle yadā śete vāsudevaḥ payonidhau
bhogibhoge nijāṃ māyāṃ yoganidrāṃ ca mānayan 007.014
viśiṣṭā na pravartante tadā yajñādikāḥ kriyāḥ
devānāṃ sā bhaved rātrir dakṣiṇāyanasaṃjñitā 007.015
yadā svapiti govindo yas tu māsaṃ catuṣṭayam
adhaḥśāyī brahmacārī keśavārpitamānasaḥ 007.016
namo namo 'stu kṛṣṇāya keśavāya namo namaḥ
namo 'stu narasiṃhāya viṣṇave ca namo namaḥ 007.017
iti prātas tathā sāyaṃ japed devakriyāparaḥ
śamayaty atiduṣpāraṃ duritaṃ janmasaṃcitam 007.018
madhu māṃsaṃ ca yo māsāñ caturas tān nirasyati
devakriyāratir viṣṇor anusmaraṇatatparaḥ 007.019
so 'pi svargaṃ samabhyeti cyutas tasmāt tu jāyate
arogī dhanadhānyāḍhyaḥ kulasaṃtatimān naraḥ 007.020
samastamandirāṇāṃ ca yaḥ supte madhusūdane
nirvṛttiṃ kurute so 'pi devo vaimāniko bhavet 007.021
anenaiva vidhānena naro viṣṇukriyāparaḥ
ekāhāro bhaved yas tu sarvapāpaiḥ pramucyate 007.022
supte ca sarvalokeśe naktabhojī bhavet tu yaḥ
sarvapāpavinirmuktaḥ svargaloke 'maro bhavet 007.023
śastaṃ tv anantaraṃ puṃsāṃ tataś caivekabhojanam
naktabhojanatulyaṃ tu nopavāsaphalaṃ kvacit 007.024
tailābhaṅgaṃ ca yo māsāṃś caturas tān nirasyati
so 'py aṅgalāvaṇyaguṇam ārogyaṃ ca naro labhet 007.025
yas tv etāni samastāni māsān etān naraś caret
sa viṣṇulokam āsādya viṣṇor anucaro bhavet 007.026
caturbhiḥ pāraṇaṃ māsair niṣpādyaṃ haritatparaiḥ
brāhmaṇān bhojayed dadyāt tatas tebhyaś ca dakṣiṇām 007.027
pūjayec ca jagannāthaṃ sarvapāpaharaṃ harim
prīyasva deva govindety evaṃ caiva prasādayet 007.028
iti dālbhya samākhyātaṃ cāturmāsye hi yad vratam
devadevasya suptasya dvādaśīṃ śṛṇu cāparām
yasyām anantasmaraṇād anantaphalabhāg bhavet 007.029
māsi proṣṭhapade śukle dvādaśyāṃ jalaśāyinam
praṇamyānantam abhyarcya puṣpadhūpādibhiḥ śuciḥ 008.001
pāṣaṇḍādibhir ālāpam akurvan niyatātmavān
viprāya dakṣiṇāṃ dattvā naktaṃ bhuṅkte tu yo naraḥ 008.002
tiṣṭhan vrajan svapaṃś caiva kṣutapraskhalitādiṣu
anantanāmasmaraṇaṃ kurvann uccāraṇaṃ tathā 008.003
anenaiva vidhānena māsān dvādaśa vai kramāt
upoṣya pāraṇe pūrṇe samabhyarcya jagadgurum
gītavādyena hṛdyena prīṇayan vyuṣṭim aśnute 008.004
anantaṃ gītavādyena yataḥ phalam udāhṛtam
tenānantaṃ samabhyarcya tad eva labhate phalam 008.005
evaṃ yaḥ puruṣaḥ kuryād anantārādhanaṃ śuciḥ
nārī vā svargam abhyetya so 'anantaphalam aśnute 008.006
evaṃ dālbhya hṛṣīkeśo narair bhaktyā yathāvidhi
phalaṃ dadāty asulabhaṃ salilenāpi pūjitaḥ 008.007
na viṣṇur vittadānena puṣpair vā na phalais tathā
ārādhyate suśuddhena hṛdayenaiva kevalam 008.008
rāgādyapetaṃ hṛdayaṃ vāg duṣṭā nānṛtādinā
hiṃsādirahitaḥ kāyaḥ keśavārādhanatrayam 008.009
rāgādidūṣite citte nāspadī madhusūdanaḥ
karoti na ratiṃ haṃsaḥ kadācit kardamāmbhasi 008.010
na yogyā keśavastutyai vāg duṣṭā cānṛtādinā
tamaso nāśanāyālaṃ nendor lekhā ghanāvṛtā 008.011
hiṃsādidūṣitaḥ kāyaḥ keśavārādhane kutaḥ
janacittaprasādāya na nabhas timirāvṛtam 008.012
tasmāc chraddhasva bhāvena satyabhāvena ca dvija
ahiṃsakena govindo nisargād eva toṣitaḥ 008.013
sarvasvam api kṛṣṇāya yo dadyāt kuṭilāśayaḥ
sa naivārādhayaty enaṃ sadbhāvenārcayācyutam 008.014
rāgādyapetaṃ hṛdayaṃ kuru tvaṃ keśavārpitam
tataḥ prāpsyasi duḥprāpyam ayatnenaiva keśavam 008.015
bhagavan kathitaḥ samyak kāmyo 'yaṃ keśavaṃ prati
ārādhanavidhiḥ sarvo bhūyaḥ pṛcchāmi tad vada 008.016
kule janma tathārogyaṃ dhanarddhiś ceha durlabhā
tritayaṃ prāpyate yena tan me vada mahāmune 008.017
mātāmahaṃ kāṇvam udāravīryaṃ maharṣim abhyarcya kulaprasūtim
papraccha puṃsām atha yoṣitāṃ ca duṣvantaputro bharataḥ praṇamya 008.018
yathāvad ācaṣṭa tato mahātmā sa rājavaryāya yathā kuleṣu
prayānti sūtiṃ puruṣāḥ striyaś ca yathā ca samyak sukhino bhavanti 008.019
pauṣe site dvādaśame 'hni sārke tathārkṣayoge jagataḥ prasūtim
saṃpūjya viṣṇuṃ vidhinopavāsī sraggandhadhūpānnavaropahāraiḥ 008.020
gṛhṇīta māsaṃ pratimāsapūjām dānādiyuktaṃ vratam abdam ekam
dadyāc ca dānaṃ dvijapuṅgavebhyas tad ucyamānaṃ vinibodha bhūpa 008.021
ghṛtaṃ tilān vrīhiyavaṃ hiraṇyaṃ yavānnam ambhaḥkarakānnapānam
chattraṃ payo 'nnaṃ guḍaphāṇitāḍhyaṃ srakcandanaṃ vastram anukrameṇa 008.022
māse ca māse vidhinoditena tasyāṃ tithau lokaguruṃ prapūjya
aśnīta yāny ātmaviśuddhihetoḥ saṃprāśanānīha nibodha tāni 008.023
gomūtram ambho ghṛtam āmaśākaṃ dūrvā dadhi vrīhiyavāṃs tilāṃś ca
sūryāṃśutaptaṃ jalam ambu dārbhaṃ kṣīraṃ ca māsakramaśopayuñjyāt 008.024
kule pradhāne dhanadhānyapūrṇe vivekavaty astasamastaduḥkhe
prāpnoti janmāvikalendriyaś ca bhavaty arogo matimān sukhī ca 008.025
tasmāt tvam apy etad amoghavid yo nārāyaṇārādhanam apramattaḥ
kuruṣva viṣṇuṃ bhagavantam īśam ārādhya kāmān akhilān upaiti 008.026
yadā ca śukladvādaśyāṃ nakṣatraṃ śravaṇaṃ bhavet
tadā sā tu mahāpuṇyā dvādaśī vijayā smṛtā 009.001
tasyāṃ snātaḥ sarvatīrthaiḥ snāto bhavati mānavaḥ
saṃpūjya varṣapūjāyāḥ sakalaṃ phalam aśnute 009.002
ekaṃ japtvā sahasrasya japtasyāpnoti yat phalam
dānaṃ sahasraguṇitaṃ tathā vai vipra bhojanam
homas tathopavāsaś ca sahasrākhyaphalapradaḥ 009.003
yat kṣemam api vai tasyāṃ sahasraṃ śrāvaṇe tu tat
anyasyām eva tithyāṃ śubhāyāṃ śrāvaṇaṃ yadā 009.*(7)
rohiṇyāś ca yadā kṛṣṇa- pakṣe 'ṣṭamyāṃ dvijottama
jayantī nāma sā proktā sarvapāpaharā tithiḥ 010.001
yad bālye yac ca kaumāre yauvane vārddhike ca yat
saptajanmakṛtaṃ pāpaṃ svalpaṃ vā yadi vā bahu 010.002
tat kṣālayati govindaṃ tasyām abhyarcya bhaktitaḥ
homajapyādidānānāṃ phalaṃ ca śatasaṃmitam 010.003
saṃprāpnoti na saṃdeho yac cānyan manasecchati
upavāsaś ca tatrokto mahāpātakanāśanaḥ 010.004
ekadaśyāṃ śuklapakṣe yadā rkṣaṃ vai punarvasuḥ
nāmnā sātijayākhyātā tithīnām uttamā tithiḥ 011.001
yo dadāti tilaprasthaṃ tṛṣkālaṃ vatsaraṃ naraḥ
upavāsaṃ ca tasyāṃ yaḥ karoty etat samaṃ smṛtam 011.002
tasyāṃ jagatpatir devaḥ sarvaḥ sarveśvaro hariḥ
pratyakṣatāṃ prayāty alpaṃ tadānantaphalaṃ smṛtam 011.003
sagareṇa kakutsthena duṃdhumāreṇa gādhinā
tasyām ārādhitaḥ kṛṣṇo dattavān nikhilāṃ bhuvam 011.004
ayane cottare prāpte yaḥ snāpayati keśavam
ghṛtaprasthena pāpaṃ saḥ sakalaṃ vai vyapohati 012.001
kapilāṃ vipramukhyāya dadāty anudinaṃ hi yaḥ
ghṛtasnānaṃ ca devasya tasmin kāle samaṃ hi tat 012.002
snāpyamānaṃ ca paśyati ye ghṛtenottarāyaṇe 012.003
te yānti viṣṇusālokyaṃ sarvapāpavivarjitāḥ 012.003,013.*(8)
maitreyī brāhmaṇī pūrvaṃ yājñavalkyam apṛcchata
praṇipatya mahābhāgaṃ yogeśvaram akalmaṣam 013.001
pāpapraśamanāyālaṃ yat puṇyasyopavṛṃhakam
manorathapradaṃ yac ca tad vrataṃ kathyatāṃ mama 013.002
kāni dānāni śastāni snānāni ca yatavrata
praśastās tithayaḥ kāś ca prāśanāni ca śaṃsa me 013.003
sarvadānāni śastāni yāny uddiśya janārdanam
dīyante vipramukhyebhyaḥ śraddhāpūtena cetasā 013.004
tā eva tithayaḥ śastā yāsv abhyarcya janārdanam
kriyante śradhayā samyag upavāsavratāḥ sadā 013.005
prāpyate vividhair yajñair yat phalaṃ sādhvasādhubhiḥ
upavāsais tad āpnoti samabhyarcya janārdanam 013.006
manorathānāṃ saṃprāpti- kārakaṃ pāpanāśanam
śrūyatāṃ mama dharmajñe vratānām uttamaṃ vratam 013.007
yat kṛtvā na jaḍo nāndho badhiro na ca duḥkhitaḥ
na caiveṣṭaviyogārtiṃ kaścit prāpnoti mānavaḥ 013.008
na cāpriyo 'sya lokasya na daridro na durgatiḥ
sapta janmāni bhavati sarvapāpaiḥ pramucyate 013.009
viṣṇuvratam idaṃ khyātaṃ bhāṣitaṃ viṣṇunā svayam 013.010
pauṣaśukladvitīyādi kṛtvā dinacatuṣṭayam
ṣaṇmāsapāraṇaprāyaṃ gṛhṇīyāt paramaṃ vratam 013.011
pūrvaṃ siddhārthakaiḥ snānaṃ tataḥ kṛṣṇatilaiḥ smṛtam
vacayā ca tṛtīye 'hni sarvauṣadhyā tataḥ param 013.012
nāmnā kṛṣṇācyutākhyena tathānantena pūjayet
tathaiva ca caturthe 'hni hṛṣīkeśena keśavam
devam abhyarcya puṣpaiś ca pattrair dhūpānulepanaiḥ 013.013
udgacchataś ca bālendor dadyād arghyaṃ samāhitaḥ
puṣpaiḥ pattraiḥ phalaiś caiva sarvadhānyaiś ca bhaktitaḥ 013.014
dinakrameṇa caitāni candranāmāni kīrtayet
śaśicandraśaśāṅkendu- saṃjñāni brahmavādini 013.015
naktaṃ bhuñjīta matimān yāvat tiṣṭhati candramāḥ
astaṃgate na bhuñjīta vratabhaṅgabhayāc chubhe 013.016
evaṃ sarveṣu māseṣu jyeṣṭhānteṣu yaśasvini
kartavyaṃ vai vrataśreṣṭhaṃ dvitīyādicaturdinam 013.017
viprāya dakṣiṇāṃ dadyāt pañcamyāṃ ca svaśaktitaḥ
evaṃ samāpayen māsaiḥ ṣaḍbhiḥ prathamapāraṇam 013.018
pāraṇante ca devasya prīṇanaṃ bhaktitaḥ śubhe
yathāśaktyā tu kartavyaṃ vittaśāṭhyaṃ vivarjayet 013.019
āṣāḍhādidvitīyaṃ tu ṣaṇmāsena tapodhane
pāraṇaṃ vai samākhyātaṃ vratasyāsya śubhapradam 013.020
vratam etad dilīpena duṣvantena yayātinā
tathānyaiḥ pṛthivīpālair upavāsavidhānataḥ
caritaṃ munimukhyaiś ca ṛcīkacyavanādibhiḥ 013.021
surambhayā sukaikeyyā śāṇḍilyā dhūmrapiṅgayā
sudeṣṇayāthavā riṇyā matimatyā kṛtāśayā 013.022
sāvitryā paurṇamāsyā ca vairiṇyā ca subhadrayā
brāhmaṇakṣatriyaviśām iti strībhir anuṣṭhitam 013.023
urvaśyā rambhayā caiva saurabheyyā tathā vratam
varāpsarobhir dharmajñe caritaṃ dharmavāṃchayā 013.024
prathame pādapūjā syād dvitīye nābhipūjanam
tṛtīye vakṣasaḥ pūjā caturthe śiraso hareḥ 013.025
etac cīrtvā samastebhyaḥ pāpebhyaḥ śraddhayānvitaḥ
mucyate sakalāṃś caiva saṃprāpnoti manorathān 013.026
vratānām uttamaṃ hy etat svayaṃ devena bhāṣitam
pāpapraśamanaṃ śastaṃ manorathaphalapradam 013.027
yaṃ ca kāmam abhidhyāyan kriyate niyatavrataiḥ
vratam etan mahābhāge taṃ tu pūrayate nṛṇām 013.028
manorathān pūrayati sarvapāpaṃ vyapohati
avyāhatendriyatvaṃ ca sapta janmāni yacchati 013.029
māghe snātasya yat puṇyaṃ prayāge pāpanāśanam
sakalaṃ tad avāpnoti śrutvā viṣṇuvrataṃ tv idam 013.030
sākṣād bhagavatā proktaṃ paramaṃ pāpanāśanam 013.*(9)
śuklapakṣe tu pauṣasya saṃprāptidvādaśīṃ śṛṇu
yām upoṣya samāpnoti sarvān eva manorathān 014.001
pāṣaṇḍādibhir ālāpam akurvan viṣṇutatparaḥ
pūjayet praṇato devam ekāgramatir acyutam 014.002
pauṣādipāraṇaṃ māsaiḥ ṣaḍbhir jyeṣṭhāntakaṃ smṛtam
prathame puṇḍarīkākṣaṃ nāma devasya gīyate 014.003
dvitīye mādhavākhyaṃ tu viśvarūpaṃ tu phālgune
puruṣottamākhyaṃ ca tataḥ pañcame cācyuteti ca 014.004
ṣaṣṭhe jayeti devasya guhyaṃ nāma prakīrtyate
pūrveṣu ṣaṭsu māseṣu snānaprāśanayos tilāḥ 014.005
āṣāḍhādiṣu māseṣu pañcagavyam udāhṛtam
snāne ca prāśane caiva praśastaṃ pāpanāśanam 014.006
pratimāsaṃ ca devasya kṛtvā pūjāṃ yathāvidhi
viprāya dakṣiṇāṃ dadyāc śraddadhānaḥ svaśaktitaḥ 014.007
pāraṇānte ca devasya prīṇanaṃ bhaktipūrvakam
kruvīta śaktyā govinde sadbhāvābhyarcano yataḥ 014.008
naktaṃ bhuñjīta ca tatas tailakṣāravivarjitaṃ
ekādaśyām uṣitvaivaṃ dvādaśyām athavā dine 014.009
etām uṣitvā dharmajñe prīṇanaṃ devatatparaḥ
sarvakāmān avāpnoti sarvapāpaiḥ pramucyate 014.010
yataḥ sarvam avāpnoti yad yad icchati cetasā
tato lokeṣu vikhyātā saṃprāptidvādaśīti vai 014.011
kṛtābhilaṣitā hy eṣā prārabdhā dharmatatparaiḥ
pūrayaty akhilān kāmān saṃśrutā ca dine dine 014.012
tasminn eva dine puṇye govindadvādaśīṃ śṛṇu
yasyāṃ samyag anuṣṭhānāt prāpnoty abhimataṃ phalam 015.001
pauṣamāse site pakṣe dvādaśyāṃ samupoṣitaḥ
saṃyak saṃpūjya govindaṃ nāmnā devam adhokṣajam
puṣpadhūpopahārādyair upavāsaiḥ samāhitaḥ 015.002
govindeti japan nāma punas tadgatamānasaḥ
viprāya dakṣiṇāṃ dadyād yathāśakti tapodhane 015.003
svapan vibuddhaḥ skhalito govindeti ca kīrtayet
pāṣaṇḍādivikarmasthair ālāpaṃ ca vivarjayet 015.004
gomūtraṃ gomayaṃ vāpi dadhi kṣīram athāpi vā
godehataḥ samutpannaṃ saṃprāśnītātmaśuddhaye 015.005
dvitīye 'hni punaḥ snātas tathaivābhyarcya taṃ prabhum
tenaiva nāmnā saṃstūya dattvā viprāya dakṣiṇām
tato bhuñjīta godeha- saṃbhūtena samanvitam 015.006
evam evākhilān māsān upoṣya prayataḥ śuciḥ
dadyād gavāhnikaṃ bhaktyā pratimāsaṃ svaśaktitaḥ 015.007
pārite ca punar varṣe yathāśakti gavāhnikam
dattvā paragave bhūyaḥ śṛṇu yat phalam aśnute 015.008
suvarṇaśṛṅgāḥ pañca gāḥ ṣaṣṭhaṃ ca vṛṣabhaṃ naraḥ
pratimāsaṃ dvijāgrebhyo yad dattvā phalam aśnute 015.009
tad āpnoty akhilaṃ samyag vratam etad upoṣitaḥ
taṃ ca lokam avāpnoti govindo yatra tiṣṭhati 015.010
govindadvādaśīm etām upoṣya divi tārakāḥ
vidyotamānā dṛśyante lokair adyāpi śobhane 015.011
upavāsavratānāṃ tu vaikalyaṃ yan mahāmune
dānakarmakṛtaṃ tasya vipāko vada yādṛśaḥ 016.001
yajñānām upavāsānāṃ vratānāṃ ca yatavrate
vaikalyāt phalavaikalyaṃ yādṛśaṃ tac chṛṇuṣva me 016.002
upavāsādinā rājyaṃ saṃprāpyaṃ te tathā vasu
bhraṣṭaiśvaryā nirdhanāś ca bhavanti puruṣāḥ punaḥ 016.003
rūpaṃ tathottamaṃ prāpya vratavaikalyadoṣataḥ
kāṇāḥ kuṇṭhāś ca bhūyas te bhavanty andhāś ca mānavāḥ 016.004
upavāsān naraḥ patnīṃ nārī prāpya tathā patim
viyogaṃ vratavaikalyād ubhayaṃ tad avāpnute 016.005
ye dravye saty adātāras tathānyenāhitāgnayaḥ
kule ca sati duḥśīlā dauṣkulāḥ śīlinaś ca ye 016.006
vastrānulepanair hīnā bhūṣaṇaiś cātirūpiṇaḥ
virūparūpāś ca tathā prasādhanaguṇānvitāḥ 016.007
te sarve vratavaikalyāt phalavaikalyam āgatāḥ
guṇino 'pi hi doṣeṇa saṃyuktāḥ saṃbhavanti te 016.008
tasmān na vratavaikalyaṃ yajñavaikalyam eva vā
upavāse ca kartavyaṃ vaikalyād vikalaṃ phalam 016.009
kathaṃcid yadi vaikalyam upavāsādike bhavet
kiṃ tatra vada kartavyam acchidraṃ yena jāyate 016.010
akhaṇḍadvādaśīm etām aśeṣeṣv eva karmasu
vaikalyapraśamāyālaṃ śṛṇuṣva gadato mama 016.011
mārgaśīrṣe site pakṣe dvādaśyāṃ niyataḥ śuciḥ
kṛtopavāso deveśaṃ samabhyarcya janārdanam 016.012
pañcagavyajalasnātaḥ pañcagavyakṛtāśanaḥ
yavavrīhibhṛtaṃ pātraṃ dadyād viprāya bhaktitaḥ
idaṃ coccārayed bhaktyā devasya purato hareḥ 016.013
sapta janmāni yat kiṃcid mayā khaṇḍavrataṃ kṛtam
bhagavaṃs tvatprasādena tad akhaṇḍam ihāstu me 016.014
yathākhaṇḍaṃ jagat sarvam tvam eva puruṣottama
tathākhilāny akhaṇḍāni vratāni mama santu vai 016.015
evam evānumāsaṃ vai cāturmāsyavidhiḥ smṛtaḥ 016.016
caturbhir eva māsais tu pāraṇaṃ prathamaṃ smṛtam
prīṇanaṃ ca hareḥ kuryāt pārite pāraṇe tataḥ 016.017
caitrādiṣu ca māseṣu caturṣv anyaṃ tu pāraṇam
tatrāpi saktupātrāṇi dadyāc chraddhāsamanvitaḥ 016.018
śrāvaṇādiṣu māseṣu kārttikānteṣu pāraṇam
yatnāt tu ghṛtapātrāṇi dadyād viprāya bhaktitaḥ 016.019
evaṃ samyag yathānyāyam akhaṇḍadvādaśīṃ naraḥ
yad upoṣyaty akhaṇḍaṃ sa vratasya phalam aśnute 016.020
sapta janmasu vaikalyam yad vratasya kvacit kṛtam
karoty avikalaṃ sarvam akhaṇḍadvādaśīvratam 016.021
tasmād eṣātiyatnena naraiḥ strībhiś ca suvrate
akhaṇḍadvādaśī samyag upoṣyā phalakāṃkṣibhiḥ 016.022
evaṃ purā yājñavalkyaḥ pṛṣṭaḥ patnyā mahāmuniḥ
ācaṣṭa puṇyaphaladam upavāsavidhiṃ param 017.001
tathā tvam api viprarṣe keśavārādhane rataḥ
vratopavāsaparamo bhavethā nānyamānasaḥ 017.002
punaś caitan mahābhāga śrūyatāṃ gadato mama
proktaṃ nareṇa devānāṃ tithimāhātmyam uttamam 017.003
vijayātijayā caiva jayantī pāpanāśanī
tathottarāyaṇaṃ śastaṃ sarvadā keśavārcane 017.004
yad anyakāle varṣeṇa keśavāl labhyate phalam
sakṛd evārcite kṛṣṇe tad etāsv api labhyate 017.005
vijayātijayā caiva jayantī pāpanāśanī
tathottarāyaṇaṃ caiva yac chastaṃ keśavārcane 017.006
tat sarvaṃ kathayehādya tithimāhātmyam uttamam
yatra saṃpūjitaḥ kṛṣṇaḥ sarvapāpaṃ vyapohati 017.007
ekādaśyāṃ site pakṣe puṣyarkṣaṃ yatra sattama
tithau bhavati sā proktā viṣṇunā pāpanāśanī 017.008
tasyāṃ saṃpūjya govindaṃ jagatām īśvareśvaram
saptajanmakṛtāt pāpān mucyate nātra saṃśayaḥ 017.009
yaś copavāsaṃ kurute tasyāṃ snāto dvijottama
sarvapāpavinirmukto viṣṇuloke mahīyate 017.010
dānaṃ yad dīyate kiṃcit samuddiśya janārdanam
homo vā kriyate tasyām akṣayaṃ labhate phalam 017.011
ekā ṛg devapurato japtā śraddhāvatā tathā
ṛgvedasya samastasya japatā yacchate phalam 017.012
sāmavedaphalaṃ sāma yajurvedaphalaṃ yajuḥ
japtam ekaṃ muniśreṣṭha dadāty atra na saṃśayaḥ 017.013
tārakā divi rājante dyotamānā dvijottama
samabhyarcya tithāv asyāṃ devadevaṃ janārdanam 017.014
yataḥ pāpam aśeṣaṃ vai nāśayaty atra keśavaḥ
puṣyarkṣaikādaśī brahmaṃs tenoktā pāpanāśanī 017.015
tathānyad api dharmajña śrūyatāṃ gadato mama
padadvayaṃ jagaddhātur devadevasya śārṅgiṇaḥ 018.001
saṃvatsaraḥ pādapīṭhaṃ tatra nyastaṃ padadvayam
vāsudevena viprendra bhūtānāṃ hitakāmyayā 018.002
vāmam asya padaṃ brahman uttarāyaṇasaṃjñitam
devādyaiḥ sakalair vandyaṃ dakṣiṇaṃ dakṣiṇāyanam 018.003
tasmin yaḥ prayataḥ samyag devadevasya mānavaḥ
karoty ārādhanaṃ tasya toṣam āyāti keśavaḥ 018.004
katham ārādhanaṃ tasya devadevasya śārṅgiṇaḥ
kriyate muniśārdūla tan mamākhyātum arhasi 018.005
uttare tv ayane dālbhya snāto niyatamānasaḥ
ghṛtakṣīrādinā devaṃ snāpayed dharaṇīdharam 018.006
cāruvastropahāraiś ca puṣpadhūpānulepanaiḥ
samabhyarcya tataḥ samyag brāhmaṇānāṃ ca tarpaṇaiḥ
padadvayavrataṃ samyag gṛhṇīyād viṣṇutatparaḥ 018.007
snāto nārāyaṇaṃ vakṣye bhuñjan nārāyaṇaṃ tathā
bhuṅktvā nārāyaṇaṃ cāhaṃ gacchan nārāyaṇaṃ tataḥ 018.008
svapan vibuddhaḥ praṇaman homaṃ kurvaṃs tathārcanam
nārāyaṇasyānudinaṃ kariṣye nāmakīrtanam 018.009
yāvad adyadināt prāptaṃ kramaśo dakṣiṇāyanam
skhalite 'haṃ kṣute caiva vedanārto 'thavā sadā
tāvan nārāyaṇaṃ vakṣye sarvam evottarāyaṇam 018.010
yāvaj jīvavadhaṃ kiṃcid jñānato 'jñānato 'pi vā
kariṣye 'haṃ tathā caiva kīrtayiṣyāmi taṃ prabhum 018.011
yadā tadānṛtaṃ kiṃcid atha vakṣyāmi durvacaḥ
ajñānād athavā jñānāt kīrtayiṣyāmi taṃ prabhum 018.012
ṣaṇmāsam eṣa me jāpo nārāyaṇamayaḥ paraḥ
taṃ smaran maraṇe yāti yāṃ gatiṃ sāstu me gatiḥ 018.013
ṣaṇmāsābhyantare mṛtyur yady akasmād bhaven mama
tan mayā vāsudevāya svayam ātmā niveditaḥ 018.014
paramārthamayaṃ brahma vāsudevamayaṃ param
yam ante saṃsmaran yāti sa me viṣṇuḥ parā gatiḥ 018.015
yadā prātas tadā sāyaṃ madhyāhne vā mriye hy aham
ṣaṇmāsābhyantare nyāsaḥ kṛto vratamayo mayā 018.016
tathā kuru jagannātha sarvalokaparāyaṇa
nārāyaṇa yathā nānyaṃ tvatto yāmi mṛte gatim 018.017
evam uccārya ṣaṇmāsa- pāraṇaṃ pravaraṃ vratam
tāvan niṣpādayed yāvat saṃprāptaṃ dakṣiṇāyanam 018.018
tataś ca prīṇanaṃ kuryād yathāśaktyā jagadguroḥ
bhojayed brāhmaṇān samyag dadyāt tebhyaś ca dakṣiṇām 018.019
evaṃ vratam idaṃ dālbhya yaḥ pārayati mānavaḥ
nārī vā sarvapāpebhyaḥ ṣaṇmāsād vipra mucyate 018.020
ṣaṇmāsābhyantare cāsya maraṇaṃ yadi jāyate
prāpnoty anaśanasyoktaṃ yat phalaṃ tad asaṃśayam 018.021
padadvayaṃ ca kṛṣṇasya samyak tena tathārcitam
bhagavān ujjagau viṣṇuḥ purā gārgyāya pṛcchate 018.022
harer nāma japan bhaktyā 018.*(10)
sa purā na janeśvara 18*(10)
phālgunāmalapakṣasya ekādaśyām upoṣitaḥ
naro vā yadi vā nārī samabhyarcya jagadgurum 019.001
harer nāma japed bhaktyā sapta vārān nareśvara
uttiṣṭhan prasvapaṃś caiva harim evānukīrtayet 019.002
tato 'nyadivase prāpte dvādaśyāṃ prayato harim
snātvā samyak tam abhyarcya dadyād viprāya dakṣiṇām 019.003
harim uddiśya caivāgnau ghṛtahomakṛtakriyaḥ
praṇipatya jagannātham iti vāṇīm udīrayet 019.004
pātālasaṃsthā vasudhā yaṃ prasādya manorathān
avāpa vāsudevo 'sau pradadātu manorathān 019.005
yam abhyarcyāditiḥ prāptā sakalāṃś ca manorathān
putrāṃś caivepsitān devaḥ pradadātu manorathān 019.006
bhraṣṭarājyaś ca devendro yam abhyarcya jagatpatim
manorathān avāpāgryān sa dadātu manorathān 019.007
evam abhyarcya pūjāṃ ca niṣpādya haraye tataḥ
bhuñjīta prayataḥ samyag haviṣyaṃ manujarṣabha 019.008
phālgunaṃ caitravaiśākhau jyeṣṭhamāsaṃ ca pārthiva
caturbhiḥ pāraṇaṃ māsair ebhir niṣpāditaṃ bhavet 019.009
raktapuṣpais tu caturo māsān kurvīta cārcanam
dahec ca guggulaṃ prāśya gośṛṅgakṣālanaṃ jalam 019.010
haviṣyānnaṃ ca naivedyam ātmanaś caiva bhojanam
tataś ca śrūyatām anyad āṣāḍhādau tu yā kriyā 019.011
jātīpuṣpāṇi dhūpaś ca śastaḥ sarjaraso nṛpa
prāśya darbhodakaṃ cātra śālyannaṃ ca nivedanam 019.012
svayaṃ tad eva cāśnīyāc śeṣaṃ pūrvavad ācaret
kārttikādiṣu māseṣu gomūtraṃ kāyaśodhanam 019.013
sugandhaṃ cecchayā dhūpaṃ pūjābhṛṅgārakeṇa ca
kāsāraṃ cātra naivedyam aśnīyāt tac ca vai svayam 019.014
pratimāsaṃ ca viprāya dātavyā dakṣiṇā tathā
prīṇanaṃ cecchayā viṣṇoḥ pāraṇe pāraṇe gate 019.015
yathāśakti yathāprīti vittaśāṭhyaṃ vivarjayet
sadbhāvenaiva govindaḥ pūjitaḥ prīyate yataḥ 019.016
pāraṇānte yathāśaktyā snāpitaḥ pūjito hariḥ
prīṇitaś cepsitān kāmān dadāty avyāhatān nṛpa 019.017
eṣā dhanyā pāpaharā dvādaśī phalam icchatām
yathābhilaṣitān kāmān dadāti manujeśvara 019.018
pūrayaty akhilān bhaktyā yataś caiṣā manorathān
manorathadvādaśīyaṃ tato lokeṣu viśrutā 019.019
upoṣyaitāṃ tribhuvanaṃ prāptam indreṇa vai purā
adityā cepsitāḥ putrā dhanaṃ cośanasā nṛpa 019.020
dhaumyena cāpy adhyayanam anyaiś cābhimataṃ phalam
rājarṣibhis tathā vipraiḥ strībhiḥ śūdraiś ca bhūpate 019.021
yaṃ yaṃ kāmam abhidhyāyed vratam etad upoṣitaḥ
taṃ tam āpnoty asaṃdigdhaṃ viṣṇor ārādhanodyataḥ 019.022,*(11)
aputro labhate putram adhano labhate dhanam
rogābhibhūtaś cārogyaṃ kanyā prāpnoti satpatim 019.023
samāgamaṃ pravasitair upoṣyaitām avāpnute
sarvān kāmān avāpnoti mṛtaḥ svarge ca modate 019.024
nāputro nādhano neṣṭa- viyogī na ca nirguṇaḥ
upoṣyaitad vrataṃ martyaḥ strī jano vāpi jāyate 019.025
ya eva vratasaṃcīrṇo viṣṇuloke mahīyate 019.*(12)
svargaloke sahasrāṇi varṣāṇāṃ manujādhipa
bhogān abhimatān bhuktvā svargaloke 'bhikāṅkṣitān 019.026
iha puṇyavatāṃ nR̥ṇāṃ dhanināṃ sādhuśīlinām
gṛheṣu jāyate rājan sarvavyādhivivarjitaḥ 019.027
aśokapūrṇimāṃ cānyāṃ śṛṇuśva vadato mama
yām upoṣya naraḥ śokaṃ nāpnoti strī tathāpi vā 020.001
phālgunāmalapakṣasya pūrṇimāsyāṃ nareśvara
mṛjjalena naraḥ snātvā dattvā śirasi vai mṛdam 020.002
mṛtprāśanaṃ tathā kṛtvā kṛtvā ca sthaṇḍilaṃ mṛdā
puṣpaiḥ patrais tathābhyarcya bhūdharaṃ nānyamānasaḥ
dharaṇīṃ ca tathā devīm aśokety abhidhīyate 020.003
yathā viśokāṃ dharaṇīṃ kṛtavāṃs tvaṃ janārdanaḥ
tathā māṃ sarvapāpebhyo mocayāśeṣadhāriṇi 020.004
yathā samastabhūtānāṃ dhāraṇaṃ tvayy avasthitam
tathā viśokaṃ kuru māṃ sakalecchāvibhūtibhiḥ 020.005
dhyātamātre yathā viṣṇau svāsthyaṃ yātāsi medini
tathā manaḥ svasthatāṃ me kuru tvaṃ bhūtadhāriṇi 020.006
evaṃ stutvā tathābhyarcya candrāyārghyaṃ nivedya ca
upoṣitavyaṃ naktaṃ vā bhoktavyaṃ tailavarjitam 020.007
anenaiva prakāreṇa catvāraḥ phālgunādayaḥ
upoṣyā nṛpate māsāḥ prathamaṃ tat tu pāraṇam 020.008
āṣāḍhādiṣu māseṣu tadvat snānaṃ mṛdambunā
tad eva prāśanaṃ pūjā tathaivendos tathārhaṇam 020.009
caturṣv anyeṣu caivoktaṃ tathā vai kārttikādiṣu
pāraṇaṃ tritayaṃ caiva cāturmāsikam ucyate 020.010
prathamaṃ dharaṇī nāma stutyai māsacatuṣṭayam
dvitīye medinī vācyā tṛtīye ca vasuṃdharā 020.011
pāraṇe pāraṇe vastra- pūjayā pūjayen nṛpa
dharaṇīṃ devadevaṃ ca ghṛtasnānena keśavam 020.012
vastrābhāve tu sūtreṇa pūjayed dharaṇīṃ tathā
ghṛtābhāve tathā kṣīraṃ śastaṃ vā salilaṃ hareḥ 020.013
pātālamūlagatayā cīrṇam etan mahāvratam
dharaṇyā keśavaprītyai tataḥ prāptā samunnatiḥ 020.014
devena coktā dharaṇī varāhavapuṣā tadā
upavāsaprasannena samuddhṛtya rasātalāt 020.015
vratenānena kalyāṇi praṇato yaḥ kariṣyati
vratam etad upāśritya pāraṇaṃ ca yathāvidhi 020.016
tasya prasādam apy aham karomi tava medini
tathaiva kurute pūjāṃ bhaktyā mama śubho janaḥ
tathaiva tava kalyāṇi praṇato yaḥ kariṣyati 020.*(13)
sarvapāpavinirmuktaḥ sapta janmāntarāṇy asau
viśokaḥ sarvakalyāṇa- bhājano matimāñ janaḥ 020.017
sarvatra pūjyaḥ satataṃ sarveṣām aparājitaḥ
yathāham evaṃ vasudhe bhavitā nirvṛteḥ padam 020.018
tathā tvam api kalyāṇi bhaviṣyasi na saṃśayaḥ 020.*(14)
evam etan mahāpuṇyaṃ sarvapāpopaśāntidam
viśokākhyaṃ vrataṃ dhanyaṃ tat kuruṣva mahīpate 020.019
strīṇāṃ dharmaṃ dvijaśreṣṭha upavāsaṃ bhavan mama
kathayeha yathātattvam upavāsavidhiś ca yaḥ 021.001
kaumārake gṛhasthāyā vidhavāyāś ca sattama
dharmaṃ prabrūhy aśeṣeṇa bhagavan prītikārakam 021.002
śrūyatām akhilaṃ brahman yady etad anupṛcchasi
upakārāya ca strīṇāṃ triṣu lokeṣv anuttamam 021.003
praśnam etat purā devī śailarājasutā patim
papraccha śaṅkaraṃ brahman kailāsaśikhare sthitam 021.004
kumārikābhir deveśa gṛhasthābhiś ca keśavaḥ
vidhavābhis tathā strībhiḥ katham ārādhyate vada 021.005
sādhu sādhvi tvayā pṛṣṭam etan nārāyaṇāśritam
upavāsādi yat tattvaṃ śrūyatām asya yo vidhiḥ 021.006
yogyaṃ patiṃ samāsādya nārī dharmam avāpnute
duḥśīle 'pi hi kāmārte nārī prāpnoti bhartari 021.007
anārādhya jagannāthaṃ sarvalokeśvaraṃ harim
katham āpnoti vai nārī patiṃ śīlaguṇānvitam 021.008
sukalatrapradaṃ tasmād vratam acyutatuṣṭidam
kartavyaṃ lakṣaṇaṃ tasya śrūyatāṃ varavarṇini 021.009
yac cīrtvā sarvanārīṇāṃ śreṣṭham āpnoty asaṃśayam
aihikaṃ ca sukhaṃ prāpya svarge bhuṅkte sukhāny api 021.010
anujñāṃ prāpya pitṛto mātṛtaś ca kumārikā
pūjayec ca jagannāthaṃ bhaktyā pāpaharaṃ harim 021.011
triṣūttareṣu svṛkṣeṣu patikāmā kumārikā
mādhavākhyaṃ tu vai nāma japen nityam atandritā 021.012
priyaṅguṇā raktapuṣpair bandhūkakusumais tathā
samabhyarcya tato dadyād raktam evānulepanam 021.013
sarvauṣadhyā svayaṃ snātvā samabhyarcya jagatpatim
namo 'stu mādhavāyeti homayen madhusarpiṣī 021.014
sa devam uttarāyoge samabhyarcya janārdanam
śobhanaṃ patim āpnoti pretya svargaṃ ca gacchati 021.015
atibālye ca yat kiṃcit tayā pāpam anuṣṭhitam
tasmāc ca mucyate devi sukhinī caiva jāyate 021.016
abdenaikena tanvaṅgi dhūtapāpā yad icchati
tad eva prāpnuyād bhadre nārāyaṇaparāyaṇā 021.017
ṣaṇmāsaṃ prīṇanaṃ kāryaṃ bhaktyā śaktyā ca vai hareḥ
pāraṇānte mahābhage tathā brāhmaṇatarpaṇam 021.018
gārhasthye 'vasthitā nārī bhaktyā saṃpūjayet patim
sa eva devatā tasyāḥ pūjyaḥ pūjyataraś ca saḥ 022.001
tasmiṃs tuṣṭe paro dharmas tasyaiva paricaryayā
toṣam āyāti sarvātmā paramātmā janārdanaḥ 022.002
naiva tasyāḥ pṛthag yajño na śrāddhaṃ nāpy upoṣitam
bhartṛśuśrūṣaṇenaiva prāpnoti strī yathepsitam 022.003
tenaiva sāpy anujñātā tasya śuśrūṣaṇād anu
toṣayej jagatām īśam anantam aparājitam 022.004
vratair nānāvidhair devi aihikāmuṣmikāptaye
viṣṇuvratādibhir divyais tathā dānair mano'nugaiḥ 022.005
ghṛtakṣīrābhiṣekaiś ca brāhmaṇānāṃ ca tarpaṇaiḥ
manojñair vividhair dhūpaiḥ puṣpavastrānulepanaiḥ 022.006
gītavādyais tathā hṛdyair upavāsaiś ca bhāmini
evam ārādhya govindam anujñātā yathāvidhi
patinā sakalān kāmān avāpnoti na saṃśayaḥ 022.007
patinā tv ananujñātā kiṃcit puṇyaṃ karoti yā
viphalaṃ tad aśeṣaṃ vai tasyāḥ śailavarātmaje 022.008
na ca prasādaṃ kurute bhagavān madhusūdanaḥ
nānujñātā tu yā nārī patinārcati keśavam 022.009
yā tu bhartṛparā nārī nārāyaṇam atandritā
bhaktyā saṃpūjayed devaṃ toṣam āyāti keśavaḥ 022.010
yā tu bhartrā parityaktā tathā yā mṛtabhartṛkā
pāṣaṇḍānugato vāpi yasyā bhartā maheśvara 022.011
prāyo dadāti nānujñāṃ viṣṇor ārādhane tadā
katham ārādhanaṃ kāryaṃ viṣṇos tad vada śaṃkara 022.012
yā tu bhartrā parityaktā sā saṃpūjya nijaṃ patim
manasā tanmanaskā ca tasyaiva hitakāriṇī 022.013
na nindākaraṇī tasya śreyo'bhidhyāyinī tathā
tasyaiva sarvakāleṣu sarvakalyāṇam icchati 022.014
ārādhayej jagannāthaṃ sarvadhātāram acyutam
kṛtopavāsā puṣpādi nivedya sakalaṃ tataḥ 022.015
bhartur manorathāvāptiṃ prārthayet prathamaṃ varam
svayaṃ yathābhilaṣitaṃ prārthayet taṃ varaṃ tataḥ 022.016
evaṃ bhartṛparityaktā yoṣid ārādhanaṃ hareḥ
kurvāṇā sakalān kāmān avāpnoti na saṃśayaḥ 022.017
bhartā karoti yac casyāḥ kiṃcit puṇyam aharniśam
tasya puṇyasya saṃpūrṇam ardhaṃ prāpnoti sā śubhe 022.018
yat tu sā kurute puṇyaṃ vinā doṣeṇa yojjhitā
tat tasyāḥ sakalaṃ devi tasyārdhaṃ na labhet patiḥ 022.019
bhartary evaṃ pravasite tyaktā ca patinā śubhe
kurvītārādhanaṃ nārī upavāsādinā hareḥ 022.020
etat tavoktaṃ yat pṛṣṭaṃ tvayāhaṃ girinandini
vidhavānām ato dharmaṃ śrūyatāṃ viṣṇutuṣṭidam 022.021
mṛte bhartari sādhvī strī brahmacaryavratoditā
snātā pratidinaṃ dadyāt svabhartṛsalilāñjalim 022.022
kuryād yānudinaṃ bhaktyā devānām api pūjanam
atithes tarpaṇaṃ tadvad agnihotram amantrakam 022.023
pūrtadharmāśritaṃ cānyat kuryān nityam atandritā
nityakarma ṛte cāsyā neṣṭaṃ karma vidhīyate 022.024
viṣṇor ārādhanaṃ caiva kuryān nityam upoṣitā
dānādi vipramukhyebhyo dadyāt puṇyavivṛddhaye
upavāsāṃś ca vividhān kuryāc chāstroditān śubhe 022.025
lokāntarasthaṃ bhartāram ātmānaṃ ca varānane
tārayaty ubhayaṃ nārī yetthaṃ dharmaparāyaṇā 022.026
putraiśvaryasthitā nārī upavāsādinā harim
yā toṣayati siddhiṃ sā putrebhyo 'pi prayacchati 022.027
śubhāṃl lokāṃs tathā bhartur ātmanaś ca yathepsitān
sakalaṃ pūrayaty astaṃ pāpaṃ nayati cākhilam 022.028
ātmanaś caiva bhartuś ca nārī paramikāṃ gatim
dadāty ārādhya govindaṃ saputrā vidhavā ca yā 022.029
tasmād ebhir vidhānais tu sarvakālaṃ tu yoṣitaḥ
keśavārādhanaṃ kāryaṃ lokadvayaphalapradam 022.030
ye narā mṛtapatnikās tair apy etad aśeṣataḥ
pūrtadharmāśritaṃ kāryaṃ nityakarma ca kevalam 022.031
putraiśvaryasthitaiḥ samyag brahmacaryaguṇānvitaiḥ
viṣṇor ārādhanaṃ kāryaṃ tīrthasthair athavā gṛhe 022.032
brāhmaṇaḥ kṣatriyo vaiśyaḥ strī śūdraś ca varānane
anārādhya hṛṣīkeśaṃ nāpnoti paramāṃ gatim 022.033
aiśvaryaṃ saṃtatiṃ śreṣṭhām ārogyaṃ dravyasaṃpadam
dadāti bhagavān viṣṇur gatim agryāṃ sutoṣitaḥ 022.034
evaṃ śailasutā proktā svayaṃ devena śaṃbhunā
pṛṣṭena samyak kathitaṃ bhavato 'pi mahāmune 022.035
sarvavarṇais tathā strībhir anyair api janair hariḥ
ārādhanīyo nātuṣṭe viṣṇau saṃprāpyate gatiḥ 022.036
na durgatiṃ rauravādīn narakāṃś ca na gacchati
yam ārādhyeśvaraṃ vandyaṃ kas taṃ viṣṇuṃ na pūjayet 022.037
tasmād amuṣmikān kleśān narake yāś ca yātanāḥ
sadaivodvijatā dālbhya samārādhyo janārdanaḥ 022.038
bhagavan yātanā ghorāḥ śrūyante narakeṣu yāḥ
tāsāṃ svarūpam atyugraṃ yathāvad vaktum arhasi 023.001
śṛṇu dālbhyātighorāṇāṃ yātanānāṃ mayoditam
svarūpaṃ nārakair yat tu narakeṣv anubhūyate 023.002
yojanānāṃ sahasrāṇi rauravo narako dvija
aṅgārapūrṇamadhyo 'sau jvālāmālāpariṣkṛtaḥ 023.003
tanmadhye patito yāti yojanāni sahasraśaḥ
satyahānyānṛtī yāti tatra pāparatir naraḥ 023.004
rauravād dviguṇaś caiva mahārauvarasaṃjñitaḥ
taptatāmrapuṭāṅgāra- jvalatpāvakasaṃvṛtaḥ 023.005
paropatāpinas tatra patanti narake narāḥ
nāścaryaṃ dvijaśārdūla varṣalakṣayutāni ca 023.006
kālasūtreṇa cchidyante cakrārūḍhāś ca mānavāḥ
kālāṅgulisthena sadā āpādatalamastakāt 023.007
kālasūtra iti khyāto ghoraḥ sa narakottamaḥ
tatrāpi vañcakā yānti ye caivotkocajīvinaḥ 023.008
taptakumbhas tathaivānyo narako bhṛśadāruṇaḥ
tailakumbheṣu pacyante tatrāpy agnibhṛteṣu te 023.009
devavedadvijātīnāṃ ye nindāṃ kurvate sadā
saṃśṛṇvanti ca ye mūḍhā ye ca matsariṇo 'dhamāḥ 023.010
karambhavālukākumbha- saṃjñaṃ ca narakaṃ śṛṇu
paradāraratā ye tu patanti narake 'dhamāḥ 023.011
hṛtaṃ yaiś ca jalaṃ te 'pi tasmin yānti narādhamāḥ
gonipāneṣu vighnāni mūḍhā ye cāpi kurvate
karambhavālukākumbha- narake te patanti vai 023.012
andhe tamasi duṣpāre śītārtiparikampitāḥ
bhrāmyante mānavā gātraiḥ samastaiḥ sphuṭitāsthibhiḥ 023.013
govadhaḥ strīvadhaḥ pāpaiḥ kṛtaṃ yaiś ca gavānṛtam
te tatrātimahābhīme patanti narake narāḥ 023.014
utpāṭyate tathā jihvā saṃdaṃśair bhṛśadāruṇaiḥ
ākriśakānāṃ duṣṭānāṃ sadaivābaddhabhāṣiṇām 023.015
karapatraiś ca pāṭyante yamasya puruṣais tathā
paradāraparadravya- hiṃsakāḥ puruṣādhamāḥ 023.016
āyasīṃ ca śilāṃ taptām aśeṣāṅgais tathā narāḥ
paradāraratā evaṃ samāliṅganti pāpinaḥ 023.017
sarvāṅgair vikṛtair raktam udgiranto 'tipīḍitāḥ
yantreṣv anyeṣu pīḍyante jantupīḍākarā narāḥ 023.018
vṛkaiḥ saṃbhakṣyate pṛṣṭhaṃ narāṇāṃ pāpakāriṇām
janasya pṛṣṭhamāṃsaṃ yair bhakṣitaṃ pāpakāribhiḥ 023.019
asipatravanair ghoraiś chidyante pāpakarmiṇaḥ
sadbhāvapravaṇā yais tu bhagnā viśrambhino janāḥ 023.020
ayomukhaiḥ khagair bhagnāḥ khaṇḍakhaṇḍaṃ tathāparaiḥ
vrajanti pāpakarmāṇaḥ śvaśṛgālais tathāparaiḥ 023.021
sūṣāyām api dhāsyante jvaladagnicayāvṛtāḥ
pāṣāṇapeṣyaṃ piṣyante tathānye pāpakarmiṇaḥ 023.022
devatātithibhṛtyāṇām adattvā bhuñjate tu ye
mṛṣāgatās tathāivaikyaṃ trapuṣā sīsakena ca
prayānti puruṣās tailaiḥ kvāthyante 'nye punaḥ punaḥ 023.023
varṇadharmaparityāge naikyaṃ ye puruṣā gatāḥ
te 'pi pāpasamācārā varṇasaṃkarakāriṇaḥ 023.024
svarūpaṃ nārakasyāgneḥ śṛṇuṣva kathayāmi te
muktas tato 'nyavahnishtaḥ śete saṃprāpya nirvṛtim 023.025
śastradhārās tathaivaitā mṛṇālaprastaraṃ naraḥ
manyate nārakaiḥ śastrair vikṣato dvijasattama 023.026
himakhaṇḍacayāchanno nivātaṃ manyate naraḥ
vimukto nārakāc chītāt prakāśaṃ tamasas tamaḥ 023.027
protā gudeṣu bhinnāṅgā ārtā rāvavirāviṇaḥ
śūleṣu loheṣv apare triśūleṣu tathāpare 023.028
yājyopādhyāyadāmpatya- suhṛnmitrasutādiṣu
kṛto bhedo durācārair yair alīkoktibhāṣibhiḥ 023.029
āyasāḥ kaṇṭakās tīkṣṇā narake kūṭaśālmalau
teṣu protā durātmānaḥ paradārabhujo narāḥ 023.030
kṛmikīṭajalaukādi- tīkṣṇadaṃṣṭrāsyavikṣatāḥ
bhrāmyante cāndhatāmisre vṛthāmāṃsāśino hi ye 023.031
etāṃś cānyāṃś ca narakāñ śataśo 'tha sahasraśaḥ
karmāntaraṃ jano bhuṅkte pariṇāmāṃś ca cetasaḥ 023.032
yādṛk karma manuṣyāṇāṃ tādṛg viṣayarūpavat
pariṇāmaṃ mano yāti śubhāśubhamayaṃ dvija 023.033
atīvabhīṣaṇān itthaṃ śastrāgnibhayadān naraḥ
kathaṃ na gacchen narakān etan me vaktum arhasi 024.001
aho 'tikaṣṭapāpānāṃ vipāko narakasthitaiḥ
puruṣair bhujyate brahmaṃs tanmokṣaṃ vada sattama 024.002
puṇyasya karmaṇaḥ pākaḥ puṇya eva dvijottama
cetasaḥ pariṇāmottaḥ svargasthair bhujyate naraiḥ 024.003
tathaiva pākaḥ pāpānāṃ puruṣair narakasthitaiḥ
bhujyate tāvad akhilaṃ yāvat pāpaṃ kṣayaṃ gatam 024.004
yadā tu pāpasya jayaḥ kṣīyate sukṛtaṃ tadā
śubhasya karmaṇo vṛddhau kṣayam āyāty aśobhanam 024.005
jaye yateta puruṣas tasmāt sukṛtakarmaṇaḥ
pāpaṃ karma vinā naiva narakaprāptir iṣyate 024.006
jayāya dvādaśī śastā nR̥ṇāṃ sukṛtakarmaṇām
yām upoṣya dvijaśreṣṭha na yāti narakaṃ naraḥ 024.007
phālgunāmalapakṣasya ekādaśyām upoṣitaḥ
dvādaśyāṃ tu dvijaśreṣṭha pūjayen madhusūdanam 024.008
ekādaśyāṃ samuddiṣṭaṃ viṣṇor nāmānukīrtanam
pūjāyāṃ vāsudevasya kurvīta susamāhitaḥ 024.009
namo nārāyaṇāyeti vācyaṃ ca svapatā niśi 024.010,*(15)
krodhaḥ prapañca īrṣyā ca dambho lobhaś ca varjitaḥ 024.010
kāmo droho madaś cāpi mānamātsaryam eva ca
sarvam etat parityajya viṣṇubhaktena cetasā 024.011
asāratāṃ ca loke 'smin saṃsāre bhāvayen matim
tathaiva kuryād dvādaśyāṃ nāmnām uccāraṇaṃ dvija 024.012
kāmaṃ krodhaṃ ca lobhaṃ ca dambham īrṣyāṃ ca varjayet
mānadrohādidoṣāṃś ca sarvān dhanamadodbhūtān
bhāvayed viṣṇubhaktāṃś ca saṃsārāsāratāṃ tathā
evaṃ bhāvitacittena prāṇināṃ hitam icchatā 024.*(15)
yavapātrāṇi pūrvaṃ tu dadyān māsacatuṣṭayam
āṣāḍhādidvitīyaṃ tu pāraṇaṃ yan mahāmate
tatrāpi ghṛtapātrāṇi dadyāc chraddhāsamanvitaḥ 024.013
kārttikādiṣu māseṣu māghanteṣu tathā tilān
viprāya dadyāt pātrashtān pratimāsam upoṣitaḥ 024.014
nāmatrayam aśeṣeṣu māsi māsi dinadvayam
tathaivoccārayed dadyād dvādaśyāṃ ca yavādikam
praṇamya ca hṛṣīkeśaṃ kṛtapūjaḥ prasādayet 024.015
viṣṇo namas te jagataḥ prasūte oṃ vāsudevāya namo namas te
nārāyaṇa tvāṃ praṇato 'smy acintya jayo 'stu me śāśvatapuṇyarāśeḥ 024.016
prasīda puṇyaṃ jayam etu viṣṇo oṃ vāsudeva rddhim upaitu puṇyam
nārāyaṇoṃ bhūtim upaitu puṇyam prayātu cāśeṣam aghaṃ vināśam 024.017
viṣṇo puṇyodbhavo me 'stu vāsudevāstu me śubham
nārāyaṇāstu dharmo me jahi pāpam aśeṣataḥ 024.018
anekajanmajanitaṃ bālyayauvanavārddhike
puṇyaṃ vivṛddhim āyātu yātu pāpaṃ tu saṃkṣayam 024.019
ākāśādiṣu śabdādau śrotrādau mahadādiṣu
prakṛtau puruṣe caiva brahmaṇy api ca sa prabhuḥ
yathaika eva sarvātmā vāsudevo vyavasthitaḥ 024.020
tena satyena me pāpaṃ narakārtipradaṃ kṣayam
prayātu sukṛtasyāstu mamānudivasaṃ jayaḥ
pāpasya hāniḥ puṇyaṃ ca vṛddhim abhyety anuttamām 024.021
evam uccārya viprāya dattvā yat kathitaṃ tava
bhuñjīta kṛtakṛtyas tu pāraṇe pāraṇe gate 024.022
pāraṇānte ca devasya prīṇanaṃ śaktito dvija
kurvītākhilapāṣaṇḍair ālāpaṃ ca vivarjayet 024.023
ity etat kathitaṃ dālbhya sukṛtasya jayāvahā
dvādaśī narakaṃ mṛtyo yām upoṣya na paśyati 024.024
nāgnayo na ca śastrāṇi na ca lohamūkhāḥ khagāḥ
nārakās taṃ prabādhante matir yasya janārdane 024.025
nāmoccāraṇamātreṇa viṣṇoḥ kṣīṇo 'ghasaṃcayaḥ
bhavaty apāstapāpasya narake gamanaṃ kutaḥ 024.026
namo nārāyaṇa hare vāsudeveti kīrtayet
na yāti narakaṃ martyaḥ saṃkṣīṇāśeṣapātakaḥ 024.027
tasmāt pāṣaṇḍisaṃsargam akurvan dvādaśīm imām
upoṣya puṇyopacayī na yāti narakaṃ naraḥ 024.028
pāṣaṇḍibhir asaṃsparśam asaṃbhāṣaṇam eva ca
viṣṇor ārādhanaparair naraiḥ kāryam upoṣitaiḥ 025.001
kiṃ brūhi lakṣaṇaṃ teṣāṃ yādṛśān varjayed vratī
kathaṃcid yadi saṃlāpa- darśanasparśanādikam 025.002
upoṣitānāṃ pāṣaṇḍair narāṇāṃ vipra jāyate
kiṃ tatra vada kartavyaṃ yenākhaṇḍaṃ vrataṃ bhavet 025.003
śrutismṛtyuditaṃ dharmaṃ varṇāśramavibhāgajam
ullaṅghya ye pravartante svecchayā kūṭayuktibhiḥ 025.004
vikarmābhiratā mūḍhā yuktiprāgalbhyadurmadāḥ
pāṣaṇḍinas te duḥśīlā narakārhā narādhamāḥ 025.005
tāṃs tu pāṣaṇḍinaḥ pāpān vikarmasthāṃś ca mānavān
vaiḍālavratikāṃś caiva nityam eva tu nālapet 025.006
saṃbhāṣyaitāñ śuciṣadaṃ cintayed acyutaṃ budhaḥ
idaṃ codāharet samyak kṛtvā tatpravaṇaṃ manaḥ 025.007
śārīram antaḥkaraṇopaghātaṃ vācaś ca viṣṇur bhagavān aśeṣam
śamaṃ nayatv astu mameha śarma pāpād anante hṛdi saṃniviṣṭe 025.008
antaḥśuddhiṃ bahiḥśuddhiṃ śuddho 'ntar mama yo 'cyutaḥ
sa karotv amale tasmiñ śucir evāsmi sarvadā 025.009
bāhyopaghātād anagho boddhā ca bhagavān ajaḥ
śuddhiṃ nayatv anantātmā viṣṇuś cetasi saṃsthitaḥ 025.010
etat saṃbhāṣya japtavyaṃ pāṣaṇḍibhir upoṣitaiḥ
namaḥ śuciṣadety uktvā sūryaṃ paśyeta vīkṣitaiḥ 025.011
śrūyate ca purā martyāḥ svecchayā svargagāminaḥ
babhūvur anaghāḥ sarve svadharmaparipālanāt 025.012
devāś ca balino martyair varṇakarmaṇy anuvrataiḥ
yajñādhyayanadāneṣu vartamānaiś ca mānavaiḥ 025.013
daiteyāś ca parābhāvam atuṣṭāv asurā yayuḥ
tataś ca ṣaṇḍo markaś ca daityendrāṇāṃ purohitau
cakratuḥ karma devānāṃ vināśāyātibhīṣaṇam 025.014
tatrotpanno 'tikṛṣṇāṅgas tamaḥprāyo 'tidāruṇaḥ
dambhādhāraḥ śāṭhyasāro nidrāprakṛtir ulvaṇaḥ 025.015
mahāmoha iti khyātaḥ kṛtyarūpo vibhīṣaṇaḥ
caturdhā sa vibhaktaś ca tābhām atra mahīyate 025.016
vedadevadvijātīnām ekāṃśena sa nindanam
karoty anyena na ratiṃ yogakarmasu vindati 025.017
vikarmaṇy apareṇāpi saṃyojayati mānavān
jñānāpahāram anyena karoti dvijasattama 025.018
jñānabuddhyā tathājñānaṃ gṛhṇāty ajñānamohitaḥ
vedavādavirodhena yā kathā sāsya rocate 025.019
evaṃ sa tu mahāmohaḥ ṣaṇḍamarkopapāditaḥ
dambhādidūṣito 'dharma- svarūpo 'tibhayaṃkara 025.020
sa lokān vividhopāyair lokeṣv eva vyavasthitaḥ
mohābhibhavaniḥsārāṇ karoti dvijasattama 025.021
tanmohitānām acirād viveko yāti saṃkṣayam
kṣīṇajñānā vikarmāṇi kurvanty aharaho dvija 025.022
nijavarṇātmakaṃ dharmaṃ parityajya vimohitāḥ
dharmabuddhyā tataḥ pāpaṃ kurvanty ajñānadurmadāḥ 025.023
jñānāvalepas tatraiva tatas teṣāṃ prajāyate
suhṛdbhir vāryamāṇās te paṇḍitaiś ca dayālubhiḥ
prayacchanty uttaraṃ ṃūḍhāḥ kūṭayuktisamanvitam 025.024
tatas te svayam ātmānam anyaṃ cālpamatiṃ naram
vikarmaṇā yojayantaś cyavayanti svadharmataḥ 025.025
pāṣaṇḍino durācārāḥ parānnaguṇavādinaḥ
asaṃskṛtānnabhoktāro vrātyāḥ saṃskāravarjitāḥ 025.026
pāṣaṇḍāḥ pāpasaṃkalpā dāmbhikāḥ śaṭhabuddhayaḥ
varṇasaṃkarakartāro māyāvyājopajīvinaḥ
niḥśaucā vakramatayo nānyadastītivādinaḥ 025.027
evaṃvidhās te sanmārgād vedaproktād bahiḥsthitāḥ
kriyākalāpaṃ nindanta ṛgyajuḥsāmasaṃjñitam
ātmānaṃ ca parāṃś caiva kurvanti narakasthitān 025.028
teṣāṃ darśanasaṃbhāṣa- sparśanāni naraiḥ sadā
parityājyāni dṛṣṭe ca proktaḥ saṃbhāṣaṇe ca yaḥ
saṃsparśe ca budhaḥ snātvā śuciḥ śuciṣadaṃ smaret 025.029
bhavaty ataḥ sadaivaiṣām ālāpaspar1śanaṃ tyajet
puṇyakāmo mahābhāgaḥ kiṃ punar yad upoṣitaḥ 025.030
yato hi nindite karmaṇy abhyāso ratir eva ca
pāṣaṇḍinām aśeṣāṇām aprītir vedakarmaṇi
te hy adhogāminaḥ proktā āsuraṃ bhāvam āśritāḥ 025.031
aprāptir na tathā duḥkham aiśvaryāder dvijottama
yathā manorathair labdhair vicyutir dharmahānijā 026.001
aiśvaryād vittato vāpi saṃtater devalokataḥ
abhīṣṭād anyato vāpi padād yena na vicyutim 026.002
prāpnoti puruṣo brahman nārī vāpuṇyasaṃkṣayāt
tan mamācakṣva viprarṣe duḥkham ebhyo hi vicyutiḥ 026.003
satyam etan mahābhāga duḥkhaṃ prāptasya saṃkṣayaḥ
aiśvaryād atha vittasya bandhuvargasukhasya vā 026.004
tad etac chrūyatāṃ dālbhya yathā neṣṭāt paricyutiḥ
sargāder jāyate samyag upavāsavatāṃ satām 026.005
dvādaśarkṣāṇi viprarṣe pratimāsaṃ tu yāni vai
tannāmāny acyutaṃ teṣu samyak saṃpūjayed budhaḥ 026.006
puṣpair dhūpais tathāmbhobhir abhīṣṭair aparais tathā
āditaḥ kṛttikāṃ kṛtvā kārttike munipuṅgava 026.007
naivedyaṃ kṛsaraṃ pūrvam annaṃ māsacatuṣṭayam
nivedayet kārttikādi saṃyāvaṃ ca tataḥ param 026.008
āṣāḍhādau ca devāya pāyasaṃ vai nivedayet
tenaivānnena viprarṣe brāhmaṇān bhojayed budhaḥ 026.009
pañcagavyajalasnātas tasyaiva prāśanāc chuciḥ
naivedyaṃ svayam aśnīyān naktaṃ saṃpūjite 'cyute 026.010
evaṃ saṃvatsarasyānte tataḥ suptotthite 'cyute
saṃyak saṃpūjya viprarṣe tam eva puruṣottamam
praṇamya prārthayed vidvāñ śuciḥ snāto yathāvidhi 026.011
namo namas te 'cyuta saṃkṣayo 'stu pāpasya vṛddhiṃ samupaitu puṇyam
aiśvaryavittādi sadākṣayaṃ me 'kṣayā ca me saṃtatir acyutāstu 026.012
yathācyutas tvaṃ parataḥ parasmāt sa brahmabhūtāt parataḥ parātman
tathācyutaṃ me kuru vāñchitaṃ yan mayā padaṃ pāpaharāprameya 026.013
acyutānanta govinda prasīda yad abhīpsitam
tad akṣayam ameyātman kuruṣva puruṣottama 026.014
evam ante samabhyarcya prārthayitvā tathāśiṣaḥ
yathāvan muniśārdūla cyutiṃ nāpnoti mānavaḥ 026.015
saṃtateḥ svargavittāder aiśvaryasya tathā mune
yad vābhimatam atyantaṃ tato na cyavate naraḥ 026.016
tasmāt sarvaprayatnena māsanakṣatrapūjane
yatetākṣayakāmas tu sadaiva munipuṅgava 026.017
atrāpi śrūyate siddhā kācit svarge mahāvratā
nārī tapodhanā bhūtvā prakhyātā śāmbharāyaṇī
samastasaṃdehaharā sadā svargaukasāṃ hi sā 027.001
kasyacit tv atha kālasya devarājaḥ śatakratuḥ
pūrvendracaritaṃ brahman papracchedaṃ bṛhaspatim 027.002
pūrvendrā parataḥ pūrve ye babhūvuḥ sureśvarāḥ
teṣāṃ caritam icchāmi śrotum āṅgirasāṃ vara 027.003
evam uktas tadā tena devendreṇāmaladyutiḥ
prāha dharmabhṛtāṃ śreṣṭhaḥ paramarṣir bṛhaspatiḥ 027.004
nāhaṃ cirantanān vedmi devarāja sureśvarān
ātmanaḥ samakālīnaṃ mām avaihi sureśvara 027.005
tataḥ papraccha devendraḥ ko 'smābhir munipuṅgava
praṣṭavyo 'tra mahābhāga kṛtādivasatir divi 027.006
bṛhaspatiś ciraṃ dhyātvā punar āha śacīpatim
tapasvinīṃ mahābhāgāṃ smṛtvāsau śāmbharāyaṇīm 027.007
na devā na ca gandharvā na cānye cirasaṃsthitāḥ
cirantanānāṃ cariteṣv abhijñā tridaśeśvara 027.008
ekaiva cirakālajñā dharmajñā śakra kevalam
jānāty akhiladevendra- caritaṃ śāmbharāyaṇī 027.009
ity uktas tena devendraḥ kautūhalasamanvitaḥ
yayau yatra mahābhāgā tāpasī śāmbharāyaṇī 027.010
sā tau dṛṣṭvā samāyātau devarājabṛhaspatī
samyag arghyena saṃpūjya praṇipatya śubhavratā 027.011
namo 'stu devarājāya tathaivāṅgirase namaḥ
yad vāṃ kāryaṃ mahābhāgau sakalaṃ tad ihocyatām 027.012
āvām abhyāgatau praṣṭuṃ tvām atrātivivekinīm
yac ca kāryaṃ mahābhāge tat pṛṣṭā kathayeha nau 027.013
yadi smarasi kalyāṇi pūrvendracaritāni nau
tadākhyāhi mahābhāge devendrasya kutūhalāt 027.014
yadi śakyaṃ mayā kartuṃ tat kariṣye vimṛṣyatu 027.*(16)
yo vai pūrvaḥ surendrasya tataś ca prathamo hi yaḥ
tasmāt pūrvataro yaś ca tasyāpi prathamāś ca ye 027.015
teṣāṃ pūrvatarā ye ca vedmi tān akhilān aham
teṣāṃ ca caritaṃ kṛtsnaṃ jānāmy āṅgirasāṃ vara 027.016
manvantarāṇy anekāni sṛṣṭiṃ ca tridivaukasām
saptarṣīn subahūn deva manūnāṃ ca sutān nṛpa
tat pṛccha tvaṃ vadāmy eṣā pūrvendracaritaṃ mune 027.017
evam ukte tatas tābhyāṃ pṛṣṭā sā śāmbharāyaṇī
yathāvad ācaṣṭa tayoḥ pūrvendracaritaṃ dvija 027.018
svāyambhuve yas tu manau manau svārociṣe tu yaḥ
uttame tāmase caiva raivate cākṣuṣe tathā 027.019
yo yo babhūva devendras tasya tasya tapasvinī
tayor jagāda caritaṃ yathāvac chāmbharāyaṇī 027.020
tataḥ kautūhalaparo devarāṭ tāṃ tapasvinīm
uvāca jānāsi kathaṃ tvam etac chāmbharāyaṇi 027.021
sarva eva hi devendrāḥ svargasthā ye manīṣiṇaḥ
babhūvur etac caritam eteṣāṃ vedmi tena vai 027.022
kiṃ kṛtaṃ vada dharmajñe tvayā yeneyam akṣayā
svarloke vasatiḥ prāptā yathā nānyena kenacit 027.023
aho sarvavratānāṃ tad upoṣitaṃ mahad vratam
pradhānataram atyarthaṃ svargasaṃvāsadaṃ matam 027.024
caritaṃ ca mayā teṣāṃ śrutaṃ dṛṣṭaṃ tathaiva ca 027.*(17)
evam uktā tatas tena devendreṇa yaśasvinī
pratyuvāca mahābhāgā yathāvac chāmbharāyaṇī 027.025
māsarkṣeṣv acyuto devaḥ pratimāsaṃ sureśvara
yathoktavratayā samyak sapta varṣāṇi pūjitaḥ 027.026
tasyeyaṃ karmaṇo vyuṣṭir acyutārādhanasya me
devalokād abhimatā devarāja yad acyutiḥ 027.027
svargaṃ dravyamayaiśvaryaṃ saṃtatiṃ vāpi yo 'cyutām
naro vāñchati tenetthaṃ toṣaṇīyo 'cyutaḥ prabhuḥ 027.028
etat te pūrvadevendra- caritaṃ sakalaṃ mayā
svargavāsākṣayatvaṃ ca māsarkṣācyutapūjanāt 027.029
yathāvat kathitaṃ deva pṛcchatas tridaśeśvara
dharmārthakāmamokṣāṃs tu vāñchatāṃ vibudhādhipa
viṣṇor ārādhanān nānyat paramaṃ siddhikāraṇam 027.030
tasyās tad vacanaṃ śrutvā devarājabṛhaspatī
tāṃ tathety ūcatuḥ sādhvīṃ ceratuś cāpi tad vratam 027.031
tasmād dālbhya prayatnena pratimāsaṃ samāhitaḥ
māsarkṣācyutapūjāyāṃ bhavethās tanmanāḥ sadā 027.032
bhagavan prāṇinaḥ sarve viṣarogādyupadravaiḥ
duṣṭagrahopaghātaiś ca sarvakālam upadrutāḥ 028.001
ābhicārukakṛtyābhiḥ sparṣarogaiś ca dāruṇaiḥ
sadā saṃpīḍyamānās te tiṣṭhanti munisattama 028.002
yena karmavipākena viṣarogādyupadravāḥ
na bhavanti nṛṇāṃ tan me yathāvad vaktum arhasi 028.003
vratopavāsair yair viṣṇur nānyajanmani pūjitaḥ
te narā muniśārdūla graharogādibhāginaḥ 028.004
yair na tatpravaṇaṃ cittaṃ sarvadaiva naraiḥ kṛtam
viṣagrahajvarāṇāṃ te manuṣyā dālbhya bhājanāḥ 028.005
ārogyaṃ paramām ṛddhiṃ manasā yad yad icchati
tat tad āpnoty asaṃdigdhaṃ paratrācyutatoṣakṛt 028.006
nādhīn prāpnoti na vyādhīn na viṣagrahabandhanam
kṛtyāsparśabhayaṃ vāpi toṣite madhusūdane 028.007
sarvaduṣṭaśamas tasya saumyās tasya sadā grahāḥ
devānām apradhṛṣyo 'sau tuṣṭo yasya janārdanaḥ 028.008
yaḥ samaḥ sarvabhūteṣu yathātmani tathāpare
upavādādinā tena toṣyate madhusūdanaḥ 028.009
toṣite tatra jāyante narāḥ pūṛṇamanorathāḥ
arogāḥ sukhino bhoga- bhoktāro munisattama 028.010
na teṣāṃ śatravo naiva sparśarogābhicārukāḥ
graharogādikaṃ vāpi pāpakāryaṃ na jāyate 028.011
avyāhatāni kṛṣṇasya cakrādīny ātmayudhāni tam
rakṣanti sakalāpadbhyo yena viṣṇur upāsitaḥ 028.012
anārādhitagovindā ye narā duḥkhabhāginaḥ
teṣāṃ duḥkhābhibhūtānāṃ kartavyaṃ yad dayālubhiḥ 028.013
paśyadbhiḥ sarvabhūtasthaṃ vāsudevaṃ mahāmune
samadṛṣṭibhir īśeśaṃ tan mama brūhy aśeṣataḥ 028.014
kuśamūlasthito brahmā kuśamadhye janārdanaḥ 028.*(18).002
kuśāgre śaṃkaraṃ vidyāt trayo devā vyavasthitāḥ 028.*(18).003
gṛhītvā ca sa mūlāgrān kuśāñ śuddhān upaspṛśet 028.*(18).004
mārjayet sarvagātrāṇi kuśāgrair dālbhya śāntikṛt 028.*(18).005
śarīre yasya tiṣṭhanti kuśasthajalabindavaḥ 028.*(18).006
naśyanti tasya pāpāni garuḍenaiva pannagāḥ 028.*(18).007
viṣṇubhaktā viśeṣeṇa ....cidgatamānasaḥ 028.*(18).008
rogagrahaviṣārtānāṃ kuryāc chāntim imāṃ śubhām 028.*(18).009
nārasiṃhaṃ samabhyarcya śucau deśe kuśāsane 028.*(18).010
mantrair etair yathā liṅgaṃ kuryād digbandham ātmanaḥ 028.*(18).011
vārāhaṃ nārasiṃhaṃ ca vāmanaṃ viṣṇum eva ca 028.*(18).012
dhyātvā samāhito bhūtvā dikṣu nāmāni vinyāset 028.*(18).013
pūrve nārāyaṇaḥ pātu vārijākṣas tu dakṣiṇe 028.*(18).014
pradyumnaḥ paścimasyāṃ tu vāsudevas tathottare 028.*(18).015
īśānyām avatād viṣṇur āgneyyāṃ ca janārdanaḥ 028.*(18).016
nairṛtyāṃ padmanābhaś ca vāyavyāṃ caiva mādhavaḥ 028.*(18).017
ūrdhvaṃ govardhanadharo adharāyāṃ trivikramaḥ 028.*(18).018
etābhyo daśadigbhyas tu sarvataḥ pātu keśavaḥ 028.*(18).019
aṅguṣṭhāgre tu govindaṃ tarjanyāṃs tu mahīdharam 028.*(18).020
madhyamāyāṃ hṛṣīkeśam anāmikyāṃ trivikramam 028.*(18).021
kaṇiṣṭhāyāṃ nyased viṣṇuṃ karamadhye tu mādhavam 028.*(18).022
evaṃ nyāsaṃ purā kṛtvā paścād aṅgeṣu vinyaset 028.*(18).023
śikhāyāṃ keśavaṃ nyasya mūrdhni nārāyaṇaṃ nyaset 028.*(18).024
cakṣurmadhye nyased viṣṇuṃ karṇayor madhusūdanam 028.*(18).025
trivikramaṃ kapālasthaṃ vāmanaṃ karṇamūlayoḥ 028.*(18).026
dāmodaraṃ dantavaktrau vārāhaṃ cibuke nyaset 028.*(18).027
uttaroṣṭhe hṛṣīkeśaṃ padmanābhaṃ tathādhare 028.*(18).028
jihvāyāṃ vāsudevaṃ ca tālvake garuḍadhvajam 028.*(18).029
vaikuṇṭhaṃ kanṭhamadhyastham anantaṃ nāsikopari 028.*(18).030
dakṣiṇe tu bhuje vipra vinyaset puruṣottamam 028.*(18).031
vāmabhuje mahābhāgaṃ rāghavaṃ hṛdi vinyaset 028.*(18).032
pītāmbaraṃ sarvatanau hariṃ nābhau tu vinyaset 028.*(18).033
kare tu dakṣiṇe vipra tataḥ saṃkarṣaṇaṃ nyaset 028.*(18).034
vāme vipra hariṃ vidyāt kaṭimadhye 'parājitam 028.*(18).035
pṛṣṭhe kṣitidharaṃ vidyād acyutaṃ skandhayor api 028.*(18).036
mādhavaṃ bāhu kukṣau tu dakṣiṇe yogaśāyinam 028.*(18).037
svayaṃbhuvaṃ meḍhramadhye ūrubhyāṃ tu gadādharam 028.*(18).038
cakriṇaṃ jānumadhye tu jaṅghayor acyutaṃ nyaset 028.*(18).039
gulpayor narasiṃhaṃ ca pādapṛṣṭhe 'mitaujasam 028.*(18).040
śrīdharaṃ cāṅgulīṣu syāt padmākṣaṃ sarvasandhiṣu 028.*(18).041
romakūpe guḍākeśaṃ kṛṣṇaṃ raktāsthimajjāsu 028.*(18).042
manobuddhyor ahaṃkāreṣv evaṃ citte janārdanam 028.*(18).043
nakheṣu mādhavaṃ caiva nyaset pādatale 'cyutam 028.*(18).044
evaṃ nyāsavidhiṃ kṛtvā sākṣān nārāyaṇo bhavet 028.*(18).045
tanur viṣṇumayī tasya yāvat kiṃcin na bhāṣate 028.*(18).046
evaṃ nyāsaṃ tataḥ kṛtvā yat kāryaṃ śṛṇu tad dvija 028.*(18).047
pādamūle tu devasya śaṅkhaṃ tatraiva vinyaset 028.*(18).048
vanamālāṃ tu vinyasya sarvadevābhipūjitām 028.*(18).049
gadāṃ vakṣaḥsthale caiva cakraṃ caiva tu pṛṣṭhataḥ 028.*(18).050
śrīvatsāṅgaṃ śiro nyasya pañcāṅgakavacaṃ nyaset 028.*(18).051
āpādāmastake caiva vinyaset puruṣottamam 028.*(18).052
oṃ apāmārjanako nyāsaḥ sarvavyādhivināśanaḥ 028.*(18).053
viṣṇur ūrdhvam adho rakṣed vaikuṇṭho vidiśo diśaḥ 028.*(18).054
pātu māṃ sarvato rāmo dhanvī cakrī ca keśavaḥ 028.*(18).055
pūjākāle tu devasya japakāle tathaiva ca 028.*(18).059
homārambheṣu sarveṣu trisaṃdhyāsu ca nityaśaḥ 028.*(18).060
āyur ārogyam aiśvaryaṃ jñānaṃ vittaṃ phalaṃ bhavet 028.*(18).061
yad yat sukhakaraṃ proktaṃ tat sarvaṃ prāpnuyān naraḥ 028.*(18).062
abhayaṃ sarvabhūtebhyo viṣṇulokaṃ ca gacchati 028.*(18).063
atha dhyānaṃ pravakṣyāmi sarvapāpapraṇāśanam 028.*(18).077
vārāharūpiṇaṃ devaṃ saṃsmaraty aparājitam 028.*(18).078
bṛhattanuṃ bṛhadgātraṃ bṛhaddaṃṣṭrasuśobhanam 028.*(18).079
samastavedavedāṅgaṃ yuktāṅgaṃ bhūṣaṇair yutam 028.*(18).080
uddhṛtya bhūmiṃ pātālād hastābhyām upagṛhṇatām 028.*(18).081
āliṅgya bhūmiṃ śirasi mūrdhni jighrantam āsthitam 028.*(18).082
ratnavaiḍūryamukhyābhir muktābhir upaśobhitam 028.*(18).083
pītāmbaradharaṃ devaṃ śuklamālyānulepanam 028.*(18).084
trayastriṃśakoṭidevaiḥ stūyamānaṃ mudāniśam 028.*(18).085
nṛtyadbhir apsarobhiś ca gīyamānaṃ ca kinnaraiḥ 028.*(18).086
itthaṃ dhyātvā mahātmānaṃ japen nityaṃ mahātmanaḥ 028.*(18).087
suvarṇamaṇḍapāntasthaṃ padmaṃ dhyāyet sakesaram 028.*(18).088
sakarṇikadalair iṣṭair aṣṭabhiḥ pariśobhitam 028.*(18).089
karaṃ karahitaṃ devaṃ pūrṇacandrāptasuprabham 028.*(18).090
taḍitsamaśaṭāśobhi kaṇṭhanālopaśobhitam 028.*(18).091
śrīvatsāṅkitavakṣaḥsthaṃ tīkṣṇadaṃṣṭraṃ trilocanam 028.*(18).092
javākusumasaṃkāśaṃ raktahastatalānvitam 028.*(18).093
pītavastraparīdhānaṃ śuklayastrottarīyakam 028.*(18).094
karaṃ karahitaṃ devaṃ pūrṇacandrāptasuprabham 028.*(18).095
kaṭisūtreṇa haimena nūpureṇa virājitam 028.*(18).096
vanamālādiśobhāḍhyaṃ muktāhāropaśobhitam 028.*(18).097
anekasūryasaṃkāśaṃ mukuṭāṭopamastakam 028.*(18).098
śaṅkhacakragṛhītābhyām udbāhubhyāṃ virājitam 028.*(18).099
paṅkajābhaṃ caturhastaṃ tatpatrābhasulocanam 028.*(18).100
prātaḥ sūryasamaprakhya- kuṇḍalābhyāṃ virājitam 028.*(18).101
keyūrakāntisasyarddhi- muktikāratnaśobhitam 028.*(18).102
jānūparinyastahastaṃ vararatnanakhāṅkuram 028.*(18).103
jaṅghābharaṇasasyarddhi- visphuryatkaṅkanatviṣam 028.*(18).104
muktāphalābdasamahad- dantapaṅktivirājitam 028.*(18).105
campakāmukulaprakhya- sunāsāmukhapaṅkajam 028.*(18).106
atiraktauṣṭhavadanaṃ vyāttāsyam atibhīṣaṇam 028.*(18).107
vāmāṅkasthaṃ śivabhakta- śāntidāṃ sunitambinīm 028.*(18).108
arhaṇīyāṃ sujātoruṃ sunāsāṃ śubhalakṣaṇām 028.*(18).109
subhrūṃ sukeśīṃ suśroṇīṃ suśubhāṃ sudvijānanām 028.*(18).110
supratiṣṭhāṃ suvadanāṃ caturhastāṃ vicintayet 028.*(18).111
dukūle caiva cārvaṅgīṃ hāriṇīṃ sarvakāmadām 028.*(18).112
taptakañcanasaṃkāśāṃ sarvābharaṇabhūṣitām 028.*(18).113
suvarṇakalaśaprakhya- pīnonnatapayodharām 028.*(18).114
gṛhītapadmayugalaṃ udbāhubhyāṃ tathānyayoḥ 028.*(18).115
gṛhītamātulaṅgākhyaṃ jāmbunadakarān tathā 028.*(18).116
evaṃ devīṃ nṛsiṃhasya vāmāṅkopari saṃsmaret 028.*(18).117
ativimalasugātraṃ raupyapātrastham annaṃ 028.*(18).118
sulalitadadhikhaṇḍaṃ pāṇinā dakṣiṇena 028.*(18).119
kalaśam amṛtapūrṇaṃ savyahaste dadhānaṃ 028.*(18).120
tadatisakaladuḥkhaṃ vāmanaṃ bhāvayed yaḥ 028.*(18).121
anyā bhāskarasaprabhābhir akhilair bhābhir diśo bhāsayan 028.*(18).122
bhīmākṣasphuradaṭṭahāsavilasāddaṃṣṭrāgradīptānanaḥ 028.*(18).123
dorbhiś cakradharau gadābjamukulau trāsāṃś ca pāśāṅkuśau 028.*(18).124
bibhratpiṅgaśiro 'ruhoddhatasaṭaś cakravidhāno hariḥ 028.*(18).125
manobhūtānīndriyāṇi guṇāḥ sattvaṃ rajas tamaḥ 028.*(18).139
trailokyasyeśvaraṃ sarvam ahaṃkāre pratiṣṭhitāḥ 028.*(18).140
oṃ namaḥ paramārthāya puruṣāya mahātmane
arūpabahurūpāya vyāpine paramātmane
niṣkalmaṣāya śuddhāya sarvapāpaharāya ca 028.015
namas te devadevāya suraśūra namo 'stu te
lokādhyakṣa jagatpūjya paramātman namas te (!) 028.*(19)
namaskṛtvā pravakṣyāmi yat tat sidhyatu me vacaḥ 028.016,*(20),*(21)
varāhanarasiṃhāya vāmanāya mahātmane
trivikramāya rāmāya vaikuṇṭhāya narāya ca 028.017
govindapadmanābhāya vāmadevāya bhūpate 028.*(20).001
nārāyaṇāya devāya anantāya mahātmane 028.*(20).003
garuḍadhvajāya kṛṣṇāya pītāmbaradharāya ca 028.*(20).005
yogīśvarāya siddhāya guhyāya paramātmane 028.*(20).007
janārdanāya kṛṣṇāya upendraśrīdharāya ca 028.*(20).009
bhaktapriyāya vidhaye viṣvaksenāya śārṅgine 028.*(20).011
hiraṇyagarbhapataye hiraṇyakaśipucchide 028.*(20).013
cakrahastāya śūlāya tarjanyapatrāya dhīmate 028.*(20).015
ādityāya upendrāya bhūtānāṃ jīvanāya ca 028.*(20).017
vāsudevāya vandyāya varadāya mahātmane 028.*(20).019
viṣūvṛcchravase tasmai kṣīrāmbunichiśāyine 028.*(20).021
adhokṣajāya bhadrāya śrīdharāyādimūrtaye 028.*(20).023
viśveśadvāramūrtiś ca mṛtyurāyohito 'sti saḥ 028.*(20).025
nānārāgāṃś ca dakṣāṃś ca vikaṭāya mahābhītī 028.*(20).027
jātupatiṃ vyagrahastaṃ vararatnanakhākaram 028.*(20).028
nārāyaṇāya viśvāya viśveśāyāmbarāya ca 028.*(20).032
dāmodarāya devāya anantāya mahātmane 028.*(20).034
namaskṛtvā pravakṣyāmi yat tat sidhyatu me vacaḥ 028.018
varāhanarasiṃheśa vāmaneśa trivikrama
hayagrīveśa sarveśa hṛṣīkeśa harāśubham 028.019
aparājitacakrādyaiś caturbhiḥ paramāyudhaiḥ
akhaṇḍitaprabhāvais tvaṃ sarvaduṣṭaharo bhava 028.020
harāmukasya duritaṃ duṣkṛtaṃ durupoṣitam
mṛtyubandhārtibhayadaṃ duriṣṭasya ca yat phalam 028.021
parāpadhyānasahitaṃ prayuktaṃ cābhicāruka
garasparśamahāyoga- prayogajarayājara 028.022
oṃ namo vāsudevāya namaḥ kṣṛṇāya śārṅgiṇe
namaḥ puṣkaranetrāya keśavāyādicakriṇe 028.023
namaḥ kamalakiñjalka- pītanirmalavāsase
mahāhavaripuskandha- ghṛṣṭacakrāya cakriṇe 028.024
daṃṣṭroddhṛtakṣitidhṛte trayīmūrtimate namaḥ
mahāyajñavarāhāya śeṣabhogoruśāyine 028.025
taptahāṭakakeśānta jvalatpāvakalocana
vajrādhikanakhasparśa divyasiṃha namo 'stu te 028.026
kapila hemāśvaśīrṣa atiriktavilocana
vidyutsphuritadaṃṣṭrāgra divyasiṃha namo 'stu te 028.*(22)
kāśyapāyātihrasvāya ṛgyajuḥsāmabhūṣita
tubhyaṃ vāmanarūpāya sṛjate gāṃ namo namaḥ 028.027
varāhāśeṣaduṣṭāni sarvapāpaharāṇi vai
marda marda mahādaṃṣṭra marda marda ca tatphalam 028.028
narasiṃha karālāsya dantaprāntānalojjvala
bhañja bhañja ninādena duṣṭāny asyārtināśana 028.029
ṛgyajuḥsāmagarbhābhir vāgbhir vāmanarūpadhṛk
praśamaṃ sarvaduḥkhāni nayatv asya janārdanaḥ 028.030
ekāhikaṃ dvyāhikaṃ ca tathā tridivasaṃ jvaram
cāturthakaṃ tathātyugraṃ tathaiva satatajvaram 028.031
doṣotthaṃ saṃnipātotthaṃ tathaivāgantukaṃ jvaram
śamaṃ nayāśu govinda chittvā cchittvā tu vedanām 028.032
netraduḥkhaṃ śiroduḥkhaṃ duḥkhaṃ codarasaṃbhavam
anucchvāsam atiśvāsaṃ paritāpaṃ savepathuṃ 028.033
gudaghrāṇāṃhrirogāṃś ca kuṣṭharogaṃ tathā kṣayam
kāmalādīṃs tathā rogān pramehāṃś cātidāruṇān 028.034
bhagaṃdarātisārāṃś ca mukharogaṃ savalgulim
aśmarīmūtrakṛcchrāṃś ca rogān anyāṃś ca dāruṇān 028.035
ye vātaprabhavā rogā ye ca pittasamudbhavāḥ
kaphodbhavāś ca ye kecid ye cānye sāṃnipātikāḥ 028.036
āgantavaś ca ye rogā lūtāvisphoṭakādayaḥ
te sarve praśamaṃ yāntu vāsudevāpamārjitāḥ 028.037
vilayaṃ yāntu te sarve viṣṇor uccāraṇena ca
kṣayaṃ gacchantu cāśeṣās te cakrābhihatā hareḥ 028.038
acyutānantagovinda- nāmoccāraṇabhīṣitāḥ
naśyantu sakalā rogāḥ satyaṃ satyaṃ vadāmy aham 028.039
sthāvaraṃ jaṅgamaṃ vāpi kṛtrimaṃ vāpi yad viṣam
dantodbhavaṃ nakhabhavam ākāśaprabhavaṃ viṣam 028.040
lūtādiprabhavaṃ yac ca viṣam atyantaduḥkhadam
śamaṃ nayatu tat sarvaṃ kīrtito 'sya janārdanaḥ 028.041
grahān pretagrahāṃś caiva tathā vai ḍākinīgrahān
vetālāṃś ca piśācāṃś ca gandharvān yakṣarākṣasān 028.042
śakunīpūtanādyāṃś ca tathā vaināyakagrahān
mukhamaṇḍinikāṃ krūrāṃ revatīṃ vṛddharevatīm 028.043
vṛddhikākhyān grahāṃś cogrāṃs tathā mātṛgrahān api
bālasya viṣṇoḥ caritaṃ hantu bālagrahān imān 028.044
vṛddhānāṃ ye grahāḥ kecid ye ca bālagrahāḥ kvacit
narasiṃhasya te dṛṣṭyā dagdhā ye cāpi yauvane 028.045
saṭākarālavadano narasiṃho mahāravaḥ
grahān aśeṣān niḥśeṣān karotu jagato hitam 028.046
narasiṃha mahāsiṃha jvālāmālojjvalānana
grahān aśeṣān sarveśa khāda khādāgnilocana 028.047
ye rogā ye mahotpātā yad viṣaṃ ye mahāgrahāḥ
yāni ca krūrabhūtāni grahapīḍāś ca dāruṇāḥ
śastrakṣateṣu ye doṣā jvālāgardabhakādayaḥ 028.048
yāni cāryāṇi bhūtāni prāṇipīḍākarāṇi vai 028.*(23)
tāni sarvāṇi sarvātman paramātmañ janārdana
kiṃcid rūpaṃ samāsthāya vāsudeva vināśaya 028.049
kṣiptvā sudarśanaṃ cakraṃ jvālāmālāvibhīṣaṇam
sarvaduṣṭopaśamanaṃ kuru devavarācyuta 028.050
sudarśana mahācakra govindasya karāyudha 028.*(24).001
jvalatpāvakasaṃkāśa sūryakoṭisamaprabha 028.*(24).002
trailokyarakṣakartṛ tvaṃ tvaṃ duṣṭadānavadāraṇa 028.*(24).003
tīkṣṇadhāra mahāvega chindhi cchindhi mahājvaram 028.*(24).004
chindhi cchindhi mahāvyādhiṃ chindhi cchindhi mahāgrahān 028.*(24).005
chindhi vātaṃ ca dhūtaṃ ca chindhi ghoraṃ mahāviṣam 028.*(24).006
rujadāghaṃ ca śūlaṃ ca nimiṣajvālagardabham 028.*(24).007
sudarśana mahājvāla chindhi cchindhi mamārayaḥ
sarvaduṣṭāni rakṣāṃsi kṣapayātivibhīṣaṇa 028.051
hāṃ hāṃ hūṃ hūṃ phaṭkāreṇa ṭhadvayena hatadviṣaḥ 028.*(25).001
sudarśanasya mantreṇa grahā yānti diśo diśaḥ 028.*(25).002
trailokyasyābhayaṃ kartum ājñāpaya janārdana 028.*(25).009
sarvaduṣṭāni rakṣāṃsi kṣayaṃ yānti vibhīṣayā 028.*(25).010
prācyāṃ pratīcyāṃ ca diśi dakṣiṇottaratas tathā
rakṣāṃ karotu sarvātmā narasiṃhaḥ svagarjitaiḥ 028.052
bhūmyantarikṣe ca tathā pṛṣṭhataḥ pārśvato 'grataḥ
rakṣāṃ karotu bhagavān bahurūpī janārdanaḥ 028.053
vyāghrasiṃhavarāheṣu andicorabhayeṣu ca (?) 028.*(26)
yathā viṣṇuṛ jagat sarvaṃ sadevāsuramānavam
tena satyena duṣṭāni śamam asya vrajantu vai 028.054
yathā viṣṇau smṛte samyak saṃkṣayaṃ yāti pātakam
satyena tena sakalaṃ duṣṭam asya praśāmyatu 028.055
paramātmā yathā viṣṇur vedānteṣv abhidhīyate
tena satyena sakalaṃ duṣṭam asya praśāmyatu 028.056
yathā yajñeṣvaro viṣṇur vedeṣv api tu gīyate
tena satyena sakalaṃ yan mayoktaṃ tathāstu tat 028.057
yathā yajñeśvaro viṣṇur yajñānte api gīyate
tena satyena sakalaṃ yan mayoktaṃ tathāstu tat 028.*(27)
śāntir astu śivaṃ cāstu praśāmyatv asukhaṃ ca yat
vāsudevaśarīrotthaiḥ kuśair nirmārjitaṃ mayā 028.058
apāmārjati govindo naro nārāyaṇas tathā
tavāstu sarvaduḥkhānāṃ praśamo vacanād dhareḥ 028.059
idaṃ śāstraṃ paṭhed yas tu saptāhan niyataḥ śuciḥ 028.*(28)
śāntiṃ samastarogās te grahāḥ sarve viṣāni ca
bhūtāni ca prayāntv īśe saṃsmṛte madhusūdane 028.060
etat samastarogeṣu bhūtagrahabhayeṣu ca
apamārjanakaṃ śastaṃ viṣṇunāmābhimantritam 028.061
ete kuśā viṣṇuśarīrasaṃbhavā janārdano 'haṃ svayaṃ eva cāgataḥ
hataṃ mayā duṣṭam aśeṣam asya svastho bhavaty eṣa vaco yathā hareḥ 028.062
śāntir astu śivaṃ cāstu duṣṭam asya praśāmyatu
yad asya duritaṃ kiṃcit tat kṣiptaṃ lavaṇārṇave 028.063
svāsthyam asya sadaivāstu hṛṣīkeśasya kīrtanāt
yata evāgataṃ pāpaṃ tatraiva pratigacchatu 028.064
etad rogādipīḍāsu jantūnāṃ hitam icchatā
viṣṇubhaktena kartavyam apamārjanakaṃ param 028.065
anena sarvaduṣṭāni praśamaṃ yānty asaṃśayam
sarvabhūtahitārthāya kuryāt tasmāt sadaiva hi 028.066
sarvāparādhaśamanam apāmārjanakaṃ param 028.*(29).001
etat stotram idaṃ puṇyaṃ paṭhed āyuṣyavardhanam 028.*(29).002
vināśāya ca rogāṇām avamṛtyukṣayāya ca 028.*(29).003
vyāghrāpasmārakuṣṭhādi piśācoragarākṣasāḥ 028.*(29).004
tasya pārśvaṃ na gacchanti stotram etad yathā paṭhet 028.*(29).005
smarañ japann idaṃ stotraṃ sarvavyādhivināśanam 028.*(29).006
paṭhatāṃ śṛṇvatāṃ nityaṃ viṣṇulokaṃ sa gacchati 028.*(29).007
surūpatā manuṣyāṇāṃ strīṇāṃ ca dvijasattama
karmaṇā jāyate yena tan mamākhyātum arhasi 029.001
surūpāṇāṃ sugātrāṇāṃ suveṣāṇāṃ tathā mune
nyūnaṃ tathādhikaṃ vāpi kiṃcid aṅgaṃ prajāyate 029.002
samastaiḥ śobhanair aṅgair narāḥ kecit tathā dvija
kāṇāḥ kubjāś ca jāyante truṭitaśravaṇās tathā 029.003
narāṇāṃ yoṣitāṃ caiva samastāṅgsurūpatā
karmaṇā yena bhavati tat sarvaṃ kathayāmala 029.004
lāvaṇyagativākyāni sati rūpe mahāmate
prayānti cārutāṃ rūpaṃ tenoktaḥ paramo guṇaḥ 029.005
vākyalāvaṇyasaṃskāra- vilāsalalitā gatiḥ
viḍambanā kurūpāṇāṃ strīpuṃsām abhijāyate 029.006
rūpakāraṇabhūtāya yateta matimāṃs tataḥ
karmaṇā tan mamācakṣva karma yac cārurūpadam 029.007
samyak pṛṣṭaṃ tvayā hīdam upavāsāśritaṃ dvija
kathayāmi yathā proktaṃ vasiṣṭhena mahātmanā 029.008
vasiṣṭham ṛṣim āsīnaṃ saptarṣipravaraṃ patim
papracchārundhatī praśnaṃ yad etad bhavatā vayam 029.009
tasyāḥ sa paripṛcchantyā jagāda munisattamaḥ
yat tac chṛṇuṣva dharmajña mameha vadato 'khilam 029.010
śrūyatāṃ mama yat pṛṣṭas tvayāhaṃ brahmavādini
surūpatā nṛṇāṃ yena yoṣitāṃ copajāyate 029.011
anabhyarcya yathānyāyam anārādhya ca keśavam
rūpādikā guṇāḥ kena prāpyante 'nyena karmaṇā 029.012
tasmād ārādhanīyo vai viṣṇur eva yaśasvini
paratra prāptukāmena rūpasaṃpatsutādikam 029.013
yas tu vāñchati dharmajñe rūpaṃ sarvāṅgaśobhanam
nakṣatrapuruṣas tena saṃpūjyaḥ puruṣottamaḥ 029.014
nakṣatrāṅgaṃ yathāhāraḥ samupoṣyati yo harim
surūpair akhilāṅgaiś ca rūpavān abhijāyate 029.015
yoṣitā ca paraṃ rūpam icchantyā jagataḥ patiḥ
sa evārādhanīyo 'tra nakṣatrāṅgo janārdanaḥ 029.016
nakṣatrarūpī bhagavān pūjyate puruṣottamaḥ
mune yena vidhānena tan mamākhyātum arhasi 029.017
caitramāsaṃ samārabhya viṣṇoḥ pādādipūjanam
yathā kurvīta rūpārthī tan niśāmaya tattvataḥ 029.018
nakṣatram ekam ekaṃ vai snātaḥ samyag upoṣitaḥ
nakṣatrapuruṣasyāṅgaṃ pūjayet sādhvī cakriṇaḥ 029.019
mūle pādau tathā jaṅghe rohiṇīṣv arcayec chubhe
jānunī cāśvinīyoga āṣāḍhe corusaṃjñite 029.020
phālgunīdvitaye guhyaṃ kṛttikāsu tathā kaṭim
pārśve bhadrapadāyugme dve kukṣī revatīṣu ca 029.021
anurādha uraḥ pṛṣṭhaṃ śraviṣṭhāsv abhipūjayet
bhujayugmaṃ viśākhāsu haste caiva karadvayam 029.022
punarvasāv aṅgulīṃś ca āśleṣāsu tathā nakhān
jyeṣṭhāyāṃ pūjayed grīvaṃ śravaṇe śravaṇe tathā 029.023
puṣye mukhaṃ tathā svātau daśanān abhipūjayet
hanvau śatabhiṣāyoge maghāyoge ca nāsikām 029.024
mṛgottamāṅge nayane pūjayed bhaktitaḥ śubhe
citrāyoge lalāṭaṃ ca bharaṇyāṃ ca tathā śiraḥ
saṃpūjanīyā vidvadbhiś cādrāsu ca śiroruhāḥ 029.025
nakṣatrayogeṣv eteṣu pūjito jagataḥ patiḥ
nakṣatrapuruṣākhyo 'yaṃ yathāvat puruṣottamaḥ 029.026
pāpāpahāraṃ kurute samyac chraddhāvatāṃ satām
aṅgopāṅgāni caivāsya pāpādīni yaśasvini 029.027
surūpāny abhijāyante sapta janmāntarāṇi vai
sarvāṇi caiva bhadrāṇi śarīrārogyam uttamam 029.028
saṃtatiṃ manasaḥ prītiṃ rūpaṃ cātīvaśobhanam
vāṅmādhūryaṃ tathā kāntiṃ yac cānyad abhivāñchitam 029.029
dadāti nakṣatrapumān pūjitaś ca janārdanaḥ
upoṣya samyag eteṣu krameṇa rkṣeṣu śobhane 029.030
saṃpūjanīyo bhagavān nakṣatrāṅgo janārdanaḥ
pratinakṣatrayoge ca bhojanīyā dvijottamāḥ 029.031
gandhapuṣpādisaṃyuktaṃ pūjayitvā yadāvidhi
jānubhyāṃ dharaṇīṃ gatvā idaṃ codāharet tataḥ
svarūpam ārogyam atīva varcasaṃ susaṃtatiṃ tv asthitabhaktim acyutām
api sarvam etaṃ protaṃ sūtre maṇigaṇā iva
ekapuruṣa mahāpuruṣa ṛkṣapuruṣa namo 'stu te 029.*(30)
nakṣatrajñāya viprāya dadyād dānaṃ ca śaktitaḥ
pārite ca punar dadyāt strīpūṃsāṃ cāruhāsini 029.032
chattropānadyugaṃ caiva saptadhānyaṃ sakāñcanam
ghṛtapātraṃ ca dharmajñe yac cānyad ativallabham 029.033
strī vā sādhvī sadā viṣṇor ārādhanaparāyaṇā
anenaiva vidhānena saṃpūjyaitad avāpnuyāt 029.034
sarvakāmān avāpnoti samārādhya janārdanam
prakārair bahubhir brahman yān yān icchati cetasā 030.001
nR̥ṇāṃ strīṇāṃ ca viprarṣe nānyac chokasya kāraṇam
apatyād adhikaṃ kiṃcid vidyate hy atra janmani 030.002
aputratā mahad duḥkham atiduḥkhaṃ kuputratā
aputraḥ sarvaduḥkhānāṃ hetubhūto mato mama 030.003
dhanyās te ye sutaṃ prāpya sarvaduḥkhavivarjitam
śastaṃ praśāntaṃ balinaṃ parāṃ nirvṛtim āgatāḥ 030.004
svakarmanirataṃ nityaṃ devadvijaparāyaṇam
śāstrajñaṃ dharmatattvajñaṃ dīnānāthajanāśrayam 030.005
vinirjitāriṃ sarvasya manohṛdayanandanam
devānukūlatāyuktaṃ yuktaṃ samyag guṇena ca 030.006
mitrasvajanasammāna- labdhanirvāṇam uttamam
yaḥ prāpnoti sutaṃ tasmān nānyo dhanyataro bhuvi 030.007
so 'ham icchāmi tac chrotuṃ tvattaḥ karma mahāmune
yenedṛglakṣaṇaḥ putraḥ prāpyate bhuvi mānavaiḥ 030.008
evam etan mahābhāga pitroḥ putrasamudbhavam
duḥkhaṃ prayāty upaśamaṃ tena yeneha kenacit 030.009
atrāpi śrūyatāṃ vṛttaṃ yat pūrvam abhavan mune
utpattau kārtavīryasya haihayasya mahātmanaḥ 030.010
kṛtavīryo mahīpālo haihayānām abhūt purā
tasya śīladhanā nāma babhūva varavarṇinī
patnī sahasrapravarā mahiṣī śīlamaṇḍanā 030.011
sā tv aputrā mahābhāgā maitreyīṃ paryapṛcchata
guṇavatputralābhāya kṛtāsanaparigrahām 030.012
tayā ca pṛṣṭā vai samyag maitreyī brahmavādinī
kathayām āsa paramaṃ nāmnānantavrataṃ vratam 030.013
sarvakāmaphalāvāpti- kārakaṃ pāpanāśanam
tasyāḥ sā putralābhāya rājaputrās tapasvinī 030.014
yo 'yam icchen naraḥ kāmaṃ nārī vā varavarṇini
sa taṃ samārādhya vibhuṃ samāpnoti janārdanam 030.015
mārgaśīrṣe mṛgaśiro bhīru yasmin dine bhavet
tasmin saṃprāśya gomūtraṃ snāto niyatamānasaḥ 030.016
puṣpair dhūpais tathā gandhair upahāraiḥ svaśaktitaḥ
vāmapādam anantasya pūjayed varavarṇini 030.017
anantaḥ sarvakāmānām anantaṃ bhagavān phalam
dadātv anantaṃ ca punas tad evāstv anyajanmani 030.018
anantapuṇyopacayaṃ karoty etan mahāvratam
yathābhilaṣitāvāptiṃ kurvan mā kṣayam etu ca 030.019
ity uccāryābhipūjyainaṃ yathāvad vidhinā naraḥ
samāhitamanā bhūtvā praṇipātapuraḥsaram 030.020
viprāya dakṣiṇāṃ dadyād anantaḥ prīyatām iti
samuccārya tato naktaṃ bhuñjīyāt tailavarjitam 030.021
tataś ca pauṣe puṣyarkṣe tathaiva bhagavatkaṭim
vāmām abhyarcayet kṛtvā gomūtraprāśanaṃ budhaḥ 030.022
anantaḥ sarvakāmānām iti coccārayed budhaḥ
bhuñjīta ca tathā vipraṃ vācayitvā yathāvidhi 030.023
māghe maghāsu tadvac ca bāhuṃ devasya pūjayet
skandhaṃ ca phalgunīyoge phālgune māsi bhāmini 030.024
caturṣv eteṣu gomūtra- prāśanaṃ nṛpanandini 030.025
brāhmaṇāya tathā dadyāt tilān kanakam eva ca 030.025,*(31)
devasya dakṣiṇaskandhaṃ caitre citrāsu pūjayet
tathaiva prāśanaṃ cātra pañcagavyam udāhṛtam 030.026
vipre vācanake dadyād yāvan māsacatuṣṭayam
vaiśākhe ca viśākhāsu bāhuṃ saṃpūjya dakṣiṇam 030.027
tathaivoktayavān dadyāt tadvan naktaṃ bhujikriyā
kaṭipūjāṃ ca jyeṣṭhāsu jyeṣṭhamūle śubhavrate 030.028
āṣāḍhāsu tathāṣāḍhe kuryāt pādārcanaṃ śubhe
padadvayaṃ ca śravaṇe śrāvaṇe subhru pūjayet 030.029
ghṛtaṃ viprāya dātavyaṃ prāśanīyaṃ tathā dadhi
kārttikānteṣu māseṣu prāśanaṃ dānam eva ca 030.030
etad eva samākhyātaṃ devaṃ tadvac ca pūjayet 030.030,*(32)
guhyaṃ proṣṭhapadāyoge māsi bhādrapade 'rcayet
tadvad āśvayuje pūjyaṃ hṛdayaṃ cāśvinīṣu vai 030.031
kuryāt samāhitamanāḥ snānaprāśanaśaucavān
anantaśirasaḥ pūjāṃ kārttike kṛttikāsu ca 030.032
yasmin yasmin dine pūjā tatra tatra tadā dine
nāmānantasya japtavyaṃ kṣutapraskhalitādiṣu 030.033
ghṛtenānantam uddiśya pūrvamāsacatuṣṭayam
kurvīta homaṃ caitrādau śālinā kulanandini 030.034
kṣīreṇa śrāvaṇādau tu homaṃ māsacatuṣṭayam
śastaṃ tu sarvamāseṣu haviṣyānnaṃ ca bhojanam 030.035
evaṃ dvādaśabhir māsaiḥ pāraṇaṃ tritayaṃ śubhe
pārite samavāpnoti sarvān eva manorathān 030.036
putrārthibhir vittakāmair bhṛtyadārān abhīpsubhiḥ
prārthayadbhiś ca kartavyam ārogyabalasaṃpadam 030.037
etad vrataṃ mahābhāge puṇyaṃ svastyayanapradam
anantavratasaṃjñaṃ vai sarvapāpapraṇāśanam 030.038
tat kuruṣvaiva devi tvaṃ vrataṃ śīladhane varam
viśiṣṭaṃ sarvalokasya yadi putram abhīpsasi 030.039
iti śīladhanā śrutvā maitreyīvacanaṃ śubham
cacāraitad vratavaraṃ susamāhitamānasā 030.040
putrārthinyās tatas tasyā vratenānena suvrata
viṣṇus tutoṣa tuṣṭe ca viṣṇau sā suṣuve sutam 030.041
tasya vai jātamātrasya pravavāv anilaḥ śivaḥ
nīrajaskam abhūd vyoma mudaṃ prāpākhilaṃ jagat 030.042
devadundubhayo neduḥ puṣpavṛṣṭiḥ papāta ca
prajagur divi gandharvā nanṛtuś cāpsarogaṇāḥ
dharme manaḥ samastasya dālbhya lokasya cābhavat 030.043
tasya nāma pitā cakre tanayasyārjuneti vai
kṛtavīryasutatvāc ca kārtavīryo babhūva saḥ 030.044
tenāpi bhagavān viṣṇur dattātreyasvarūpavān
ārādhito 'timahatā tapasā dālbhya bhūbhṛtā 030.045
tasya tuṣṭo jagannāthaś cakravartitvam uttamam
dadau śauryabale cāti- sakalāny āyudhāni ca 030.046
sa ca vavre varaṃ deva vadhas tvatto bhaved iti
purānusmaraṇaṃ jñānaṃ bhītānāṃ cārtināśanam
smaraṇād upakāritvaṃ jagato 'sya jagatpate 030.047
tam āha devadeveśaḥ puṇḍarīkanibhekṣaṇaḥ
sarvam etan mahābhāga tava bhūpa bhaviṣyati 030.048
yaś ca prabhāte rātrau ca tvāṃ naraḥ kīrtayiṣyati
namo 'stu kārtavīryāyety abhidhāsyati caiva yaḥ
tilaprasthapradānasya sa naraḥ puṇyam āpsyati 030.049
anaṣṭadravyatā caiva tava nāmābhikīrtanaiḥ
bhaviṣyati mahīpālety uktvā taṃ prayayau hariḥ 030.050
sa cāpi varam āsādya prasannād garuḍadhvajāt
pālayām āsa bhūpālaḥ saptadvīpāṃ vasuṃdharām 030.051
teneṣṭaṃ vividhair yajñaiḥ samāptavaradakṣiṇaiḥ
jitvārivargam akhilaṃ dharmataḥ pālitāḥ prajāḥ 030.052
anantavratamāhātmyād āsādya tanayaṃ ca tam
pitroḥ putrodbhavaṃ duḥkhaṃ nāsīt svalpam api dvija 030.053
evam etat samākhyātam anantākhyaṃ vrataṃ tava
yac cīrtvā rājapatnī sā kārtavīryam asūyata 030.054
yaś caitac chṛṇuyāj janma kārtavīryasya mānavaḥ
strī vā duḥkham apatyotthaṃ sapta janmāni nāśnute 030.055
rūpasaṃpat samākhyātā strīpuṃsāṃ jāyate śubhā
samupoṣya jagannāthaṃ nakṣatrapuruṣaṃ harim 031.001
vāso'tiśobhanaṃ cāru- vastrādyābharaṇojjvalam
gṛhaṃ sarvaguṇopetam aśeṣopaskarānvitam 031.002
karmaṇā yena viprarṣe toṣito madhusūdanaḥ
dadāti bhagavān karma tan no vistarato vada 031.003
yan māṃ pṛcchasi dālbhya tvaṃ gṛhopaskarabhūṣaṇam
narāṇāṃ jāyate yena tat sarvaṃ kathayāmi te 031.004
nandā bhadrā jayā riktā pūrṇā ca dvijasattama
tithayo vai samākhyātāḥ pratipatkramasaṃjñayā 031.005
pañcamī daśamī caiva tathā pañcadaśī tithiḥ
pūrṇā etāḥ samākhyātāṣ tithayo munisattama 031.006
mṛdā dhātuvikārair vā varṇakair gomayena vā
viṣṇor āyatane tāsu yaḥ karoty upalepanam 031.007
pravātāvātaguṇavad varṣāsv atimanoramam
anuliptaṃ śubhākāraṃ sugṛhaṃ labhate mune 031.008
pūrṇaṃ dhānyahiraṇyādyair maṇimuktāphalojjvalam
pratyāsannajalābhogaṃ gṛham āpnoti śobhanam 031.009
sāmnatasvajanānāṃ yat sarveṣām uttamottamam
tad āpnoti gṛhaṃ brahmann anulepanakṛn naraḥ 031.010
yenānulipte tiṣṭhanti viṣṇvāyatanabhūtale
brāhmaṇakṣatriyaviśaḥ śūdrāḥ sādhvyas tathā striyaḥ
tasya pūṇyaphalaṃ dālbhya śrūyatāṃ yat prajāyate 031.011
apsarogaṇasaṃkīrṇaṃ muktāhāragaṇojjvalam
śreṣṭhaṃ sarvavimānānāṃ svarge dhiṣṇyam avāpnute 031.012
yāvatyas tithayo liptaṃ divyābdāṃs tāvato dvija
tasmin vimāne sa naraḥ strī vā tiṣṭhati sattama 031.013
sugandhagandhasadvastra- sarvabhūṣaṇabhūṣitaḥ
gandharvāpsarasāṃ saṃbhaiḥ pūjyamānaḥ sa tiṣṭhati 031.014
liptaṃ ca yāvato hastān viṣṇor āyatanaṃ dvija
tāvadyojanavistīrṇa- svargasthānādhipo hi saḥ 031.015
pūjyamānaḥ suragaṇaiḥ śītoṣṇādivivarjitaḥ
manojñagātro viprendras tiṣṭhaty astāghasaṃhatiḥ 031.016
cyutas tasmād ihāgamya viśiṣṭe jāyate kule
tato 'sya sadgṛhavaraṃ martyaloke 'bhijāyate 031.017
na tatra tāvad dāridryaṃ nopasargā na vā kaliḥ
na cāpi mṛtaniṣkrāntir yāvaj jīvaty asau dvija 031.018
viṣṇuḥ samastabhūtāni sasarjaitāni yāni vai
teṣāṃ madhye jagaddhātur atīveṣṭā vasuṃdharā 031.019
kṛte saṃmārjane tasyās tathaivoparilepane
prayāti paramaṃ toṣaṃ vaiṣṇavīyaṃ mahī yataḥ 031.020
brahman yena vidhānena devāgāropalepalam
kartavyaṃ puruṣaiḥ samyak strībhir vā tad udīraya 031.021
riktāyās tu tither madhye kuryāt saṃkalpam ātmanaḥ
upalepanakṛd vipro viṣṇor āyatane bhuvi 031.022
dvitīye 'hni tato devaṃ praṇamya yatamānasaḥ
dharaṇīpitaraṃ viṣṇum idaṃ vākyam udīrayet 031.023
tvaṃ sarvabhūtaprabhavo jagatpate tvayy etad īśeśa jagat pratiṣṭhitam
tvam eva bhūtāni yatas tato 'haṃ tvām pūjayāmy adya mahīsvarūpam 031.024
tvaṃ mahī jagatāṃ nātha sarvanātha namo 'stu te
śuśrūṣitaḥ prasīdeśa bhuvo lepanakarmaṇā 031.025
ity uccārya kṣitau kṣiptvā prathamaṃ dhāranītale
puṣpāṇi vā dvijaśreṣṭha yaḥ karoty anulepanam
na tasya jāyate bhaṅgo gārhasthyasya kadācana 031.026
yā ca nārī karoty evaṃ yathāvad anulepanam
nāpnoti sā ca vaidhavyaṃ gṛhabhaṅgaṃ kadācana 031.027
kṛtvopalepanaṃ bhūyaḥ praṇipatya janārdanam
snāto viṣṇuṃ samabhyarcya idaṃ vākyam udīrayet 031.028
prasīda bhūdharānanta mayā yad upalepanam
kṛtaṃ tena samastaṃ me nāśam abhyetu pātakam 031.029
evaṃ saṃpūjya bhuñjīyād aparāhne dvijottama
svanulipte mahābhāge bhuktvā limpec ca tat punaḥ 031.030
pakṣe pakṣe trirātraṃ tu yaḥ karoty upalepanam
sarvapāpavinirmuktaḥ svargaṃ gacchaty asaṃśayam 031.031
tatkṣayāt svargeloke tu jāto gṛhavaraṃ yathā
samāpnoti yathākhyātaṃ tat sarvaṃ tava sattama 031.032
sarvābharaṇasaṃpūrṇaṃ sarvopaskaradhānyavat
gomahiṣyādisaṃbhogaṃ gṛham āpnoti mānavaḥ 031.033
tasmād abhīpsatā samyag gārhasthyam avikhaṇḍitam
viṣṇor āyatane kāryaṃ sarvadaivopalepanam 031.034
saptadvīpavatīṃ kṛtsnāṃ yathendras tridivaṃ tathā 031.*(33)
alpopalepanād yasya māndhātā sakalāṃ mahīm
avāpa viṣṇvāyatanaṃ nopalimpeta ko hi tat 031.035
dīpaṃ prayacchati naro viṣṇor āyatane hi yaḥ
sadakṣiṇasya yajñasya phalaṃ prāpnoty asaṃśayam 032.001
kārttike tu viśeṣeṇa kaumude māsi dīpakam
dattvā yat phalam āpnoti dālbhya tat kena labhyate 032.002
dālbhyānyad api vakṣyāmi purāvṛttam idaṃ śṛṇu
vidarbharājatanayā lalitā yad uvāca ha 032.003
vidarbharāṭ citraratho babhūvāstraviśāradaḥ
tasya putraśataṃ rājño jajñe pañcadaśottaram 032.004
ekaiva kanyā dālbhyāsīl lalitā nāmanāmataḥ
sarvalakṣaṇasaṃpūrṇā bhrātR̥ṇāṃ pitur eva ca 032.005
samastabhṛtyavargasya mātR̥ṇāṃ svajanasya ca
tathaiva pauravargasya yaś cānyo dadṛśe śubhām
tasya tasyāticārvaṅgī babhūveṣṭā dvijottama 032.006
tāṃ dadau kāśirājāya sa pitā cāruvarmane
upayeme ca tāṃ subhrūṃ cāruvarmā mahīpatiḥ 032.007
śatāny anyāni bhāryāṇāṃ trīṇy āsaṃś cāruvarmaṇaḥ
tāsāṃ madhye 'gramahiṣī lalitā tasya cābhavat 032.008
sā ca nityaṃ jagaddhātur devadevasya cakriṇaḥ
dīpavartiparā tadvat tailasyāharaṇodyatā 032.009
viṣṇor āyatane tasyāḥ sahasraṃ dvijasattama
dīpānāṃ vai prajajvāla divārātram atandritam 032.010
tasyā dyutiparābhūtās tasyā lāvaṇyanirjitāḥ
sarvāḥ sapatnyo lalitāṃ papracchur idam āditaḥ 032.011
lalite vada bhadraṃ te bhadraṃ te lalite vada
kautūhalaparāḥ sarvā yat pṛcchāmas tad ucyatām 032.012
viṣaye sati vaktavyaṃ yan mayā tad ihocyatām
nāhaṃ matsariṇī bhadrā na ca rāgādidūṣitā 032.013
bhavatyo mama sarvāsāṃ bhavatīnām ahaṃ tathā
apṛthagbhartṛsāmanyā devalokābhikāmukāḥ 032.014
pūrvaṃ yūyam ahaṃ caiva bhavatīnāṃ sadharmiṇī 032.*(34)
na tathā puṣpadhūpeṣu na tathā dvijapūjane
prayatnaṃ tava paśyāmo viṣṇor āyatane śubhe 032.015
yathāhani tathā rātrau yathā rātrau tathāhani
tava dīpapradānāya yathā subhru sadodyamaḥ 032.016
tad etat kathayāsmākaṃ lalite kautukaṃ param
manyāmo dīpadānasya bhavatyā viditaṃ phalam 032.017
evam uktā tatas tābhir lalitā lalitaṃ vacaḥ
vyājahāra sapatnīs tā na kiṃcid api bhāminī 032.018
punaḥ punaś ca sā tābhir bahuṣo dālbhya coditā
dākṣiṇyasārā lalitā kathāyām āsa bhāminī 032.019
kautukaṃ bhavatīnāṃ ced atīvālpe 'pi vastuni
tad eṣā kathayāmy etad yad vṛttaṃ mama śobhanāḥ 032.020
sauvīrarājasya purā maitreyo 'bhūt purohitaḥ
tena cāyatanaṃ viṣṇoḥ kāritaṃ devikātaṭe 032.021
ahany ahani śuśrūṣāṃ puṣpadhūpopalepanaiḥ
dīpadānādibhiś caiva cakre tatra sa vai dvijaḥ 032.022
kārttike dīpako brahman pradattas tena vai tadā
āsīn nirvāṇabhūyiṣṭho devārcāpurato niśi 032.023
devatāyatane cāsaṃ tatrāham api mūṣikā
pradīpavartiharaṇe kṛtabuddhir varānanāḥ 032.024
gṛhītā ca mayā vartir vṛṣadaṃśo nanāda ca
naṣṭā cāhaṃ tadā tasya mārjārasya bhayāturā 032.025
vartiprāntena naśyantyā sa dīpaḥ prerito mayā
jajvāla pūrvavad dīptyā tasminn āyatane punaḥ 032.026
mṛtāhaṃ ca tato jātā vaidarbhī rājakanyakā
jātismarā kāntimatī bhavatīnāṃ samā guṇaiḥ 032.027
eṣa prabhāvo dīpasya kārttike māsi śobhanāḥ
dattasya viṣṇvāyatane yasyeyaṃ vyuṣṭir uttamā 032.028
asaṃkalpitam apy asya preraṇaṃ yat kṛtaṃ mayā
viṣṇvāyatanadīpasya yasyedaṃ bhujyate phalam 032.029
lobhābhibhūtā hartuṃ taṃ pradīpam aham āgatā
avaśenaiva tadvartyā preraṇaṃ tatra me kṛtam 032.030
tato jātismṛtir janma mānuṣyaṃ śobhanaṃ vapuḥ
vaśyaḥ patiḥ pṛthivīśaḥ kiṃ punar dīpadāyinām 032.031
etasmāt kāraṇād dīpān aham etān aharniśam
prayacchāmi harer dhāmni jñātam asya hi yat phalam 032.032
bhavatīnām idaṃ satyaṃ mayoktaṃ keśavālaye
mūṣikatvād ahaṃ yena karmaṇā siddhim āgatā 032.033
eṣa prabhāvo dīpasya kārttike māsi sattama
viṣṇvāyatanadattasya jagāda lalitā yathā 032.034
dine dine jagannātha keśaveti samāhitaḥ
dadāti kārttike yas tu viṣṇvāyatanadīpakam 032.035
jātismaratvaṃ prajñāṃ ca prākāśyaṃ sarvavastuṣu
avyāhatendriyatvaṃ ca saṃprāpnoti na saṃśayaḥ 032.036
śeṣakāle ca cakṣuṣmān medhāvī dīpado naraḥ
jāyate narakaṃ vāpi tamaḥsaṃjñaṃ na paśyati 032.037
ekādaśīṃ dvādaśīṃ vā pratipakṣaṃ ca yo naraḥ
dīpaṃ dadāti kṛṣṇāya tasyāpi śṛṇu yat phalam 032.038
suvarṇamaṇimuktāḍhyaṃ manojñam atiśobhanam
dīpamālākulaṃ divyaṃ vimānaṃ so 'dhirohati 032.039
tasmād āyatane viṣṇor dadyād dīpaṃ dvijottama
tāṃś ca dattān na hiṃseta na ca tailaviyojitān
kurvīta dīpahartā tu mūko 'ndho jāyate yataḥ 032.040
jāyate narakaṃ cāpi tapaḥsaṃjñaṃ sa paśyati 032.*(35)
andhe tāmasi duṣpāre narake patitān kila
vikrośamānān kṣutkṣāmāñ jagāda yamakiṃkaraḥ 032.041
vilāpair alam atrāpi kiṃ vo vilapite phalam
yadā pramādibhiḥ pūrvam ātmātyantam upekṣitaḥ 032.042
pūrvam ālocitaṃ naitat kim apy ante bhaviṣyati
idānīṃ yātanābhogaḥ kiṃ vilāpaḥ kariṣyati 032.043
deho dināni svalpāni viṣayāś cātidurdharāḥ
etat ko na vijānāti yena yūyaṃ pramādinaḥ 032.044
jantujanmasahasrebhya etasmin mānuṣyo yadi
tatrāpy ativimūḍhatvāt kiṃ bhogān abhidhāvati 032.045
viruddhaviṣayāsvāda- muditair hasitaṃ ca yat
bhavadbhir āgataṃ duḥkhaṃ vilāpapariṇāmikam 032.046
adyakālikayā buddhyā yad āgāmi na cintitam
paritāpāya taj jātaṃ duḥkhaṃ karmavipākajam 032.047
svalpam āyur manuṣyāṇāṃ tadante paratantratā
bhujyate ca kṛtaṃ pūrvam etat kiṃ vo na cintitam 032.048
yad abhūt paradāreṣu prītaye 'ṅgakucādikam
yātanāduḥkharūpāya narake ca tad āgatam 032.049
paradāramanohāri yad bhavadbhir agīyata
hā māta ityādi rutaṃ tad idānīṃ vilapyate 032.050
saṃdigdhaparalokānām aihike nihatātmanām
mṛtānāṃ svakṛtaṃ karma paścāttāpāya kevalam 032.051
muhūrtārdhasukhāsvāda- lubdhānām akṛtātmanām
anekavarṣakoṭiṣu duḥkhadaṃ karma jāyate 032.052
hā mātas tāta tāteti bhavadbhiḥ kiṃ vilapyate
śubhāśubhaṃ nijaṃ karma tad adya hy atra bhujyate 032.053
putradāragṛhakṣetra- hitāya satatodyatāḥ
na kurvatni kathaṃ mūḍhāḥ svalpam apy ātmano hitam 032.054
vañcito 'sau mayā labdham idam asmād upāyataḥ 032.055
na vetti kaścid ātmārthaṃ vetti prakramato naraḥ 032.056
na vetti sūryacandrādīn kālam ātmānam eva ca
sākṣibhūtān aśeṣasya śubhasyehāśubhasya ca 032.057
janmāny anyāni jāyante putradārādidehinām
tadarthaṃ yat kṛtaṃ karma tasya janmaśatāni tat 032.058
aho mohasya māhātmyaṃ mamatvaṃ narakeṣv api
krandate mātaraṃ tātaṃ pīḍyamāno 'pi yat svayam 032.059
evam ākṛṣṭacittānāṃ viṣayāsvādatarṣulaiḥ
nR̥ṇāṃ na jāyate buddhiḥ paramārthāvalokinī
tathā ca viṣayāsaktiṃ karoty avirataṃ manaḥ 032.060
ko 'tibhāro harer nāmni jihvāyāḥ parikīrtane 032.061
vartitaile 'lpamaulye 'pi yad agnir labhyate mudhā
ato 'dhikataro lobhaḥ ko vaś citte 'bhavat tadā 032.062
yeneyaṃ teṣu hasteṣu svātantrye sati dīpakaḥ
mahāphalo viṣṇugṛhe na datto narakāpahaḥ 032.063
na vo vilapite kiṃcid idānīṃ dṛśyate phalam
asvātantrye vilapatāṃ svātantrye 'tipramādinām 032.064
avaśyaṃpātinaḥ prāṇā bhoktā jīvo hy aharniśam
dattaṃ ca labhate bhoktā samaye viṣayān iti 032.065
etat svātantryavadbhir vo yuktam āsīt parīkṣitum
idānīṃ kiṃ vilāpena sahadhvaṃ yad upāgatam 032.066
yady etad anabhīṣṭaṃ vo yad duḥkhaṃ samupasthitam
tad bhūyo 'pi matiḥ pāpe na kartavyā kathaṃcana 032.067
kṛte 'pi pāpake karmaṇy ajñānād aghanāśanam
kartavyam avyavasthitaṃ smaradbhir madhusūdanam 032.068
nārakās tadvacaḥ śrutvā tām ūcur atiduḥkhitāḥ
kṣutkṣāmakaṇṭhās tṛṣayā parisphuṭitatālukāḥ 032.069
bho bho sādho kṛtaṃ karma yad asmābhis tad ucyatām
narakasthair vipāko 'yaṃ bhujyate yasya dāruṇaḥ 032.070
yuṣmābhir yauvanonmāda- muditair avivekibhiḥ
dyūtodyotāya govinda- gṛhād dīpaḥ purā hṛtaḥ 032.071
tenāsmin narake ghore kṣuttṛṣṇāparipīḍitāḥ
bhavantaḥ patitās tīvra- śītavātavidāritāḥ 032.072
etat te dīpadānasya pradīpaharaṇasya ca
puṇyaṃ pāpaṃ ca kathitaṃ keśavāyatane dvija 032.073
sarvatraiva hi dīpasya pradānaṃ dvija śasyate
viśeṣeṇa jagaddhātuḥ keśavasya niveśane 032.074
ye 'ndhā mūkā niḥśrutā nirvivekā hīnās tais taiḥ sādhanair vipravarya
tais tair dīpāḥ sādhulokapradattā devāgārād anyato vipraṇītāḥ 032.075
āhlādaṃ cakṣuṣaḥ prītiṃ karoti manasas tathā
keṣāṃcid darśanaṃ brahman manuṣyāṇām aharniśam 033.001
udvejanīyā bhūtānām animittaṃ tathāpare
vadante vipriyaṃ naiva prītiṃ kurvanti mānavāḥ 033.002
etad yasya phalaṃ brahman dānasya tapaso 'thavā
upavāsasya vā tan me yathāvad vaktum arhasi 033.003
aprītidasya viprarṣe vipāko yasya karmaṇaḥ
manuṣyāṇām aśeṣaṃ vai tan mamācakṣva sattama 033.004
devabrāhmaṇavedeṣu yajñeṣu ca narādhamaiḥ
yair jugupsā kṛtā dālbhya manasāpy atimānibhiḥ 033.005
teṣāṃ saṃdarśanāt sarvo na sukhaṃ vindate dvija
vadanty apy anukūlāni na teṣu prīyate janaḥ 033.006
sparśād udvijate lokaḥ kaṭu teṣāṃ ca darśanam
saṃbhāṣaṇaṃ ca nindā vai kṛtā vedadvijātike 033.007
tasmān na nindāṃ vedādau na jugupsāṃ ca paṇḍitaḥ
yajñādau ca naraḥ kuryād ya icchec chreya ātmanaḥ 033.008
yais tu prītiḥ samasteṣu vedadevadvijātiṣu
yajñādike caiva kṛtā dālbhya taddarśanaṃ nṛṇām 033.009
āhlādaś cakṣuṣaḥ prītir manaso nirvṛtiḥ parā
saṃbhāṣaṇe tathāhlādaḥ sarvalokasya jāyate 033.010
stutāḥ praśastāḥ saṃprītyā pūjitā bahumānataḥ
śreyaḥ paraṃ prayacchanti devā vedā makhā dvijāḥ 033.011
lokadvaye 'pi cāprītiṃ paśuputradhanakṣayam
kurvanti dvijaśārdūla eta eva vininditāḥ 033.012
eta eva samākhyātāḥ stavādigrahaṇe guṇāh
nindāyāḥ śravaṇe doṣa eteṣām evam eva hi 033.013
tasmāt stavyāḥ praśaṃsyāś ca devā vedā dvijātayaḥ
yajñāś ca manasāpy eṣāṃ na nindām ācared budhaḥ 033.014
anāyāsena bhagavan dānenānyena kenacit
pāpaṃ praśamam āyāti yena tad vaktum arhasi 034.001
śṛṇu dālbhya mahāpuṇyāṃ dvādaśīṃ pāpanāśanīm
yām upoṣya paraṃ puṇyaṃ prāpnute śraddhayānvitaḥ 034.002
māghamāse tu saṃprāpta āṣāḍhārkṣaṃ bhaved yadi
mūlaṃ vā kṛṣṇapakṣasya dvādaśyāṃ niyatas tadā 034.003
gṛhṇīyāt puṇyaphaladaṃ vidhānaṃ tasya me śṛṇu
devadevaṃ samabhyarcya susnātaḥ prayataḥ śuciḥ 034.004
kṛṣṇanāmnā ca saṃstūya ekādaśyāṃ mahāmate
upoṣito dvitīye 'hni punaḥ saṃpūjya keśavam 034.005
saṃstūya nāmnā ca tataḥ kṛṣṇākhyena punaḥ punaḥ
dadyāt tilāṃs tu viprāya kṛṣṇo me prīyatām iti
snānaprāśanayoḥ śastās tathā kṛṣṇatilā mune 034.006
tilaprarohe jāyante yāvatsaṃkhyās tilā dvija
tāvadvarṣasahasrāṇi svargaloke mahīyate 034.007
jātaś cehāpy arogo 'sau naro janmani janmani
nāndho na badhiraś ceha na kuṣṭhī na jugupsitaḥ
bhavaty etām uṣitvā tu tilākhyāṃ dvādaśīṃ naraḥ 034.008
viṣṇoḥ prīṇanam atroktaṃ samāpte varṣapāraṇe
pūjāṃ ca kuryād viprāya bhūyo dadyāt tathā tilān 034.009
anena dālbhya vidhinā tiladānād asaṃśayam
mucyate pātakaiḥ sarvair nirāyāsena mānavaḥ 034.010
udbhṛtapulakaḥ sarvān nirāyāsena mānavaḥ 034.*(36)
dānavidhis tathā śraddhā sarvapātakaśāntaye
nārthaḥ prabhūto nāyāsaḥ śārīro munisattama 034.011
anantasyāprameyasya vyāpinaḥ paramātmanaḥ
nāmnāṃ nakṣatrabhedena tithibhedena vā dvija 035.001
dānabhedena cākhyāto vibhinnaphaladas tvayā
viśeṣaḥ kṣetrabhedena kathyatāṃ yadi vidyate 035.002
yatha rkṣatithibhedena teṣām eva punaḥ punaḥ
viśeṣaḥ kathito nāmnāṃ viśeṣaphaladāyakaḥ
tathā kṣetraviśeṣeṇa bhedaṃ nāmakṛtaṃ vada 035.003
śṛṇu dālbhya yathākhyātam arjunāya mahātmane
praṇipātaprasannena viṣṇunā prabhaviṣṇunā 035.004
kṛte bhārāvataraṇe nivṛtte bhārate raṇe
āgamya śibiraṃ viṣṇū rathasthaḥ prāha phālgunam 035.005
iṣudhīgāṇḍivaṃ caiva samādāya tvarānvitaḥ
avatīrya rathād vīra dūre tiṣṭḥa dhanaṃjaya 035.006
avarokṣyāmy ahaṃ paścād avatīrṇe tatas tvayi
etat kuru mahābāho mā vilambasva phālguna 035.007
evam uktas tathā cakre vākyaṃ pārtho gadādhṛtaḥ
avārohat tataḥ paścāt svayam eva janārdanaḥ 035.008
avatīrṇe jagannāthe svasamutthena vahninā
jajvāla sa rathaḥ sadyo bhasmībhūtaś ca tatkṣaṇāt
sopaskarapatāko 'tha sadhvajaḥ saha vājibhiḥ 035.009
sacchattro vahninā sadyo ratho bhasmalavīkṛtaḥ
vahninā ca yathā kāṣṭhaṃ sadyo bhasmalavīkṛtam 035.010
tad adbhutaṃ mahad dṛṣṭvā pārthaḥ papraccha keśavam
hṛṣṭaromā dvijaśreṣṭha bhayavismayagadgadaḥ 035.011
āścaryaṃ puruṣavyāghra kim etan madhusūdana
vināgninā ratho 'yaṃ me dagdhas tṛṇacayo yathā 035.012
bhīṣmadroṇakṛpādīnāṃ karṇādīnāṃ ca phālguna
dagdho 'strair vividhair eṣa pūrvam eva rathas tava 035.013
madadhiṣṭhitatvāt kaunteya na śīrṇo 'yaṃ tadābhavat
pratyahan niśi cakreṇa mayā nyastena rakṣitaḥ 035.014
so 'yaṃ dagdho mahābāho tvayy adya kṛtakarmaṇi
mayāvatārite cakre mā pārtha kuru vismayam 035.015
kaṃ bhavantam ahaṃ vidyām atimānuṣaceṣṭitam
karmaṇātyadbhutenāgnir dhūmenaiveha sūcitaḥ 035.016
pūrvam eva yathākhyātaṃ raṇārambhe tavārjuna
kālo 'smi lokanāśāya pravṛtto 'haṃ yathādhunā 035.017
tan mayā sādhitaṃ kāryaṃ tridaśānāṃ tathā bhuvaḥ
bhārāvataraṇārthāya mama janma mahītale 035.018
evam ukto 'rjunaḥ samyak praṇipatya janārdanam
tuṣṭāva vāgbhir iṣṭābhir udbhūtapulakas tataḥ 035.019
namo 'stu te cakradharograrūpa namo 'stu te śārṅgadharāruṇākṣa
namo 'stu te 'bhyudyatakhaḍga raudra namo 'stu vibhrāntagadāntakārin 035.020
bhayena sanno 'smi savepathena nāṅgāni me deva vaśaṃ prayānti
vācaḥ samuccārayataḥ skhalanti keśā hṛṣīkeśa samucchvasanti 035.021
kālo bhavān kālakarālakarmā yenaitad evaṃ kṣayam akṣayātman
kṣatraṃ samudbhūtaruṣā samastam nītaṃ bhuvo bhāravirecanāya 035.022
prasīda kartar jaya lokanātha prasīda sarvasya ca pālanāya
sthitau samastasya ca kālarūpa kṛtodyameśāna jayāvyayātman 035.023
na me dṛg eṣā tava rūpam etad draṣṭuṃ samarthā kṣubhito 'smi cāntaḥ
pūrvasvabhāvasthitavigraho 'pi saṃlakṣyase 'tyantam asaumyarūpa 035.024
smarāmi rūpaṃ tava viśvarūpaṃ yad darśitaṃ pūrvam abhūn mamaiva
yasmin mayā viśvam aśeṣam āsīd dṛṣṭaṃ sayakṣoragadevadaityam 035.025
sā me smṛtir darśanabhāṣanādi- prakurvato nātha gatā praṇāśam
kālo 'ham asmīty udite tvayā tu samāgateyaṃ punar apy ananta 035.026
kartā bhavān kāraṇam apy aśeṣam kāryaṃ ca niṣkāraṇa kartṛrūpa
ādau sthitau saṃharaṇe ca deva viśvasya viśvaṃ svayam eva ca tvam 035.027
brahmā bhavān viśvasṛg ādikāle viśvasya rūpo 'si tathā visṛṣṭau
viṣṇuḥ sthitau pālanabaddhakakṣo rudro bhavān saṃharaṇe prajānām 035.028
ebhis tribhir nātha vibhūtibhedair yaś cintyate kāraṇam ātmano 'pi
vedāntavedoditam asti viṣṇoḥ padaṃ dhruvaṃ tat paramaṃ tvam eva 035.029
yan nirguṇaṃ sarvavikalpahīnam anantam asthūlam arūpagandham
paraṃ padaṃ vedavido vadanti tvam eva tac chabdarasādihīnam 035.030
yathā hi mūle viṭapī mahādrumaḥ pratiṣṭhitaskandhavarograśākhaḥ
tathā samastāmaramartyatiryag- vyomādiśabdādimayaṃ tvayīdam 035.031
muñcāmi yāvat paramāyudhāni vairiṣv anantāhavadurmadeṣu
dṛṣṭvā hi tāvat sahasā patanto nūnaṃ tavaivācyuta sa prabhāvaḥ 035.032
hatā hatās te bhavato dṛśaiva mayā punaḥ keśava śastrapūgaiḥ
kāh karṇabhīṣmapramukhān vijetuṃ yuṣmatprasādena vinā samarthaḥ 035.033
triśūlapāṇir mama yaḥ purastān niṣūdayan vairibalaṃ jagāma
jñātaṃ mayā sāṃpratam etad īśa tava prasādasya hi sā vibhūtiḥ 035.034
yamendravitteśajaleśavahni- sūryātmako yaś ca mamāstrapūgaḥ
nāśāya nābhūt patito 'pi kāye tvatsaṃnidhānasya hi so 'nubhāvaḥ 035.035
bālye bhavān yāni cakāra deva karmāṇy asahyāni surāsurāṇām
tair eva jānīma na yat paraṃ tvāṃ doṣaḥ sa nirdoṣo manuṣyatāyāḥ 035.036
tālocchritāgraṃ gurubhārasāram āyāmavistāravad adyajātaḥ
pādāgravikṣepavibhinnabhāṇḍaṃ cikṣepa ko 'nyaḥ śakaṭaṃ yathā tvam 035.037
anyena kenācyuta pūtanāyāḥ prāṇaiḥ samaṃ pītam asṛgvimiśram
tvayā yathā stanyam atīvabālye goṣṭhe ca bhagnau yamalārjunau tau 035.038
viṣānaloṣṇāmbunipātabhīmam āsphoṭya ko vā bhuvi manuṣo 'nyaḥ
nanarta pādābjanipīḍitasya phaṇaṃ samāruhya ca kāliyasya 035.039
sureśasaṃdeśavirodhavatsu varṣatsu megheṣu gavān nimittam
dināni saptāsti ca kasya śaktir govardhanaṃ dhārayituṃ kareṇa 035.040
pralambacāṇūramukhān nihatya kaṃsāsuraṃ yasya bibheti śakraḥ
tam aṣṭavarṣo nijaghāna ko 'nyo nirāyodho nātha manuṣyajanmā 035.041
bāṇārtham abhyudyatam ugraśūlaṃ nirjitya saṃkhye tripurārim ekaḥ
sakārttikeyajvaram astrabāhuṃ karoti ko bāṇam anacyuto 'nyaḥ 035.042
kaḥ pārijātaṃ surasundarīṇāṃ sadopabhogyaṃ vijitendrasainyaḥ
svargān mahīm ucchritavīryadhairyaḥ samānayām āsa yathā prabho tvam 035.043
hatvā hayagrīvam udāravīryaṃ niśumbhaśumbhau narakaṃ ca ko 'nyaḥ
jagrāha kanyāpuram ātmano 'rthaṃ prāgjyotiṣākhye nagare mahātman 035.044
sthitau sthitas tvaṃ paripāsi viśvaṃ tais tair upāyair avinītabhītaiḥ
maitrī na yeṣāṃ vinayāya tāṃs tān sarvān bhavān saṃharate 'vyayātman 035.045
hitāya teṣāṃ kapilādirūpiṇā tvayānuśastā bahavo 'nujīvāḥ
yeṣāṃ na maitrī hṛdi te na neyā viśvopakārī vadha eva teṣām 035.046
itthaṃ bhavān duṣṭavadhena nūnaṃ viśvopakārāya vibho pravṛttaḥ
sthitau sthitaṃ pālanam eva viṣṇuḥ karoti hanty antagato 'ntarudraḥ 035.047
etāni cānyāni ca duṣkarāṇi dṛṣṭāni karmāṇi tathāpi satyam
manyāmahe tvāṃ jagataḥ prasūtiṃ kiṃ kurma māyā tava mohanīyam 035.048
tvaṃ sarvam etat tvayi sarvam etat tvattas tathaitat tava caitad īśa
etat svarūpaṃ tava sarvabhūtaṃ vibhūtibhedair bahubhiḥ sthitasya 035.049
prasīda kṛṣṇācyuta vāsudeva janārdanānanta nṛsiṃha viṣṇo
manuṣyasāmānyadhiyā yadīśa dṛṣṭo mayā tat kṣamasvādideva 035.050
na vedmi sadbhāvam ahaṃ tavādya sadbhāvabhūtasya carācarasya
yo vai bhavān ko 'pi nato 'smi tasmai manuṣyarūpāya caturbhujāya 035.051
devadeva jagannātha sarvapāpaharo bhava
hetumātras tv ahaṃ tatra tvayaitad upasaṃhṛtam 035.052
prasīdeśa hṛṣīkeśa akṣauhiṇyā daśāṣṭa ca
tvayā grastā bhuvo bhūtyai hetubhūtā hi madvidhāḥ 035.053
vayam anye ca govinda narāḥ krīḍanakās tava
madvidhaiḥ karaṇair deva karoṣi sthitipālanam 035.054
yad atra sad asad vāpi kiṃcid uccāritaṃ mayā
bhaktimān iti tat sarvaṃ kṣantavyaṃ mama keśava 035.055
evaṃ stutas tataḥ prāha prītimāṃs taṃ janārdanaḥ
pariṣvajya mahābāhuṃ samāśvāsya ca phālgunam 036.001
prvāca bhagavān devaḥ prahṛṣṭenāntarātmanā 036.*(37)
yas tvāṃ vetti sa māṃ vetti yas tvām anu sa mām anu
abhedenātmanā vedmī tvām ahaṃ pāṇḍunandana 036.002
mamāṃśatvaṃ mahābāho jagataḥ pālanecchayā
bhuvo bhārāvatārārthaṃ pṛthak pārtha mayā kṛtam 036.003
devadaityoragā yakṣā gandharvāḥ kiṃnarāpsarāḥ
rākṣasāś ca piśācāś ca paśupakṣisarīsṛpāḥ 036.004
vṛkṣagulmādayaḥ śailāḥ sarvabhūtāni cārjuna
mamaivāṃśāni bhūtāni viddhi sarvāṇy ariṃdama 036.005
bhagavan sarvabhūtātman sarvabhūteṣu vai bhavān
paramātmasvarūpeṇa sthitaṃ vedmi tad avyayam 036.006
kṣetreṣu yeṣu yeṣu tvaṃ cintanīyo mayācyuta
cetasaḥ praṇidhānārthaṃ tan mamākhyātum arhasi 036.007
yatra yatra ca yan nāma prītaye bhavataḥ stutau
prasādasumukho nātha tan mamāśeṣato vada 036.008
sarvagaḥ sarvabhūto 'haṃ na hi kiṃcid mayā vinā
carācare jagaty asmin vidyate kurusattama 036.009
tathāpi yeṣu sthāneṣu cintanīyo 'ham arjuna
stotavyo nāmabhir yais tu śrūyatāṃ tad vadāmi te 036.010
puṣkare puṇḍarīkākṣaṃ gayāyāṃ ca gadādharam
lohadaṇḍe tathā viṣṇuṃ stuvaṃs tarati duṣkṛtam 036.011
kṣvāmācye kumāraṃ nepāle lokabhāvanam 036.*(38)
rāghavaṃ citrakūṭe tu prabhāse daityasūdanam
vṛndāvane ca govindaṃ mā stuvan puṇyabhāg bhavet 036.012
mandodapāne vaikuṇṭhaṃ māhantre cācyutaṃ vibhum 036.*(39)
jayaṃ jayantyāṃ tadvac ca jayantaṃ hastināpure
vārāhaṃ kardamāle tu kāśmīre cakrapāṇinam 036.013
janārdanaṃ ca kubjāmre mathurāyāṃ ca keśavam
kubjake śrīdharaṃ tadvad gaṅgādvāre surottamam 036.014
śālagrāme mahāyogiṃ hariṃ govardhanācale
piṇḍārake caturbāhuṃ śaṅkhoddhāre ca śaṅkhinam 036.015
vāmanaṃ ca kurukṣetre yamunāyāṃ trivikramam
viśveśvaraṃ tathā śoṇe kapilaṃ pūrvasāgare 036.016
vanamālaṃ ca kiṣkindhāyāṃ devaṃ raivatake dvija
kāśījale mahāyogaṃ devaṃ cāmitatejasam
vaiśākhayūpe ajitaṃ virajāyāṃ viprakṣayam 036.*(40)
śvetadvīpapatiṃ cāpi gaṅgāsāgarasaṃgame
bhūdharaṃ devikānadyāṃ prayāge caiva mādhavam 036.017
naranārāyaṇākhyaṃ ca tathā badarikāśrame
samudre dakṣiṇe stavyaṃ padmanābheti phālguna 036.018
dvārakāyāṃ tathā kṛṣṇaṃ stuvaṃs tarati durgatim
rāmaṃ nāma mahendrādrau hṛṣīkeśaṃ tathārbude 036.019
aśvatīrthe hayagrīvaṃ viśvarūpaṃ himācale
nṛsiṃhaṃ kṛtasauce ca vipāśāyāṃ dvijapriyam 036.020
naimiṣe yajñapuruṣaṃ jambūmārge tathācyutam
anantaṃ saindhavāraṇye daṇḍake śāṅgadhāriṇam 036.021
utpalāvartake śauriṃ narmadāyāṃ śriyaḥ patim
dāmodaraṃ raivatake nandāyāṃ jalaśāyinam 036.022
sarvayogeśvaraṃ caiva sindhusāgarasaṃgame
sahyādrau devadeveśaṃ vaikuṇṭhaṃ māgadhe vane 036.023
sarvapāpaharaṃ vindhye uḍreṣu puruṣottamam
hṛdaye cāpi kaunteya paramātmānam ātmanaḥ 036.024
vaṭe vaṭe vaiśravaṇaṃ catvare catvare śivam
parvate parvate rāmaṃ sarvatra madhusūdanam 036.025
naraṃ bhūmau tathā vyomni kaunteya garuḍadhvajam
vāsudevaṃ ca sarvatra saṃsmarañ jyotiṣāṃ patim 036.026
arcayan praṇamaṃs tu tvaṃ saṃsmaraṃś ca dhanaṃjaya
eteṣv etāni nāmāni naraḥ pāpaiḥ pramucyate 036.027
sthāneṣv eteṣu mannāmnām eteṣāṃ prīṇanaṃ naraḥ
dvijānāṃ prīṇanaṃ kṛtvā svargaloke 'bhijāyate 036.028
nāmāny etāni kaunteya sthānāny etāni cātmavān
jayaṃ vai pañcapañcāśat trisandhyaṃ matparāyaṇaḥ 036.029
trīṇi janmāni yat pāpam avasthātritaye kṛtam
tat kṣālayaty asaṃdigdhaṃ jāyate ca satāṃ kule 036.030
dviṣkālaṃ vā japann eva divārātrau ca yat kṛtam
tasmād vimucyate pāpāt sadbhāvaparamo naraḥ 036.031
japtāny etāni kaunteya sakṛcchraddhāsamanvitam
mocayante naraṃ pāpād yat tatraiva dine kṛtam 036.032
dhanyaṃ yaśasyam āyuṣyaṃ jayaṃ kuru kulodvaha
grahānukūlatāṃ caiva karoty āśu na saṃśayaḥ 036.033
upoṣito matparamaḥ sthāneṣv eteṣu mānavaḥ
kṛtāyatanavāsaś ca prāpnoty abhimataṃ phalam 036.034
utkrāntir apy aśeṣeṣu sthāneṣv eteṣu śasyate
anyasthānāc chataguṇam eteṣv anaśanādikam 036.035
yas tu matparamaḥ kālaṃ karoty eteṣu mānavaḥ
devānām api pūjyo 'sau mama loke mahīyate 036.036
yan na tāpāya vai puṃsāṃ bhavaty āmuṣmikaṃ kṛtam
tāpāya yac ca bhavati tad ācakṣva mahāmune 037.001
upavāsaprabhāvaṃ ca kṛṣṇārādhanakāṅkṣiṇaḥ
kathayeha mama brahman na ca tṛpyāmi kathyate 037.002
śrūyatāṃ dālbhya yat pṛṣṭāḥ kautukād bhavatā vayam
āmuṣmikaṃ na tāpāya yac ca tāpāya jāyate 037.003
upoṣitaprabhāvaṃ ca kṛṣṇārādhanakāṅkṣiṇaḥ
kathayāmi yathāvṛttaṃ pūrvam eva mahāmate 037.004
vaidiśaṃ nāma nagaraṃ prakhyātam iha sattama
tatra vaiśyo 'bhavat pūrvaṃ vīrabhadra iti śrutaḥ 037.005
bhāryājāmātṛduhitṛ- putrapautrasnuṣānvitaḥ
prabhūtabhṛtyavargaś ca bahuvyāpārakārakaḥ 037.006
putrapautrādibharaṇa- vyāsaktamatir eva ca
paralokaṃ prati matis tasya cātyantadurmukhā 037.007
cakārānudinaṃ so 'tha nyāyānyāyair dhanārjanam
sarvatrānyatra niḥsnehaḥ parasve cātitarṣulaḥ 037.008
na juhoty udite kāle na dadāty atitṛṣṇayā
babhūva codyamas tasya putrādibharaṇe paraḥ 037.009
nityanaimittikānāṃ ca hāniṃ cakre svakarmaṇām
tṛṣṇābhibhūto viprarṣe svavargabharaṇādhṛtaḥ 037.010
kālena gacchatā so 'tha mṛto vindhyāṭavītaṭe
yātanādehabhṛt preto grīṣmakāle 'bhavan mune 037.011
taṃ dadarśa mahābhāgo divyajñānasamanvitaḥ
vedavedāntavid vidvān pipīto nāma vai dvijaḥ 037.012
bhāskarasyāṃśubhir dīptair dahyantam anivāraṇaiḥ
prataptavālukāmadhye tṛṣā cātyantapīḍitam 037.013
kṣutkṣāmakaṇṭhaṃ śuṣkāsyaṃ stabdhodvṛttavilocanam
niṣkrāntajihvam aṅgeṣu visphoṭaiḥ sarvataś citam 037.014
niśvāsāyāsakhedena viralāsyam anādaram
nijena karmaṇā baddham asamarthaṃ palāyane 037.015
śrāntaṃ makṣikayākīrṇaṃ durdagdhaṃ cātidāruṇam 037.*(41)
taṃ tādṛśam atho dṛṣṭvā gārdabheyo mahāmuniḥ
pipītaḥ prāha viprarṣiḥ kāruṇyastimitaṃ vacaḥ 037.016
jānann api tathā prāptaṃ tadanuṣṭhānajaṃ phalam
jantos tasyopakārāya sarvato hlādayann iva 037.017
adhaḥ sūryāṃśubhis taptair bahubhir yānapāṃsubhiḥ
upary arkakarair ugrais tṛṣā cārtas tathā kṣudhā 037.018
anyais tathādhibhir ghorair aviṣahyair avāraṇaiḥ
kathayeha yathātattvam ekākī dahyase katham 037.019
tasyaitad vacanaṃ śrutvā pipītasya savedanam
yātanāstha uvācedaṃ kṛcchrād ucchvāsya mastakam 037.020
brahman nālocitaṃ pūrvaṃ katham ante bhaviṣyati
aśāśvate śāśvatadhīs tena dahyāmi durmatiḥ 037.021
dhanāpaṇagṛhakṣetra- putradārahite rataḥ
nātmano 'haṃ hitārambhī tena dahyāmi durmatiḥ 037.022
idaṃ kariṣye kṛtvedaṃ kariṣyāmy aparaṃ tv idam
itīcchāśatasaro 'haṃ tena dahyāmi durmatiḥ 037.023
juhomi yadi tan nāsti dadāmi yadi sīdati
kuṭumbam iti mūḍho 'ham tena dahyāmi durmatiḥ 037.024
śītoṣṇavarṣābhibhavaṃ lobhāt soḍḥaṃ mayāśubham
tad eva hi na dharmārthaṃ tena dahyāmi durmatiḥ 037.025
pitṛdevamanuṣyāṇām adattvāpoṣitā hi ye
te 'nyatra kvāpi vartante dahyāmy eko 'tra durmatiḥ 037.026
putrabhṛtyakalatreṣu mama tv ādṛtamānasaḥ
kṛtvā karmāṇy asādhūni dahyāmy eko 'tra durmatiḥ 037.027
mṛte mayi dhane tasminn anyāyopārjite mayā
nūnaṃ mameti vartante dahyāmy eko 'tra durmatiḥ 037.028
na hi naḥ pūjitā gehān nirgatā dvijasattamāḥ
svavargahitakāmasya tena dahyāmy aharniśam 037.029
yan me na pūjitā devāḥ kuṭumbaṃ poṣītaṃ param
ekākī tena dahyāmi ye puṣṭās te 'nyato gatāḥ 037.030
nityanaimittikaṃ karma kṛte yeṣāṃ na ma kṛtam
ekākī tena dahyāmi tair manye kvāpi ramyate 037.031
yan me parijanasyārthe kṛtaṃ karma śubhāśubham
ekākī tena dahyāmi gatās te phalabhoginaḥ 037.032
dārāḥ putrāś ca bhṛtyāś ca pāpavyāptyā mayaidhitāḥ
ekākī tena dahyāmi gatās te phalabhoginaḥ 037.033
putradārādibhṛtyārthe mayānyāyārthasaṃcayāḥ
kṛtās tenātra dahyāmi bhuñjate 'py anyato gatāḥ 037.034
kṛtaṃ pāpaṃ mayā bhuktam anyais tatkarmasaṃcitam
dahyāmy eko 'ham atyantaṃ tyaktas taiḥ phalabhogibhiḥ 037.035
yan mamatvābhibhūtena mayā dhanam upārjitam
anyasya te 'dya kasyāpi kevalaṃ mama duṣkṛtam 037.036
antarduḥkhena dagdho 'ntar bahir dahyāmi bhānunā
nāntarduḥkhaṃ na vā bhānuḥ pāpam eva dvidhā sthitam 037.037
kaṃcit karmasamuddhāraṃ paśyasy asukhasāgarāt
mama yenāham āhlādam āpnuyāṃ munisattama 037.038
alpakālikam uddhāraṃ tava paśyāmy asaṃśayam
prakṣīṇaprāyam etat te sukṛtaṃ cāsti te param 037.039
atīte daśame janmany acyutārādhanecchayā
sukarmajayadāṃ bhadra dvādaśīṃ tvam upoṣitaḥ 037.040
tava tasyāḥ prabhāveṇa pāpam atyantadurjayam
alpair ahobhiḥ saṃkṣīṇaṃ navapātre yathā jalam 037.041
yad anyaḥ kṣapayed varṣais tad dinair bhavataḥ kṣayam
gataṃ pāpam ayaṃ tasyāḥ prabhāvo 'tyantadurlabhaḥ 037.042
śamaṃ pāpasya kurute jayaṃ sukṛtakarmaṇaḥ
satkarmajayadā hy eṣā tato vai dvādaśī smṛtā 037.043
yac caitad vedanārtena bhavatā paridevitam
tat tathā nātra saṃdeho mamatā pāpahetukī 037.044
pāpam atra kṛtaṃ pretya bhadra tāpāya jāyate
āhlādāya tathā puṇyam iha puṇyakṛtāṃ nṛṇām 037.045
vīrabhadraṃ samāśvāsya yayāv itthaṃ mahāmuniḥ
so 'py alpenaiva kālena tato mokṣam avāptavān 037.046
evaṃ dālbhya pare loke yad atrāsukṛtaṃ kṛtam
tat tāpāya sukhāyoktaṃ yad atraiva śubhaṃ kṛtam 037.047
upavāsaprabhāvaś ca kathitas te mahāmune
yenālpair eva divasair bhūri pāpaṃ kṣayaṃ gatam 037.048
tasmān nareṇa puṇyāya patitavyaṃ na pātake
upavāsāś ca kartavyāḥ sadaivātmahitaiṣiṇā 037.049
saṃsārāsāratāṃ jñātvā viṣayāṃś cātitarṣulān
kartavyaṃ yan mahābhāga puruṣeṇa tad ucyatām 038.001
saṃsārāsāratāṃ jñātvā viṣayāṃś cātitarṣulān
gṛddhis teṣv eva saṃtyājyā tattyāgo guṇavān nṛṇām 038.002
yeṣām abdasahasrāṇāṃ sahasrair api no naraḥ
bhogāt tṛptiṃ samāpnoti kas tair bhogair virajyate 038.003
yāvato vāñchate bhogān ahany ahani mānavaḥ
teṣāṃ sahasrabhāge 'pi dālbhya prāptiṃ na vindati 038.004
atha cet tan avāpnoti sahasraguṇitān naraḥ
tathāpy atṛpta evāntam antakāle gamiṣyati 038.005
tṛptaye ye na saṃprāptāḥ prāpyante ye na vāñchitāḥ
buddhimān indriyārtheṣu teṣv asaṅgī sadā bhavet 038.006
yeṣāṃ tṛptir na bhogena tyāgaś caivopakārakaḥ
upoṣitavidhānena bhogāntyāgas tato varaḥ 038.007
kṛcchracāndrāyaṇādīni narais tasmān mumukṣubhiḥ
niṣkāmair dālbhya kāryāṇi phalāya ca phalepsubhiḥ 038.008
atrāpy udāharantīmaṃ munayo munisattama
dasrābhyāṃ saha saṃvādam ailasya ca mahātmanaḥ 038.009
ailaḥ purūravāḥ pūrvaṃ babhūva manujeśvaraḥ
cakame yaṃ mahābhāgam urvaśī surasundarī 038.010
saṃtyajya tridaśāvāsaṃ rūpaudāryaguṇānvitam
bheje tam urvaśī dālbhya budhasya tanayaṃ nṛpam 038.011
nāsatyadasrau rūpeṇa devānām adhikau tataḥ
urvaśīlobhanaṃ tasya rūpaṃ draṣṭuṃ samutsukau 038.012
pratiṣṭhānaṃ puraṃ tasya budhaputrasya dhīmataḥ
jagmatuḥ sumahābhāgau tasya dvāstham athocatuḥ 038.013
kṣatto 'smadvacanād ailaṃ brūhi tvaṃ vasudhādhipam
draṣṭuṃ tavāśvinau prāptau rūpasaṃpadguṇaṃ ṇrpa
tadehy atra mahābhāga ihāsmān saṃpraveśaya 038.014
āścaryabhūtaṃ lokeṣu urvaśīlobhanaṃ vapuḥ
tat kautukaṃ na kurute kasya pārthivapuṅgava 038.015
āvāṃ samāgatau tasmāt tvāṃ draṣṭuṃ manujottama 038.*(42)
dvāsthas tatheti tāv āha praviveśa ca satvaram
ācacakṣe ca tad rājñe nāsatyavacanaṃ dvija 038.016
tac chrutvā vacanaṃ rājā dvāstham āha muhūrtakam
vilambyatāṃ mahābhāgau tau brūhi vacanān mama 038.017
vyāyāmatailasaṃsarga- malino na vibhūṣitaḥ
prasādhanaṃ ca kṛtvāhaṃ niṣkramāmi tvarānvitaḥ 038.018
niṣkramya sa tato dvāstho yathoktaṃ bhūbhṛtakhilam
samācaṣṭa tato dālbhya tau ca bhūyas tam ūcatuḥ 038.019
aprasādhitam evāśu bhavantaṃ vasudhādhipa
paśyāvas tava bhūyo 'pi tvāṃ drakṣyāvaḥ prasādhitam 038.020
ity ukto nirgatas tūrṇaṃ bhavanād avanīpatiḥ
tailābhyaktatanur dālbhya vyāyāmaparidhānadhṛk 038.021
sa praṇāmaṃ tayoḥ kṛtvā kiṃcin nataśirā nṛpaḥ
provāca yan mayā kāryaṃ bhavatos tad ihocyatām 038.022
saptadvīpavatī pṛthvī putradārabalaṃ dhanam
yac cānyad api tat sarvaṃ yuvayor me niveditam 038.023
ity udāhṛtam ākarṇya nṛpater aśvināv api
aṅgopāṅgādikaṃ sarvaṃ śanakais tāv apaśyatām 038.024
śirolalāṭabāhuṃ sa- nayanādivilokanam
kṛtvā ca taṃ mahīpālam ūcatus tāv idaṃ surau 038.025
praviśya snāhi bhūpāla yathārthaiś ca vibhūṣaṇaiḥ
vibhūṣitaṃ tu bhūyas tvāṃ drakṣyāvo 'vāṃ nareśvara 038.026
tatheti coktvā sa nṛpaḥ praviveśa mahāmune
cakre ca sakalaṃ samyak snātvā dehaprasādhanam 038.027
snāto 'nuliptaḥ sragdhārī suvastraḥ suvibhūṣitaḥ
nāsatyadasrayoḥ pārśvam iyāya vasudhādhipaḥ 038.028
bhūyo 'pi tau yathā pūrvam aṅgopāṅgavilokanam
cakratur nṛpates tasya smitabhinnauṣṭhasaṃpuṭau 038.029
tau sahāsau samālakṣya sa tadā vasudhādhipaḥ
hāsasya kāraṇaṃ deva- bhiṣajau tāv apṛcchata 038.030
pṛcchantaṃ na tato dālbhya nṛpatiṃ hāsyakāraṇam
yad ūcatur mahābhāgau tac chṛṇuṣva vadāmi te 038.031
śṛṇu bhūpāla sakalaṃ hāsakāraṇam āvayoḥ
yuṣmaddarśanasaṃbhūtaṃ kṣaṇāpacayahetukam 038.032
asnātasyābhavad bhūpa yādṛśī te surūpatā
sāṃprataṃ tādṛśī neyaṃ bhūṣitasyāpi bhūṣaṇaiḥ 038.033
snātaḥ sragdāmadhārī tvaṃ svanuliptaḥ subhūṣitaḥ
tathāpy asnāta eva prāc śobhano 'bhūn na sāṃpratam 038.034
kiṃtu tatkāraṇaṃ yena vyāyāmamalināmbaraḥ
śobhano 'ham abhūt pūrvam idānīṃ na vibhūṣitaḥ 038.035
divyena cakṣuṣā bhūpa kālasyāsya ca tasya ca
vayaḥpariṇatiṃ sūkṣmāṃ paśyāvo 'pacayapradām 038.036
yathā hi nāḍikā pūrṇā galaty avirataṃ nṛpa
nR̥ṇāṃ pariṇatas tadvac śarīragrahaṇād anu
caturthe 'hni ca tanmayaḥ 038.037
janmato 'nantaraṃ bālyaṃ paugaṇḍatvaṃ tataḥ param
yauvanaṃ madhyadehitvaṃ vārddhakaṃ ca jarā nṛṇām
sthūladṛṣṭyā tu paśyanti na tu te sūkṣmadarśinaḥ 038.038
nimeṣaśatabhāgasya sahasrāṃśaḥ kṣaṇo nṛpa
tasyāpy ayutabhāgāṃśo bhavaty apacayo nṛṇām 038.039
sūkṣmātisūkṣmāpacayī bhavaty eṣa pumān nṛpa
pariṇāmaṃ kramād yāti tṛptiṃ vāri pibann iva 038.040
tad ahar jātabālyasya bālasyāpacayo hi saḥ
pratikṣaṇāṃśayā vṛddhir bālatvaṃ hīyate tayā 038.041
paugaṇḍe yauvane caiva vārddhake ca mahāmate
hānikramaḥ sa evokto yo bālye kathitas tava 038.042
kāntir yā nṛpa bālasya pogaṇḍasya hi sā kutaḥ
tatkāntisaukumāryādyaiḥ śūnyam eva hi yauvanam 038.043
kāntyādisaṃpado hāniḥ paramā nṛpa vārddhake
tatrāpy anukṣaṇaṃ hānir hānir ā mṛtyuto nṛpa 038.044
evaṃ pratikṣaṇāṃśāṃśo nR̥ṇām apacayapradaḥ
kurvataḥ kimu kālas te mahāsnānaprasādhanam 038.045
asmaddṛṣṭo bhavān yāvat praviṣṭo nijamandiram
tāvad dhānim anuprāptaḥ kimu yāmārdhasaṃsthitaḥ 038.046
yādṛśo 'dya bhavāṃs tādṛk tvaṃ na rūpī nareśvara
paraśvaḥ śastanaṃ naiva 038.047
evaṃ samastabhūtāni sthāvarāṇi carāṇi ca
pratikṣaṇāṃśāpacayaṃ prāpnuvanti mahītale 038.048
tasmān na kautukaṃ kāryaṃ bhavatā tu nareśvara
yat te rūpam abhūt pūrvam aprasādhitaśobhanam 038.049
rājā purūravā bhūyaḥ śrutvā vākyam idaṃ tayoḥ
cintayitvā vacaḥ prāha saṃvegotkampimānasaḥ 038.050
aho bhavadbhyāṃ kathitam anavasthitasaṃsthitam
svarūpaṃ jagato devau yena trasto 'smi sāṃpratam 038.051
ajñānatimirāndhānāṃ madvidhānāṃ bhavadvidhāḥ
pradīpabhūtāḥ saṃdeho vidyate nātra kaścana 038.052
sadāpacayadoṣeṇa duṣṭakāyaiḥ surottamau
yat kāryaṃ puruṣais tac ca kathyatāṃ hitakāmyayā 038.053
atimūḍho 'dhruve kāye sadāpacayadharmiṇi
naras tadupabhogyāni dhruvāṇi parimārgati 038.054
āsanaṃ śayanaṃ yānaṃ paridhānaṃ gṛhādikam
vāñchaty aho 'timohena susthiraṃ svayam asthiraḥ 038.055
mūḍho 'dhruvaṃ dhruvamatiḥ kim ātmānaṃ na budhyate 038.056,*(43)
bālyāt paugaṇḍatāṃ gatvā yaḥ punar yauvanaṃ gataḥ 038.056
bhuvaḥ śailaṃ samārūḍhaḥ samārūḍhas tato drumam
ārohaṇaṃ sa kim anyad ṛkṣabhītaḥ kariṣyati 038.057
bālyāt paugaṇḍatāṃ yāto yauvanād vṛddhatāṃ gataḥ
vayo'vasthā tataḥ kānyā yad bhogāya sthirecchakaḥ 038.058
tasmād etan manuṣyeṇa vicāryātmahitaiṣiṇā
śreyasy āmuṣmike yatnaḥ kartavyo 'harniśaṃ nṛpa 038.059
bhogeṣv asaktiḥ satataṃ tathaivātmāvalokanam
śreyaḥ paraṃ manuṣyāṇāṃ kapilaḥ prāha pārthivaḥ 038.060
sarvatra samadarśitvaṃ nirmamatvam asaṅgitā
śreyaḥ paraṃ manuṣyāṇāṃ prāha pañcaśikho muniḥ 038.061
āgarbhajanmabālyādi- vayo'vasthādivedanam
śreyaḥ paraṃ manuṣyāṇām aṅgāriṣṭho 'bravīn nṛpaḥ 038.062
adhyātmikādiduḥkhānām atyantādipratikriyā
śreyaḥ paraṃ manuṣyāṇāṃ janako hy āha mokṣavit 038.063
abhinnayor bhedakaraḥ pratyayo yaḥ parātmanoḥ
hiraṇyagarbhas tacchāntiṃ śreyaḥ paramam abravīt 038.064
kartavyam iti yat karma ṛgyajuḥsāmasaṃjñitam
kriyate tat paraṃ śreyo jaigīṣavyo 'bravīn muniḥ 038.065
hāniṃ sarvavidhitsānām ātmanaḥ sukhahetukīm
śreyaḥ paraṃ manuṣyāṇāṃ devalo 'py āha tattvavit 038.066
yad yat tyajati kāmānāṃ tat sukhasyābhipūryate
etad eva paraṃ śreyo vijñānaṃ hitakāminām 038.067
kāmānusārī puruṣaḥ kāmān anu vinaśyati
aśreyasaṃ paraṃ caitad yad bhūpālātikāmitā 038.068
evaṃ vijñātatattvārthaḥ sanako yogināṃ varaḥ
narendra prāha viprāṇāṃ paramārthaparaṃparam 038.069
kriyākalāpaphaladam ṛgyajuḥsāmasaṃjñitam
amuṣmin madhyamaṃ śreyaḥ prāhuḥ sapta rṣayo nṛpa 038.070
ihaiva phaladaṃ kāmyaṃ karma yat kriyate naraiḥ
tad āhur aparaṃ śreyo ṛcīkacyavanādayaḥ 038.071
dve karmaṇī naraśreṣṭha brahmaṇā samudāhṛte
pravṛttākhyaṃ nivṛttaṃ ca svargamuktiphale hi te 038.072
pravṛttam api mokṣāya karma pārthiva jāyate
karma svarūpato bhraṣṭam anākāṅkṣya phalaṃ kṛtam 038.073
sāmānyaṃ cāparaṃ śreyaḥ sarvavarṇāśrameṣu yat
tac chṛṇuṣva mahīpāla vadato mama tattvataḥ 038.074
satyaṃ vaktavyaṃ nityaṃ maitreṇa bhāvyaṃ kāryaṃ ca tyājyaṃ nityam āyāsakāri
loke 'muṣmin yad dhitaṃ ca tathāsmiṃs tasminn ātmā yojanīyo 'nudhīraiḥ 038.075
tīrthasnānaiḥ sopavāsair ajasraṃ pātre dānair homajāpaiś ca nityam
śuddhir neyo devatābhyarcanaiś ca śuddho 'py ātmā saṅgadoṣād aśuddhaḥ 038.076
śuddhaṃ vastraṃ saṅgadoṣād aśuddhaṃ bhūyaḥ śuddhiṃ śodhyamānaṃ paryāti
etaj jñātvā na pramādo manuṣyaiḥ śuddhe hy ātmany ātmavidbhir vidheyaḥ 038.077
ity uktvā tau narendraṃ tau tena cārghyādinā pṛthak
samyak saṃpūjitau yātau nāka pṛṣṭham athāśvinau 038.078
sa cāpy anityatām evam avagamya nareśvaraḥ
niṣkāmo 'nudinam eva avagamya nareśvaraḥ
niṣkāmo 'nudinaṃ yajñair iyāja puruṣottamam 038.079
bhogāsaṅgi mano dālbhya yadāsīt tasya bhūpateḥ
tad eva bhagavaddhyāna- paraṃ cakre mahāmune 038.080
tatyājārtheṣu mamatām ahaṃkāraṃ tathātmani
samatāṃ sarvabhūteṣu saṃprāpa pṛthivīpatiḥ 038.081
yasyātmany api viprarṣe nāhaṃmāno 'sti kutracit
madāvalepo pūpādau tasya syād iti kā kathā 038.082
evaṃ dālbhya manuṣyeṇa samatām anutiṣṭhatā
sarvabhogeṣu saṃtyājyo dhyeyaś ca puruṣottamaḥ 038.083
kutra tiṣṭhati govindo bāhyanivṛtacetasi
tasmān niḥsaṅgacittena śakyaś cintayituṃ hariḥ 038.084
prītidveṣādayas tyaktvā maharṣe yasya cetasā
priyātithis taddhṛdaye viṣṇur mokṣaphalapradaḥ 038.085
kāryārambheṣu sarveṣu duḥsvapneṣu ca sattama
amaṅgalyeṣu sarveṣu yaj japtavyaṃ tad ucyatām 039.001
yenārambhāś ca sidhhyanti duḥsvapnaṃ copaśāmyati
amaṅgalānāṃ sarveṣāṃ pratighātaś ca jāyate 039.002
janārdanaṃ bhūtapatiṃ jagadguruṃ smaran manuṣyaḥ satataṃ mahāmune
duṣṭāny aśeṣāṇy apahanti sādhayaty aśeṣakāryāṇi tathā yadīcchati 039.003
śṛṇuṣva cānyad vadato mamākhilaṃ vadāmi yat te dvijavarya maṅgalam
sarvārthasiddhiṃ pradadāti yaḥ sadā nihanty aśeṣāṇi ca pātakāni 039.004
pratiṣṭhitaṃ yatra jagac carācaraṃ jagac ca yo yo jagataś ca hetuḥ
jagac ca pāty atti ca yaḥ sa sarvadā 039.005
mamāstu maṅgalyavivṛddaye hariḥ 039.5-44
vyomāmbuvāyvagnimahīsvarūpair vistāravān yo 'ṇutaro 'ṇubhāgāt
sa sthūlasūkṣmaḥ satateśvareśvaro 039.006
yasmāt parastāt puruṣād anantād anādimadhyād akhilaṃ na kiṃcit
sa hetuhetuḥ parameśvareśvaro 039.007
hiraṇyagarbhācyutarudrarūpī sṛjaty aśeṣaṃ paripāti hanti
guṇāśrayī yo bhagavān sa sarvadā 039.008
paraḥ surāṇāṃ paramo 'surāṇāṃ paro munīnāṃ paramo yatīnām
paraḥ samastasya ca yaḥ sa devo 039.009
dhyāto yatīnām apakalmaṣair yo dadāti muktiṃ parameśvareśvaraḥ
manobhir ādyaḥ puruṣaḥ sa sarvadā 039.010
surendravaivasvatavittapāmbupa- svarūparūpī paripāti yo jagat
sa śuddhasattvaḥ parameśvareśvaro 039.011
yannāmakīrtanato vimucyate anekajanmārjitapāpasaṃcayaiḥ
pāpendhanāgniḥ sa sadaiva nirmalo 039.012
yenoddhṛteyaṃ dharaṇī rasātalād aśeṣasattvasthitikāraṇād idam
bibharti viśvaṃ jagataḥ sa mūlavān 039.013
pādeṣu vedā jaṭhare carācaraṃ romasv aśeṣā munayo mukhe makhāḥ
yasyeśvareśasya sa sarvadā prabhur 039.014
samastayajñāṅgamayaṃ vapur vibhor yasyāṅgam īśeśvarasaṃstutasya
varāharūpo bhagavān sa sarvadā 039.015
vikṣobhya sarvodadhitoyasaṃpadaṃ dadhāra dhātrīṃ jagataś ca yodbhavaḥ
yajñeśvaro yajñapumān sa sarvadā 039.016
pātālamūleśvarabhogisaṃhatau vinyasya pādau pṛthivīṃ ca bibhrataḥ
yasyopamānaṃ na babhūva so 'cyuto 039.017
vighargharaṃ yasya ca bṛṃhato muhuḥ sanandanādyair janalokasaṃsthitaiḥ
śrutaṃ jayetyuktiparaiḥ sa sarvadā 039.018
ekārṇavād yasya mahīyaso mahīm ādāya vegena samutpatiṣyataḥ
nutaṃ vapur yogivaraiḥ sa sarvadā 039.019
hato hiraṇyākṣamahāsuraḥ purā purāṇapuṃsā parameṇa yena
varāharūpaḥ sa patiḥ prajāpater 039.020
daṃṣṭrākarālaṃ surabhītināśanaṃ kṛtvā vapur divyanṛsiṃharūpiṇaṃ
trātaṃ jagad yena sa sarvadā prabhur 039.021
daityendravakṣaḥsthaladāradāruṇaiḥ karoruhaiḥ śatrurujānukāribhiḥ
ciccheda lokasya bhayāni cāvyayo 039.022
dantāntadīptidyutinirmalāṇi cakāra sarvāṇi diśaṃ mukhāni
ninādavitrāsitadānavo hy asau 039.023
yannāmasaṃkīrtanato mahābhayād vimokṣam āpnoti na saṃśayaṃ naraḥ
samastalokārtiharo nṛkesarī 039.024
saṭākalāpabhramaṇānilahatāḥ sphuṭanti yasyāmbudharāḥ samantataḥ
sa divyasiṃhaḥ sphuritākulekṣaṇo 039.025
yadīkṣaṇajyotiṣi raśmimaṇḍalaṃ pralīnam eva na rarāja bhāsvataḥ
kutaḥ śaśāṅkasya sa siṃharūpadhṛṅ 039.026
dravanti daityāḥ praṇamanti devatā naśyanti rakṣāṃsy apayānti cārayaḥ
yatkīrtanāt so 'dbhutarūpakesarī 039.027
aśeṣadeveśanareśvareśvaraiḥ sadā stutaṃ yac caritaṃ mahādbhutam
sa sarvalokārtiharo mahāharir 039.028
ṛkkāritaṃ yo yajuṣātiśāntimat sāmadhvanidhvastasamastapātakam
cakre jagad vāmanakaḥ sa sarvadā 039.029
yatpādavinyāsapavitratāṃ mahī yayau viyad ṛgyajuṣām udīraṇāt
sa vāmano divyaśarīradhṛk sadā 039.030
yasmin prayāte surabhūbhṛto 'dhvaraṃ nanāma khedād avaniḥ sasāgarā
sa vāmanaḥ sarvajaganmayaḥ sadā 039.031
mahādyutau daityapater mahādhvaraṃ yasmin praviṣṭe kṣubhitaṃ mahāsuraiḥ
sa vāmano 'ntasthitasaptalokadhṛṅ 039.032
samastadeveṣṭimayaṃ mahādyutir dadhāra yo rūpam atīndriyaṃ prabhuḥ
trivikramākrāntajagattrayaḥ sadā 039.033
saṅghaiḥ surāṇāṃ divi bhūtale sthitais tathā manuṣyair gagane sa sarvadā
stutaḥ kramād yaḥ pradade sa sarvadā 039.034
krāntvā dharitrīṃ gaganaṃ tathā divaṃ marutpater yaḥ pradadau triviṣṭapam
sa devadevo bhuvaneśvareśvaro 039.035
anugrahaṃ cāpi baler anuttamaṃ cakāra yaś cendrapadopalakṣaṇaṃ
surāṃś ca yajñasya bhujaḥ sa sarvadā 039.036
rasātalād yena purā samāhṛtāḥ samastavedā varavājirūpiṇā
sa kaiṭabhārir madhusūdano mahān 039.037
niḥkṣatriyāṃ yaś ca cakāra medinīm anekaśo bāhuvanaṃ tathāchinat
yaḥ kārtavīryasya sa bhārgavottamo 039.038
nihatya vāliṃ ca kapīśvaraṃ hi yo nibadhya setuṃ jaladhau daśānanam
jaghāna cānyān rajanīcarān asau 039.039
cikṣepa bālaḥ śakaṭaṃ babhañja yo yamalārjunau kaṃsam ariṃ jaghāna
mamarda cāṇūramukhaṃ sa sarvadā 039.040
prātaḥ sahasrāṃśumarīcinirmalaṃ kareṇa bibhrad bhagavān sudarśanam
kaumodakīṃ cāpi gadām anuttamāṃ 039.041
himendukundasphaṭikābhrakomalaṃ mukhānilāpūritam īśvareśvaraḥ
madhyāhnakāle ca sa śaṅkham uttamam 039.042
tathāparāhne pravikāsipaṅkajaṃ vakṣaḥsthalena śriyam udvahad vibhuḥ
vistāripadmotpalapatralocano 039.043
sarveṣu kāleṣu samastadeśeṣv aśeṣakāryeṣu tatheśvareśvaraḥ
sarvaiḥ svarūpair bhagavān anādimān 039.044
etat paṭhan dālbhya samastapāpair vimucyate viṣṇuparo manuṣyaḥ
sidhyanti kāryāṇi tathāsya sarvāṇy arthān avāpnoti tathā yatheṣṭam 039.045
duḥsvapnaṃ praśamam upaiti paṭhyamāne stotre 'smiñ śravaṇavidhau sadotthitasya
prārambho drutam upayāti siddhim īśaḥ pāpāni kṣapayati cāsya vāsudevaḥ 039.046
maṅgalyaṃ paramam idaṃ sadārthasiddhiṃ nirvighna tv adhikaphalaṃ sadā dadāti
kiṃ loke tad iha paratra cāsti puṃsām yad viṣṇupravaṇadhiyā na dālbhya sādhyam 039.047
devendras tribhuvanam artham ekapiṅgaḥ sarvarddhiṃ tribhuvanagāṃ ca kārtavīryaḥ
vaidehaḥ paramapadaṃ prasādya viṣṇuṃ saṃprāptaḥ sakalaphalaprado hi viṣṇuḥ 039.048
sarvārambheṣu dālbhyaitad duḥsvapneṣu ca paṇḍitaḥ
japed ekamatir viṣṇau tathāmaṅgalyadarśane 039.049
śamaṃ prayānti duṣṭāni grahapīḍāś ca dāruṇāḥ
karmārambhāś ca sidhyanti puṇyam āpnoti cottamam 039.050
harir dadāti bhadrāṇi maṅgalyastutisaṃstutaḥ
karoty akhilarūpaiś ca rakṣām akṣataśaktidhṛk 039.051
kurvīta kiṃ pumān sthānaṃ kaḥ pumān brahmaṇo balam
brahmaṇaś ca kathaṃ bhedo jñeyo 'bhinnaphalapradaḥ 040.001
svakarmaṇā dhanaṃ labdhvā nityanaimittikāḥ kriyāḥ
kurvīta śuddhim āsthāya svecchayā ca tathā paraḥ 040.002
tyaktvā rāgādikān doṣān samaḥ sarvatra vai bhavet
sarvatra maitrīṃ kurvīta dadyād iṣṭāni cārthinām 040.003
kuryād dīneṣu karuṇāṃ duḥśīlān parivarjayet
muditāṃ dharmaśīleṣu bhāvanāṃ munisattama
niḥśeṣārthamalāpetāṃ 040.004
ekatra vā jagannāthe bhāvanāṃ puruṣottame
śuddhāṃ kurvīta paṇḍitaḥ 040.005
śarīrabāhyatāṃ śaśvad dhiṃsāṃ kurvīta na kvacit
nindāvamānam anyeṣāṃ yac cānyad upaghātakam 040.006
śarīravāṅmanaḥśuddhiṃ kurvīta ca sadātmanaḥ
bhūtānām upakāraś ca tapobhiś cātmakarṣaṇam 040.007
eṣa dharmaḥ samāsena dālbhyākhyāto mayā tava
adharmaś cāyam evokto viparīto manīṣibhiḥ 040.008
ete yatra guṇāḥ pūrvaṃ kathitā jñānasaṃyutāḥ
brahmaṇaḥ sāśrayaḥ śuddha upacārāt tad eva saḥ 040.009
ekasyaiva satas tasya brahmaṇo dvijasattama
nāmnāṃ bahutvaṃ lokānām upakārakaraṃ śṛṇu 040.010
nimittaśaktayo nāmno bhedatas tadudīraṇāt
vibhinnāny eva sādhyante phalāni kurunandana 040.011
yacchakti nāma tat tasya tat tasminn eva vastuni
sādhakaṃ puruṣavyāghra saumyakrūreṣu vastuṣu 040.012
vāsudevācyutānanta- satyājyapuruṣottamaiḥ
paramātmeśvarādyaiś ca stuto nāmabhir avyayaḥ 040.013
nimittabhāvaṃ bhagavān vimukter yāty adhokṣajaḥ
tathānyakāryasaṃsiddhau yad yat tat tan niśāmaya 040.014
dhanakṛd dharmakṛd dharmī dharmātmā viśvakṛc chuciḥ
śuciṣad viṣṇur abjākṣaḥ puṣkarākṣo hy adhokṣayaḥ
śuciśravāḥ śipiviṣṭo yajñeśo yajñabhāvanaḥ 040.015
nāmnām ity evam ādīnāṃ samuccāraṇato naraḥ
dharmaṃ mahāntam āpnoti pāpabandhakṣayaṃ tathā 040.016
tathārthaprāptaye brahman devanāmāni me śṛṇu
yeṣāṃ samuccāraṇato vittam āpnoti bhaktimān 040.017
śrīdaḥ śrīśaḥ śrīnivāsaḥ śrīdharaḥ śrīniketanaḥ
śriyaḥ patiḥ śrīparamaḥ śrīmāñ śrīvatsalāñcchanaḥ 040.018
nṛsiṃho duṣṭadāmano jayo viṣṇus trivikramaḥ
stutaḥ prayacchate cārtham evam ādibhir acyutaḥ 040.019
kāmyaḥ kāmapradaḥ kāntaḥ kāmapālas tathā hariḥ
ānando mādhavaś caiva kāmasaṃsiddhaye nṛpa 040.020
rāmaḥ paraśurāmaś ca nṛsiṃho viṣṇur eva ca
vikramaś caivam ādīni japyāny arijigīṣubhiḥ 040.021
vidyām abhyasatā nityaṃ japtavyaḥ puruṣottamaḥ
dāmodaraṃ bandhagato nityam eva japan naraḥ 040.022
keśavaṃ puṇḍarīkākṣaṃ puṣkarākṣaṃ tathā japet
netrabādhāsu sarvāsu hṛṣīkeśaṃ bhayeṣu ca 040.023
acyutaṃ cāmṛtaṃ caiva japed auṣadhakarmaṇi
bhrājiṣṇum agnihānau ca japed ālambane sthitam 040.024
saṃgrāmābhimukhaṃ gacchan saṃsmared aparājitam
pātālanarasiṃhaṃ ca jalaprataraṇe smaret 040.025
cakriṇaṃ gadinaṃ caiva śārṅginaṃ khaḍginaṃ tathā
kṣemārthe prasavan rājan dikṣu prācyādiṣu smaret 040.026
ajitaṃ cādhikaṃ caiva sarvaṃ sarvaśvaraṃ tathā
saṃsmaret puruṣo bhaktyā vyavahāreṣu sarvadā 040.027
nārāyaṇaṃ sarvakālaṃ kṣutapraskhalitādiṣu
grahanakṣatrapīḍāsu devabādhāṭavīṣu ca 040.028
asyuvairinirodheṣu vyāghrasiṃhādisaṃkaṭe
andhakāre ca tīvre ca narasiṃham anusmaret
taraty akhiladurgāṇi tāpārto jalaśāyinam 040.029
garuḍadhvajānusmaraṇād āpadbhyo mucyate naraḥ 040.030
jvaraduṣṭaśiroroga- viṣavīryaṃ praśāmyati 040.030,*(44)
snāne devārcane home praṇipāte pradakṣiṇe
kīrtayed bhagavannāma vāsudeveti tatparaḥ 040.031
sthagane vittadhānyāder apadhyāne ca duṣṭaje
kurvīta tanmanā bhūtvā anantācyutakīrtanam 040.032
nārāyaṇaṃ śārṅgadharaṃ śrīdharaṃ puruṣottamam
vāmanaṃ khaḍginaṃ caiva duḥsvapneṣu ca saṃsmaret 040.033
ekārṇavāhiparyaṅka- śāyinaṃ ca naraḥ smaret
vāyvagnīgṛhadāhāya pravṛddhāv upalakṣya ca 040.034
vidyārthī mohavibhrānti- vegāghūrṇitamānasaḥ
manuṣyo muniśārdūla sadāśvaśirasaṃ smaret 040.035
balabhadraṃ samṛddhyarthī sīrakarmaṇi kīrtayet
jagatsūtim apatyārthī stuvan bhaktyā na sīdati 040.036
japtavyaṃ suprajākhyaṃ tu devadevasya sattama
dampatyor ātmasaṃbandhe vivāhākhye punaḥ punaḥ 040.037
śrīśaṃ sarvābhyudayike karmaṇi saṃprakīrtayet
ariṣṭānteṣv aśeṣeṣu viśokaṃ ca sadā japet 040.038
marutpratāpāgnijala- bandhanādiṣu mṛtyuṣu
svātantryaparatantreṣu vāsudevaṃ japed budhaḥ 040.039
sarvārthaśaktiyuktasya devadevasya cakriṇaḥ
yad vābhirocate nāma tat sarvārtheṣu kīrtayet 040.040
sarvārthasiddhim āpnoti nāmnām ekārthatā yataḥ
sarvāṇy etāni nāmāni parasya brahmaṇo 'nagha 040.041
evam etāni nāmāni devadevasya kīrtayet
yaṃ yaṃ kāmam abhidhyāyet taṃ tam āpnoty asaṃśayam
sarvān kāmān avāpnoti samārādhya jagadgurum 040.042
tanmayatvena govindam ity etad dālbhya nānyathā
tanmayo vāñchitān kāmān yad avāpnoti mānavaḥ 040.043
nimittaśaktiḥ sā tasya na bhedo dālbhya mānasaḥ
vāṅmanaḥkāyikaṃ dveṣaṃ yac ca kurvan prayāty adhaḥ 040.044
svarūpaśaktiḥ sā tasya matibhedakṛtaṃ na tad
sa śākto nirguṇaḥ śuddho brahmabhūto jagadguruḥ 040.045
karmabhir nāmabhir jīvo dṛśyate dālbhya naikadhā
yathā ca gaṅgāsalilaṃ sitam atyantanirmalam 040.046
ekasvarūpam adhyātmaṃ puṇyāpuṇyavibhedibhiḥ
bhrāntijñānānvitair miśraṃ sitāsitaviceṣṭitaiḥ
dṛśyate naikadhā dālbhya prāṇibhir bhinnabuddhibhiḥ 040.047
tāpārtās tāpaśamanam atiprītyatiśītalam
kaphadoṣānvitair nāti- prītiyuktair niraṃśubhiḥ 040.048
strīyogyam etan netīti prītyaprītisamanvitaiḥ
madhyasthabuddhyā caivānye nātiśītātitāpibhiḥ 040.049
pavitram ity etad iti puṇyabuddhyā tathāparaiḥ
mṛṣṭam etad itīty anyair matsyāḍhyam iti cāparaiḥ 040.050
tulyabuddhyāpi caivānyair heyabuddhyā tathāparaiḥ
nātivegātivegaṃ ca hṛṣṭodvignais tathāparaiḥ 040.051
kim eteneti caivānyaiḥ paradārābhilāṣibhiḥ
dālbhya saṃdṛśyate cānyair jantubhir bhāyakātaraiḥ
tad eva pūyaṃ paśyanti pretādyā hṛtipāpinaḥ 040.052
etaiś cānyaiś ca bahubhir viśeṣair bahujantubhiḥ
viśeṣavat karmabhedād ekam eva hi dṛśyate 040.053
naite gaṅgāmbhaso bhedāḥ prītyaprītipradāyinaḥ
prāṇināṃ cetaso bhedād dālbhyaite karmayonayaḥ 040.054
samastakarmaṇā dālbhya saṃkṣaye bhayam ety asau
viśeṣakāraṇābhāvād viśeṣābhāva eva hi 040.055
viṣṇvākhyam evaṃ tad brahma śuddham atyantanirmalam
abhedaṃ bahudhā bhinnaṃ dṛśyate karmabhedibhiḥ 040.056
yogibhir dṛśyate śuddhaṃ rāgādyupaśamāmalaiḥ
rāgibhir viṣayākāraṃ tad eva brahma dṛśyate 040.057
karmamārgāśritaiḥ karma- bhoktṛtve ca tatheṣyate
kim apy astīti caivānyair avivekibhir ucyate 040.058
sarvam etat tad eveti vadanty advaitavādinaḥ
pratyakṣaṃ dṛśyam eveti vadanty anye duruktibhiḥ 040.059
vadanty anye tad evāhaṃ nāstīty anye vadanti tat
tiryaṅmanuṣyadevākhyaṃ tad anyair abhidhīyate 040.060
vandyabuddhyā tu tat kaiścid dhyeyabuddhyā tathāparaiḥ
gamyabuddhyā tathānyaiś ca labhyabuddhyā ca jantubhiḥ 040.061
gṛhyate tat paraṃ brahma ripubuddhyā tathāparaiḥ
parabuddhyā ca naikadhā 040.062
ātmaputrasuhṛdbhartṛ- 040.062,*(45)
parabuddhyā tathāparaiḥ 040.*(45)
prāṇibhiḥ karmavaiṣamya- bhinnabuddhibhir avyayam
tad brahma gṛhyate dālbhya paramārthaṃ nibodha me 040.063
bhūtendriyāntaḥkaraṇa- pradhānapuruṣātmakam
aparaṃ brahmaṇo rūpaṃ paraṃ dālbhya niśāmaya 040.064
aheyam akṣaraṃ śuddham asaṃbhūtinirañjanam
viṣṇvākhyaṃ paramaṃ brahma yad vai paśyanti sūrayaḥ 040.065
yathaitad bhavatā proktaṃ dharmārthādes tu sādhanam
patnī nR̥ṇāṃ muniśreṣṭha yoṣitas ca tathā naraḥ 041.001
tac chrotum icche viprarṣe vidhavā strī na jāyate
upoṣītena yenāgryā patnyā ca rahito naraḥ 041.002
aśūnyaśayanā nāma dvitīyāṃ śṛṇu tāṃ mama
yām upoṣya na vaidhavyaṃ prayāti strī dvijottama 041.003
patnīviyuktaś ca naro na kadācit prajāyate
śete jagatpatiḥ kṛṣṇaḥ śriyā sārdhaṃ yadā dvija 041.004
aśūnyaśayanā nāma tadā grāhyā hi sā tithiḥ
kṛṣṇapakṣadvitīyāyāṃ śrāvaṇe dvijasattama 041.005
idam uccārayen nāma praṇamya jagataḥ patim
śrīvatsadhāriṇaṃ śrīśaṃ bhaktyābhyarcya śriyā saha 041.006
śrīvatsadhāriñ śrīkānta śrīdhāma śrīpate 'cyuta
gārhasthyaṃ mā praṇāśaṃ me yātu dharmārthakāmadam 041.007
agnayo mā praṇaśyantu mā praṇaśyantu devatāḥ
pitaro mā praṇaśyantu matto dāmpatyabhedataḥ 041.008
lakṣmyā prayujyate deva na kadācid yathā bhavān
tathā kalatrasaṃbandho deva mā me vibhidyatām 041.009
lakṣmyā na śūnyaṃ varada yathā te śayanaṃ sadā
śayyā mamāpy aśūnyāstu tathaiva madhusūdana 041.010
evaṃ prasādya pūjāṃ ca kṛtvā lakṣmyās tathā hareḥ
phalāni dadyāc chayyāyām abhīṣṭāni jagatpateḥ 041.011
naktaṃ praṇamyāyatane havir bhuñjīta vāgyataḥ
brāhmaṇāya dvitīye 'hni śaktyā dadyāc ca dakṣiṇām 041.012
evaṃ karoti yaḥ samyag naro māsacatuṣṭayam
tasya janmatrayaṃ dālbhya gṛhabhaṅgo na jāyate 041.013
aśūnyaśayanaś cāsau dharmakarmārthasādhakaḥ
bhavaty avyāhataiśvaryaḥ puruṣo nātra saṃśayaḥ 041.014
nārī ca dālbhya dharmajñā vratam etad yathāvidhi
yā karoti na sā śocyā bandhuvargasya jāyate 041.015
vaidhavyaṃ durbhagatvaṃ vā bhartṛtyāgaṃ ca sattama
nāpnoti janmatritayam etac cīrtvā pativratā 041.016
upavāsāśritaṃ samyag lokadvayaphalapradam
kathitaṃ bhavatā sarvaṃ yat pṛṣṭo 'si mayā dvija 042.001
anyad icchāmy ahaṃ śrotuṃ tad bhavān prabravītu me
saṃsārahetuṃ muktiṃ ca saṃsārān munisattama 042.002
avidyāprabhavaṃ karma hetubhūtaṃ dvijottama
saṃsārasyāsya tanmuktiḥ saṃkṣepāc chrūyatāṃ mama 042.003
svajātivihitaṃ karma lobhadveṣavivarjitam
kurvataḥ kṣīyate pūrvaṃ manyubandhaś ca neṣyate 042.004
apūrvasaṃbhavābhavāt kṣayaṃ yāty ādikarmaṇi
dālbhya saṃsāravicchedaḥ kāraṇābhāvasaṃbhavaḥ 042.005
bhavaty asaṃśayaṃ cānyac śrūyatām atra kāraṇam
saṃsārān mucyate dālbhya samāsād vadato mama 042.006
gṛhītakarmaṇā yena puṃsāṃ jātir dvijottama 042.007,*(46)
tatprāyaścittabhūtaṃ vai śṛṇu karmakṣayāvaham 042.007
brāhmaṇakṣatriyaviśāṃ śūdrāntyānāṃ ca sattama
svajātivihitaṃ karma rāgadveṣādivarjitam 042.008
jātipradasya kṣayadaṃ tad evādyasya karmaṇaḥ
jñānakāraṇabhāvaṃ ca tad eva pratipadyate 042.009
pumāṃś cādhigatajñāno bhedaṃ nāpnoti sattama
brahmaṇā viṣṇusaṃjñena parameṇāvyayātmanā 042.010
etat te kathitaṃ dālbhya saṃsārasya samāsataḥ
kāraṇaṃ bhavamuktiś ca jāyate yogino yathā 042.011
iti dālbhyaḥ pulastyena yathāvat pratibodhitaḥ
ārādhayām āsa hariṃ lebhe kāmāṃś ca vāñchitān 043.001
tathā tvam api daityendra keśavārādhanaṃ kuru
ārādhya taṃ jagannāthaṃ na kaścid avasīdati 043.002
iti śukravacaḥ śrutvā prahlādo madhusūdanam
ārādhya prāptavān kṛtsnaṃ trailokaiśvaryam ūrjitam 043.003
etan mayoktaṃ sakalaṃ tava bhūmipa pṛcchataḥ
anārādhyācyutaṃ devaṃ kaḥ kāmān prāpnute naraḥ 043.004
ambarīso narapatir viṣṇor māhātmyam uttamam
śrutvā babhūva satataṃ keśavārpitamānasaḥ 043.005
evaṃ tvam api kauravya yadi muktim abhīṣyasi
bhogān vā vilupān devāt tasmād ārādhayācyutam 043.006
dadāti vāñchitān kāmān sakāmair arcito hariḥ
muktiṃ dadāti govindo niṣkāmair abhipūjitaḥ 043.007
bhagavān avatīrṇo 'bhūn martyalokaṃ janārdanaḥ
bhārāvataraṇārthāya bhuvo bhūtapatir hariḥ 043.008
mānuṣatve ca govindo mama pūrvapitāmahaiḥ
cakāra prītim atulāṃ sāmānyapuruṣo yathā 043.009
sārathyaṃ kṛtavāṃś caiva teṣāṃ sarveśvaro hariḥ
nistīrṇo yena bhīṣmaugho kurusainyamahodadhiḥ 043.010
upakārī mahābhāgaḥ sa teṣāṃ sarvavastuṣu
keśavaḥ pāṇḍuputrāṇāṃ sutānāṃ janako yathā 043.011
dhanyās te kṛtapuṇyāś ca mama pāṇḍusutā matāḥ
viviśur ye pariṣvaṅge govindabhujapañjaram 043.012
rājyahetor arīñ jaghnur akasmāt pāṇḍunandanāḥ
saptalokaikanāthena ye 'bhavann ekaśāyinaḥ 043.013
ātmānam avagacchāmi bhagavan dhūtakalmaṣam
jātaṃ nirdhūtapāpe 'smin kule viṣṇuparigrahe 043.014
evaṃ devavaras teṣāṃ prasādasumukho hariḥ
pṛcchatāṃ kaccid ācaṣṭe kiṃcid guhyaṃ mahātmanām 043.015
guhyaṃ janārdanaṃ yāṃs tu dharmaputro yudhiṣṭhiraḥ
papraccha dharmān akhilāṃs tan mamākhyātum arhasi 043.016
dharmārthakāmamokṣeṣu yad guhyaṃ madhusūdanaḥ
teṣām avocad bhagavāñ śrotum icchāmi tat tv aham 043.017
bahūni dharmaguhyāni dharmaputrāya keśavaḥ
purā provāca rājendra prasādasumukho hariḥ 043.018
śaratalpagatād bhīṣmād dharmāñ śrutvā yudhiṣṭhiraḥ
pṛṣṭavān yaj jagannāthaṃ tan me nigadataḥ śṛṇu 043.019
pañcamenāśvamedhena yadā snāto yudhiṣṭhiraḥ
tadā nārāyaṇaṃ devaṃ praśnam etam apṛcchata 044.001
bhagavan vaiṣṇavā dharmāḥ kiṃphalāḥ kiṃparāyaṇāḥ
kiṃ kṛtyam adhikṛtyaite bhavatotpāditāḥ purā 044.002
yadi te pāṇḍuṣu sneho vidyate madhusūdana
śrotavyāś cen mayā dharmās tatas tān kathayākhilān 044.003
pavitrāś caiva ye dharmāḥ sarvapāpapraṇāśanāḥ
tava vaktracyutā deva sarvadharmeṣv anuttamāḥ 044.004
yāñ śrutvā brahmahā goghnaḥ pitṛghno gurutalpagaḥ
surāpo vā kṛtaghnaś ca mucyate sarvakilbiṣaiḥ 044.005
etan me kathitaṃ sarvaṃ sabhāmadhye 'risūdana
vasiṣṭhādyair mahābhāgair munibhir bhāvitātmabhiḥ 044.006
tato 'haṃ tava deveśa pādamūlam upāgataḥ
dharmān kathaya tān deva yady ahaṃ bhavataḥ priyaḥ 044.007
śrutā me mānavā dharmā vāsiṣṭhāś ca mahāmate
parāśarakṛtāś caiva tathātreyasya dhīmataḥ 044.008
śrutā gārgyasya śaṅkhasya likhitasya yamasya ca
jāpāleś ca mahābāho muner dvaipāyanasya ca 044.009
umāmaheśvarāś caiva jātidharmāś ca pāvanāḥ
guṇeś ca guṇabāhoś ca kāśyapeyās tathaiva ca 044.010
bahvāyanakṛtāś caiva śākuneyās tathaiva ca
agastyagītā maudgalyāḥ śāṇḍilyāḥ saurabhās tathā 044.011
bhṛgor aṅgirasaś caiva kaśyapoddālakās tathā
saumantūgrāyaṇāgrāś ca pailasya ca mahātmanaḥ 044.012
vaiśampāyanagītāś ca piśaṅgamakṛtāś ca ye
aindrāś ca vāruṇāś caiva kauberā vātsyapauṇakāḥ 044.013
āpastambāḥ śrutā dharmās tathā gopālakasya ca
bhṛgvaṅgiraḥkṛtāś caiva sauryā hārītakās tathā
yājñavalkyakṛtāś caiva tathā saptarṣayaś ca ye 044.014
etāś cānyāś ca vividhāḥ śrutā me dharmasaṃhitāḥ
bhagavañ śrotum icchāmi tava vaktrād viniḥsṛtān 044.015
evam uktaḥ sa pārthena pratyuvāca janārdanaḥ
bahumānāc ca prītyā ca dharmaputraṃ yudhiṣṭhiram 044.016
iṣṭas tvaṃ hi mahābāho sadā mama yudhiṣṭhira
paramārthaṃ tava brūyāṃ kiṃ punar dharmasaṃhitām 044.017
paramajñānibhiḥ siddhair yuñjadbhir api nityaśaḥ
praśāntasyeva dīpasya gatir mama duratyayā 044.018
sarvavedamayaṃ brahma pavitram ṛṣibhiḥ stutam
kathayiṣyāmi te rājan dharmaṃ dharmabhṛtām vara 044.019
evam ukte tu kṛṣṇena ṛṣayo 'mitatejasaḥ
samājagmuḥ sabhāmadhye śrotukāmā harer giram 044.020
devagandharvaṛṣayo guhyakāś ca mahāyaśāḥ
vālakhilyā mahātmāno munayaḥ saṃmitavratāḥ
pāvanān sarvadharmebhyo rahasyān dvijasattama 044.*(47)
vaiṣṇavān akhilān dharmān yaḥ paṭhet pāpanāśanān
bhaveyur akṣayās tasya lokāḥ satpuṇyabhāginaḥ 044.021
kṛṣṇadṛṣṭihataṃ cāsya kilbiṣaṃ saṃpraṇaśyati
vaiṣṇavasya ca yajñasya phalaṃ prāpnoti mānavaḥ 044.022
kautūhalasamāviṣṭaḥ papracchedaṃ yudhiṣṭhiraḥ
yamalokasya cādhvānam antaraṃ mānuṣasya ca 045.001
kīdṛśaṃ kiṃpramāṇaṃ vā kathaṃ vāntaṃ janārdana
taranti puruṣāḥ kṛṣṇa kenopāyena saṃśame 045.002
tasya tad vacanaṃ śrutvā vismito madhusūdanaḥ
pratyuvāca mahātmānaṃ dharmaputraṃ yudhiṣṭhiram 045.003
sādhu sādhur ayaṃ praśnaḥ śrūyatāṃ bho yudhiṣṭhira
ṣaḍaśītisahasrāṇi yojanānāṃ narādhipa 045.004
yamalokasya cādhvānam antaraṃ mānuṣasya ca
tāmrapātram ivātaptaṃ śūlavyāmiśrakaṇṭakam 045.005
dvādaśādityasaṃkāśaṃ bhairavaṃ duratikramam
na tatra vṛkṣā na cchāyā pānīyaṃ ketanāni ca 045.006
yatra viśramate śrāntaḥ puruṣo 'dhvānako nṛpa
yāmyair dūtair nīyamāno yamasyājñākarair balāt 045.007
avaśyaṃ ca mahārāja sa gantavyo mahāpathaḥ
naraiḥ strībhis tathā tiryaiḥ pṛthivyāṃ jīvasaṃjñakaiḥ 045.008
ekaviṃśac ca narakā yamasya viṣaye smṛtāḥ
ye tu duṣkṛtakarmāṇas te patanti pṛthak pṛthak 045.009
narako rauravo nāma mahāraurava eva ca
kṣuradhārā mahāraudraḥ sūkaras tāla eva ca 045.010
vajrakumbho mahāghoraḥ śālmalo 'tha vimohanaḥ
kīṭādaḥ kṛmibhakṣaś ca śālmaliś ca mahādrumaḥ 045.011
tathā pūyavahaḥ pāpā rudhirāndho mahattamaḥ
agnijvālo mahānādaḥ saṃdāmśaḥ śunabhojanaḥ
tathā vaitaraṇī coṣṇā asipattravanaṃ tathā 045.012
viṣṇos tad vacanaṃ śrutvā papāta bhuvi pāṇḍavaḥ
sa saṃjñaś ca muhūrtena bhūyaḥ keśavam abravīt 045.013
bhītaś cāsmi mahābāho śrutvā mārgasya vistaram
kenopāyena taṃ mārgaṃ taranti puruṣāḥ sukham 045.014
brāhmaṇebhyaḥ pradānāni nānārūpāṇi pārthiva
yo dadyāc chraddhayā yuktaḥ sukhaṃ yāti mahāpatham 045.015
upānahapradā yānti sukhaṃ chāyāsu cchattradāḥ
na teṣām aśubhaṃ kiṃcic śūlādi na ca kaṇṭakāḥ 045.016
upānahau yo dadāti pātrabhūte dvijottame
aśvataryaḥ pradātāram upatiṣṭhanti taṃ naram 045.017
vitṛṣṇāś cāmbudātāras tarpitāś cānnadās tathā
auprāvṛtā vastradāś ca nagnā vai yānty avastradāḥ 045.018
hiraṇyadāḥ sukhaṃ yānti puruṣāḥ svābhyalaṃkṛtāḥ
gopradā yānti ca sukhaṃ vimuktāḥ sarvakilbiṣaiḥ 045.019
bhūmidāḥ sukham adhante sarvakāmaiḥ sutarpitāḥ
yānti caivāparikliṣṭā narāḥ śayyāsanapradāḥ 045.020
tataḥ sukhataraṃ yānti vimāneṣu gṛhapradāḥ
kṣīrapradā hi divyābhiḥ sasarpibhis tathaiva ca 045.021
gopradātā labhet tṛptiṃ tasmin deśe sudurlabhām
ārāmaropī cchāyāsu śītalāsu sukhaṃ vrajet 045.022
sugandhigandhino yānti gandhamālyapradā naraḥ
adattadānā gacchanti padbhyāṃ yānena yānadāḥ
dīpapradāḥ sukhaṃ yānti dīpayantaś ca tatpatham 045.023
vimānair haṃsayuktais tu yānti māsopavāsinaḥ
cakravākaprayuktena pañcarātropavāsinaḥ
tato barhiṇayuktena ṣaḍrātram upavāsinaḥ 045.024
trirātram ekabhaktena kṣapayed yas tu pāṇḍava
anantaraṃ ca yo 'śnīyāt tasya lokā yathā mama 045.025
panīyaṃ paralokeṣu pāvanaṃ paramaṃ smṛtam
pānīyasya pradānena tṛptir bhavati śāśvatī
pānīyasya guṇā divyāḥ pretaloke sukhāvahāḥ 045.026
tatra puṇyodakā nāma nadī teṣāṃ pravartate
śītalaṃ salilaṃ tatra pibanti hy amṛtopamam 045.027
ye ca duṣkṛtakarmāṇaḥ pūyaṃ teṣāṃ pravartate
eṣā nadī mahārāja sarvakāmadughā śubhā 045.028
adhvani khinnagātras tu dvijo yaḥ kṣuttṛṣṇānvitaḥ
pṛcchan sadānnadātāram abhyeti gṛham āśayā
taṃ pūjaya prayatnena so 'tithir brāhmaṇaḥ smṛtaḥ 045.029
pitaro devatāś caiva ṛṣayaś ca tapodhanāḥ
pūjitāḥ pūjite tasmin nirāśe tu nirāśakāḥ 045.*(50)
tam eva gacchantam anuvrajanti devāś ca sarve pitaras tathaiva
tasmin dvije pūjite pūjitās te gate nirāśe pratiyānti nāśam 045.030
ahany ahani dātavyaṃ brāhmaṇebhyo yudhiṣṭhira
āgamiṣyati yat pātraṃ tat pātraṃ tārayiṣyati 045.*(51)
na tathā haviṣo homair na puṣpair nānulepanaiḥ
agnau vā suhute rājan yathā hy atithipūjane 046.001
kapilāyāṃ tu dattāyāṃ yat phalaṃ jyeṣṭhapuṣkare
tat phalaṃ pāṇḍavaśreṣṭha viprāṇāṃ pādaśaucane 046.002
dvijapādodakaklinnā yāvat tiṣṭhati medinī
tāvat puṣkarapātreṣu pibanti pitaro jalam 046.003
devamālyāpanayanaṃ dvijocchiṣṭāpamārjanam
śrāntasaṃvāhanaṃ caiva dīnasya paripālanam
ekaikaṃ pāṇḍavaśreṣṭha gopradānād viśiṣyate 046.004
pādaśaucaṃ tathābhyaṅgaṃ dīpam annaṃ pratiśrayam
dadanti ye mahārāja nopasarpanti te yamam 046.005
svāgatenāgnayaḥ prītā āsanena śatakratuḥ
pitaraḥ pādaśaucena annādyena prajāpatiḥ 046.006
abhayasya pradānena bhavet prītir mamātulā 046.*(52)
yeṣāṃ taḍāgāni bahūdakāni prapāś ca kūpāś ca pratiśrayāś ca
annapradānaṃ madhurā ca vāṇī yamasya te nirvacanā bhavanti 046.007
savṛṣaṃ gośataṃ tena dattaṃ bhavati śāśvatam 046.008
pāpaṃ karma ca yat kiṃcid brahmahatyāsamaṃ bhavet
śochayet kapilāṃ dattvā etad vai nātra saṃśayaḥ 046.009
prāsādā yatra sauvarṇā vasordhārā ca syandate
gandharvāpsaraso yatra tatra gacchanti gopradāḥ 046.010
prayacchate yaḥ kapilāṃ savatsāṃ kāṃsyopadohāṃ kanakāgraśṛṅgīm
yān yān hi kāmān abhivāñchate 'sau tāṃs tān avāpnoty amalāṃś ca lokān 046.011
yāvad vatsasya dvau pādau śiraś caiva pradṛśyate
tāvad gauḥ pṛthivī jñeyā yāvad garbhaṃ na muñcati
tasmin kāle pradātavyā vidhinā yā mayoditā 046.012
antarikṣagato vatso yāvad yonyāṃ pradṛśyate
tāvad gauḥ pṛthivī jñeyā yāvad garbhaṃ na muñcati 046.013
yāvanti tasya romāṇi tāvadvarṣāṇi mānavaḥ
gandharvāpsarasodgītaiḥ svargaloke mahīyate 046.014
haṃsayuktena yānena yuktenāpsarasāṃ gaṇaiḥ 046.*(53)
tiladhenuṃ pravakṣyāmi yaś cāsyā vidhir uttamaḥ
suvarṇanābhiṃ yaḥ kṛtvā sukhūraṃ kṛṣṇamārgaṇām 046.015
kutapaprastarasthāṃ tu tilāṃ kṛtvā prayatnataḥ
tilaiḥ prasthādi tāṃ dadyāt sarvaratnair alaṃkṛtām 046.016
sasamudradrumā caiva saśailavanakānanā
caturantā bhaved dattā pṛthivī nātra saṃśayaḥ 046.017
kṛṣṇājine tilāṃ kṛtvā kṛṣṇāṃ vā yadi vetarām
prīyatāṃ dharmarājeti yad vā manasi vartate
yāvaj jīvakṛtaṃ pāpaṃ tena dānena pūyate 046.018
rājateṣu tu pātreṣu koṇeṣu madhusarpiṣī 046.*(54)
dhanaṃ prāpnoti puṇyena maunenājñāṃ prayacchati
upabhogaṃ tu dānena jīvitaṃ brahmacaryayā 047.001
ahiṃsayā paraṃ rūpam dīkṣayā kulajanma ca
phalamūlāśanād rājyaṃ svargaḥ parṇāśano bhavet 047.002
payobhakṣa divaṃ yānti snānena draviṇādhikāḥ
śākaṃ sādhayato rājyaṃ nākapṛṣṭham anāśanāt 047.003
sthaṇḍile ca śayānasya gṛhāṇi śayanāni ca
cīravalkaladhāriṇāṃ vastrāṇy ābharaṇāni ca 047.004
śayanāsanayānāni ye gatā hi tapovanam
agnipraveśī niyataṃ brahmaloke mahīyate 047.005
rasānāṃ pratisaṃhārāt saubhāgyam abhijāyate
āmiṣapratiṣedhāt tu bhavaty āyuṣmatī prajā 047.006
udavāsaṃ vased yas tu nāgānām adhipo bhavet
satyavādī naraśreṣṭha devataih saha modate 047.007
kīrtir bhavati dānena ārogyaṃ cāpy ahiṃsayā
dvijaśuśrūṣayā rājyaṃ divyarūpam avāpnute 047.008
dvijaśuśrūṣayā rājyaṃ dvijatvaṃ cāpi puṣkalam 047.*(55)
annapānapradānena kāmabhogais tu tṛpyate
dīpālokapradānena cakṣuṣmāñ jāyate naraḥ 047.009
gandhamālyapradānena tuṣṭir bhavati puṣkalā
keśaśmaśrūn dhārayato hy agrā bhavati saṃtatiḥ 047.010
vākśaucaṃ manasaḥ śaucaṃ yac ca śaucaṃ jalāśrayam
tribhiḥ śaucair upeto yaḥ sa svargī nātra saṃśayaḥ 047.011
tāmrāyasānāṃ bhaṇḍānāṃ dātā ratnādhipo bhavet
labhate tu paraṃ sthānaṃ balavān puṣyate sadā 047.012
dhānyaṃ krameṇārjitavittasaṃcayaṃ vipre suśīle te prayacchate yaḥ
vasuṃdharā tasya bhavet sutuṣṭā dhārā vasūnāṃ pratimuñcatīha 048.001
puṣpopabhogaṃ ca phalopabhogaṃ yaḥ pādapaṃ sparśayate dvijāya
sa śrīsamṛddhaṃ bahuratnapūrṇaṃ labhaty adhiṣṭhānavaraṃ samṛddham 048.002
indhanāni ca yo dadyād dvijebhyaḥ śiśirāgame
kāyāgnidīptiṃ saubhāgyam aiśvaryaṃ cādhigacchati 048.003
chattrapradānena gṛhaṃ variṣṭhaṃ rathaṃ tathopānahasaṃpradānāt
dhuryapradānena gavām tathaiva lokān avāpnoti puraṃdarasya
svargīyam apy āha hiraṇyadānam tathā variṣṭhaṃ kanakapradānam 048.004
naiveśikaṃ sarvaguṇopapannaṃ prayacchate yaḥ puruṣo dvijāya
svādhyāyacāritraguṇānvitāya tasyāpi lokāḥ pravarā bhavanti 048.005
yo brahmadeyāṃ pradadāti kanyāṃ bhūmipradānaṃ ca karoti vipre
hiraṇyadānaṃ ca tathā viśiṣṭaṃ sa śakro lokaṃ labhate durāpam 048.006
sucitravastrābharaṇopadhānaṃ dadyān naro yaḥ śayanaṃ dvijāya
rūpānvitāṃ dakṣavatīṃ manojñāṃ bhāryām ayatnopacitāṃ labhet saḥ 048.007
lavaṇasya tu dātāras tilānāṃ sarpiṣas tathā
tejasvino 'bhijāyante bhoginaṣ cirajīvinaḥ 048.008
svarge 'psarobhiḥ saha bhuktabhogas tataś cyutaḥ śīlavatīṃ sa bhāryām
rūpānvitāṃ dakṣavatīṃ suraktāṃ sukhena dharmeṇa tathāpi kāle
tasyaiva sārdhaṃ suralokam eti tasyaiva cānyat punar eti janma 048.*(56)
kīdṛgvidhāsv avasthāsu dattaṃ dānaṃ janārdana
ihalokeṣv anubhavet puruṣas tad bravīhi me 049.001
garbhasthāsyāthavā bālye yauvane vārddhake 'pi vā
avasthāṃ kṛṣṇa kathaya paraṃ kautūhalaṃ hi me 049.002
vṛthājanmāni catvāri vṛthādānāni ṣoḍaśa
aputrāṇāṃ vṛthā janma ye ca dharmabahiṣkṛtāḥ
parapākaṃ ca ye 'śnanti paradāraratāś ca ye 049.003
pary asthānaṃ vṛthā dānaṃ sadoṣaṃ parikīrtitam
ārūḍhapatite caiva anyāyopārjitaṃ ca yat 049.004
vyarthaṃ cābrāhmaṇe dānaṃ patite taskare tathā
guroś cāprītijanake kṛtaghne grāmayājake 049.005
brahmabandhau ca yad dattaṃ yad dattaṃ vṛṣalīpatau
vedavikrayiṇe caiva yasya copapatir gṛhe 049.006
strīnirjiteṣu yad dattaṃ vyālagrāhe tathaiva ca
paricārake ca yad dattaṃ vṛthādānāni ṣoḍaśa 049.007
tamovṛtas tu yo dadyād bhayāt krodhāt tathaiva ca
vṛthā dānaṃ tu tat sarvaṃ bhuṅkte garbhastha eva tu 049.008
serṣyāmanyumanāś caiva dambhārthaṃ cārthakāraṇāt
yo dadāti dvijātibhyaḥ sa bālatve tad aśnute 049.009
yaḥ śuddhiḥ prayato bhūtvā prasannamānasendriyaḥ
pradadāti dvijātibhyo yauvanasthas tad aśnute 049.*(58)
deśe deśe ca pātre ca yo dadāti dvijātiṣu
manasā parituṣṭena yauvanasthas tad aśnute 049.010
tasmāt sarvāsv avasthāsu sarvadānāni pārthiva
dātavyāni dvijātibhyaḥ svargamargam abhīpsatā 049.011
trailokya kṛṣṇa bhūtānāṃ sarvalokātmako hy asi
nR̥ṇāṃ yaduvaraśreṣṭha tuṣyase kena karmaṇā 050.001
brāhmaṇaiḥ pūjitair nityaṃ pūjito 'haṃ na saṃśayaḥ
nirbhartsitaiś ca nirbhagnas tasyāhaṃ sarvakarmasu 050.002
viprāparā gatir mahyaṃ yas tān pūjayate nṛpa
tam ahaṃ tena rūpeṇa prapaśyāmi yudhiṣṭhira 050.003
kāṇāḥ kubjāś ca khañjāś ca daridrā vyādhitāś ca ye
nāvamanyed dvijān prājño mama rūpaṃ hitaṃ tathā 050.004
bahavo 'pi na jānante narā jñānabahiṣkṛtāḥ
yathāhaṃ dvijarūpeṇa carāmi pṛthivītale 050.005
ye kecit sāgarāntāyāṃ pṛthivyāṃ kīrtitā dvijāḥ
tad rūpaṃ hi paraṃ mahyaṃ yo 'rcayed arcayet tu saḥ 050.006
tadrūpān ghnanti ye viprān vikarmasu ca yuñjanti
apreṣaṇe preṣayanto dāsatvaṃ kārayanti hi 050.007
mṛtāṃs tān karapattrena yamadūtā mahābalāḥ
nikṛntanti yathā kāṣṭhaṃ sūtramārgeṇa śilpinaḥ 050.008
ye caivāślakṣṇayā vācā tarjayanti narādhamāḥ
vadanti krodhaniḥsparśaṃ pādenābhihananti ca 050.009
mṛtāṃs tān yamalokeṣu nihatya dharaṇītale
uraḥ pādena cākramya krodhasaṃraktalocanaḥ
agnivarṇaiś ca saṃdaṃśair jihvām uddharate yamaḥ 050.010
pāpāś ca nārake vahnau dhāsyante yamakiṃkaraiḥ 050.*(59)
ye tu viprān nirīkṣanti pāpāḥ pāpena cakṣuṣā
abrahmaṇyāḥ śruter bāhyā nityaṃ brahmadviṣo narāḥ 050.011
teṣāṃ ghorā mahākāyā vajratuṇḍā bhayānakāḥ
uddharanti muhūrtena cakṣuḥ kākā yamājñayā 050.012
yas tāḍayati viprāṃs tu kṣataṃ kuryāt saśoṇitam
asthibhaṅgaṃ ca yaḥ kuryāt prāṇair vāpi viyojayet 050.013
brahmaghnaḥ so 'nupūrveṇa narake vasudhādhipa
kīlair vinihataḥ pāpo mīrāyāṃ pacyate bhṛśam 050.014
subahūni sahasrāṇi varṣāṇāṃ kleśabhāg bhavet
ravān muñcati durbuddhir na tasmai niṣkṛtiḥ smṛtā 050.015
tasmād viprā naraśreṣṭha namaskāryāś ca nityaśaḥ
annapānapradānais tu pūjārhāḥ satataṃ dvijāḥ 050.016
āmantrayitvā yo viprān gandhair mālyaiś ca mānavaḥ
tarpayec chraddhayā yuktaḥ sa mām arcayate sadā
sa māṃ prasādayec caiva sa ca māṃ paritoṣayet 050.017
tapodamānviteṣv eva nityaṃ pūjāṃ prayojayet 050.*(60)
ye brāhmaṇāḥ so 'ham asaṃśayaṃ nṛpa teṣv arciteṣv arcito 'haṃ yathāvat
teṣv eva tuṣṭeṣv aham eva tuṣṭo vairaṃ ca tair yasya mamāpi vairam 050.018
sugandhidhūpādibhir abhyarcya vipraṃ 050.*(61),001
tam acyutaṃ nārcayate sadaiva 050.*(61),002
yo bhakṣatoyādibhir annapānair 050.*(61),003
anulepācamanapradānaiḥ 050.*(61),004
yaḥ pūjayed bhojayitvā dvijāgryān 050.*(61),005
saṃpūjayitvā paritoṣayec ca 050.*(61),006
arghyādinā ye 'bhipūjya pūjayanti sadācyutam 050.*(61),007
tenaiva mām eva sadā pūjayanti na saṃśayaḥ 050.*(61),008
virūpāś ca surūpāś ca vijanān niṣkalān api 050.*(61),009
kṛpayā bhāvitātmāno ye 'rcayanti dvijottamān 050.*(61),010
anasūyā hitātmāno viprān ārādhate kvacit 050.*(61),011
asaṃśayaṃ sadā bhaktyā mām evārcayate hi saḥ 050.*(61),012
tataḥ pavitram atulaṃ na puṇyam adhikaṃ tataḥ 050.*(61),013
yaś candanaiḥ sāgarugandhamālyair abhyarcayed dārumayīṃ mamārcām
nāsau mamārcām arcayate 'rcayan vai viprārcanād arcita eva cāham 050.019
vipraprasādān madha eva cāhaṃ vipraprasādād asurāñ jayāmi
vipraprasādāt puruṣottamatvaṃ vipraprasādād ajito 'smi nityam 050.020
sāyaṃ prātaś ca yaḥ saṃdhyām upāste 'skannamānasaḥ
japan hi pāvanīṃ devīṃ gāyatrīṃ vedamātaram 051.001
sa tayā pāvito devyā brāhmaṇaḥ pūtakilbiṣaḥ
na sīdet pratigṛhṇānaḥ pṛthivīṃ tu sasāgarām 051.002
ye cānye dāruṇāḥ kecid grahāḥ sūryādayo divi
te cāsya saumyā jāyante śivāḥ śivatamāh sadā 051.003
yatratatragataṃ cainaṃ dāruṇāḥ piśitāśanāḥ
ghorarūpā mahākāyā na karṣanti dvijottamam 051.004
yāvantaś ca pṛthivyāṃ hi cīrṇavedavratā dvijāḥ
acīrṇavratavedā vā vikarmapatham āśritāḥ 051.005
teṣāṃ tu pāvanārthaṃ hi nityam eva yudhiṣṭhira
dve saṃdhye hy upatiṣṭheta tad askannaṃ mahāvratam 051.006
nāsti kiṃcin naravyāghra duṣkṛtaṃ brāhmaṇasya tu
yatra sthitaḥ sadādhyātme dve saṃdhye hy upatiṣṭhati 051.007
pūrṇāhutiṃ vā prāpnoti juhute ca trayo 'ghnayaḥ
dahanti duṣkṛtaṃ tasya agnayo nātra saṃśayaḥ 051.008
evaṃ sarvasya viprasya kilbiṣaṃ nirdahāmy aham
ubhe saṃdhye hy upāsinas tasmāt sarvaśucir dvijaḥ 051.009
daive pitrye ca yatnena niyoktavyo 'jugupsitaḥ
jugupsitas tu tac chrāddhaṃ dahaty agnir ivendhanam 051.010
purāṇaṃ mānavā dharmāḥ sāṅgo vedaś cikitsitam
ājñāsiddhāni catvāri na hantavyāni hetubhiḥ
hatvā hy etāni saṃmūḍhaḥ kalpaṃ tamasi pacyate 052.001
na brāhmaṇaṃ parīkṣeta śrāddhakāle hy upasthite
sumahān parivādo hi brāhmaṇānāṃ parīkṣaṇe 052.002
kāṇāḥ kuṇṭhāś ca ṣaṇḍāś ca daridrā vyādhitās tathā
sarve śrāddhe niyoktavyā miśritā vedapāragaiḥ
akṣayaṃ tu bhavec chrāddham etad dharmavido viduḥ 052.003
brāhmaṇo hi mahad bhūtaṃ janmanā saha jāyate
lokā lokeśvarāś cāpi sarve brāhmaṇapūjakāḥ 052.004
brāhmaṇāḥ kupitā hanyur bhasma kuryuś ca tejasā
lokān anyān sṛjeyuś ca lokapālāṃs tathāparān 052.005
brāhmaṇā hi mahātmāno virajāḥ svargasaṃkramāḥ
brāhmaṇānāṃ parīvādād asurāḥ salileśayāḥ 052.006
apeyaḥ sāgaro yais tu kṛtaḥ kopān mahātmabhiḥ
yeṣāṃ kopāgnir adyāpi daṇḍake nopaśāmyati 052.007
ete svargasya netāro bhūmidevāḥ sanātanāḥ
ebhiś cādhikṛtaḥ panthā devayānaḥ sa ucyate 052.008
te pūjyās te namaskāryās teṣu sarvaṃ pratiṣṭhitam
te vai lokān imān sarvān dhārayanti parasparam 052.009
pramāṇaṃ sarvalokānāṃ niyatā brahmacāriṇaḥ
tān apāśritya tiṣṭhante trayo lokāḥ sanātanāḥ 052.010
gūḍhasvādhyāyatapaso brāhmaṇāḥ saṃśitavratāḥ
vidyāsnātā vratasnātā anapāśrityajīvinaḥ 052.011
āśīviṣā iva kruddhā upacaryā hi brāhmaṇāḥ
tapasā dīpyamānās te daheyuḥ sāgarān api 052.012
brāhmaṇeṣu ca tuṣṭeṣu tuṣyante sarvadevatāḥ
brāhmaṇānāṃ namaskāraiḥ sūryo divi virājate
brāhmaṇānāṃ parīvādāt pateyur api devatāḥ 052.013
dhuri ye nāvasīdanti praṇīte yajñavahnayaḥ
bhojanācchādanair dānais tārayanti tapodhanāḥ 052.014
te gatiḥ sarvabhūtānām adhyātmagaticintakāḥ
ādimadhyāvasānānāṃ jñānānāṃ chinnasāmśayāḥ 052.015
parāparaviśeṣajñā netāraḥ paramāṃ gatim
avadhyā brāhmaṇās tasmāt pāpeṣv api ratāḥ sadā 052.016
yaś ca sarvam idaṃ hanyād brāhmaṇaṃ vāpi tatsamam 052.017
so 'gniḥ so 'rko mahātejā viṣaṃ bhavati kopitaḥ
bhūtānāṃ agrabhug vipro varṇaśreṣṭhaḥ pitā guruḥ 052.018
na skandate na vyathate na ca naśyati karhicit
variṣṭham agnihotrād dhi brāhmaṇasya mukhe hutam 052.019
avidyo vā savidyo vā brāhmaṇo mama daivatam
praṇītaś cāpraṇītaś ca yathāgnir daivataṃ mahat 052.020
evaṃ vidvān avidvān vā brāhmaṇo daivataṃ mahat 052.*(63)
śmaśāneṣv api tejasvī pāvako naiva duṣyati
havyakavyavyapeto 'pi brāhmaṇo naiva duṣyati 052.021
sarvathā brāhmaṇāḥ pūjyāḥ sarvathā daivataṃ mahat
tasmāt sarvaprayatnena rakṣed āpatsu brāhmaṇān
śakro 'pi hi dvijendrāṇāṃ bibheti vibudhādhipaḥ 052.022
dānaṃ devāḥ praśaṃsanti iti dharmavido viduḥ
nānādānavidhiṃ tasmāc śṛṇuṣva susamāhitaḥ 053.001
hiraṇyadānaṃ godānaṃ pṛthivīdānam eva ca
etāni vai pavitrāṇi tārayanti paratra ca 053.002
yad yad iṣṭatamaṃ loke yac cāsti dayitaṃ gṛhe
tat tad guṇavate deyaṃ tad evākṣayam icchatā 053.003
suvarṇadānaṃ godānaṃ pṛthivīdānam eva ca
etat prayacchamāno vai sarvapāpaiḥ pramucyate 053.004
yad dadāsi viśiṣṭebhyo yac cāśnāsi dine dine
tat te vittam ahaṃ manye śeṣaṃ kasyāpi rakṣasi 053.005
tulyanāmāni śastāni trīṇi tulyaphalāni ca
nityaṃ deyāni rājendra gāvaḥ pṛthvī sarasvatī 053.006
tadvaj jalam amitraghna tat tulyaphalanāmataḥ
dattvā tṛptim avāpnoti yatratatrābhijāyate 053.007
saṃkalpavihito yo 'rtho brāhmaṇebhyaḥ pradīyate
arthibhyo hy arthahetubhyo manasvī tena jāyate 053.008
sīdate dvijamukhyāya yo 'rthine na prayacchati
amarthe sati durbuddhir narakāyopapadyate 053.009
dhenavo 'naḍuhaś caiva chattraṃ vastram upānahau
deyāni yācamānebhyaḥ pānam annaṃ tathaiva ca
evaṃ dānaṃ samuddiṣṭaṃ vyuṣṭimat tārakaṃ param 053.010
eṣa te vihito yajñaḥ śraddhāpūtaḥ sadakṣiṇaḥ
viśiṣṭaḥ sa ca yajñeṣu dadatām anasūyayā 053.011
dānavidbhiḥ kṛtaḥ panthā yena yānti manīṣiṇaḥ
yair dānais tarpayiṣyanti śraddhāpūtair dvijottamān 053.012
yathā hi sukṛte kṣetre phalaṃ vindati kṣetrikaḥ
evaṃ dattvā brāhmaṇebhyo dātā phalam upāśnute 053.013
brāhmaṇāś caiva vidyante satyavanto bahuśrutāḥ
na dadāti ca dānāni moghaṃ tasya dhanārjanam 053.014
utthāyotthāya boddhavyaṃ kim adya sukṛtaṃ mayā
dattaṃ vā dāpitaṃ vāpi votsāhyam api vā kṛtam 053.015
utthāyotthāya dātavyaṃ brāhmaṇebhyo yudhiṣṭhira
āgamiṣyati yat pātraṃ tat pātraṃ tārayiṣyati 053.016
yac ca vedamayaṃ pātraṃ yac ca pātraṃ tapomayam
asaṃkīrṇaṃ ca yat pātraṃ tat pātraṃ tārayiṣyati 053.017
adhyāyaṃ tapaso vakṣye tan me nigadataḥ śṛṇu
tapaso hi paraṃ nāsti tapasā vindate phalam 054.001
ṛṣayas tapa āsthāya modante daivataiḥ saha
tapasā prāpyate svargaṃ tapasā prāpyate yaśaḥ 054.002
āyuḥprakarṣaṃ bhogāṃś ca tapasā vindate naraḥ
jñānaṃ vijñānam āstikyaṃ saubhāgyaṃ rūpam uttamam 054.003
tapasā labhyate sarvaṃ manasā yad yad icchati
nātaptatapaso yānti brahmalokaṃ kadācana 054.004
yat kāryaṃ kiṃcid āsthāya puruṣas tapyate tapaḥ
sarvaṃ tat samavāpnoti paratreha ca mānavaḥ 054.005
surāpaḥ pāradārī ca bhrūṇahā gurutalpagaḥ
tapasā tarate sarvaṃ sarvataś ca vimucyate 054.006
api sarveśvaraḥ sthāṇur viṣṇuś caiva sanātanaḥ
brahmā hutāśanaḥ śakras tapasyanti sanātanāḥ 054.007
ṣaḍaśītisahasrāṇi munīnām ūrdhvaretasām
tapasā divi modante sametā daivataiḥ saha 054.008
tapasā prāpyate rājyaṃ śakraḥ sarvasureśvaraḥ
tapasā pālayan sarvam ahany ahani vṛtrahā 054.009
sūryācandramasau devau sarvalokahite ratau
tapasaiva prakāśete nakṣatrāṇi grahās tathā 054.010
na cāsti tat sukhaṃ loke yad vinā tapasā kila
tapasaiva sukhaṃ sarvam iti dharmavido viduḥ 054.011
viśvāmitraś ca tapasā brāhmaṇatvam upāgataḥ 054.*(64)
sarvaṃ ca tapasābhyeti sarvaṃ ca sukham aśnute
tapas tapyati yo 'raṇye munir mūlaphalāśanaḥ
ṛcam ekāṃ api paṭhan sa yāti paramāṃ gatim 054.012
tasmāt tapaḥ samāsthāya prārthayed yad abhīpsitam 054.*(65)
satyam eva paraṃ brahma satyam eva paraṃ tapaḥ
satyam eva paro yajñaḥ satyam eva paraṃ śrutam
satyaṃ deveṣu jāgarti muktiḥ satyataroḥ phalam 055.001
tapo yaśaś ca puṇyaṃ ca pitṛdevarṣipūjanam
ādyo vidhiś ca vidyā ca sarvaṃ satye pratiṣṭhitam 055.002
satyaṃ yajñas tathā vedā mantrā devī sarasvatī
vratacaryā tathā satyam oṃkāraḥ satyam eva ca 055.003
satyena vāyur abhyeti satyena tapate raviḥ
satyena cāgnir dahati svargaṃ satyena gacchati
satyena cāpaḥ kṣipati parjanyaḥ pṛthivītale 055.004
pāraṇaṃ sarvavedānāṃ sarvatīrthāvagahanah
satyaṃ ca vadato loke tat samaṃ syān na saṃśayaḥ 055.005
aśvamedhasahasraṃ ca satyaṃ ca tulayā dhṛtam
aśvamedhasahasrād dhi satyam etad viśiṣyate 055.006
munayaḥ satyaniratā munayaḥ satyavikramāḥ
munayaḥ satyaprapathāḥ parāṃ siddhim ito gatāḥ 055.*(66)
satyena devāḥ prīyante pitaro brāhmaṇās tathā
satyam āhuḥ paraṃ dharmaṃ tasmāt satyaṃ na lopayet 055.007
munayaḥ satyaniratās tasmāt satyaṃ viśiṣyate
svarge satyaparā nityaṃ modante devatā iva 055.008
apsarogaṇasaṃkīrṇair vimānair upayānti te
vaktavyaṃ hi sadā satyaṃ na satyād vidyate param 055.009
etat pramāṇaṃ yaḥ kuryāt sarvayajñaphalaṃ labhet 055.*(67)
agādhe vimale śuddhe satyatīrthe hrade śubhe
snātavyaṃ manasā yuktaiḥ snānaṃ tat paramaṃ smṛtam 055.010
ātmārthe ca parārthe vā putrārthe vāpi pārthiva
ye 'nṛtaṃ nābhibhāṣante te narāḥ svargagāminaḥ 055.011
api cedaṃ purā gītaṃ dharmavidbhir yudhiṣṭhira
yaḥ satyavādī puruṣo nānṛtaṃ paribhāṣate 055.012
saṃprāpya virajāṃl lokān uṣitvā śāśvatīḥ samāḥ
śucīnāṃ śrīmatāṃ gehe jāyate sumahāmatiḥ 055.013
vidyārogyasukhaiśvaryair yukto yogaparo bhavet 055.*(68)
ādityacandrāv analānilau ca dyaur bhūmir āpo hṛdayaṃ yamaś ca
ahaś ca rātriś ca ubhe ca saṃdhye dharmaś ca jānāti narasya vṛttam 055.014
tasmān na vācyam anṛtaṃ hi sadbhir evaṃvidhair dharmavido vadanti
satyaṃ vadaṃs tejasā dīpyamāno na hīyate dharmayaśo 'rthakāmaiḥ 055.015
eṣa vāṇīkṛto dharmo vaidiko dharmaniścaye
evam etad yathānyāyaṃ satyādhyāye prakīrtitam
tat pramāṇaṃ budhaḥ kuryān na satyād vidyate param 055.016
sarveṣām eva varṇānāṃ pravakṣyāmi yudhiṣṭhira
upoṣitaiś ca kaunteya yat prayojyaṃ yathāvidhi 056.001
phalaṃ yad upavāsasya tan nibodha ca pāṇḍava
avāpnoti yathā kāmān upavāsaparāyaṇaḥ 056.002
mayaite nṛpate kāmyā vihitā hitam icchatā
upavāsā manuṣyāṇāṃ mayy evārpitacetasām 056.003
pañcamīṃ caiva ṣaṣṭhīṃ ca paurṇamāsīṃ ca pāṇḍava
upoṣya rūpavān dhanyaḥ subhagaś caiva jāyate 056.004
aṣṭamīṃ caiva kaunteya śuklapakṣe caturdaśīm
upoṣya vyādhirahito vīryavāṃś caiva jāyate 056.005
mārgaśīrṣaṃ tu yo māsaṃ nityam ekāśano bhavet
kṛṣibhāgī bhaved rājan bahuputraś ca jāyate 056.006
pauṣamāse tu rājendra bhaktenaikena yaḥ kṣapet
subhago darśanīyaś ca jñānabhāgī ca jāyate 056.007
pitR̥n uddiśya māghaṃ tu yaḥ kṣaped ekabhojanam
māsena puruṣavyāghra so 'nantyaṃ phalam aśnute 056.008
bhagadaivatamāsaṃ tu yaḥ kṣaped ekabhojanam
strīṣu vallabhatāṃ yāti vaśyāś cāsya bhavanti tāḥ 056.009
caitraṃ tu puruṣavyāghra yaḥ kṣaped ekabhojanam 056.010
māsena puruṣavyāghra maunan tu phalam aśnute (?)
bhagadaivatamāsaṃ tu yaḥ kṣaped ekabhojanaḥ
strīṣu vallabhatāṃ yāti vaśyāś cāsya bhavanti tāḥ
caitraṃ tu puruṣavyāghra yaḥ kṣaped ekabhojanaḥ 056.*(69)
suvarṇamaṇimuktāḍhye kule mahati jāyate 056.010,*(69)
nistared ekabhaktena vaiśākhaṃ yo narādhipa 056.011,*(69)
naro vā yadi vā nārī jñātīnāṃ śreṣṭhatāṃ vrajet 056.011
jyeṣṭhamāsam apānīyam ekabhaktena yaḥ kṣapet
aiśvaryaṃ puruṣavyāghra strībhāgī copajāyate 056.012
āṣāḍhaṃ bharataśreṣṭha ekabhaktena yaḥ kṣapet
śūraś ca bahudhānyaś ca bahuputraś ca jāyate 056.013
śrāvaṇaṃ tu naravyāghra bhaktenaikena yaḥ kṣapet
yatra yatropapadyeta tatra syāj jñātivardhanaḥ 056.014
māsaṃ bhādrapadaṃ rājann ekabhaktena yaḥ kṣapet
dhanāḍhyo vīryavāṃś caiva aiśvaryaṃ pratipadyate 056.015
yaḥ kṣaped ekabhaktena māsam āśvayujaṃ naraḥ
dhanavān vāhanāḍhyaś ca bahuputraś ca jāyate 056.016
kārttikaṃ tu naro māsaṃ nityam ekāśano bhavet
śūraś ca bahubhāryaś ca kīrtimāṃś caiva jāyate 056.017
ete māsā naraśreṣṭha ekabhaktena kīrtitāḥ
tithīnāṃ niyamāṃś caiva tāñ śṛṇuṣva narādhipa 056.018
pakṣe pakṣe caturthaṃ tu bhaktaṃ yaḥ kṣapayen naraḥ
vipulaṃ dhanam āpnoti bhagavān agnir abravīt 056.019
māse māse caturthaṃ tu bhaktam ekaṃ tu yaḥ kṣapet
kṛṣibhāgī yaśobhāgī tejasvī cāpi jāyate 056.020
pakṣe pakṣe trirātraṃ tu yaḥ kṣapen narapuṅgava
gaṇe ghoṣe pure grāme māhātmyaṃ pratipadyate 056.021
māse māse trirātraṃ tu bhaktenaikena yaḥ kṣapet
gaṇādhipatyaṃ labhate niḥsapatnam akaṇṭakam 056.022
yas tu sāyaṃ tathā kalyaṃ bhuṅkte naivāntarā pibet
ahiṃsānirato nityaṃ juhvāno jātavedasam 056.023
ṣaḍbhir eva tu varṣais tu sidhyate nātra saṃśayaḥ
agniṣṭomasya yajñasya phalaṃ prāpnoti mānavaḥ 056.024
aṣṭamena tu bhaktena rājan saṃvatsaraṃ nayet
gavāmayasya yajñasya phalaṃ prāpnoti mānavaḥ 056.025
haṃsasārasayuktena vimānena sa gacchati
pūrṇaṃ varṣasahasraṃ tu svargaloke mahīyate 056.026
ārto vā vyādhito vāpi gacched anaśanaṃ tu yaḥ
pade pade yajñaphalaṃ tasya mannāmakīrtanāt 056.027
divyaṛkṣaprayuktena vimānena sa gacchati
śatam apsarasāṃ caiva ramayantīha taṃ naram 056.028
sahasraśatasaṃyukte vimāne sūryavarcase
ārūḍhastrīśatākīrṇe viharan sukham edhate 056.029
na kruddho vyādhito nārtaḥ prasannamanasendriyaḥ
gacched anaśanaṃ yas tu tasyāpi śṛṇu yat phalam 056.030
śataṃ varṣasahasrāṇāṃ svargaloke mahīyate
svasthaḥ saphalasaṃkalpaḥ sukhī vigatakalmaṣaḥ
strīsahasrasamākīrṇe suprabhe sukham edhate 056.031
yāvanti romakūpāni tasya gātreṣu bhārata
tāvadvarṣasahasrāṇi divyāni divi modate 056.032
nāsti vedāt paraṃ śāstraṃ nāsti mātṛsamo guruḥ
na dharmāt paramo lābhas tapo nānaśanāt param 056.033
brāhmaṇebhyaḥ paraṃ nāsti divi ceha ca pāvanam
upavāsais tathā tulyaṃ tapo hy anyan na vidyate 056.034
upoṣya vidhivad devās tridivaṃ pratipedire
munayaś ca parāṃ siddhim upavāsair avāpnuvan 056.035
divyaṃ varṣasahasraṃ tu viśvāmitreṇa dhīmatā
kṣāntam ekena bhaktena yena vipratvam āgataḥ 056.036
cyavano jamadagniś ca vasiṣṭho gautamo bhṛguḥ
sarve hy ete divaṃ prāptāḥ kṣamāvanto bahuśrutāḥ
vidhinānena rājendra yo mayā parikīrtitaḥ 056.037
paṭheta yo vai śṛṇuyāc ca bhaktyā na vidyate tasya narasya pāpam
upadravair mucyate sarvāṅgikair na cāpi pāpair abhibhūyate naraḥ 056.038
brāhmaṇatvaṃ suduṣprāpaṃ nisargād brāhmaṇo bhavet
kṣatriyo vāthavā vaiśyo nisargād eva jāyate 057.001
duṣkṛtena tu duṣṭātmā sthānād bhraśyati mānavaḥ
śreṣṭhaṃ sthānaṃ samāsādya tasmād rakṣeta paṇḍitaḥ 057.002
yas tu vipratvam utsṛjya kṣatriyatvaṃ niṣevate
brāhmaṇyāt sa paribhraṣṭaḥ kṣatrayonyāṃ prasūyate 057.003
vaiśyakarmāṇi vā kurvan vaiśyayonau prajāyate
śūdrakarmāṇi kurvāṇaḥ śūdratvam upapadyate 057.004
sa tatra durgatiṃ prāpya sthānād bhraṣṭo yudhiṣṭhira
śūdrayonim anuprāpto yadi dharmaṃ na sevate 057.005
mānuṣyāt sa paribhraṣṭas tiryagyonau prajāyate
adharmasevanān mūḍhas tamopahatacetanaḥ 057.006
jātyantarasahasrāṇi tatraiva parivartate
tasmāt prāpya śubhaṃ sthānaṃ pramādān na tu nāśayet 057.007
śūdrānnenāvaśeṣeṇa yo mriyej jaṭhare dvijaḥ
āhitāgnis tathā yajvā sa śūdragatibhāg bhavet 057.008
kṣatrānnenāvaśeṣeṇa kṣatratvam upapadyate
vaiśyānnenāvaśeṣeṇa vaiśyatvam upapadyate
tāṃ yoniṃ labhate vipro bhuktvānnaṃ yasya vai mṛtaḥ 057.009
brāhmaṇatvaṃ śubhaṃ prāpya durlabhaṃ yo 'vamanyate
bhojyābhojyaṃ na jānāti sa bhavet kṣatriyo dvijaḥ 057.010
karmaṇā yena medhāvī śūdro vaiśyo 'bhijāyate
tat te vakṣyāmi nikhilaṃ yena varṇottamo bhavet 057.011
śūdrakarma yathoddiṣṭaṃ śūdro bhūtvā samācaret
yathāvat paricaryāṃ tu triṣu varṇeṣu nityadā
kurute 'vimanā yas tu sa śūdro vaiśyatāṃ vrajet 057.012
kṣatriyatvaṃ yathā vaiśyas tad vakṣyāmy anupūrvaśaḥ
caukṣaḥ pāpajanadveṣṭā śeṣānnakṛtabhojanaḥ 057.013
agnihotram upādāya juhvānaś ca yathāvidhi
sa vaiśyaḥ kṣatriyakule jāyate nātra saṃśayaḥ 057.014
kṣatriyo brahmayonyāṃ tu jāyate śṛṇu tad yathā
dadāti yajate yajñair vidhivac cāptadakṣiṇaiḥ
adhīte svargam anvicchaṃs tretāgniśaraṇaḥ sadā 057.015
ārtahastaprado nityaṃ prajā dharmeṇa pālayan
ṛtukāle tu svāṃ bhāryām abhigacchan vidhānataḥ 057.016
sarvātithyaṃ trivargasya dīyatāṃ bhujyatām iti
śūdrāṇāṃ yācakānāṃ ca nityaṃ siddhim iti bruvan 057.017
gobrāhmaṇasya cārthāya raṇe cābhimukho hataḥ
tretāgnimantrapūtātmā kṣatriyo brāhmaṇo bhavet
vidhijñaḥ kṣatriyakule yājakaḥ sa tu jāyate 057.018
prāpyate 'vikalaḥ svargo varṇaiḥ satpatham āsthitaiḥ
brāhmaṇatvaṃ suduṣprāpaṃ kṛcchreṇāsādyate naraiḥ
tasmāt sarvaprayatnena rakṣed brāhmaṇyam uttamam 057.019
suvarṇaṃ paramaṃ dānaṃ suvarṇaṃ dakṣiṇā parā
etat pavitraṃ paramam etat svastyayanaṃ mahat 058.001
daśa pūrvāparān vaṃśān ātmānaṃ ca viśāmyate
api pāpaśataṃ kṛtvā dattvā vipreṣu tārayet 058.002
suvarṇaṃ ye prayacchanti narāḥ śuddhena cetasā
devatās te prayacchanti samastā iti naḥ śrutam 058.003
agnir hi devatāḥ sarvāḥ suvarṇaṃ ca hutāśanaḥ
tasmāt suvarṇaṃ dadatā dattāḥ sarvāś ca devatāḥ 058.004
agnyabhāve ca kurvanti vahnisthāneṣu kāñcanam
sarvavedapramāṇajñā vedaśrutinidarśanāt 058.005
ye tv enaṃ jvālayitvāgnim ādityodayanaṃ prati
dadyur vai vratam uddiśya sarvān kāmān avāpnuyuḥ 058.006
suvarṇadaḥ svargaloke kāmān iṣṭān upāśnute
virajāmbarasaṃvītaḥ pariyāti yatas tataḥ 058.007
vimānenārkavarṇena bhāsvareṇa virājatā
apsarogaṇasaṃkīrṇe bhāsvatā svena tejasā 058.008
haṃsabarhiṇayuktena kāmagena narottamaḥ
divyagandhavahaḥ svarge parigacched itas tataḥ 058.009
tasmāt svaśaktyā dātavyaṃ kāñcanaṃ mānavair bhuvi
na hy ataḥ paramaṃ loke sadyaḥ pāpavimocanam 058.010
suvarṇasya tu śuddhasya suvarṇaṃ yaḥ prayacchati
bahūny abdasahasrāṇi svargaloke mahīyate 058.011
lokāṃs tu sṛjatā pūrvaṃ gāvaḥ sṛṣṭāḥ svayaṃbhuvā
prītyarthaṃ sarvabhūtānāṃ tasmāt tā mātaraḥ smṛtāḥ 059.001
tās tu dattvā saurabheyīḥ svargaloke mahīyate
tasmāt tā varṇayiṣyāmi dānaṃ cāsāṃ yathāvidhi 059.002
yādṛśī vidhinā yena dātavyā yādṛśāya ca
dvijāya poṣaṇārthaṃ tu homadhenukṛte na vai 059.003
prathamā gaurakapilā dvitīyā gaurapiṅgalā
tṛtīyā raktakapilā caturthī nīlapiṅgalā
pañcamī śuklapiṅgākṣī ṣaṣṭhī tu śuklapiṅgalā
saptamī citrapiṅgākṣī aṣṭamī babhrurohiṇī
navamī śvetapiṅgākṣī daśamī śvetapiṅgalā
tādṛśā ye 'py anaḍvāhaḥ kapilās te prakīrtitāḥ
brāhmaṇo vāhayet tāṃs tu nānyo varṇaḥ kadācana 059.*(70)
dhenuṃ dattvā suvratāṃ sopadhānāṃ kalyāṇavatsāṃ ca payasvinīṃ ca
yāvanti romāṇi bhavanti dhenvā duhyeta kāmān nṛpa varṣāṇi tāvat 059.004
prayacchate yaḥ kapilāṃ savatsāṃ kāṃsyopadohāṃ kanakāgraśṛṅgīm
tais tair guṇaiḥ kāmdughā hi bhūtvā naraṃ pradātāram upaiti sā gauḥ 059.005
gosahasraṃ tu yo dadyāt sarvakāmair alaṃkṛtam
parāṃ vṛddhiṃ śriyaṃ prāpya svargaloke mahīyate 059.006
daśa cobhayataḥ pretya mātāmahapitāmahaiḥ
gacchet sukṛtināṃ lokān gāvo dattvā yathāvidhi 059.007
dāyādalabdhair arthair yo gavāḥ krītvā prayacchati
tasyāpi cākṣayā lokā bhavantīha paratra ca 059.008
yo dyūtena dhanaṃ jitvā krītvā gāvaḥ prayacchati
sa gacched virajāṃl lokān gopradānaphalārjitān 059.009
pratigṛhya tu yo dadyād gāvaḥ śuddhena cetasā
sa gatvā durgamaṃ sthānam amaraiḥ saha modate 059.010
yaś cātmavikrayaṃ kṛtvā gāvo dadyād yathāvidhi
sa gatvā virajāṃl lokān sukhaṃ vasati devavat 059.011
saṃgrāme yas tanuṃ tyaktvā gāvaḥ krītvā prayacchati
dehavikrayamūlyas tāḥ śāśvatāḥ kāmadohanāḥ 059.012
rūpānvitāḥ śīlavayopapannāḥ sarvāḥ praśastā hi sugandhavatyaḥ
yathā hi gaṅgā saritāṃ variṣṭhā tathārjunīnāṃ kapilā variṣṭhā 059.013
antarjātāḥ sukrayajñānalabdhāḥ prāṇāṃs tyaktvā sodakāḥ sodvahāś ca
kṛcchrotsṛṣṭāḥ poṣaṇāyābhyupetā dvārair etair goviśeṣā variṣṭhāḥ 059.014
tisro rātryaś cāpy upoṣyeha dātā tṛptā gā vai tarpitebhyaḥ prayacchet
vatsaiḥ pītāḥ sopadhānās tryahaṃ ca dattvā gā vai gorasair vartitavyam 059.015
loke jyeṣṭhā lokavṛttāntavṛttā vedair gītāḥ somaniṣyandabhūtāḥ
saumyāḥ puṇyāḥ kāmadāḥ prāṇadāś ca gāvo dattvā sarvadā santi santaḥ 059.016
na caivāsāṃ dānamātraṃ praśastaṃ pātraṃ kālo goviśeṣo vidhiś ca
dṛṣṭvā gāvaḥ pāvakādityabhūtāḥ svādhyāyāḍhye pātravarye viśiṣṭe 059.017
vaitānasthaṃ satyavākyaṃ kṛtajñaṃ goṣu kṣāntaṃ gośaraṇyaṃ suvṛttaṃ
śastaṃ pātraṃ gopradānasya bhūmes tathā suvarṇasya ca sarvakālam 059.018
bhikṣādānaṃ cādhikaṃ saṃpraśastaṃ pāthodānaṃ cānnadānaṃ tathā ca 059.*(71)
bhikṣate bahubhṛtyāya śrotriyāyāhitāgnaye
dātavyā gauḥ prayatnena ekāpy atiphalā hi sā 059.019
tāṃ ced vikrīṇate rājan vacasā kaluṣīkṛtām
nāsau praśasyate vipro brāhmaṇo naiva sa smṛtaḥ 059.020
tasyādharmapravṛttasya lubdhasyānṛtavādinaḥ
havyakavyavyapetasya na deyā gauḥ kathaṃcana 059.021
jīrṇāṃ caivopabhuktāṃ ca jaratkūpam ivāphalām
tamaḥ praviśate dātā dvijaṃ kleśena yojayan 059.022
duṣṭāḥ kṛśāś caiva pālayatīś ca naitādṛśā dānayogyā bhavanti
kleśair vipraṃ yo 'phalaiḥ saṃyunakti gacchet sa tiryag viphalāṃś ca lokān 059.023
anaḍvāhaṃ suvrataṃ yo dadāti halasya voḍhāram anantavīryam
yugaṃdharaṃ balavantaṃ yuvānaṃ prāpnoti lokān daśadhenudasya 059.024
prayacchate yaḥ puruṣo dvijāya svādhyāyacāritraguṇānvitāya
balena yuktaṃ vṛṣabhaṃ tu nīlaṃ ṣaḍāṅgavaṃ prītikaraṃ surūpam 059.025
yuvānaṃ balinaṃ śyāmaṃ śatena saha yūthapam
gavendraṃ brāhmaṇendrāya bhūriśṛṅgam alaṃkṛtam 059.026
vṛṣabhaṃ ye prayacchanti śrotriyāyāhitāgnaye
aiśvarye te 'bhijāyante jāyamānāḥ punaḥ punaḥ 059.027
te gatvā tadgavāṃ lokaṃ devalokān mahattaram
tatra sthitvā tu suciraṃ sarvakāmaiḥ sutarpitāḥ 059.*(72)
sadakṣiṇāṃ kāñcanarūpyaśṛṅgīṃ kāṃsyopadohāṃ kanakottarīyām
dhenuṃ tilānāṃ kanakottarīyām lokā vasūnām acalā bhavanti 059.028
tilālābhe tu yo dadyād ghṛtadhenuṃ yatavrataḥ
sa durgāt tārito dhenvā brahmaloke mahīyate 059.029
ghṛtālābhe tu yo dadyāj jaladhenuṃ yatavrataḥ
sa sarvaṃ tarate durgaṃ jalaṃ divyaṃ samaśnute 059.030
brāhmaṇāś caiva gāvaś ca kulam ekaṃ dvidhākṛtam
ekatra mantrās tiṣṭhanti havir ekatra tiṣṭhati 059.031
upagamya tu yo dadyād gāvaḥ śuddhena cetasā
yāvanti tāsāṃ romāṇi tāvat svarge mahīyate 059.032
śṛṇu tvaṃ me gavāṃ lokā yādṛśā yatra vā sthitāḥ
manojñā ramaṇīyāś ca sarvakāmadughāḥ sadā 059.033
puṇyāḥ pāpaharāś caiva gavāṃ lokā na saṃśayaḥ
atyantasukhinas tatra sarvapāpavivarjitāḥ 059.034
pramodante mahāsthāne narā vigatakalmaṣāḥ
te vrajante vimāneṣu grahā divi gatā iva 059.035
evaṃ yair dattasatkārāḥ surabhyaś cārcitāḥ sadā
kāmarūpā mahātmānaḥ pūtā vigatakilbiṣāḥ 059.036
tulyaprabhāvā devais te modante 'psarasāṃ gaṇaiḥ
gandharvair upagīyante gośaraṇyā na saṃśayaḥ 059.037
brahmaṇyāḥ sādhuvṛttāś ca dayāvanto 'nukampinaḥ
ghṛṇinaḥ śubhakarmāṇo modante te 'maraiḥ saha 059.038
yathaiva salile matsyaḥ salilena sahohyate
gobhiḥ pāpakṛtaṃ karma dṛḍham eva mayohyate 059.039
mātaraḥ sarvabhūtānāṃ prajāsaṃrakṣaṇe smṛtāḥ
brahmaṇā lokasāreṇa gāvaḥ pāpabhayāpahāḥ 059.040
tāsu dattāsu rājendra kiṃ na dattaṃ bhaved iha
kṛśāya tu viśeṣeṇa vṛttiglānāya sīdate 059.041
bhūdānena samaṃ dānaṃ na bhūtaṃ na bhaviṣyati
iti dharmavidaḥ prāhus tan me nigadataḥ śṛṇu 060.001
ṣaṣṭiṃ varṣasahasrāṇi svarge vasati bhūmidaḥ
ācchettā cānumantā ca tāny eva narake vaset 060.002
atidānaṃ tu sarveṣāṃ bhūmidānam ihocyate
acalā hy akṣayā bhūmiḥ sarvān kāmān prayacchati 060.003
bhūmidaḥ svargam āruhya śāśvatīr edhati samāḥ
punaś ca janma saṃprāpya bhaved bhūmipatir dhruvam 060.004
yathā bhūmiḥ sadā devī dātāraṃ kurute patim
evaṃ sadakṣiṇā dattā kurute gaur janādhipam 060.005
api pāpakṛtaṃ prāpya pratigṛhṇīta bhūmidam
mahīṃ dadan pavitrī syāt puṇyā hi jagatī yataḥ 060.006
nāma vai priyadatteti guhyam etat sanātanam
tad asyāḥ satataṃ prītyai kīrtanīyaṃ prayacchatā 060.007
yat kiṃcit kurute pāpaṃ puruṣo vṛttikarṣitaḥ
api gocarmamātreṇa bhūmidānena śudhyati 060.008
suvarṇaṃ rajataṃ tāmraṃ maṇimuktāvasūni ca
sarvān etān mahāprājña dadāti vasudhāṃ dadan 060.009
tapo yajñāḥ śrutaṃ śīlam alobhaḥ satyavāditā
gurudaivatapūjā ca nātikramanti bhūmidam 060.010
bhartur niḥśreyase yuktās tyaktātmāno raṇe hatāḥ
brahmalokagatāḥ santo nātikrāmanti bhūmidam 060.011
phalakṛṣṭāṃ mahīṃ dattvā sodakāṃ saphalānvitām
sodakaṃ vāpi śaraṇaṃ prāpnoti mama saṃpadam 060.012
ratnopakīṛṇāṃ vasudhāṃ yo dadāti dvijātaye
muktaḥ sa kaluṣaiḥ sarvaiḥ svargaloke mahīyate 060.013
ikṣubhiḥ saṃtatāṃ bhūmiṃ yavagodhūmaśāḍbalām
ye prayacchanti viprebhyo nopasarpanti te yamam 060.014
sarvakāmadughāṃ dhenuṃ sarvasasyasamudbhavām
yo dadāti dvijendrāya brahmalokaṃ sa gacchati 060.015
bhūmidānaṃ naraḥ kurvan mucyate mahato bhayāt
na bhūyo bhūmidānād dhi dānam anyad viśiṣyate 060.016
puṇyāṃ sarvarasāṃ bhūmiṃ yo dadāti nararṣabha
na tasya lokāḥ kṣīyante bhūmidasya mahātmanaḥ 060.017
yathā janitrī puṣṇāti kṣīreṇa svasutaṃ nṛpa
evaṃ sarvaguṇā bhūmir dātāram anupuṣyati 060.018
agniṣṭomādibhir yajñair iṣṭvā vipuladakṣiṇaiḥ
na tat phalaṃ avāpnoti yad dattvā vasudhāṃ nṛpa 060.019
mṛtyor hi kiṃkarā daṇḍā hy agnitāpāḥ sudāruṇāḥ
ghorāś ca vāruṇāḥ pāśā nopasarpanti bhūmidam 060.020
pitaraḥ pitṛlokasthā devaloke divaukasaḥ
saṃtarpayanti dātāraṃ bhūmeḥ prabhavatāṃ vara 060.021
kṛśāya kṛśabhṛtyāya vṛttikṣīṇāya sīdate
bhūmiṃ vṛttikārīṃ dattvā sattrī bhavati mānavaḥ 060.022
siṃhāsanaṃ tathā cchattraṃ varāśvā varavāraṇāḥ
bhūmidānasya puṣpāṇi phalaṃ svargaṃ tathaiva ca 060.023
ādityā iva dīpyante tejasā divi mānavāḥ
ye prayacchanti vasudhāṃ brāhmaṇāyāhitāgnaye 060.024
yathā bījāni rohanti prakīrṇāni mahītale
tathā kāmādhirohanti bhūmidānaguṇārjitāḥ 060.025
āsphoṭayanti pitaraḥ pravalganti pitāmahāḥ
bhūmido naḥ kule jātaḥ sa naḥ saṃtārayiṣyati 060.026
ādityā vasavo rudrā hy aśvinau vasubhiḥ saha
śūlapāṇiś ca bhagavān abhinandanti bhūmidam 060.027
sa naḥ kulasya puruṣaḥ sa no bandhuḥ sa no gatiḥ
sa dātā sa ca vikrānto yo dadāti vasuṃdharām 060.028
dātāram anugṛhṇāti yathā dattena rocate
pūrvadattāṃ haran bhūmiṃ narakāyopapadyate 060.029
vindhyāṭavīṣv atoyāsu śuṣkakoṭaravāsinaḥ
kṛṣṇasarpā hi jāyante ye haranti vasuṃdharām 060.030
patanty aśrūṇi rudatāṃ dīnānām avasīdatām
brāhmaṇānāṃ hṛtaṃ kṣetraṃ hanyāt tripuruṣaṃ kulam 060.031
sādhubhyo bhūmim ākṣipya na bhūtiṃ vindate kvacit
dattvā hi bhūmiṃ sādhubhyo vindate bhūtim uttamām 060.032
pūrvadattāṃ dvijātibhyo yatnād rakṣa yudhiṣṭhira
mahīṃ mahībhṛtāṃ śreṣṭha dānāc chreyo 'nupālanam 060.033
yatraiṣaḥ paṭhyate śrāddhe bhūmidānasya saṃstavaḥ
na tatra rakṣasāṃ bhāgo nāsurāṇāṃ kathaṃcana 060.034
akṣayaṃ tu bhavec chrāddhaṃ pitR̥ṇāṃ nātra saṃśayaḥ
tasmād viśrāvayed enaṃ śrāddheṣu brāhmaṇān sadā 060.035
evam etad yathoddiṣṭaṃ pitR̥ṇāṃ dattam akṣayam
bhūmidānaṃ mahārāja sarvapāpāpahaṃ śubham 060.036
agniṣṭomādibhir yajñair iṣṭvā vipuladakṣiṇaiḥ
na tat phalam avāpnoti saṃgrāme yad avāpnuyāt 061.001
iti yajñavidaḥ prāhur yajñakarmaviśāradāḥ
tasmāt tat te pravakṣyāmi yat phalaṃ śastrajīvinām 061.002
dharmalābho 'rthalābhaś ca yaśolābhas tathaiva ca
yaḥ śūro vadhyate yuddhe vimṛdan paravāhinīm
tasya dharmārthakāmāś ca yajñāś caivāptadakṣiṇāḥ 061.003
paraṃ hy abhimukhaṃ hatvā tadyānaṃ yo 'dhirohati
viṣṇukrāntaṃ sa yajata evaṃ yudhyan raṇājire
aśvamedhān avāpnoti caturas tena karmaṇā 061.004
yas tu śastram anutsṛjya vīryavān vāhinīmukhe
saṃmukho vartate śūraḥ sa svargān na vivartate 061.005
rājānaṃ rājaputraṃ vā senāpatim athāpi vā
hanyāt kṣatreṇa yaḥ śūras tasya loko 'kṣayo dhruvaḥ 061.006
yāvanti tasya śastrāṇi bhindanti tvacam āhave
tāvato labhate lokān sarvakāmadugho 'kṣayān 061.007
vīrāsanaṃ vīraśayyā vīrasthānasthitiḥ sthirā
gavārthe brāhmaṇārthe vā svāmyarthe tu kṛtaṃ ca yaiḥ
te gacchanty amalaṃ sthānaṃ yathā sukṛtinas tathā 061.008
abhagnaṃ yaḥ paraṃ hanyād bhagnaṃ ca parirakṣati
yasmin sthite palāyanti so 'pi prāpnoti svargatim 061.009
ūrdhvaṃ tiryak ca yaś cārvāk prāṇān saṃtyajate yudhi
hatāśvaś ca pated yuddhe sa svargān na nivartate 061.010
yasya cihnīkṛtaṃ gātraṃ śaraśaktyṛṣṭitomaraiḥ
devakanyās tu taṃ vīraṃ ramayanti ramanti ca 061.011
varāpsaraḥsahasrāṇi śūram āyodhane hatam
tvaritāny abhidhāvanti mama bhartā mameti ca 061.012
hatasyābhimukhasyājau patitasyānivartinaḥ
hriyate yat parair dravyaṃ naramedhaphalaṃ tu tat 061.013
bhūyo gatiṃ pravakṣyāmi raṇe ye 'bhimukhā hatāḥ 061.014
śakyaṃ tv iha samṛddhais tu yaṣṭuṃ kratuśatair naraiḥ
ātmadehaṃ tu viprārthe tyaktuṃ yuddhe suduṣkaram 061.015
yāṃ yajñasaṃghais tapasā ca viprāḥ svargaiṣiṇas tatra cayaiḥ prayānti
kṣaṇena tām eva gatiṃ prayānti mahāhave svāṃ tanuṃ saṃtyajantaḥ 061.016
sarvāṃś ca vedān saha ṣaḍbhir aṅgaiḥ sāṃkhyaṃ ca yogaṃ ca vane ca vāsam
etān guṇān eka evātiśete saṃgrāmadhāmny ātmatanuṃ tyajed yaḥ 061.017
imāṃ giraṃ citrapadāṃ śubhākṣarāṃ subhāṣitāṃ vṛtabhidāṃ divaukasām
camūmukhe yaḥ smarate dṛḍhasmṛtir na hanyate hanti ca so 'raṇe ripūn 061.018
eṣa puṇyatamaḥ svargyaḥ suyajñaḥ sarvatomukhaḥ
sarveṣām eva varṇānāṃ kṣatriyasya viśeṣataḥ 061.019
bhūyaś caiva pravakṣyāmi bhīṣmavākyam anuttamam
yādṛśāya prahartavyaṃ yādṛśaṃ parivarjayet 061.020
ātatāyinam āyāntam api vedāntagaṃ raṇe
jighāṃsantaṃ jighāṃsīyān na tena brahmahā bhavet 061.021
hatāśvaś ca na hantavyaḥ pānīyaṃ yaś ca yācate
vyādhito durbalaś caiva rathahīnas tathaiva ca 061.022
bhagnadhanvācchinaguṇaḥ prāṇepsuḥ kṛpaṇaṃ bruvan
vimuktakeśo dhāved yo yaś conmattākṛtir bhavet 061.023
parṇaśākhātṛṇagrāhī tavāsmīti ca yo vadet
brāhmaṇo 'smīti yaś cāha bālo vṛddho napuṃsakaḥ 061.024
tasmād etān parihared yathoddiṣṭān raṇājire
hato na hanyate sadbhir hatā eva hi bhīravaḥ 061.025
amāṃsabhakṣaṇe rājan yo dharmaḥ kurupuṅgava
tan me śṛṇu yathātathyaṃ yaś cāsya vidhir uttamaḥ 062.001
māsi māsy aśvamedhena yo yajeta śataṃ samāḥ
na ca khādati yo māṃsaṃ samam etad yudhiṣṭhira 062.002
sadā yajati sattreṇa sadā dānaṃ prayacchati
sadā tapasvī bhavati madhumāṃsavivarjanāt 062.003
sarvavedā na tat kuryuḥ sarvadānāni caiva hi
yo māṃsarasam āsvādya sarvamāṃsāni varjayet 062.004
duṣkaraṃ hi rasajñena māṃsasya parivarjanam
caturvratam idaṃ śreṣṭhaṃ prāṇināṃ mṛtyubhīruṇām 062.005
tadā bhavati loke 'smin prāṇināṃ jīvitaiṣiṇām
viśvāsyaś copagamyaś ca na hi hiṃsārudir yadā 062.006
duṣṭarāṃs tarate ma....āṃ māṃsasya parivarjanāt 062.*(74)
prāṇā yathātmano 'bhīṣṭā bhūtānām api te tathā
ātmaupamyena gantavyaṃ buddhimadbhir mahātmabhiḥ 062.007
ahiṃsā paramo dharmaḥ satyam eva ca pāṇḍava
ahiṃsā caiva satyaṃ ca dharmo hi paramaḥ smṛtaḥ 062.008
na hi māṃsaṃ tṛṇāt kāṣṭhād upalād vāpi jāyate
yadi vai khādako na syān na tadā ghātako bhavet 062.009
jīvād utpadyate māṃsaṃ tasmād garhanti tad budhāḥ 062.*(75)
lobhād vā buddhimohād vā yo māṃsāny atti mānavaḥ
nirghṛṇaḥ sa hi mantavyaḥ saddharmaparivarjitaḥ 062.010
svamāṃsaṃ paramāṃsena yo vardhayitum icchati
udvignavāse vasati yatratatrābhijāyate 062.011
dhanena krāyako hanti upabhogena khādakaḥ
ghātako vadhabandhābhyām ity eṣa trividho vadhaḥ 062.012
bhakṣayitvā tu yo māṃsaṃ paścād api nivartate
tasyāpi sumahān dharmo yaḥ pāpād vinivartate
idam anyat pravakṣyāmi purāṇam ṛṣinirmitam 062.013
varam ekasya sattvasya dadyād akṣayadakṣiṇām
na tu viprasahasrasya gosahasraṃ sakāñcanam
yo dadyāt kāñcanaṃ meruṃ kṛtsnāṃ vāpi vasuṃdharām
abhakṣaṇaṃ ca māṃsasya na tu tulyaṃ yudhiṣṭhira 062.*(76)
śrūyate ca purākalpe hy ṛṣīṇāṃ vrīhayaḥ paśuḥ
yajante yena vai yajñān ṛṣayaḥ puṇyakarmiṇaḥ 062.014
ṛṣibhiḥ saṃśayaṃ pṛṣṭo vasū rājā tataḥ purā
abhakṣyaṃ bhakṣyam iti vai māṃsam āha narādhipa 062.015
ākāśān medinīṃ prāptas tataḥ sa pṛthivīpatiḥ
etad eva punaś coktvā viveśa dharaṇītalam 062.016
kaumudaṃ tu viśeṣeṇa śuklapakṣe narādhipa
varjayet sarvamāṃsāni dharmo hy atra vidhīyate 062.017
caturo vārṣikān māsān yo māṃsaṃ parivarjayet
catvāri bhadrāṇy āpnoti kīrtir āyur yaśo balam 062.018
apy ekam iha yo māsaṃ sarvamāṃsāni varjayet
atītya sarvaduḥkhāni sukhaṃ jīven nirāmayaḥ 062.019
yo hi varṣaśataṃ pūrṇaṃ tapas tapyet sudāruṇam
apy ekaṃ varjayen māsaṃ māṃsam etat samaṃ matam 062.020
yo varjayati māṃsāni māsaṃ pakṣam athāpi vā
sa vai hiṃsānivṛttas tu brahmaloke mahīyate 062.021
sarvakālaṃ tu māṃsāni varjitāni maharṣibhiḥ
manvā kṣupeṇa śvetena tathaivekṣvākunāpi ca 062.022
bhṛguṇā nalarāmābhyāṃ dilīparaghupauravaiḥ
āyuṣā caiva gārgyeṇa janakaiś cakravartibhiḥ 062.023
dhundhumārāmbarīṣābhyāṃ nahuṣeṇa ca dhīmatā
gādhinā purukutsena kuruṇā puruṇā tathā 062.024
mucukundena māndhātrā sagareṇa mahātmanā
śibinā cāśvapatinā vīrasenādibhis tathā 062.025
saṃjayenātha bhīṣmeṇa puṣkareṇātha pāṇḍunā
suvarṇaṣṭhīvinā caiva duṣvantanṛgarohitaiḥ 062.026
etaiś cānyaiś ca bahubhiḥ sarvair māṃsaṃ na bhakṣitam
śaratkaumudikaṃ māsaṃ tataḥ svargaṃ gatā nṛpāḥ
sarvakāmasamṛddhās te vasanti divi saṃsthitāḥ 062.027
brahmaloke ca pūjyante jvalamānāḥ śriyāvṛtāḥ
upāsyamānā gāndharvaiḥ strīsahasrasamanvitāḥ 062.028
tad evam uttamaṃ dharmam ahiṃsālakṣaṇaṃ śubhan
ye rakṣanti mahātmāno nākapṛṣṭhe vasanti te 062.029
madhu māṃsaṃ ca ye nityaṃ varjayantīha mānavāḥ
janmaprabhṛti madyaṃ ca sarve te munayaḥ smṛtāḥ 062.030
āpannaś cāpado mucyed baddho mucyeta bandhanāt
vyādhito mucyate rogād duḥkhān mucyeta duḥkhitaḥ 062.031
yaś cainaṃ paṭhate nityaṃ prayatnād bharatarṣabha
ghoraṃ saṃtarate durgaṃ svargavāsaṃ ca vindati
tiryagyoniṃ na gacchec ca rūpavāṃś caiva jāyate 062.032
etat te kathitaṃ rājan māṃsasya parivarjanam
pravṛttau ca nivṛttau ca pramāṇam ṛṣisattamaiḥ 062.033
gobrāhmaṇahitārthāya cāturvarṇyahitāya ca
aśiṣṭanigrahārthāya śiṣṭānāṃ rakṣaṇāya ca
yudhiṣṭhirasya rājarṣer evaṃ nārāyaṇo 'bravīt 063.001
pañca rūpāṇi rājāno dhārayanty amitaujasaḥ
agner indrasya somasya yamasya varuṇasya ca 063.002
tān na hiṃsen na cākrośen nākṣipen nāpriyaṃ vadet
devā mānuṣarūpeṇa caranti pṛthivīm imām 063.003
indrāt prabhutvaṃ jvalanāt pratāpaṃ krauryaṃ yamād vaiśravaṇāt prabhāvam
sattvasthitiṃ rāmajanārdanābhām ādāya rājñaḥ kriyate śarīram 063.004
na cāpi rājā mantavyo manuṣyo 'yam iti prabho
mahatī devatā hy eṣā nararūpeṇa tiṣṭhati 063.005
svayam indro naro bhūtvā pṛthivīm anuśāsati
na hi pālayituṃ śakto manuṣyaḥ pṛthivīm imām 063.006
yat prajāpālanaiḥ puṇyaṃ prāpnuvantīha pārthivāḥ
na tat kratusahasreṇa prāpnuvanti dvijottamāḥ 063.007
adhītahutataptasya karmaṇaḥ sukṛtasya ca
ṣaṣṭhaṃ labhati bhāgaṃ tu prajā dharmeṇa pālayan 063.008
grāmādhipatyaṃ nagarādhipatyaṃ deśādhipatyaṃ pṛthivīpatitvam
na prāpnuvantīha manuṣyamātrā ye devatānāṃ na bhavanti bhāgāḥ 063.009
na tad asti vrataṃ loke yad rājñaś caritopamam
na tad vedarahasyaṃ vā yad rājñaḥ phalato 'dhikam
evaṃvṛttās tu rājāno devabhāgā na mānuṣāḥ 063.010
caturvedyaṃ hutaca.ṇa yo hiṃseta narādhipaḥ
daṇḍasyaite bhayād bhītā na khādanti parasparam
ja.ḍaṇḍabhayāt ke... na durvanti hi pātakam
yamadaṇḍabhayād anye na durvanti parasparam
nābhīto yajate kāṃścan (?) nābhīto daṇḍam icchati 063.*(77)
ya eva devā hantāras tāṃl loko 'rcayate bhṛśam
hantā śakraś ca rudraś ca hantā vaiśravaṇo yamaḥ
varuṇo vāyur ādityaḥ parjanyo 'gnir bṛhaspatiḥ 063.011
etān devān namasyanti pratāpapraṇatā janāḥ
na brahmāṇaṃ na dhātāraṃ na pūṣāṇaṃ kathaṃcana 063.012
daṇḍagrastaṃ jagat sarvaṃ vaśyatvam anugacchati
nāyaṃ klībasya loko 'sti na paraḥ pārthivottama 063.013
na hi paśyāmi jīvantaṃ rājan kaṃcid ahiṃsayā
udake jantavo nityaṃ pṛthivyāṃ ca phaleṣu ca
na hatvā lipyate rājā prajā dharmeṇa pālayan 063.014
yadi daṇḍo na vidyeta durvinītās tatho narāḥ
hanyuḥ paśūn manuṣyāṃś ca yājñiyāni haviṃṣi ca 063.015
vṛkavat kṣapayeyuś ca yo yasya balavattaraḥ 063.*(78)
tasmāt prāṇihite daṇḍe hiṃsādoṣo na bādhate 063.*(79)
naivostrā na balīvardā nāśvāśvataragardabhāḥ
yuktā vaheyur yānāni daṇḍaś cen nodyato bhavet 063.016
satyaṃ kilaitad yad uvāca śakro daṇḍaḥ prajā rakṣati sādhuvṛttaḥ
yasyāgnayaḥ pratimāsasya bhītāḥ saṃtarjitā daṇḍabhayāj jvalanti 063.017
yatra śyāmo lohitākṣo daṇḍaś carati pāpahā
prajās tatra na muhyante netā cet sādhu paśyati 063.018
daṇḍanītau sunītāyāṃ sarve sidhyanty upakramāḥ
daṇḍaś cen na pravarteta vinaśyeyur imāḥ prajāḥ 063.019
vṛkavad bhakṣayeyuś ca yo yasya balavattaraḥ
kākādyāś ca purodāśaṃ śvā caivāvalihed dhaviḥ 063.020
svāmyaṃ ca na syāt kasmiṃścit pravartetādharottaram
cāturvarṇyavimokṣāya durvinītabhayāya ca 063.021
daṇḍena niyato loko dharmasthānaṃ ca rakṣati
sarvo daṇḍajito loko durlabho hi śucir janaḥ 063.022
daṇḍasya hi bhayād bhītā narās tiṣṭhanti śāsane
ti 'pi bhogāya kalpante daṇḍenoparipīḍitāḥ 063.023
gurur ātmavatāṃ śāstā śāstā rājā durātmanāṃ
ihapracchannapāpānāṃ śāstā vaivasvato yamaḥ 063.024
pāpānām atha mūḍhānāṃ paradravyāpahāriṇām
paradāraratā ye ca ye ca pātakasaṃjñitāḥ
teṣāṃ tu śāsanārthāya mayaitat samudāhṛtam 063.025
brāhmaṇyaṃ duṣkaraṃ jñātvā tasya daṇḍaṃ nipātayet
karmānurūpo daṇḍaḥ syād gohiraṇyādiko bhavet
avadhyo brāhmaṇo rājan strī vṛddho bāla eva ca 063.026
yaś cared aśubhaṃ karma pāpaṃ rājavigarhitam
pātakeṣu ca varteta nigrahaṃ tasya kārayet 063.027
śiraso muṇḍanaṃ kṛtvā gomayenānulepayet
kharayānena nagaraṃ ḍiṇḍimena tu bhrāmayet
rājanirdiṣṭadaṇḍasya prāyaścittaṃ na vidyate 063.028
eṣa te kathito daṇḍo brāhmaṇasya yudhiṣṭhira
kṣatriyasya tu yo daṇḍas taṃ vakṣyāmy anupūrvaśaḥ 063.029
paradravyādiharaṇe paradārābhimardane
pātakeṣu ca sarveṣu yo hi varteta kṣatriyaḥ
tasya daṇḍaṃ pravakṣyāmi tan me nigadataḥ śṛṇu 063.030
hastapādaparicchedaṃ karṇanāsāvakartanam
sarvasvaharaṇaṃ kṛtvā pararāṣṭrāya preśayet 063.031
rājyaṃ kāṅkṣeta yo mūḍho rājapatnīm athāpi vā
śarais tu rājā vidhyeta śakticakragadādibhiḥ 063.032
kṣatriyasya tu duṣṭasya daṇḍa eṣa vidhīyate
vaiśyasyāpi ca yo daṇḍas taṃ pravakṣyāmi bhārata 063.033
pātakeṣv eva krūreṣu yas tu vaiśyaḥ pravartate
paradāre paradravye tasya nigraham ādiśet 063.034
śūlāyāṃ bhedanaṃ tasya vṛkṣaśākhāvalambanam
etad vaiśyasya nirdiṣṭaṃ śūdrasyāpy anupūrvaśaḥ 063.035
śūle śūdrasya yo duṣṭas tasyaikasya vadhaḥ smṛtaḥ
kuñjareṇābhimardeta mīnīyām atha pācayet
etac chūdrasya nirdiṣṭaṃ nānyo daṇḍo vidhīyate 063.036
naikasyārthe kulaṃ hanyān na rāṣṭraṃ na ca grāmakam
ekaṃ suśiṣṭitaṃ kṛtvā śeṣaṃ kośaṃ praveśayet 063.037
dhanalobhān na moktavyo rāgād vā śāsanaṃ vinā 063.*(80)
yudhiṣṭhirasya rājarṣer evaṃ nārāyaṇo 'bravīt
samāsena yathānyāyaṃ daṇḍanītim anuttamām 063.038
uttamādhamakāryeṣu sameṣu viṣameṣu ca
rājadharmāṃs tu paśyeta viṣṇunā samudāhṛtān 063.039
etān dharmāñ jagannāthaḥ pāṇḍuputrāya pṛcchate
jagāda puruṣavyāghra kim anyac chrotum icchasi 064.001
bhagavan vahatāṃ bhaktiṃ devadeve janārdane
yat phalaṃ kathitaṃ tajjñais tan me vistarato vada 064.002
yat phalaṃ vahatāṃ bhaktim acyute bhavati prabho
na tad varṇayituṃ śakyaṃ hariḥ sarvepsitapradaḥ 064.003
yādṛk sattvaṃ manuṣyāṇāṃ tādṛg ārādhya keśavam
phalam icchanti tādṛc ca labhyate tair nareśvara 064.004
muktikāmā narā muktiṃ svargaṃ devatvam īpsavaḥ
gandharvayakṣasiddhānāṃ vṛṇvanty anye salokatām 064.005
varṣeṣv abhīpsavo viṣṇuṃ pātāleṣu tathāpare
bhogān abhīpsavo viṣṇuṃ toṣayaṇti narādhipa 064.006
tathāpare naraiśvaryam ārogyaṃ guṇavad bhuvi
prārthayanty acyutaṃ devam ārādhya jagato gatim 064.007
dharmopadeśād acalāṃ vahan bhaktiṃ janārdane
saśarīro gataḥ svargaṃ dharmaputro yudhiṣṭhiraḥ 064.008
tathaiva janakaḥ kṛṣṇe viniveśya svamānasam
avāpa paramāṃ siddhiṃ vasuḥ prāyāt tripiṣṭapam 064.009
anye ca ye ye munayo ye ye ca vasudhādhipāḥ
avāpur atulān kāmāṃs te te saṃtoṣya keśavam 064.010
anārādhya jagannāthaṃ sarvapāpaharaṃ harim
sadgatiḥ kena saṃprāptā bhogāś cāpi manoramāḥ 064.011
drauṇibrahmāstranirdagdhas tava rājan pitāmahaḥ
viṣṇoḥ kāryamanuṣyasya darśanād utthitaḥ punaḥ 064.012
nāmasaṃkīrtanād yasya pāpam anyair upadravaiḥ
samaṃ vināśam āyāti devaḥ ko 'bhyadhikas tataḥ 064.013
rāṣṭrasya śaraṇaṃ rājā pitarau bālakasya ca
dharmaḥ samastamartyānāṃ sarvasya śaraṇaṃ hariḥ 064.014
muktihetum anādyantam ajam akṣayam acyutam
namasyan sarvalokasya namasyo jāyate naraḥ 064.015
na hi tasya guṇāḥ sarve sarvair munigaṇair api
vaktuṃ śakyā viyuktasya sattvādyair akhilair guṇaiḥ 064.016
śrutaṃ mayā yathā pūrvam āryako me yudhiṣṭhiraḥ
saśarīro gataḥ svargaṃ jitam ātmīyakarmabhiḥ 064.017
yat tv etad bhagavān āha sa yathā pāṇdupūrvajaḥ
dharmopadeśād govindam ārādhayata tad vada 064.018
purā śāsati dharmajñe dharmaputre yudhiṣṭhire
tasyaiva vaiśvadevānte caṇḍālo 'bhyāgamat kila 064.019
samupetya gṛhaṃ tasya dharmaputrasya vismitaḥ
uvāca śvapaco dvāḥsthaṃ praśrayāvanatasthitaḥ 064.020
kasyaitad bhavanaṃ divyaṃ maṇiratnavibhūṣitam
śuddhasphaṭikasopānaṃ maṇikāñcanatoraṇam 064.021
aṣṭāśītisahasrāṇi brāhmaṇānāṃ dine dine
yudhiṣṭhiram ṛte bhūpaṃ bhuñjate kasya veśmani 064.022
katham etan na jānīṣe candrabimbam ivāparam
yudhiṣṭhirasya bhavanaṃ devarājagṛhopamam 064.023
abalasya balaṃ rājā bālasya ruditaṃ balam
balaṃ mūrkhasya vai maunaṃ taskarasyānṛtaṃ balam 064.024
gaccha jalpa svarājānaṃ pratīhāra vaco mama
duḥkhārtaḥ kāryavān rājaṃś caṇḍālo dvāri tiṣṭhati 064.025
kenāpi hetumātreṇa bhavantaṃ duṣṭam āgataḥ 064.*(81)
ity ukto dharmarājasya pratīhāro yathoditam
nivedayām āsa tathā dharmarājo 'bravīd idam 064.026
kiṃ rūpaṃ kīdṛśaṃ śīlaṃ ko 'syārthaḥ kiṃ prayojanam
brūhi dvāḥstha yathāvan me naras tiṣṭhati kīdṛśaḥ 064.027
kākakokilakṛṣṇāṅgo bhagnanāsāruṇekṣaṇaḥ
yavamadhyaḥ kṛśagrīvo vakrapādo mahāhanuḥ 064.028
brūhi gaccha durācāraṃ caṇḍālaṃ pāpakarmiṇam
devakāryasya velāyāṃ dutas tvaṃ pratyupasthitaḥ 064.029
caṇḍālapatitau dṛṣṭvā naraḥ paśyeta bhāskaram
snātas tv etāv athālokya sacailasnānam arhati 064.030
ity ājñapte tathoktas tu caṇḍālas tena vai tataḥ
pratyuvāca pratīhāram īṣan manyupariplutaḥ 064.031
kiṃ devakāryeṇa narādhipasya kṛtvā hi manyuṃ viṣayasthitānām
tad devakāryaṃ sa ca yajñahomo yad aśrupātā na patanti rāṣṭre 064.032
idaṃ vacanam avyagraṃ pratīhāra tvarā mama
nivedaya svarājendraṃ yatheṣṭaṃ sa karotu vai
ity uktaḥ satvaraṃ gatvā dharmarājaṃ tathā tathaṃ (?)
kathayām āsa tat sarvaṃ cāṇḍālena yad īritam
suśobhanam idaṃ vākyaṃ na bhaved antyajātiṣu
cintayitvā tato rājā nirjagāma yudhiṣṭhiraḥ 064.*(82)
ity etad vacanaṃ śrutvā nirjagāma yudhiṣṭhiraḥ
pratyuvāca ca caṇḍālam īṣan kopasamanvitaḥ 064.033
kutas te bhayam utpannaṃ yena tvaṃ gṛham āgataḥ
āvādhākāraṇaṃ sarvaṃ yathāvat kathayasva me 064.034
tad ahaṃ te pratijñāya caṇḍakarmakarakṣaṇam
apāsya devakāryārthaṃ praviśyāmy antaraṃ punaḥ 064.035
na bhuñjate brāhmaṇā me sarvāś codvijate janaḥ
prāṇihiṃsā ca no vṛttir deva puṣṇāti me 'nṛtam 064.036
anekajanmasāhasrīṃ prāpya saṃsārapaddhatim
mānuṣye kutsitāṃ jātim āpanno muṣito 'smi bhoḥ 064.037
karmabhūmim imāṃ rājan prārthayanti divaukasaḥ
tāṃ saṃprāpya vṛthājanmā muṣṭo 'smi kurusattama 064.038
duḥkhe duḥkhādhikān paśyet sukhe paśyet sukhādhikān
ātmānaṃ śokaharṣābhyāṃ śatrubhyām iva nārpayet 064.039
so 'ham icchāmi vijñātum atiduṣkṛtakarmakṛt
vaktum arhasi dharmajña kaḥ pāpiṣṭhataro mayā 064.040
adhvānam upari śrāntaṃ brāhmaṇaṃ gṛham āgatam
anarcayitvā yo bhuṅkte sa pāpiṣṭhataras tvayā 064.041
mātaraṃ pitaraṃ caiva vikalaṃ netradurbalam
yo nābhyuddharate putraḥ sa pāpiṣṭhataras tvayā 064.042
godhanasya tṛṣārtasya jalārthaṃ paridhāvataḥ
vighnam ācarate yas tu sa pāpiṣṭhataras tvayā 064.043
vivāhayitvā yaḥ kanyāṃ kulajāṃ śīlamaṇḍanām
vinā tyajati doṣeṇa sa pāpiṣṭhataras tvayā 064.044
āśākāras tv adātā yo dātuś ca pratiṣedhakaḥ
dattaṃ ca yaḥ kīrtayati sa pāpiṣṭhataras tvayā 064.045
bahubhṛtyair daridraiś ca dhanaṃ santaṃ dvijottamaiḥ
yācito na prayacched yaḥ sa pāpiṣṭhataras tvayā 064.046
brāhmaṇaḥ kṣatriyo vāpi vaiśyaḥ śūdro 'pi vā naraḥ
svadharmaṃ saṃtyajed yas tu sa pāpiṣṭhataras tvayā 064.047
kṛtārtho 'haṃ gamiṣyāmi yaśodharmam avāpnuhi
tuṣṭo 'smy ahaṃ svayā yonyā mattaḥ proktās tvayādhamāḥ 064.048
devatānām ṛṣīṇāṃ ca pitR̥ṇāṃ ca kṛtaṃ mayā
sāṃprataṃ deśakālo 'yaṃ tvam evātra bhavātithiḥ 064.049
caṇḍālo 'haṃ mahārāja patito lokavarjitaḥ
kathaṃ nihīno varṇebhyo bhokṣyāmi bhavato gṛhe 064.050
caṇḍālo bhava pāpo vā śatrur vā pitṛghātakaḥ
deśakālābhyupetaṃ tvāṃ bharaṇīyaṃ hi vedmy aham 064.051
daśasūnāsamaṃ cakraṃ daśacakrasamo dhvajaḥ
daśadhvajasamā veśyā daśaveśyāsamo nṛpaḥ 064.052
daśa sūnāsahasrāṇi kurute yo hi saunikaḥ
tena tulyaḥ smṛto rājā ghoras tasya pratigrahaḥ 064.053
nānāgotrādicaraṇā bhuñjate brāhmaṇā mama
na te vadanti vāgduṣṭaṃ yathaitat kīrtitaṃ tvayā 064.054
lobhātmāno na jānīyur brāhmaṇā rājakilbiṣam
varaṃ svamāṃsam attavyaṃ na tu rājapratigraham 064.055
rājakilbiṣadagdhānāṃ brāhmaṇānāṃ yudhiṣṭhira
chinnānām iva bījānāṃ punarjanma na vidyate 064.056
rājapratigraho ghoro madhvāsvādo viṣopamaḥ
budhena pratihartavyaḥ svamāṃsasyeva bhakṣaṇam 064.057
adhītya caturo vedān sarvaśāstrārthatattvavit
narendrabhavane bhuṅktvā viṣṭhāyāṃ jāyate kṛmiḥ 064.058
nindase sarvarājāno na cātmānaṃ praśaṃsasi
athavā nindyarūpeṇa pitā nas tvam ihāgataḥ 064.059
dhairyavān ātmano 'nindyo nāśvāsārthaṃ ca pṛcchasi
vimuktakrodhaharśaś ca ko 'py atra pratibhāsi naḥ
anindyo nindyarūpeṇa mahātmā tvaṃ hi me mataḥ
ko bhavān brūhi satyaṃ me kimartham iha cāgataḥ
bhavān upendraḥ śakro vā śarvo vā tvaṃ pinākadhṛk 064.*(84)
jñāto 'smi pṛthivīpāla tuṣṭaś ca tava darśanāt
nandantu bhūmibhāgās te yeṣu tvaṃ pṛthivīpatiḥ 064.060
nirjitya parasainyāni kṣitiṃ dharmeṇa pālaya
svalpam apy astu te velāṃ mā govindojjhitaṃ manaḥ 064.061
kiṃ me rājyena bhos tāta viṣayair jīvitena vā
yo 'haṃ sūnāsahasrais tu daśabhiḥ pariveṣṭitaḥ 064.062
mā viṣādaṃ naraśreṣṭha samupaihi yudhiṣṭhira
yajñeśvaraṃ yajñamūrtiṃ tvaṃ ca viṣṇuṃ samāśritaḥ 064.063
yeṣāṃ na viṣaye viprā yajñair yajñapatiṃ harim
yajanti bhūbhujas teṣām etat sūnoditaṃ phalam 064.064
yeṣāṃ pāṣaṇḍasaṃkīrṇaṃ na rāṣṭraṃ brāhmaṇotkaṭam
te tu sūnāsahasrāṇāṃ daśānāṃ bhāgino nṛpāḥ 064.065
yeṣāṃ na yajñapuruṣaḥ kāraṇaṃ puruṣottamaḥ
te tu pāpasamācārāḥ sūnāpāpaughabhāginaḥ 064.066
tvaṃ tu matprabhavas tāta viṣṇubhaktas tathaiva ca
iṣṭir vaiśvānarī pāpam upahaṃsyati te 'khilam 064.067
avaśyaṃ viṣaye kaścid brāhmaṇaḥ saṃśritavrataḥ
iṣṭiṃ vaiśvānarīṃ kḷptāṃ nirvaped abdaparyaye
tasya ṣaḍbhāgamātreṇa tvaṃ pāpaṃ nirdahiṣyasi 064.068
sa tvaṃ varaya bhadraṃ te varaṃ yan manasecchasi
samyak śraddhāsamācārād aham ārādhitas tvayā 064.069
atha pātakabhītas tvaṃ sarvabhāvena bhārata
vimuktānyasamārambho nārāyaṇaparo bhava 064.070
paraḥ parāṇām ādyo 'sau jñeyo dhyeyo janārdanaḥ
tadartham api karmāṇi kurvan pāpaṃ vyapohati 064.071
lobhādivyāptahṛdayo yat pāpaṃ kurute naraḥ
vilayaṃ yāti tat sarvam acyute hṛdaye sthite 064.072
śamāyālaṃ jalaṃ vahnes tamaso bhāskarādayaḥ
kṣāntiḥ kaler aghaughasya nāmasaṃkīrtanaṃ hareḥ 064.073
prasanno yadi me tāta varārho yadi cāpy aham
varaṃ tad ekam evaitaṃ prāptum icchāmy ahaṃ pitaḥ 064.074
jāgratsvapnasuṣupteṣu yogasthasya sadā mama
yā kācin manaso vṛttiḥ sā bhavatv acyutāśrayā 064.075
yā yā jāyeta me buddhir yāvaj jīvāmy ahaṃ pitaḥ
sā sā chinattu saṃdehān kṛṣṇāptau paripanthinaḥ 064.076
yathā govindam ārādhya saśarīraḥ surālayam
prāpnuyām iti me tāta prayaccha pravaraṃ varam 064.077
evam etad aśeṣaṃ te matprasādād bhaviṣyati
nāsti govindabhaktānāṃ vāñchitaṃ bhuvi durlabham 064.078
iti dharmopadeśena sarvadevavaraṃ harim
ārādhya pāṇḍavo yātaḥ saśarīraḥ surālayam 064.079
bhūyaś ca śṛṇu rājendra janakena mahātmanā
yad gītaṃ vahatā bhaktiṃ jñānam āsādya keśave 065.001
sarvatra samadṛṣṭiṃ taṃ janakaṃ mithileśvaram
paśyantam acyutamayaṃ sarvaṃ ca sacarācaram 065.002
dvijarūpaṃ samāsthāya devadevo janārdanaḥ
upatasthe mahābhāgaṃ pratyuvāca ca pārthivam 065.003
rājañ janaka bhadraṃ te yad bravīmi nibodha tat
kuruṣva ca mahābuddhe yadi sādhu mataṃ tava 065.004
pṛthivīṃ pṛthivīpālaḥ pālayitvā pitā tava
svargaṃ gatas tathā bhrātā samyak satyadhvajo nṛpaḥ 065.005
tvaṃ punar nirabhīmānaḥ sarvatra samadarśanaḥ
ripumitrādivargeṣu katham etad bhaviṣyati 065.006
mitreṣu mitravan na tvaṃ nāhiteṣv arivad bhavān
madhyasthabhāg na caiva tvaṃ tathodāsīnavṛttiṣu 065.007
śabdādayo ye viśayās te vairāgyaphalā nṛpa
nītyā vihīnas tu bhavān kathaṃ rājyaṃ kariṣyati 065.008
sarvair nītiṃ samāsthāya yathā te prapitāmahaiḥ
kṛtaṃ rājyaṃ tathā bhūpa kuru mātijaḍo bhava 065.009
tava prajñā matā hy eṣā mama moho mahīpate
trivargasādhanaṃ prajñā na dharmādivirodhinī 065.010
samyag āha bhavān vipra vācyam evaṃ bhavadvidhaiḥ
mamāpi śrūyatāṃ vākyaṃ bhavato yadi rocate 065.011
yadā sarvagato viṣṇuḥ paramātmā prajāpatiḥ
tadā mitrādimadhyastha- saṃjñā keṣu nipātyatām 065.012
pitā mātā tathā bhrātā yadā nānyaj janārdanāt
pitṛmātṛmayīṃ saṃjñāṃ tadā kutra karomy aham 065.013
so 'haṃ bravīmi yad vākyaṃ tan nibodha dvijottama
anekarūparūpo 'yaṃ viṣṇur evākhilaṃ jagat 065.014
viṣṇuḥ pitā me jagataḥ pratiṣṭhā viṣṇur mātā viṣṇur evāgrajo me
viṣṇur gatir viṣṇumayas tathāsmi viṣṇau sthito 'smy akṣagataś ca viṣṇuḥ 065.015
yo me mamatvopagataḥ sa viṣṇur yaś cāribhūto mama so 'pi viṣṇuḥ
divaṃ viyad bhūḥ kakubhaś ca viṣṇur bhūtāni viṣṇur bhuvanāni viṣṇuḥ 065.016
paśyāmi viṣṇuṃ na paraṃ tato 'nyac śṛṇomi viṣṇuṃ na paraṃ tato 'nyat
spṛśāmi viṣṇuṃ na paraṃ tato 'nyaj jighrāmi viṣṇuṃ na paraṃ tato 'nyat 065.017
rasāmi viṣṇuṃ na paraṃ tato 'nyan manye ca viṣṇuṃ na paraṃ tato 'nyat
budhyāmi viṣṇuṃ na paraṃ tato 'nyat sarvaṃ hi viṣṇur na paraṃ tato 'nyat 065.018
jighrāmi viṣṇuṃ na paraṃ tato 'nyac namāmi viṣṇuṃ na paraṃ tato 'nyat 065.*(85)
viṣṇuḥ samastaṃ na paraṃ tato 'sti viṣṇuḥ samastaṃ na paraṃ ca devaḥ
viṣṇur laghīyān na paraṃ tato 'sti viṣṇur garīyān na paraṃ tato 'nyat 065.019
viṣṇuḥ sthārīyān na paraṃ tato 'sti 065.*(86)
yathā na viṣṇuvyatiriktam anyac śṛṇomi paśyāmi tathā spṛśāmi
satyena tenopaśamaṃ prayāntu doṣā vimukteḥ paripanthino ye 065.020
na me 'sti bandhur na ca me 'sti śatrur na bhūtavargo na jano madanyaḥ
tvaṃ cāhaṃ anye ca śarīrabhedair vibhinnam īśasya hareḥ svarūpam 065.021
mūrtāmūrtiviśeṣaṃ tu paśyatas tanmayaṃ dvija
krodhaharṣādayo bhāvāḥ sthāsyanti hṛdaye katham 065.022
sa tvaṃ prasīda moho 'yam atha cen mama suvrata
tathāpi mā ruṣaṃ kārṣīr acikitsyā hi mohitāḥ 065.023
bahurūpas tato rūpaṃ śaṅkhacakragadādharam
darśayām āsa suprīto janakāya janārdanaḥ 065.024
tatas taddarśanād bhūpaṃ śirasā praṇataṃ prabhuḥ
ādyaḥ prajāpatipatiḥ pratyuvācācyuto hariḥ 065.025
varaṃ varaya bhūpāla parituṣṭo 'smi te 'nagha
mayy arpitamanobuddheḥ sadaivāhaṃ na durlabhaḥ 065.026
yadi deva prasanno 'si samyag ārādhito mayā
tad vṛṇomi varaṃ bhaktis tvayy evāstu sadā mama 065.027
evaṃ bhaviṣyatīty uktvā gato 'ntardhānam īśvaraḥ
so 'pi lebhe layaṃ viṣṇau bhaktyā yogisudurlabham 065.028
iti kṛṣṇe naravyāghra kurvan bhaktiṃ naraḥ sadā
prāpnoti puruṣavyāghra muktiṃ cāpy atidurlabhām 065.029
jagaddhātur anantasya vāsudevasya bhārgava
mamāvatārān akhilāñ śrotum icchā pravartate 066.001
yathā yathā hi kṛṣṇasya katheyaṃ kathyate tvayā
jāyate manasaḥ prītir udbhūtapulakas tathā 066.002
manaḥprītir anāyāsād apuṇyacayasaṃkṣayaḥ
prāpyate puruṣair brahmañ śṛṇvadbhir bhagavatkathām 066.003
sa kuruṣvāmalamate prasādapravaṇaṃ manaḥ
avatārān sureśasya viṣṇor icchāmi veditum 066.004
jagadguruṃ jagadyonim anantam udakeśayam
nārāyaṇaṃ purākalpe pṛṣṭavān kamalodbhavaḥ 066.005
vinirjagmur mukhebhyas tu brahmaṇo vyaktajanmanaḥ
oṃkārapravaṇā vedā jagmus te ca rasātalam 066.006
ekārṇave jagaty asmin brahmaṇy amitatejasi
kṛṣṇanābhihradodbhūta- kamalodaraśāyini 066.007
bhogiśayyāśayaḥ kṛṣṇo dvitīyāṃ tanum ātmanaḥ
kṛtvā mīnamayīṃ sadyaḥ praviveśa rasātalam 066.008
vedamūrtis tato vedān āninye brahmaṇo 'ntikam
madhukaiṭabhābhyāṃ ca punar bhogiśayyāgato hariḥ
hṛtān hayaśirā bhūtvā vedān āhṛtavān rasāt 066.009
āhṛteṣv atha vedeṣu devadevaṃ pitāmahaḥ
tuṣṭāva praṇato bhaktyā tasya cāvir babhau hariḥ 066.010
athāmaraguruṃ viṣṇum anantam ajam avyayam
uvāca prakaṭībhūtaṃ praṇipatyābjasaṃbhavaḥ 066.011
namaḥ sūkṣmātisūkṣmāya namas tubhyaṃ trimūrtaye
bahurūpādimadhyānta pariṇāmavivarjita 066.012
jagadīśasya sarvasya jagataḥ sarvakāmada
aham ātmabhavo deva tvayādhyakṣo nirūpitaḥ 066.013
so 'ham icchāmi taṃ jñātum ātmānaṃ prabhavāvyayam
viśvasya ca virūpasya sthāvarasya carasya ca 066.014
yadi te 'nugrahakṛtā mayi buddhir janārdana
tan māṃ bhakta iti jñātvā kathayātmānam acyuta 066.015
kathayāmi tavātmānam anākhyāgodaraṃ param
na vācāṃ viṣaye yo 'sāv aviśeṣaṇalakṣaṇaḥ 066.016
prasādasumukhaḥ so 'ham imaṃ yacchāmi te varam
anākhyātasvarūpaṃ māṃ bhavāñ jñāsyati yogataḥ 066.017
bhakto māṃ tattvato vetti mayi bhaktiś ca te parā
majjijñāsā parā brahmaṃs tena jātā matis tava 066.018
evam uktas tato brahmā viṣṇunā prabhaviṣṇunā
viṣṇoḥ svarūpaṃ jijñāsur yuyojātmānam ātmanā 066.019
sa dadarśātisūkṣmaṃ ca sūkṣmajyotiṣy ajaṃ vibhum
niyutārdhārdhamātreṇa vyāptāśeṣacarācaram 066.020
ātmānam indrarudrārka- candrāśvivasumārutān
khādīny atha ca śabdādīn dadṛśe ca sa tanmayān 066.021
ye vyaktā ye tathāvyaktā bhāvā ye cāpi pauruṣāḥ
tāṃś ca tatrātisūkṣmo 'pi dṛṣṭavān akhilān vibhuḥ 066.022
tataḥ praṇamya deveśam ajam ārtiharaṃ harim
pitāmahaḥ prahvatanur vākyam etad uvāca ha 066.023
jñātaṃ svarūpam ajñāta- svarūpa bhagavaṃs tava
mayā na yad vāgviṣaye tatrasthaṃ cākhilaṃ jagat 066.024
dhanyo 'smy anugṛhīto 'smi svarūpaṃ yan mayā tava
bhagavañ jñātam ajñātam anantāja namo 'stu te 066.025
yadi prasādaṃ deva tvaṃ prakaroṣi mamāparam
paramaṃ cāvatāreṣu yad rūpaṃ tad vadasva me 066.026
keṣu keṣu mayā jñeyaḥ sthāneṣu tvam adhokṣaja
saṃbhūtayo mamācakṣva yā bhaviṣyanti te bhuvi 066.027
devaloke nṛloke vā pātāle khe 'nyato 'pi vā
saṃbhūtayo yās tu bhavān kariṣyati vadasva tāḥ 066.028
tvaṃ kartā sarvabhūtānāṃ saṃhartā ceśvareśvaraḥ
tavāpi kartā nānyo 'sti svecchayā krīḍate bhavān
ahaṃ vedmi bhavantaṃ hi na tavānyo 'sti veditā 066.029
yan māṃ tvaṃ pṛcchasi brahman avatārāśritaṃ param
tat te samyak pravakṣyāmi nibodha mama suvrata 066.030
mama prakṛtyā saṃyogaḥ svecchayā saṃpravartate
deveṣu nR̥ṣu tiryakṣu sthāvareṣu careṣu ca
mamāvatārāḥ kāryārthaṃ jagataś copakāriṇaḥ 066.031
yadā yadā hi dharmasya glāniḥ samupajāyate
abhyutthānam adharmasya tadātmāṅgaṃ sṛjāmy aham 066.032
paritrāṇāya sādhūnāṃ vināśāya ca duṣkṛtāṃ
dharmasaṃsthāpanārthāya saṃbhavāmi yuge yuge 066.033
pūrvotpanneṣu bhūteṣu nṛdevādiṣu cāpy aham
anupraviśya dharmasya karomi paripālanam 066.034
praviśya ca tathā pūrvaṃ tanuṃ dharmabhṛtāṃ vara
jagato 'sya jagatsṛṣṭiṃ karomi sthitipālanam 066.035
devatve devikā ceṣṭā tiryaktve mama tāmasī
icchayā mānuṣatve ca vicarāmi nṛceṣṭayā 066.036
pratikṣaṇaṃ ca bhūteṣu sṛjāmi jagataḥ sthitim
karomi vidyamāneṣu dharmasaṃsthāpaneṣu ca 066.037
yad vai dharmopakārāya yac ca duṣṭanivarhaṇam
caritaṃ mānuṣādīnāṃ tad vai jānīhi matkṛtam 066.038
yac ca pṛcchasi māṃ brahman kāḥ kāḥ saṃbhūtayas tava
tāḥ śṛṇuṣva samāsena yā bhaviṣyanti sāṃpratam 066.039
matsyena bhūtvā pātālāt tava vedāḥ samuddhṛtāḥ
madhukaiṭabhābhyāṃ ca hṛtā dattāśvaśirasā mayā 066.040
tvam apy atra mahābhāga madaṃśaḥ kamalodarāt
mannābhisaṃbhavāj jātaḥ prajāsṛṣṭikaraḥ paraḥ 066.041
ekārṇavaṃ ca yad idaṃ brahman paśyasy aśeṣataḥ
asmin vasumatīṃ devīṃ magnāṃ pātālam āgatām 066.042
vedapādo yūpadaṃṣṭraḥ kratudantaś citīmukhaḥ
agnijihvo darbharomā brahmaśīrṣo mahātapāḥ 066.043
ahorātrekṣaṇadharo vedāṅgaśrutibhūṣaṇaḥ
ājyanāsaḥ śruvastuṇḍaḥ sāmaghoṣasvaro mahān 066.044
prāgvaṃśakāyo dyutimān nānādīkṣābhir ācitaḥ
dakṣiṇāhṛdayo yogī mahāsattramayo mahān 066.045
upakarmeṣṭiruciraḥ pravargāvartabhūṣaṇaḥ
nānācchandogatipatho brahmoktikarmavikramaḥ 066.046
bhūtvā yajñavarāho 'ham iti brahman rasātalāt
pṛthivīm uddhariṣyāmi sthāpayaiṣyāmi ca sthitau 066.047
parvatānāṃ nadīnāṃ ca dvīpādīnāṃ ca yā sthitiḥ
tāṃ ca tadvat kariṣyāmi śailādīnām anukramāt 066.048
hiraṇyākṣaṃ ca durvṛttaṃ kaśyapasyātmasaṃbhavam
tenaiva ghātayiṣyāmi rūpeṇāhaṃ prajāpate 066.049
utpādya pṛthivīṃ samyak sthāpayitvā yathā purā
sṛṣṭiṃ tataḥ kariṣyāmi tvām āviśya prajāpatim 066.050
jānāsi kāpilaṃ rūpaṃ prathamaṃ pauruṣaṃ mama
sarvavidyāpraṇetāraṃ tvayā vedeṣu darśitam
ravimaṇḍalamadhyastham agner yat paramaṃ padam 066.*(88)
tata utsṛjya rūpāṇi amarādivibhedataḥ
vyāpayiṣyāmi lokāṃs tu bhūlokādīm aśeṣataḥ 066.051
sṛṣṭaṃ jagad idaṃ deva- mānuṣyādiviśeṣaṇam
hiraṇyakaśipur daityas tāpayiṣyati vikramāt 066.052
vyaṃsayitvā varāṃs tasya tais tair hetubhir ātmavān
nṛsiṃharūpaṃ kṛtvāhaṃ ghātayiṣyāmi taṃ ripum 066.053
kṣīrābdau kūrmarūpo 'haṃ devānāṃ kamalodbhava
mandaraṃ dhārayiṣyāmi pṛṣṭhenāmṛtamanthane 066.054
hariṣyati ca devānāṃ yajñabhāgān yadā baliḥ
tadāhaṃ vāmano bhūtvā gatvā tasya mahādhvaram 066.055
vañcayitvāsurapatiṃ kariṣyāmi tripiṣṭapam
baliṃ cāpi kariṣyāmi pātālatalavāsinam 066.056
atrer dattvā varaṃ caiva tasya putratvam āgataḥ
dattātreyo bhaviṣyāmi nihaṃsyāmi tathāsurān 066.057
sattvānām upakārāya pradhānapuruṣāntaram
darśayiṣyāmi lokeṣu kāpilaṃ rūpam āsthitaḥ 066.058
kārtavīryādibhiś cānyaiś caturdaśabhir anvitāḥ
bhaviṣyanti madaṃśena tretāyāṃ cakravartinaḥ 066.059
tataś ca bhārgavo rāmo gṛhītaparaśur dvijaḥ
bhūtvā kṣatriyahīnāṃ ca kariṣyāmi vasuṃdharām 066.060
punaś ca rāghavo rāmo bhūtvā daśarathātmajaḥ
baddhvā mahodadhiṃ kartā rākṣasānāṃ kulakṣayam 066.061
uttīrya ca paraṃ pāraṃ laṅkām āsādya durjayām
nihatya rāvaṇaṃ vīraṃ varadānena darpitam
māyāvināṃ mahāvīryaṃ rakṣasāṃ vanaśāyinām
lakṣmaṇānucaro rāmaḥ kariṣyāmi kulakṣayam 066.*(89)
aṣṭāviṃśatime prāpte dvāpare kaṃsam ucchritam
keśinaṃ dhenukaṃ caiva śakuniṃ pūtanāṃ tathā
ariṣṭaṃ ca haniṣyāmi muruṃ narakam eva ca 066.062
niśumbhaṃ sahayagrīvaṇ tathānyāṃś cāsureśvarān
haniṣyāmi sudurvṛttāṃl lokānāṃ hitakāmyayā 066.063
pravarṣati sa devendre mahobhaṅgavirodhite
govardhanaṃ girivaraṃ dhārayiṣyāmi bāhunā 066.064
bhārākrāntām imām urvīṃ dhanaṃjayasahāyavān
ghātayitvākhilān bhūpāṃl laghvīṃ kartāsmi sattama 066.065
prāpte kaliyuge kṛtsnam upasaṃhṛtya vai kulam
dvārakāṃ plāvayiṣyāmi utsrakṣyāmi manuṣyatām 066.066
dvitīyo yo mamāṃśas tu rāmo 'nantaḥ sa lāṅgalī
so 'pi saṃtyajya vasudhāṃ rasātalam upeṣyati 066.067
tataḥ kaliyuge ghore saṃprāpte 'bjasamudbhava
śuddhodanasuto buddho bhaviṣyāmi vimatsaraḥ 066.068
bauddhaṃ dharmam upāśritya kariṣye dharmadeśanām
narāṇām atha nārīṇāṃ dayāṃ bhūteṣu darśayan 066.069
raktāmbarā hy āñjitākṣāḥ praśāntamanasas tataḥ
śūdrā dharmaṃ pravakṣyanti mayi buddhatvam āgate 066.070
eḍūkacihnā pṛthivī na devagṛhabhūṣitā
bhavitrī prāyaśo brahman mayi buddhatvam āgate 066.071
skandhadarśanamātraṃ hi paśyantaḥ sakalaṃ jagat
śūdrāḥ śūdreṣu dāsyanti mayi buddhatvam āgate 066.072
alpāyuṣas tato martyā mohopahatacetasaḥ
narakārhāṇi karmāṇi kariṣyanti prajāpate 066.073
svādhyāyeṣv avasīdanto brāhmaṇāḥ śaucavarjitāḥ
antyapratigrahādānaṃ kariṣyanty alpamedhasaḥ 066.074
na śroṣyanti pituḥ putrāḥ śvaśrūśvaśurayoḥ snuṣāḥ
na bhāryā bhartur īśasya na bhṛtyā vinayasthitāḥ 066.075
varṇasaṃkaratāṃ prāpte loke 'smin dasyutāṃ gate
brāhmaṇādiṣu varṇeṣu bhaviṣyaty adharottaram 066.076
dharmakañcukasaṃvītā vidharmarucayas tathā
mānuṣān bhakṣayiṣyanti mlecchāḥ pārthivarūpiṇaḥ 066.077
tataḥ kaliyugasyānte vedo vājasaneyakaḥ
daśa pañca ca vai śākhāḥ pramāṇena bhaviṣyati 066.078
tato 'haṃ saṃbhaviṣyāmi brāhmaṇo haripiṅgalaḥ
kalkī viṣṇuyaśaḥputro yājñavalkyapurohitaḥ 066.079
mlecchān utsādayiṣyāmi gṛhītāstraḥ kuśāyudhaḥ
sthāpayiṣyāmi maryādāś cāturvarṇye yathoditāḥ 066.080
tathāśrameṣu sarveṣu brahmacārivratādikāḥ
sthāpayitvā tataḥ sarvāḥ prajāḥ saddharmavartmani
kalkirūpaṃ parityajya divam eṣyāmy ahaṃ punaḥ 066.081
tataḥ kṛtayugaṃ bhūyaḥ pūrvavat saṃpravartsyate
varṇāśramāś ca dharmeṣu dveṣu sthāsyanti sattama 066.082
evaṃ sarveṣu kalpeṣu sarvamanvantareṣu ca
mamāvatārāḥ śataśo ye bhavanti jagaddhitāḥ 066.083
saṃkarṣaṇātmajaś caiva kalpānte ca rasātalāt
samutpatsyet tadā rudraḥ kālāgnir iti yaḥ śrutaḥ 066.084
tataḥ kṣayaṃ kariṣyāmi jagat sthāvarajaṅgamam
bhūyaś caiva hi svapsyāmi jagaty ekārṇave sthite
tvadrūpī ca tato bhūtvā jagat srakṣyāmy ahaṃ punaḥ 066.085
etat saṃkṣepato brahman mayākhyātaṃ yathātatham
aṃśāvataraṇaṃ sarvaṃ mattaḥ saṃkṣepataḥ śṛṇu 066.086
yad dṛśyaṃ yac ca vai spṛśyaṃ yad ghreyaṃ rasyate ca yat
yac chravyaṃ yac ca mantavyaṃ bodhavyaṃ cāham aṃśagaḥ 066.087
yat tu buddheḥ parataram anākhyeyam anopamam
tad ahaṃ brahma nirdvandvaṃ yad vai paśyanti sūrayaḥ 066.088
idaṃ janmarahasyaṃ me yo naraḥ kīrtayiṣyati
sulabho 'haṃ bhaviṣyāmi tasya janmani janmani 066.089
paṭhann etad brahmahā tu surāpo gurutalpagaḥ
steyī kṛtaghno goghnaś ca sarvapāpaiḥ pramucyate 066.090
garbhiṇī janayet putraṃ kanyā vindati satpatim
labhante 'bhimatān kāmān narās tāṃs tān yathepsitān 066.091
iti devātidevena brahmaṇo vyaktajanmanaḥ
rahasyam idam ākhyātaṃ tavāpi kathitaṃ mayā 066.092
viṣṇuḥ sarvagato 'nantaḥ sarvaṃ tatra pratiṣṭhitam
sa ca sarvam idaṃ rājan na tato vidyate param 066.093
etat pavitraṃ paṭhitaṃ tathā duḥsvapnanāśanam
jātismaratvaṃ prajñāṃ ca dadāti paṭhatāṃ nṛṇām 066.094
mayā hi devadevasya viṣṇor amitatejasaḥ
śrutāḥ saṃbhūtayaḥ sarvā gadatas tava suvrata 067.001
yadi prasanno bhagavān anugrāhyo 'smi vā yadi
tad ahaṃ śrotum icchāmi nR̥ṇāṃ duḥsvapnanāśanam 067.002
svapnā hi sumahābhāga dṛśyante ye śubhāśubhāḥ
phalāni te prayacchanti tadguṇāny eva bhārgava 067.003
yad yat puṇyaṃ pavitraṃ ca nR̥ṇām atiśubhapradam
duḥsvapnopaśamāyālaṃ tan me vistarato vada 067.004
idam eva mahārāja pṛṣṭavāṃs te pitāmahaḥ
bhīṣmaṃ dharmabhṛtāṃ śreṣṭhaṃ dharmaputro yudhiṣṭhiraḥ 067.005
devavrataṃ mahāprājñaṃ sarvaśāstraviśāradam
vinayenopasaṃgamya paryapṛcchad yudhiṣṭhiraḥ 067.006
duḥsvapnadarśanaṃ ghoram avekṣya bharatarṣabha
prayataḥ kiṃ japej japyaṃ vibuddhaḥ kim anusmaret 067.007
pitāmaha mahābuddhe buddher bhedo mahān ayam
tad ahaṃ śrotum icchāmi brūhi me vadatāṃ vara 067.008
śṛṇu rājan mahābāho vartayiṣyāmi te 'khilam
duḥsvapnadarśane japyaṃ yad vai nityaṃ samāhitaiḥ 067.009
atrāpy udāharantīmam itihāsaṃ purātanam
gajendramokṣaṇaṃ puṇyaṃ kṛṣṇasyākliṣṭakarmaṇaḥ 067.010
sarvaratnamayaḥ śrīmāṃs trikūṭo nāma parvataḥ
sutaḥ parvatarājasya sumeror bhāskaradyuteḥ 067.011
kṣīrodajalavīcyagrair dhautāmalaśilātalaḥ
utthitaḥ sāgaraṃ bhittvā devarṣigaṇasevitaḥ 067.012
apsarobhiḥ samākīrṇaḥ śrīmān prasravaṇākulaḥ
gandharvaiḥ kiṃnarair yakṣaiḥ siddhacāraṇapannagaiḥ 067.013
vidyādharaiḥ sapatnikaiḥ saṃyataiś ca tapasvibhiḥ 067.*(92)
mṛgair dvīpair dvijaiś caiva vṛtaḥ sauvarṇarājataiḥ
puṃnāgaiḥ karṇikāraiś ca puṣpitair upaśobhitaḥ 067.014
cūtanīpakadambaiś ca candanāgarucampakaiḥ
śālais tālais tamālaiś ca kuṭajaiś cārjunais tathā 067.015
evaṃ bahuvidhair vṛkṣaiḥ sarvataḥ samalaṃkṛtaḥ
nānādhātūjjvalaiḥ śṛṅgaiḥ prasravadbhiḥ samantataḥ 067.016
mṛgaiḥ śākhāmṛgaiḥ siṃhair mātaṃgaiś ca sadāmadaiḥ
jīvaṃjīvakasaṃghuṣṭaṃ cakoraśikhināditam 067.017
tasyaikaṃ kāñcanaṃ śṛṅgaṃ sevate yad divādaraḥ
nānāpuṣpasamākīrṇaṃ nānāgandhasamākulam 067.018
dvitīyaṃ rājataṃ śṛṅgaṃ sevate yan niśākaraḥ
pāṇḍurāmbudasaṃkāśaṃ tuṣāracayasaṃnibham 067.019
vajrendranīlavaiḍūrya- tejobhir bhāsayan nabhaḥ
tṛtīyaṃ brahmasadanaṃ prakṛṣṭaṃ śṛṅgam uttamam 067.020
na tat kṛtaghnāḥ paśyanti na nṛśaṃsā na nāstikāḥ
nātaptatapasaḥ śailaṃ taṃ vai paśyanti mānavāḥ 067.021
tasya sānumataḥ pṛṣṭhe saraḥ kāñcanapaṅkajam
kāraṇḍavasamākīrṇaṃ rājahaṃsopaśobhitam 067.022
mattabhramarasaṃghuṣṭaṃ phullapaṅkajaśobhitam
kumudotpalakalhāra- puṇḍarīkopaśobhitam 067.023
utpalaiḥ śatapattraiś ca kāñcanaiḥ samalaṃkṛtam
pattrair maṇidalaprakhyaiḥ puṣpaiḥ kāñcanasaṃnibhaiḥ
gulmaiḥ kīcakaveṇūnāṃ samantāt parivāritam 067.024
tasmin sarasi duṣṭātmā virūpo 'ntarjalāśayaḥ
āsīd grāho gajendrāṇāṃ durādharṣo mahābalaḥ 067.025
atha dantojjvalamukhaḥ kadācid gajayūthapaḥ
ājagāmāsitābhrābhaḥ kareṇuparivāritaḥ 067.026
madasrāvī mahāraudraḥ pādacārīva parvataḥ
vāsayan madagandhena girim airāvatopamaḥ 067.027
sa gajo 'ñjanasaṃkāśo madāc calitamānasaḥ
salīlaṃ paṅkajavane yūthamadhyagato 'vrajat 067.028
gandhahastīti vikhyātaḥ saraḥ samabhigamya tat
tṛṣitaḥ sa jalaṃ prāpya kusumākaraśītalam
apibat sahasā rājan kareṇuparivāritaḥ 067.*(94)
gṛhītas tena raudreṇa grāheṇāvyaktamūrtinā
paśyantīnāṃ kareṇūnāṃ krośantīnāṃ ca dāruṇam 067.029
kriyate paṅkajavane grāheṇātibalīyasā 067.*(95)
gajaś cākarṣate tīraṃ grāhaś cākarṣate jalam
tayor dvandva mahāyuddhaṃ divyavarṣasahasrikam 067.*(96)
vāruṇaiḥ saṃyataḥ pāśair niḥprayatnagatiḥ kṛtaḥ
veṣṭyamānaḥ sughorais tu pāśair nāgo dṛḍhais tathā 067.030
visphurjya ca yathāśakti vikruśya ca mahāravān
vyathitaḥ saṃnirutsāho gṛhīto ghorakarmaṇā 067.031
paramāpadam āpanno manasācintayad dharim
sa tu nāgavaraḥ śrīmān nārāyaṇaparāyaṇaḥ 067.032
tam eva paramaṃ devaṃ gataḥ sarvātmanā tadā
ekāgraṃ cintayām āsa viśuddhenāntarātmanā 067.033
janmajanmāntarābhyāsād bhaktimān garuḍadhvaje
ādyaṃ devaṃ mahātmānaṃ pūjayām āsa keśavam 067.034
navameghapratīkāśaṃ śaṅkhacakragadādharam
sahasraśubhanāmānam ādidevam ajaṃ param 067.035
digbāhuṃ sarvamūrdhānaṃ bhūpādaṃ gaganodaram
ādityacandranayanaṃ samagraṃ lokasākṣiṇam 067.*(98)
bhagavantaṃ prasanno 'haṃ viṣṇum apratimaujasam 067.*(99)
pragṛhya puṣkarāgreṇa kāñcanaṃ kamalottamam
āpadvimokṣam anvicchan gajaḥ stotram udairayat 067.036
oṃ namo mūlaprakṛtaye ajitāya mahātmane 067.*(100),001
anāśritāya devāya niḥspṛhāya namo namaḥ 067.*(100),002
nama ādyāya bījāya śivāya ca praśāntāya 067.*(100),003
ārṣeyāya pravartine niścalāya yaśasvine 067.*(100),004
anantarāya caikāya sanātanāya pūrvāya 067.*(100),005
avyaktāya namo namaḥ purāṇāya namo namaḥ 067.*(100),006
namo guhyāya gūḍhāya 067.*(100),007
guṇāyāguṇavartine 067.*(100),008
atarkyāyāprameyāya 067.*(100),009
anantāya namo namaḥ 067.*(100),010
namo devātidevāya 067.*(100),011
aprabhāya namo namaḥ 067.*(100),012
namo jagatprasthitāya govindāya namo namaḥ 067.*(100),013
namo 'stu padmanābhāya sāṃkhyayogodbhavāya ca 067.*(100),014
viśveśvarāya devāya śivāya haraye namaḥ 067.*(100),015
namo 'stu tasmai devāya nirguṇāya guṇātmane 067.*(100),016
nārāyaṇāya viśvāya devānāṃ paramātmane 067.*(100),017
namo namaḥ kāraṇavāmanāya nārāyaṇāyāmitavikramāya
śrīśārṅgacakrāsigadādharāya namo 'stu tasmai puruṣottamāya 067.037
ādyāya vedanilayāya mahodarāya siṃhāya daityanidhanāya caturbhujāya
brahmendrarudramunicāraṇasaṃstutāya devottamāya varadāya namo 'cyutāya 067.038
nāgendrabhogaśayanāsanasupriyāya gokṣīrahemaśukanīlaghanopamāya
pītāmbarāya madhukaiṭabhanāśanāya bhaktipriyāya varadīptasudarśanāya 067.039
viśvāya cārumukuṭāya namo 'kṣarāya 067.*(101)
nābhiprajātakamalasthacaturmukhāya kṣīrodakārṇavaniketayaśodhanāya
nānāvicitramukuṭāṅgadabhūṣaṇāya sarveśvarāya varadāya namo varāya 067.040
viśvātmane paramakāraṇakāraṇāya phullāravindavimalāyatalocanāya
devendradānavaparīkṣitapauruṣāya yogeśvarāya vijayāya namo varāya 067.041
lokāyanāya tridaśāyanāya brahmāyanāyātmabhavāyanāya
dharmāyanāyaikajalāyanāya mahāvarāhāya sadā nato 'smi 067.042
acintyam avyaktam anantarūpaṃ nārāyaṇaṃ kāraṇam ādidevam
yugāntaśeṣaṃ puruṣaṃ purāṇaṃ taṃ vāsudevaṃ śaraṇaṃ prapadye 067.043
yogeśvaraṃ cāruvicitramaulim ājñeyamaukhyaṃ prakṛteḥ parastham
kṣetrajñam ātmaprabhavaṃ vareṇyaṃ taṃ vāsudevaṃ śaraṇaṃ prapadye 067.*(104)
adṛśyam acchedyam anādimadhyaṃ maharṣayo brahmavidaḥ sureśam
vadanti yaṃ vai puruṣaṃ sanātanaṃ taṃ vāsudevaṃ śaraṇaṃ prapadye 067.044
yad akṣaraṃ brahma vadanti sarvagaṃ niśāmya yaṃ mṛtyumukhāt pramucyate
tam īśvaraṃ tṛptam anopamair guṇaiḥ parāyaṇaṃ viṣṇum upaimi śāśvatam 067.045
kāryaṃ kriyākāraṇam aprameyaṃ hiraṇyanābhaṃ varapadmanābham
mahābalaṃ vedanidhiṃ surottamaṃ vrajāmi viṣṇuṃ śaraṇaṃ janārdanam 067.046
vicitrakeyūramahārhaniṣkaṃ ratnottamālaṃkṛtasarvagātram
pītāmbaraṃ kāñcanabhakticitraṃ mālādharaṃ keśavam abhyupaimi 067.047
bhavodbhavaṃ vedavidāṃ variṣṭhaṃ yogātmānaṃ sāṃkhyavidāṃ variṣṭham
ādityacandrāśvivasuprabhāvaṃ prabhuṃ prapadye 'cyutam ātmabhūtam 067.048
śrīvatsāṅkaṃ mahādevaṃ vedaguhyam anuttamam
prapadye sūkṣmam acalaṃ bhaktānām abhayapradam 067.049
prabhavaṃ sarvalokānāṃ nirguṇaṃ parameśvaram
prapadye muktasaṃgānāṃ yatīnāṃ paramāṃ gatim 067.050
bhagavantaṃ surādhyakṣam akṣaraṃ puṣkarekṣaṇam
śaraṇyaṃ śaraṇaṃ bhaktyā prapadye brāhmaṇapriyam 067.051
trivikramaṃ trilokeśam ādyam ekam anāmayam
bhūtātmānaṃ mahātmānaṃ prapadye madhusūdanam 067.052
ādidevam ajaṃ śambhuṃ vyaktāvyaktaṃ janārdanam 067.*(105)
kṣetrajñaṃ puruṣaṃ yajñaṃ triguṇātītam avyayam
nārāyaṇam aṇīyāṃsaṃ prapadye parameśvaram 067.053
ekāya lokatrayāya parataḥ paramātmane
namaḥ sahasraśirase anantāya mahātmane 067.054
vareṇyam anaghaṃ devam ṛṣayo vedapāragāḥ
kīrtayanti ca yaṃ sarve taṃ prapadye sanātanam 067.055
namas te puṇḍarīkākṣa bhaktānām abhayaprada
subrahmaṇya namas te 'stu trāhi māṃ śaraṇāgatam 067.056
bhaktiṃ tasyānusaṃcintya nāgasyāmoghasaṃstavam
prītimān abhavad rājañ śaṅkhacakragadādharaḥ
sāṃnidhyaṃ kalpayām āsa tasmin sarasi mādhavaḥ 067.057
grāhagrastaṃ gajaṃ taṃ ca saṃgṛhya salilāśayāt
ujjahārāprameyātmā tarasaivārisūdanaḥ 067.058
sthalasthaṃ dārayām āsa grāhaṃ cakreṇa mādhavaḥ
mokṣayām āsa ca gajaṃ pāśebhyaḥ śaraṇāgatam 067.059
sa hi devalaśāpena hūhū gandharvasattamaḥ
gajatvam agamat kṛṣṇān mokṣaṃ prāpya divaṃ gataḥ
śāpād vimuktaḥ sadyaś ca gajo gandharvatāṃ gataḥ 067.060
grāho 'pi yakṣatāṃ yāto yaḥ kṛṣṇena nipātitaḥ
tasyāpi śāpamokṣo 'sau jaigīṣavyakṛto 'bhavat 067.061
prītimāṃs trāti govindaḥ sadyaḥ saṃsārasāgarāt
kruddho 'pi nighnan devatvam arātīnāṃ prayacchati 067.062
tau ca svaṃ svaṃ vapuḥ prāpya praṇipatya janārdanam
gandharvarāṭ tathā yakṣaḥ parāṃ nirvṛtim āgatau 067.063
idaṃ caiva mahābāho devadevo 'bhyabhāṣata
dṛṣṭvā muktau gajagrahau bhagavān madhusūdanaḥ 067.064
yo grāhaṃ nāgarājaṃ ca māṃ caiva praṇidhānavān
smariṣyati saraś cedaṃ yuvayor mokṣaṇaṃ tathā 067.065
gulmaṃ kīcakaveṇūnāṃ taṃ ca śailavaraṃ tathā
aśvatthaṃ bhāskaraṃ gaṅgāṃ naimiṣāraṇyam eva ca 067.066
saṃsmariṣyanti ye martyāḥ samyak śroṣyanti vāpi ye
na te duḥsvapnapāpasya bhoktāro matparigrahāt 067.067
sarvapāpaiḥ pramokṣyante kalyāṇānāṃ ca bhāginaḥ
bhaviṣyanti tathā puṇyāṃ gatiṃ yāsyanti mānavāḥ
duḥsvapnaṃ ca nṛṇāṃ teṣāṃ susvapnaṃ ca bhaviṣyati 067.068
kaurmaṃ mātsyaṃ ca vārāhaṃ vāmanaṃ tārkṣyam eva ca
nārasiṃhaṃ tathā rūpaṃ sṛṣṭisaṃhārakārakam 067.069
etāni prātar utthāya saṃsmariṣyanti ye narāḥ
sarvapāpavinirmuktās te yānti paramāṃ gatim 067.070
evam uktvā tu rājendra devadevo janārdanaḥ
aspṛśad gajagandharvaṃ grāhayakṣaṃ ca taṃ tadā 067.071
tena spṛṣṭāv ubhau sadyo divyamālyāmbarānvitau
vimāne 'bhimate prāpya jagmatus tridaśālayam 067.072
tato devapatiḥ kṛṣṇo mokṣayitvā gajottamam
ṛṣibhiḥ stūyamāno hi guhyair vedapadākṣaraiḥ
gataḥ sa bhagavān viṣṇur durvijñeyagatiḥ prabhuḥ 067.073
gajendramokṣaṇaṃ dṛṣṭvā sarve cendrapurogamāḥ
brahmāṇam agrataḥ kṛtvā sarve prāñjalayo 'bhavan 067.074
vavandire mahātmānaṃ prabhuṃ nārāyaṇaṃ harim
vismayotphullanayanāḥ prajāpatipuraḥsarāḥ
ya idaṃ śṛṇuyān nityaṃ prātar utthāya mānavaḥ
prāpnuyāt paramāṃ siddhiṃ duḥsvapnas tasya naśyati 067.*(107)
gajendramokṣaṇaṃ puṇyaṃ sarvapāpapramocanam
śrāvayet prātar utthāya sarvapāpaiḥ pramucyate 067.075
śraddhayā hi kuruśreṣṭha smṛtena kathitena ca
gajendramokṣaṇeneha dīrgham āyur avāpnuyāt 067.076
mayā te kathitaṃ divyaṃ pavitraṃ pāpanāśanam
kīrtayasva mahābāho mahāduḥsvapnanāśanam 067.077
kīrtyamānaṃ ca viprebhyaḥ śṛṇu bhaktyā yathoditam 067.*(108)
gajendramokṣaṇaṃ śrutvā kuntīputro yudhiṣṭhiraḥ
bhīṣmād bhagīrathīputrāt pūjayām āsa keśavam 067.078
ye cāpi pāṇḍuputrasya samīpasthā dvijottamāḥ
te 'pi bhīṣmasya pārśvasthaṃ vāsudevaṃ praṇemire 067.079
varaṃ vareṇyaṃ varapadmanābhaṃ nārāyaṇaṃ brahmanidhiṃ sureśam
taṃ devaguhyaṃ puruṣaṃ purāṇaṃ vavandire brahmavidāṃ variṣṭham 067.080
etat puṇyaṃ mahārāja narāṇāṃ pāpakarmaṇām
duḥsvapnadarśane ghore śrutvā pāpāt pramucyate
bhaktimān puṇḍarīkākṣe gajo duḥkhād vimocitaḥ 067.081
tathā tvam api rājendra prapadya śaraṇaṃ harim
vimuktaḥ sarvapāpebhyaḥ prāpsyase paramāṃ gatim 067.082
mahāmate mahāprājña sarvaśāstraviśārada
akṣīṇakarmabandhas tu puruṣo dvijasattama 068.001
maraṇe yaj japañ japyaṃ yac ca bhāvaṃ anusmaran
paraṃ padam avāpnoti tan me vada mahāmune 068.002
śrīvatsāṅkaṃ jagadbījam anantaṃ lokabhāvanam
purā nārāyaṇaṃ devaṃ nāradaḥ paryapṛcchata 068.003
bhagavan bhūtabhavyeśa śraddadhānair jitendriyaiḥ
kathaṃ bhaktair vicintyo 'si maraṇe pratyupasthite 068.004
kiṃ vā japyaṃ japen nityaṃ kalyam utthāya mānavaḥ
svapan vibudhyan dhyāyaṃś ca tan me brūhi sanātana 068.005
śrutvā tasya tu devarṣer vākyaṃ vākyaviśāradaḥ
provāca bhagavān viṣṇur nāradaṃ jagato gatiḥ 068.006
hanta te kathayiṣyāmi mune divyām anusmṛtim
maraṇe yām anusmṛtya prāpnoti paramāṃ gatim 068.007
oṃkāram āditaḥ kṛtvā mām anusmṛtya manmanāḥ
ekāgraprayato bhūtvā idaṃ mantram udīrayet 068.008
avyaktaṃ śāśvataṃ devam anantaṃ puruṣottamam
prapadye prāñjalir viṣṇum acyutaṃ parameśvaram 068.009
purāṇaṃ paramaṃ viṣṇum adbhutaṃ lokabhāvanam
prapadye puṇḍarīkākṣam īśaṃ bhaktānukampinam 068.010
lokanāthaṃ prapanno 'smi akṣaraṃ paramaṃ padam
bhagavantaṃ prapanno 'smi bhūtabhavyabhavatprabhum 068.011
sraṣṭāraṃ sarvabhūtānām anantabalapauruṣam
padmanābhaṃ hṛṣīkeśaṃ papadye satyam avyayam 068.012
hiraṇyagarbhaṃ bhūgarbham amṛtaṃ viśvatomukham
ābhāsvaram anādyantaṃ prapadye bhāskaradyutim 068.013
sahasraśirasaṃ devaṃ vaikuṇṭhaṃ tārkṣyavāhanam
prapadye sūkṣmam acalaṃ vareṇyam abhayapradam 068.014
nārāyaṇaṃ naraṃ haṃsaṃ yogātmānaṃ sanātanam
śaraṇyaṃ sarvalokānāṃ prapadye dhruvam īśvaram 068.015
yaḥ prabhuḥ sarvalokānāṃ yena sarvam idaṃ tatam 068.016
carācaragurur devaḥ sa no viṣṇuḥ prasīdatu 068.016,*(110)
yasmāj jātaḥ purā brahmā padmayoniḥ pitāmahaḥ
prasīdatu sa no viṣṇuḥ pitā mātā pitāmahaḥ 068.017
yaḥ purā pralaye prāpte naṣṭe loke carācare
ekas tiṣṭhati yogātmā sa no viṣṇuḥ prasīdatu 068.018
caturbhiś ca caturbhiś ca dvābhyāṃ pañcabhir eva ca
hūyate ca punar dvābhyāṃ sa no viṣṇuḥ prasīdatu 068.*(109)
parjanyaḥ pṛthivī sasyaṃ kālo dharmaḥ kriyā phalam
guṇākaraḥ sa no babhrur vāsudevaḥ prasīdatu 068.019
yogāvāsa namas tubhyaṃ sarvāvāsa varaprada
yajñagarbha mahābhāga pañcayajña namo 'stu te 068.020
caturmūrte jagaddhāma lakṣmyāvāsa varaprada
sarvāvāsa namas te 'stu sākṣibhūta jagatpate 068.021
ajeya khaṇḍaparaśo viśvamūrte vṛṣākape
trigarte pañcakālajña namas te jñānasāgara 068.022
avyaktād aṇḍam utpannam avyaktādyaḥ paraḥ prabhuḥ
yasmāt parataraṃ nāsti tam asmi śaraṇaṃ gataḥ 068.023
cintayanto hi yaṃ nityaṃ brahmeśānādayaḥ prabhum
niścayaṃ nādhigacchanti tam asmi śaraṇaṃ gataḥ 068.024
jitendriyā mahātmāno jñānadhyānaparāyaṇāḥ
yaṃ prāpya na nivartante tam asmi śaraṇaṃ gataḥ 068.025
ekāṃśena jagat sarvaṃ yo 'vaṣṭabhya vibhuḥ sthitaḥ
agrāhyo nirguṇaḥ śāstā tam asmi śaraṇaṃ gataḥ 068.026
divākarasya saumyaṃ hi madhye jyotir avasthitam
kṣetrajñam iti yaṃ prāhuḥ sa mahātmā prasīdatu 068.027
avyaktam anavasthāno durvijñeyaḥ sanātanaḥ
āsthitaḥ prakṛtiṃ bhuṅkte sa mahātmā prasīdatu 068.028
kṣetrajñaḥ pañcadhā bhuṅkte prakṛtiṃ bahubhir guṇaiḥ
manoguṇāṃś ca yo bhuṅkte sa mahātmā prasīdatu 068.029
sāṃkhyā yogāś ca ye cānye siddhāś caiva maharṣayaḥ
yaṃ viditvā vimucyante sa mahātmā prasīdatu 068.030
namas te sarvatobhadra sarvato'kṣiśiromukha
nirvikāra namas te 'stu sākṣibhūta hṛdi sthita
atīndriya namas tubhyaṃ liṅgebhyas tvaṃ pramīyase 068.031
ye tu tvāṃ nābhijānanti saṃsāre saṃsaranti te
rāgadveṣavinirmuktaṃ lobhamohavivarjitam
aśarīraṃ śarīrasthaṃ samaṃ sarveṣu dehiṣu 068.032
avyaktaṃ buddhyahaṃkārau mahābhūtendriyāṇi ca
tvayi tāni na teṣu tvaṃ teṣu tvaṃ tāni na tvayi 068.033
sraṣṭā bhoktāsi kūṭastho guṇānāṃ prabhur īśvaraḥ
akartā heturahitaḥ prabhuḥ svātmany avasthitaḥ 068.034
namas te puṇḍarīkākṣa punar eva namo 'stu te
īśvaro 'si jagannātha kim ataḥ param ucyate
bhaktānāṃ yad dhitaṃ deva tad dhyāya tridaśeśvara 068.035
mā me bhūteṣu saṃyogaḥ punar bhavatu janmani
ahaṃkāreṇa buddhyā vā tathā sattvādibhir guṇaiḥ 068.036
mā me dharmo hy adharmo vā punar bhavatu janmani
viṣayair indriyair vāpi mā me bhūyāt samāgamaḥ 068.037
pṛthivīṃ yātu me ghrāṇaṃ yātu me rasanā jalam
cakṣur hutāśanaṃ yātu sparśo me yātu mārutam 068.038
śabdo hy ākāśam abhyetu mano vaikārikaṃ tathā
ahaṃkāraś ca me buddhiṃ tvayi buddhiḥ sametu ca 068.039
viyogaḥ sarvakaraṇair guṇair bhūtaiś ca me bhavet
sattvaṃ rajas tamaś caiva prakṛtiṃ praviśantu me 068.040
niṣkevalaṃ padaṃ caiva prayāmi paramaṃ tava
ekībhāvas tvayaivāstu mā me janma bhavet punaḥ 068.041
namo bhagavate tasmai viṣṇave prabhaviṣṇave
tvanmanas tvadgatapṛāṇas tvadbhaktas tvatparāyaṇaḥ
tvām evānusmare deva maraṇe pratyupasthite 068.042
pūrvadehakṛtā ye me vyādhayas te viśantu mām
ārdayantu ca duḥkhāni pravimuñcāmi yad ṛṇam 068.043
upatiṣṭhantu me rogā ye mayā pūrvasaṃcitāḥ
anṛṇo gantum icchāmi tad viṣṇoḥ paramaṃ padam 068.044
ahaṃ bhagavatas tasya mama cāsau sureśvaraḥ
tasyāhaṃ na praṇaśyāmi sa ca me na praṇaśyati 068.045
namo bhagavate tasmai yena sarvam idaṃ tatam
tam eva ca prapanno 'smi mama yo yasya cāpy aham 068.046
imām anusmṛtiṃ nityaṃ vaiṣṇavīṃ pāpanāśanīm
svapañ jāgrat paṭhed yas tu trisaṃdhyaṃ vāpi yaḥ smaret 068.047
maraṇe cāpy anuprāpte yas tv imāṃ samanusmaret
api pāpasamācāraḥ so 'pi yāti parāṃ gatim 068.048
arcayann api yo devaṃ gṛhe vāpi baliṃ dadet
juhvad agniṃ smared vāpi labhate sa parāṃ gatim 068.049
paurṇamāsyām amāvāsyāṃ dvādaśyāṃ ca viśeṣataḥ
śrāvayec chraddadhānaṃs tu ye cānye mām upāśritāḥ 068.050
nama ity eva yo brūyān madbhaktaḥ śraddhayānvitaḥ
tasya syur akṣayā lokāḥ śvapākasyāpi nārada 068.051
kiṃ punar ye yajante māṃ sādhavo vidhipūrvakam
dhyāyanti ca yathānyāyaṃ te yānti paramāṃ gatim 068.052
aśvamedhasahasrāṇāṃ yaḥ sahasraṃ samācaret
nāsau tat padam āpnoti madbhaktair yad avāpyate 068.053
iṣṭaṃ dattaṃ tapo 'dhītaṃ vratāni niyamāś ca ye
sarvam etad vināśāntaṃ jñānasyānto na vidyate 068.054
tasmāt pradeyaṃ sādhubhyo dharmyaṃ sattvābhayaṃkaram
dānādīny antavantīha madbhakto nāntam aśnute 068.055
yo dadyād bhagavajjñānaṃ kuryād vā dharmadeśanām
kṛtsnāṃ vā pṛthivīṃ dadyān na tu tulyaṃ kathaṃcana 068.056
kāntāravanadurgeṣu kṛcchreṣv āpatsu saṃbhrame
dasyubhiḥ saṃniruddhaś ca nāmabhir māṃ prakīrtayet 068.057
varāho rakṣatu jale viṣameṣu ca vāmanaḥ
aṭavyāṃ nārasiṃhas tu sarvataḥ pātu keśavaḥ 068.058
rāmo rāmaś ca rāmaś ca trāyantāṃ dasyudoṣataḥ 068.*(111)
baddhaḥ parikaras tena mokṣāya gamanaṃ prati
sakṛd uccāritaṃ yena harir ity akṣaradvayam 068.059
janmāntarasahasrāṇi tapojñānasamādhibhiḥ
narāṇāṃ kṣīṇapāpānāṃ kṛṣṇe bhaktiḥ prajāyate
gatvā gatvā nivartane candrasūryādayo grahāḥ
adyāpi na nivartante dvādaśākṣaracintakāḥ
na vāsudevāt param asti maṅgalaṃ na vāsudevāt paramaṃ pavitram
na vāsudevāt param asti daivataṃ na vāsudevaṃ praṇipatya sīdati 068.*(112)
tasmān mām eva devarṣe dhyāyasvātandritaḥ sadā
avāpsyasi tataḥ siddhiṃ padaṃ drakṣyasi ca dhruvam 068.060
evaṃ sa devadevena nāradaḥ pratibodhitaḥ
cakāra keśave bhaktiṃ tasmāt tvaṃ kuru bhūpate 068.061
yaḥ paṭhet parayā bhaktyā sa gacched viṣṇusāmyatām
etat puṇyaṃ pāpaharaṃ dhanyaṃ duḥsvapnanāśanam 068.*(113)
pāpaṃ praṇaśyate yena puṇyaṃ yena vivardhate
yaj japan sugatiṃ yāti śṛṇvaṃś ca mama tad vada 069.001
kaścid āsīd dvijadrogdhā piśunaḥ kṣatriyādhamaḥ
parapīḍārucir duṣṭaḥ svabhāvād eva nirghṛṇaḥ 069.002
paribhūtāḥ sadā tena pitṛdevadvijātayaḥ
paradāreṣu caivāsya babhūvābhirataṃ manaḥ 069.003
sa tv āyuṣi parikṣīṇe jajñe ghoro niśācaraḥ
tena vai karmadoṣeṇa svena pāpakṛtāṃ varaḥ 069.004
krūrair eva tato vṛttiṃ rākṣasatve viśeṣataḥ
cakāra karmabhiḥ pāpaḥ sarvaprāṇivihiṃsakaḥ 069.005
tasya pāparatasyaivaṃ jagmur varṣaśatāni vai
tena vai karmadoṣeṇa nānyā vṛttir arocata 069.006
yad yat paśyati sattvaṃ sa tat tad ādāya rākṣasaḥ
cakhāda puruṣavyāghra bāhugocaram āgatam 069.007
evaṃ tasyātiduṣṭasya kurvataḥ prāṇināṃ vadham
jagāma sumahān kālaḥ pariṇāmaṃ tathā vayaḥ 069.008
sa dadarśa tapasyantaṃ tāpasaṃ saṃśritavratam
ūrdhvabāhuṃ mahābhāgaṃ kṛtarakṣaṃ samantataḥ 069.009
taṃ dṛṣṭvā sa tu durbuddhir brāhmaṇaṃ rākṣasādhamaḥ
samabhyadhāvad vegena samādātuṃ cikhādiṣuḥ 069.010
tena rakṣā ca yā dikṣu brāhmaṇenābhavat kṛtā
tayā nirastaṃ tad rakṣo nipapātāvidūrataḥ 069.011
bhagavan kīdṛśīṃ rakṣāṃ sa cakāra dvijottamaḥ
yayā nirdhūtavīryo 'sau nirasto rajanīcaraḥ 069.012
ekāgracitto govinde taj japaṃs tatparāyaṇaḥ
tapaś cacāra vipro 'sau praviṣṭo viṣṇupañjaram 069.013
viṣṇupañjaram icchāmi śrotuṃ dharmabhṛtāṃ vara
sadā sarvabhayebhyas tu rakṣā yā paramābhavat 069.014
tripuraṃ jaghnuṣaḥ pūrvaṃ brahmaṇā viṣṇupañjaraḥ
śaṃkarasya kuruśreṣṭha rakṣaṇāya nirūpitaḥ 069.015
vāgīśena tu śakrasya balaṃ hantuṃ prayāsyataḥ
tasya rūpaṃ pravakṣyāmi tan nibodha mahīpate 069.016
viṣṇuḥ prācyāṃ sthitaś cakrī viṣṇur dakṣiṇato gadī
pratīcyāṃ śārṅgadhṛg viṣṇur viṣṇuḥ khaḍgī mamottare 069.017
hṛṣīkeśo vikoṇeṣu tacchidreṣu janārdanaḥ
kroḍarūpī harir bhūmau narasiṃho 'mbare mama 069.018
kṣurāntam amalaṃ cakraṃ bhramaty etat sudarśanam
asyāṃśumālā duḥprekṣā hantu pretaniśācarān 069.019
gadā ceyaṃ sahasrārcir udvamatpāvakolvaṇā
rakṣobhūtapiśācānāṃ ḍākiṇīnāṃ ca nāśanī 069.020
śārṅgavisphūrjitaṃ caiva vāsudevasya madripūn
tiryaṅmanuṣyakūṣmāṇḍa- pretādīn hantv aśeṣataḥ 069.021
khaḍgadhārājvalajjyotsnā- nirdhūtā ye samāhatāḥ
te yāntu saumyataṃ sadyo garuḍeneva pannagāḥ 069.022
ye kūṣmāṇḍās tathā yakṣā ye daityā ye niśācarāḥ
pretā vināyakāḥ krūrā manuṣyā jambhakāḥ khagāḥ 069.023
siṃhādayo ye paśavo dandasūkāś ca pannagāḥ
sarve bhavantu te saumyāḥ kṛṣṇaśaṅkharavāhatāḥ 069.024
cittavṛttiharā ye me ye janāḥ smṛtihārakāḥ
balaujasāṃ ca hartāraś chāyāvibhraṃśakāś ca ye 069.025
ye copabhogahartāro ye ca lakṣaṇanāśakāḥ
kūṣmāṇḍās te praṇaśyantu viṣṇucakrarayāhatāḥ 069.026
buddhisvāsthyaṃ manaḥsvāsthyaṃ svāsthyam aindriyakaṃ tathā
mamāstu devadevasya vāsudevasya kīrtanāt 069.027
pṛṣṭhe purastān mama dakṣiṇottare vikoṇagaś cāstu janārdano hariḥ
tad īḍyam īśānam anantam īśvaraṃ janārdanaṃ praṇipatito na sīdati 069.028
yathā paraṃ brahma haris tathā paraṃ jagatsvarūpaś ca sa eva keśavaḥ
ṛtena tenācyutanāmakīrtanāt praṇāśam etu trividhaṃ mamāśubham 069.029
ity asāv ātmarakṣārthaṃ nyastavān viṣṇupañjaram
tenāsādhyaḥ sa duṣṭānāṃ babhūva nṛpa rakṣasām 070.001
etayārakṣayā rakṣo nirdhūtaṃ bhuvi pātitam
japyāvasāne vipro 'sau dadarśa vigataujasam 070.002
dṛṣṭvā ca kṛpayāviṣṭaḥ samāśvāsya niśācaram
papracchāgamane hetuṃ taṃ cācaṣṭa yathātatham
kathayitvā ca tat sarvaṃ rākṣasaḥ punar abravīt 070.003
prasīda vipravarya tvaṃ nirviṇṇasyātipāpinaḥ
pāpapraśamanāyālam upadeśaṃ prayaccha me 070.004
bahūni pāpāni mayā kṛtāni bahavo hatāḥ
kṛtāḥ striyaś ca me bahvyo vidhavā hataputrikāḥ
anāgasāṃ ca sattvānām anekānāṃ kṣayaḥ kṛtaḥ 070.005
so 'ham icchāmi viprarṣe prasādāt tava suvrata
pāpasyāsya kṣayaṃ kartuṃ kuru me dharmadeśanām 070.006
kathaṃ krūrasvabhāvasya satas tava niśācara
sahasaiva samāyātā jijñāsā dharmavartmani 070.007
tvām attum āgataḥ kṣipto rakṣayā kṛtayā tvayā
tatsaṃsparśāc ca me brahman sādhv etan manasi sthitam 070.008
kā sā rakṣā na tāṃ vedmi vedmi nāsyāḥ parāyaṇam
kiṃtv asyāḥ saṃgam āsādya nirvedaṃ prāpitaṃ param 070.009
sa kṛpāṃ kuru dharmajña mayy anukrośam āvaha
yathā pāpāpanodo me bhavaty ārya tathā kuru 070.010
ity evam uktaḥ sa muniḥ sadayas tena rakṣasā
pratyuvāca mahābhāga vimṛśya suciraṃ tadā 070.011
yat tvam ātthopadeśārthaṃ nirviṇṇaḥ svena karmaṇā
yuktam etan na pāpānāṃ nivṛtter upakārakam 070.012
kariṣye yātudhānānāṃ na tv ahaṃ dharmadeśanām
tāṃs tvaṃ pṛccha dvijān saumya ye vai pravacane ratāḥ 070.013
evam uktvā yayau vipraś cintām āpa ca rākṣasaḥ
kathaṃ pāpāpanodaḥ syād ity asau vyākulendriyaḥ 070.014
na tadā khādate sattvān kṣudhā saṃpīḍito 'pi san
ṣaṣṭhe ṣaṣṭhe tadā kāle jantum ekam abhakṣayat 070.015
sa kadācit kṣudhāviṣṭaḥ paryaṭan vipine vane
dadarśātha phalāhāram agrataḥ kauśikaṃ dvijam 070.016
taṃ jagrāha ca bhakṣārthaṃ ṣaṣṭhe kāle bubhukṣitaḥ
guror arthe phalāhāram āgataṃ brahmacāriṇam 070.017
gṛhīto rakṣasā tena sa tadā munidārakaḥ
nirāśo jīvite prāha sāmapūrvaṃ niśācaram 070.018
bho bhadramukha yatkāryaṃ gṛhīto 'ham iha tvayā
tad bravīhi yathātattvam ayam asmy anuśādhi mām 070.019
ṣaṣṭhe kāle mamāhāraḥ kṣudhitasya tvam āgataḥ
niḥśūkasyātipāpasya nirghṛṇasya dvijadruhaḥ 070.020
yady avaśyaṃ tvayādhyāhaṃ bhakṣaṇīyo niśācara
āyāsyāmi tad adyaiva nivedya gurave phalam 070.021
gurumūle tad āgatya yat phalagrahaṇaṃ kṛtam
mamātra niṣṭhāṃ prāptasya tat pāpāya niveditam 070.022
sa tvaṃ muhūrtamātraṃ mām atraiva pratipālaya
nivedya gurave yāvad ihāgacchāmy ahaṃ phalam 070.023
ṣaṣṭhe kāle na me brahman kaścid grahaṇam āgataḥ
pramucyate nibodhaitad iti me pāpajīvikām 070.024
eka evātra mokṣasya tava hetuḥ śṛṇuṣva tam
muñcāmy aham asaṃdigdhaṃ yadi tat kurute bhavān 070.025
guror yan na virodhāya yan na dharmoparodhakam
tat kariṣyāmy ahaṃ rakṣo yan na vrataharaṃ mama 070.026
mayā nisargato brahmañ jātidoṣād viśeṣataḥ
nirvivekena pāpena pāpaṃ karma sadā kṛtam 070.027
ā bālyān mama pāpeṣu na puṇyeṣu rataṃ manaḥ
tatpāpasaṃcayān mokṣaṃ prāpnuyāṃ yena tad vada 070.028
yāni pāpāni karmāṇi bālatvāc caritāni me
duṣṭāṃ yonim imāṃ prāpya tanmuktiṃ kathaya dvija 070.029
yady etad dvijaputra tvaṃ mamākhyāsyasy aśeṣataḥ
tat kṣudhārtāt samārtas tvaṃ niyataṃ mokṣam āpsyasi 070.030
na caitat pāpaśīlo 'ham adya tvāṃ kṣutpipāsitaḥ
ṣaṣṭhe kāle nṛśaṃsātmā bhakṣayiṣyāmi nirghṛṇaḥ 070.031
evam ukto munisutas tena ghoreṇa rakṣasā
cintām avāpa mahatīm aśaktas tad udīritum 070.032
vimṛśya suciraṃ vipraḥ śaraṇaṃ jātavedasam
jagāma jñānadānāya saṃśayaṃ paramaṃ gataḥ 070.033
yadi śuśrūṣito vahnir guroḥ śuśrūṣaṇād anu
vratāni vā sucīrṇāni saptārciḥ pātu māṃ tataḥ 070.034
na mātaraṃ na pitaraṃ gauraveṇa yathā gurum
yathāham avagacchāmi tathā māṃ pātu pāvakaḥ 070.035
yathā guruṃ na manasā karmaṇā vacasāpi vā
avajānāmy ahaṃ tena pātu satyena pāvakaḥ 070.036
ity evaṃ śapathān satyān kurvatas tasya tat punaḥ
saptārciṣā samādiṣṭā prādurāsīt sarasvatī
sā covāca dvijasutaṃ rākṣasagrahaṇākulam 070.037
mā bhair dvijasutāhaṃ tvāṃ mokṣayāmy atisaṃkaṭāt 070.038
yad asya rakṣasaḥ śreyo jihvāgre 'haṃ sthitā tava
tat sarvaṃ kathayiṣyāmi tato mokṣam avāpsyasi 070.039
adṛśyā rakṣasā tena proktvetthaṃ taṃ sarasvatī
adarśanam itā so 'pi dvijaḥ prāha niśācaram 070.040
śrūyatāṃ tava yac chreyas tathānyeṣāṃ ca pāpinām
samastapāpaśuddhyarthaṃ puṇyopacayadaṃ ca yat 070.041
prātar utthāya satataṃ madhyāhne 'hnaḥ kṣaye 'pi vā
ayaṃ śastaḥ sadā jāpaḥ sarvapāpopaśāntidaḥ 070.042
hariṃ kṛṣṇaṃ hṛṣīkeśaṃ vāsudevaṃ janārdanam
praṇato 'smi jagannāthaṃ sa me pāpaṃ vyapohatu 070.043
viśveśvaram ajaṃ viṣṇum aprameyaparākramam
praṇato 'smi prajāpālaṃ sa me pāpaṃ vyapohatu 070.044
viṣṇum acyutam īśānam anantam aparājitam
praṇato 'smi mahātmānaṃ sa me pāpaṃ vyapohatu 070.045
carācaraguruṃ nāthaṃ govindaṃ śeṣaśāyinam
praṇato 'smi paraṃ devaṃ sa me pāpaṃ vyapohatu 070.046
govardhanadharaṃ dhīraṃ gobrāhmaṇahite sthitam
praṇato 'smi gadāpāṇiṃ sa me pāpaṃ vyapohatu 070.047
śaṅkhinaṃ cakriṇaṃ śāntaṃ śārṅgiṇaṃ sragdharaṃ param
praṇato 'smi patiṃ lakṣmyāḥ sa me pāpaṃ vyapohatu 070.048
dāmodaram udārākṣaṃ puṇḍarīkākṣam avyayam
praṇato 'smi stutaṃ stutyaiḥ sa me pāpaṃ vyapohatu 070.049
nārāyaṇaṃ naraṃ śauriṃ mādhavaṃ madhusūdanam
praṇato 'smi dharādhāraṃ sa me pāpaṃ vyapohatu 070.050
keśavaṃ keśihantāraṃ kaṃsāriṣṭanisūdanam
praṇato 'smi caturbāhuṃ sa me pāpaṃ vyapohatu 070.051
śrīvatsavakṣasaṃ śrīśaṃ śrīdharaṃ śrīniketanam
praṇato 'smi śriyaḥ kāntaṃ sa me pāpaṃ vyapohatu 070.052
yam īśaṃ sarvabhūtānāṃ dhyāyanti yatayo 'kṣaram
vāsudevam anirdeśyaṃ tam asmi śaraṇaṃ gataḥ 070.053
samastālambanebhyo 'yaṃ saṃhṛtya manaso gatim
dhyāyanti vāsudevākhyaṃ tam asmi śaraṇaṃ gataḥ 070.054
sarvagaṃ sarvabhūtaṃ ca sarvasyādhātam īśvaram
vāsudevaṃ paraṃ brahma tam asmi śaraṇaṃ gataḥ 070.055
paramātmānam avyaktaṃ yaṃ prayānti sumedhasaḥ
karmakṣaye 'kṣayaṃ devaṃ tam asmi śaraṇaṃ gataḥ 070.056
puṇyapāpavinirmuktā yaṃ praviśya punarbhavam
na yoginaḥ prāpnuvanti tam asmi śaraṇaṃ gataḥ 070.057
brahmā bhūtvā jagat sarvaṃ sadevāsuramānuṣam
yaḥ sṛjaty acyuto devas tam asmi śaraṇaṃ gataḥ 070.058
brahmatve yasya vaktrebhyaś caturvedamayaṃ vapuḥ
sūtaṃ prabho purā jajñe tam asmi śaraṇaṃ gataḥ 070.059
brahmarūpadharaṃ devaṃ jagadyoniṃ janārdanam
sraṣṭṛtve saṃsthitaṃ sṛṣṭau praṇato 'smi sanātanam 070.060
yaḥ pāti sṛṣṭaṃ ca vibhuḥ sthitāv asurasūdanaḥ
tam ādipuruṣaṃ viṣṇuṃ praṇato 'smi sanātanam 070.061
dhṛtā mahī hatā daityāḥ paritrātās tathāmarāḥ
yena taṃ viṣṇum ādyeśaṃ praṇato 'smi sanātanam 070.062
yajñair yajanti yaṃ viprā yajñeśaṃ yajñabhāvanam
taṃ yajñapuruṣaṃ viṣṇuṃ praṇato 'smi sanātanam 070.063
varṇāśramān sthitāv ādyo yaḥ sthāpayati vartmani
tam ādipuruṣaṃ viṣṇuṃ praṇato 'smi sanātanam 070.064
kalpānte rudrarūpo yaḥ saṃharaty akhilaṃ jagat
tam ādipuruṣaṃ viṣṇuṃ praṇato 'smi janārdanam 070.065
pātālavīthībhūrādīṃs tathā lokān bibharti yaḥ
tam antapuruṣaṃ viṣṇuṃ praṇato 'smi janārdanam 070.066
saṃbhakṣayitvā sakalaṃ yathā sṛṣṭam idaṃ jagat
yo nṛtyaty atiraudrātmā praṇato 'smi janārdanam 070.067
surāsurāḥ pitṛgaṇā yakṣagandharvarākṣasāḥ
yasyāṃśabhūtā devasya sarvagaṃ taṃ namāmy aham 070.068
samastadevāḥ sakalā mānuṣāṇāṃ ca jātayaḥ
yasyāṃśabhūtā devasya sarvagaṃ taṃ namāmy aham 070.069
vṛkṣagulmādayo yasya tathā paśumṛgādayaḥ
ekāṃśabhūtā devasya sarvagaṃ taṃ namāmy aham 070.070
yasmān nānyat paraṃ kiṃcid yasmin sarvaṃ mahātmani
yaḥ sarvam avyayo 'nantaḥ sarvagaṃ taṃ namāmy aham 070.071
yathā sarveṣu bhūteṣu sthāvareṣu careṣu ca
viṣṇur eva tathā pāpaṃ mamāśeṣaṃ praṇaśyatu 070.072
yathā viṣṇumayaṃ sarvaṃ yat sarvendriyagocaram
yac ca jñānaparicchedyaṃ pāpaṃ naśyatu me tathā 070.073
pravṛttaṃ ca nivṛttaṃ ca karma viṣṇumayaṃ yathā
anekajanmakarmotthaṃ pāpaṃ naśyatu me tathā 070.074
yan niśāyāṃ tathā prātar yac ca madhyāparāhṇayoḥ
saṃdhyayoś ca kṛtaṃ pāpaṃ karmaṇā manasā girā 070.075
tiṣṭhatā vrajatā yac ca śayyāsanagatena ca
kṛtaṃ yad aśubhaṃ karma kāyena manasā girā 070.076
ajñānato jñānato vā vāsudevasya kīrtanāt
tat sarvaṃ vilayaṃ yātu toyasthaṃ lavaṇaṃ yathā 070.077
paradāraparadravya- vāñchādrohodbhavaṃ ca yat
paripīḍodbhavaṃ nindāṃ kurvato yan mahātmanām 070.078
yac ca bhojye tathā peye yac ca kaṇḍūyanādiṣu
tad yātu vilayaṃ toye yathā lavaṇabhājanam 070.079
yad bālye yac ca kaumāre yat pāpaṃ yauvane mama
vayaḥpariṇatau yac ca yac ca janmāntareṣu me 070.080
tan nārāyaṇagovinda- harikṛṣṇeśakīrtanāt
prayātu vilayaṃ toye yathā lavaṇabhājanam 070.081
viṣṇave vāsudevāya haraye keśavāya ca
janārdanāya kṛṣṇāya namo bhūyo namo namaḥ 070.082
idaṃ sārasvataṃ stotram aśeṣāghavināśanam
paṭhatāṃ śṛṇvatāṃ caiva sarvapāpavināśanam 070.083
idaṃ yaḥ prātar utthāya praṇipatya janārdanam
japaty ekamanāḥ pāpaṃ samastaṃ sa vyapohati 070.084
yas tu saṃvatsaraṃ pūrṇaṃ sāyaṃ prātaḥ samāhitaḥ
japaty etan naraḥ puṇyaṃ kṛtvā manasi keśavam 070.085
śārīraṃ mānasaṃ vāgjaṃ jñānato 'jñānato 'pi vā
kṛtaṃ tena tu yat pāpaṃ sapta janmāntarāṇi vai 070.086
mahāpātakam alpaṃ vā tathā yac copapātakam
sakalaṃ nāśayaty etat tathānyat puṇyam ṛcchati 070.087
viprāya suviśiṣṭāya tilapātrāṇi ṣoḍaśa
ahany ahani yo dadyāt paṭhaty etac ca tat samam 070.088
aviplutamatiś cānte saṃprāpya smaraṇaṃ hareḥ
viṣṇulokam avāpnoti satyam etan mayoditam 070.089
yathainaṃ paṭhati nityaṃ stavaṃ sārasvataṃ pumān
api pāpasamāyukto mokṣaṃ prāpnoty asāv api 070.*(114)
yathaitat satyam uktaṃ me nātrālpam api vai mṛṣā
rākṣasagrastasarvāṅgaṃ tathā mām eṣa muñcatu 070.090
evam uccārite muktaḥ sa tadā tena rakṣasā
akāmena dvijo bhūyas tam āha rajanīcaram 070.091
etad bhadramukhākhyātaṃ tava pātakanāśanam
viṣṇoḥ sārasvataṃ stotraṃ yaj jagāda sarasvatī 070.092
hutāśanena prahitā mama jihvāgrasaṃsthitā
jagādemaṃ stavaṃ viṣṇoḥ sarvapāpapraśāntidam 070.093
anenaiva jagannāthaṃ tvam ārādhaya keśavam
tataḥ pāpāpanodaṃ tu stute prāpsyasi keśave 070.094
aharniśaṃ hṛṣīkeśaṃ stavenānena rākṣasa
stauhi bhaktiṃ parāṃ kṛtvā tataḥ pāpād vimokṣyase 070.095
stuto hi sarvapāpāni nāśayiṣyaty asaṃśayam
bhaktyā rākṣasaśārdūla sarvapāpaharo hariḥ 070.096
tataḥ praṇamya taṃ vipraṃ prasādya ca niśācaraḥ
śālagrāmaṃ mahārāja tadaiva tapase yayau 070.097
tatrāharniśam evaitaj japañ japyaṃ narādhipa
devakriyāratir bhūtvā tapas tepe sa rākṣasaḥ 070.098
ārādhya ca jagannāthaṃ sa tatra puruṣottamam
sarvapāpavinirmukto viṣṇulokam avāptavān 070.099
tathā tvam api rājarṣe sarvapāpapraśāntidam
ārādhaya hṛṣīkeśaṃ japan sārasvataṃ stavam 070.100
ya etat paramaṃ stotraṃ vāsudevasya mānavaḥ
paṭhiṣyati sa sarvebhyaḥ pāpebhyo mokṣam āpsyati 070.101
brahmann asāre saṃsāre rogādivyāptamānasaḥ
śabdādilubdhaḥ puruṣaḥ kiṃ kurvan nāvasīdati 071.001
sve mahimni sthitaṃ devam aprameyam ajaṃ vibhum
śokamohavinirmuktaṃ viṣṇuṃ dhyāyan na sīdati 071.002
aprāṇacitikaṃ brahma vedānteṣu prakāśitam
ādyaṃ puruṣam īśānaṃ viṣṇuṃ dhyāyan na sīdati 071.003
aśanādyair asaṃspṛṣṭaṃ sevitaṃ yogibhiḥ sadā
sarvadoṣavinirmuktaṃ viṣṇuṃ dhyāyan na sīdati 071.004
dhāmatrayavinirmuktaṃ suprabhātaṃ sunirmalam
niṣkalaṃ śāśvataṃ devaṃ viṣṇuṃ dhyāyan na sīdati 071.005
kṣarākṣaravinirmuktaṃ janmamṛtyuvivarjitam
abhayaṃ satyasaṃkalpaṃ viṣṇuṃ dhyāyan na sīdati 071.006
amṛtaṃ sādhanaṃ sādhyaṃ yaṃ paśyanti manīṣiṇaḥ
jñeyākhyaṃ paramātmānaṃ viṣṇuṃ dhyāyan na sīdati 071.007
atulaṃ sukhadharmāṇaṃ vyomadehaṃ sanātanam
dharmādharmavinirmuktaṃ viṣṇuṃ dhyāyan na sīdati 071.008,*(115)
vyāsādyair munibhiḥ sarvair dhyānayogaparāyaṇaiḥ
arcitaṃ bhāvakusumair viṣṇuṃ dhyāyan na sīdati 071.009
viṣṇvaṣṭakam idaṃ puṇyaṃ yogināṃ prītivardhanam
yaḥ paṭhet parayā prītyā sa gacched viṣṇusātmyatām 071.010
etat puṇyaṃ pāpaharaṃ dhanyaṃ duḥsvapnanāśanam
paṭhatāṃ śṛṇvatāṃ caiva viṣṇor māhātmyam uttamam 071.011
kurvan bhaktiṃ hṛṣīkeśe mānavo bhṛgunandana
nirvāṇaṃ samavāpnoti yādṛśaṃ tad vadasva me 072.001
dṛśyante puruṣā bhaktim udvahanto janārdane
tathāpy anekadehārti- manastāpāturā mune 072.002
smṛtamātraḥ surendrasya yo 'rtihā madhusūdanaḥ
tasyāpi karmābhiratā duḥkhabhājaḥ kathaṃ narāḥ 072.003
kaiś ca dānair jagatsvāmī svāmī nārāyaṇo nṛṇām
upakārāya bhaktānāṃ jāyate sa mahāmune 072.004
tvadyukto 'yam anupraśno mahārāja śṛṇuṣva tam
yathā pṛṣṭam idaṃ samyak kathyamānaṃ yathākhilam 072.005
pṛthivīṃ ratnasaṃpūrṇāṃ yaḥ kṛṣṇāya prayacchati
tasyāpy anyamanaskasya sulabho na janārdanaḥ 072.006
nārādhyate 'cyuto dānair na homair bhāvavarjitaiḥ
aikātmyaṃ puruṣair yāti tanmayair eva mādhavaḥ 072.007
śrūyate ca purākhyāto rājoparicaro vasuḥ
iyāja subahūn yajñāñ śraddhāpūtena cetasā 072.008
sa vipraśāpād rājarṣiḥ kasmiṃścit kāraṇāntare
ākāśacārī sahasā praviveśa rasātalam 072.009
rasātalam anuprāptas tathāpi jagataḥ prabhum
tuṣṭāva tanmayo bhūtvā divyair mantrair janārdanam 072.010
devānām eṣa yajñāṃśair yajvī pakṣavivardhanaḥ
cedirāḍ iti daityānāṃ matir āsīd rasātale 072.011
anena vividhair yajñais tarpitas tridaśeśvaraḥ
jaghāna daityān vadhyo 'yaṃ prāpto 'smadgocaraṃ ripuḥ 072.012
iti saṃmantrya te daityāś cedirājajighāṃsavaḥ
tatsamīpam anuprāptā gṛhītavividhāyudhāḥ 072.013
paramāmarṣasaṃyuktās tatas te cedipuṅgavam
hantuṃ na śekuḥ śastrais tu yatnavanto 'pi pārthivam 072.014
sa cāpi vasur āsīnaḥ keśavārpitamānasaḥ
jajāpa mantram oṃkāraṃ praṇavaṃ dvādaśākṣaram 072.015
dadarśa ca sa viśveśaṃ dhyānāvasthitamānasaḥ
kṛtvānyaviṣayatyāgi cittam atyantaniścalam 072.016
prāg īśam akṣaraṃ dhyānaṃ jñānaṃ jñeyaṃ jagadgurum
saṃcintya vāsudevākhyam anirdeśyaṃ parāyaṇam 072.017
tato 'ntaryāmirupeṇa prākṛtena ca saṃsthitam
brahmaviṣṇuśivānāṃ ca svarūpaiḥ saṃsthitaṃ tridhā 072.018
punaś ca devagandharva- siddhādimanujādiṣu
sthāvarānteṣu bhūteṣu sarveṣv eva samāsthitam 072.019
dikṣv ambaradharābhūbhṛt- toyavāyvanalādiṣu
dṛśyādṛśyeṣu caiveśaṃ cintayām āsa pārthivaḥ 072.020
sarvatra dṛṣṭvā taṃ devam ātmany api ca sarvagam
sarvaṃ ca tanmayaṃ dṛṣṭvā virarāma samādhitaḥ 072.021
indriyāṇīndriyārtheṣu pūrvavat sa narādhipaḥ
viniveśya tato 'paśyad asurān udyatāyudhān 072.022
tān sa dṛṣṭvā gṛhītārghya ekaikasyaiva pārthivaḥ
pādyapūrveṇa vidhinā pūjayām āsa bhaktimān 072.023
prasādaṃ kuru bhadraṃ vo bhagavāñ jagataḥ patiḥ
vāsudevo bhavān prāpto mamānugrahakāmyayā 072.024
ity evaṃ cedirājo 'sāv ekaikasya ca dānavān
pūjayām āsa pādyādi nivedya vacasā tathā 072.025
te 'pi taṃ cedirājānaṃ papracchur asurās tadā
kva vāsudevo 'tra vayaṃ prāptā dākṣāyaṇīsutāḥ 072.026
ity evaṃ vadato daityān sa jagāda punar vasuḥ
praṇāmanamro rājendra sarvadarśī mahāmatiḥ 072.027
vāsudevo jagat sarvaṃ yac ceṅgaṃ yac ca neṅgati
brahmādiṣu tṛṇānteṣu sa evaiko jagadguruḥ 072.028
ahaṃ bhavanto devādyā manuṣyāḥ paśavaś ca ye
te 'pi devā jagaddhātur vyatiriktā na keśavāt 072.029
tenaiva māyā vitatā vaiṣṇavī bhinnadarśanī
tayā svāṅgeṣu devo 'sau pradarśayati sarvaśaḥ 072.030
tad yūyam aham anye ca yac ca sthāvarajaṅgamam
vāsudevātmakaṃ sarvam iti matvā namo 'stu vaḥ 072.031
ity uktās tena te daityā na śaktā manujeśvaram
yatnavanto 'pi taṃ hantuṃ prayayuḥ svān athālayān 072.032
tataḥ purohitaṃ sarve kāvyaṃ nītiviśāradam
sametya te yathāvṛttaṃ sarvam asmai nyavedayan 072.033
asmākam atyantaripur ayaṃ prāpto rasātalam
devānām upakṛd brahman yajvā cedipatir vasuḥ 072.034
asmatpakṣakṣayāyaiṣa devānāṃ pakṣavardhanaḥ
tatra yat pratipattavyaṃ tan no brūhi mahāmate 072.035
svagocaram ariḥ prāptaḥ śatrupakṣopakārakaḥ
na hantavya itīdaṃ ko nītimān pravadiṣyati 072.036
tasmāt pragṛhya divyāni sarvāstrāṇy amarārdanāḥ
nipātayata taṃ gatvā cedirājaṃ svagocare 072.037
sarvam etan mahābhāga tasminn asmābhir udyataiḥ
kṛtaṃ na śakito hantuṃ niryatno 'pi hi pārthivaḥ 072.038
kiṃ tad yogaphalaṃ tasya kiṃ vā japaphalaṃ mune
tapaso vā muniśreṣṭha vistarāt tad vadasva naḥ 072.039
nityaṃ saṃcintayaty eṣa yogayukto janārdanam
sāsya rakṣā parā manye ko hinasty acyutāśrayam 072.040
kīrtitaḥ saṃsmṛto dhyātaḥ pūjitaḥ saṃstutas tathā
aihikāmuṣmikīṃ rakṣāṃ karoti bhagavān hariḥ 072.041
yad durlabhaṃ yad aprāpyaṃ manaso yan na gocare
tad apy aprārthitaṃ dhyāto dadāti madhusūdanaḥ 072.042
śarīrārogyam arthāṃś ca bhogāṃś caivānuṣaṅgikān
dadāti dhyāyatāṃ nityam apavargaprado hariḥ 072.043
yad idaṃ cedirājānaṃ hantum icchatha dānavāḥ
tad asya keśavāc cittam upāyenāpanīyatām 072.044
tatas te tadvacaḥ śrutvā dānavāḥ kurupuṅgava
brahmarūpapraticchannā jagmur yatra sthito vasuḥ 072.045
dadṛśus te mahātmānaṃ praṇataṃ cedipuṅgavam
kṛtapūjaṃ jagaddhātur vāsudevasya pārthivam 072.046
saṃstutāv udyataṃ śāntaṃ sarvatra samadarśinam
kṛṣṇārpitamanovṛttiṃ jānubhyām avaniṃgatam 072.047
tataḥ saṃśṛṇvatāṃ teṣāṃ tuṣṭāva madhusūdanam
tannāmasmaraṇodbhūta- pulakaś cedipuṅgavaḥ 072.048
jagāda yaṃ sa rājarṣiḥ stavaṃ kṛṣṇasya śaunaka
śṛṇvatāṃ dānavendrāṇāṃ tan me pāpaharaṃ vada 072.049
śṛṇu yad devadevasya viṣṇor adbhutakarmaṇaḥ
stotraṃ jagāda rājāsau rasātalatalaṃ gataḥ 072.050
staumi devam ajaṃ nityaṃ pariṇāmavivarjitam
avṛddhikṣayam īśānam acyutaṃ parataḥ param 072.051
kalpanākṛtanāmānam anirdeśyam ajaṃ vibhum
mūlahetum ahetuṃ tvāṃ vāsudevaṃ namāmy aham 072.052
paramārthaparair īśaś cintyate yaḥ prajākaraiḥ
taṃ vāsudevam īśeśaṃ namāmy adya guṇaṃ param 072.053
yasmād idaṃ yatra cedam idaṃ yo viśvam avyayam
taṃ vāsudevam amalaṃ namāmi parameśvaram 072.054
jñeyaṃ jñātāram ajaraṃ bhoktāraṃ prakṛteḥ prabhum
puruṣasvarūpiṇaṃ devaṃ nato 'smi puruṣaṃ param 072.055
pradhānādiviśeṣānta- svarūpam ajam avyayam
sthūlasūkṣmamayaṃ sarvaṃ- vyāpinaṃ taṃ namāmy aham 072.056
sraṣṭā pālayitā cānte yaś ca saṃhārakārakaḥ
trayīmayaṃ taṃ triguṇaṃ nato 'smi puruṣottamam 072.057
ābrahmasthāvarānte ca yo jagaty atra saṃsthitaḥ
vyaktarūpī ca taṃ devaṃ nato 'haṃ viṣṇum avyayam 072.058
namo namo 'stu te deva jagatām īśvareśvara
paramārtha parācintya vidhātaḥ parameśvara 072.059
tvam ādir anto madhyaṃ ca jagato 'sya jagatpate
jagat tvayi jagac ca tvaṃ jagat tvatto jaganmaya 072.060
tavāgnir āsaṃ vasudhāṅghriyugmaṃ nabhaḥ śiraś candraravī ca netre
samastalokā jaṭharaṃ bhujāś ca diśaś catasro bhagavan namas te 072.061
yad bhūgataṃ yad gaganāntarāle yad vā nabhasy akhilalokagaṃ ca
yat sthūlaṃ sūkṣmaṃ paratas tato 'pi yad asti yan nāsti ca tat tvam īśa 072.062
vedāś ca vedyaṃ ca bhagavān ananto vedāntavedyaś ca samastaheto
vadanti tat tvā munayaḥ pareśaṃ tvayi prasanne paramārthadṛśye 072.063
namo hṛṣīkeśa tavāprameya namaś ca tubhyaṃ paramārthasāra
viṣṇo namas te 'stu parāpareśa kṛṣṇācyutānanta jagannivāsa 072.064
namo 'stu tubhyaṃ parameśvarāya namas tathāntaḥkāraṇasthitāya
pradhānabhūtāya namaś ca tubhyam vyaktasvarūpeṇa ca saṃsthitāya 072.065
saṃhṛtya viśvaṃ jalaśāyine namo namaś ca te kaiṭabhasūdanāya
svanābhipadmodaraśāyine ca brahmasvarūpopanatāya caiva 072.066
sraṣṭre namaḥ pālayitre sthitau ca sarveśa tubhyaṃ puruṣottamāya
rudrāya cānte kṣayahetave te nato 'smi saṃhārakarāya viṣṇo 072.067
jaya prapannārtiharāprameya jayāgnivasvaśvimaya prajeśa
rudrendracandrastuta devadeva jayāmarāṇām ariśātanāya 072.068
jitaṃ tvayā sarvaga sarvasāraṃ sarvātmabhūtākhila vedavedya
jitaṃ jitākṣāmalacittadṛśya carācarādhāra dharādhareḍya 072.069
yajñāśrayo yajñapumān aśeṣa deveśa martyāsurayajñabhoktaḥ
tvam īḍyamāno 'bhimataṃ dadāsi dharādhareśācyuta vāsudeva 072.070
namas te devadeva tvaṃ yathā pāsy akhilaṃ jagat
sthitau tathā samastebhyo doṣebhyo māṃ samuddhara 072.071
kṛṣṇācyuta hṛṣīkeśa sarvabhūteśa keśava
mahātmaṃs trāhi māṃ bhaktaṃ vāsudeva prasīda me 072.072
iti stotrāvasāne taṃ cedirājaṃ tato 'surāḥ
jahasuḥ satalākṣepaṃ procuś ca dvijarūpiṇaḥ 072.073
prājñaḥ kila prajāpālaś cedirāṭ saṃśruto bhuvi
tas asya jñānam akhilaṃ viparītārtham īdṛśam 072.074
kva vāsudevaḥ kva bhavān imām antyāṃ daśāṃ gataḥ
yo bhavān vipraśāpena rasātalatalāśrayaḥ 072.075
bhaviṣyati smṛto devas trātā kila tavācyutaḥ
yo 'sāv āpyāyyate viprair adhvareṣu haviḥsravaiḥ 072.076
yo 'nyatras trāṇakāmo vā yajñabhāgam abhīpsate
sa trātā tava govindo bhaviṣyaty ativismayaḥ 072.077
yadā tvaṃ bhagavadbhakto vipraśāpān nipātitaḥ
tadā sa vāsudevas te kva gato 'lpaśruto 'vyayaḥ 072.078
na vāsudevo na harir na govindo na keśavaḥ
śāpaṃ dadatsu vipreṣu paritrāṇaparo bhavet 072.079
sa tvam ārtapralāpebhyo viramādya yadīcchasi
kubuddhim etāṃ saṃtyajya svapauruṣaparo bhava 072.080
na vayaṃ puṇḍarīkākṣaṃ nānantaṃ nācyutaṃ harim
saṃśritā na ca sīdāmaḥ svapauruṣam upāśritāḥ 072.081
yady asmadvacanaṃ vīra na mohena viśaṅkase
tadāśrayasva svaṃ vīryaṃ parityajya vimūḍhatām 072.082
ity udīritam ākarṇya sa teṣāṃ cedipuṅgavaḥ
ajñānapaṭalacchannān hṛdayena śuśoca tān 072.083
uvāca cedirājo vai hṛdaye kṛtamatsaraḥ 072.*(116)
aho moho 'yam eteṣām ahaṃkārasamudbhavaḥ
yena sarveśvare viṣṇāv eteṣām āvṛtā matiḥ 072.084
prakāśaṃ ca sa tān āha dānavān prītipūrvakam
pāpatas tatparitrāṇaṃ cikīrṣur vasudhādhipaḥ 072.085
maivaṃ bho bhagavadbhaktiṃ kurudhvaṃ dvijasattamāḥ
saṃsārābdhau manuṣyāṇām ekaḥ poto janārdanaḥ 072.086
yūyaṃ vayaṃ tathaivānye tasya sarve vibhūtayaḥ
brahmādisthāvarāntaṃ hi tasya devasya vistṛtiḥ 072.087
sukhaduḥkhamayo nR̥ṇāṃ vipākaḥ karmaṇāṃ ca yaḥ
saṃśuddhihetuḥ svacchandāt so 'pi viprāḥ pravartate 072.088
parīkṣāṃ ca jagannāthaḥ karoty adṛḍhacetasām
narāṇām arthavidhvaṃsa- nikāśeṣu janārdanaḥ 072.089
alpayatnena cāyānti vimuktiṃ keśavāśrayāt
tadvighātāya śakrādyā yatante vighnahetubhiḥ 072.090
yadā janārdane bhaktiṃ vahan sīdati mānavaḥ
nirviṇṇacetāḥ śaithilyaṃ manasaḥ kurute tadā 072.091
devānāṃ mahatī śaṅkā bhaktiyuktā janārdane
muktibhājo bhaviṣyantīty atas te paripanthinaḥ 072.092
prāyo bhavanti govinde bhaktivyāghātahetavaḥ
vighnāś cittavighātā hi vimuktiparipanthinaḥ 072.093
satyaṃ śatena vighnānāṃ sahasreṇa tathā tapaḥ
vighnāyutena govinde nR̥ṇāṃ bhaktir nivāryate 072.094
svaṃ cāpi karma puruṣaḥ śubhāśubham upāgatam
bhuṅkte kim atra devasya garhyate yena keśavaḥ 072.095
maryādāṃ ca kṛtāṃ tena yo bhinatti sa mānavaḥ
na viṣṇubhakto mantavyaḥ sādhu dharmārcano hariḥ 072.096
na puṣpair na ca dhūpena nopahārānulepanaiḥ
toṣaṃ prayāti govindaḥ svakarmābhyarcito yathā 072.097
brāhmaṇā devadevena mukhāt sṛṣṭā mahātmanā
devānām api saṃpūjya bhūmidevā dvijottamāḥ
anuvṛttiḥ sadā kāryā teṣāṃ varṇair anuvrataiḥ 072.098
te pūjyās te namaskāryās toṣaṇīyāś ca yatnataḥ
teṣu tuṣṭeṣv aśeṣāṇāṃ devānāṃ prītir uttamā 072.099
teṣāṃ mayā yad ajñānāj jñānād vā kṛtam apriyam
tenāpi tuṣṭa evāhaṃ viṣṇor aṃśā dvijottamāḥ 072.100
kriyāvān mama poto 'yaṃ bhūtalād yo rasātale
patitasyātibhīme 'smin duruttāre bhavārṇave 072.101
rasātalatalottāraṃ na hi vāñchāmy ahaṃ dvijāḥ
saṃsāragartād uttāraṃ vṛṇomy ārādhanād dhareḥ 072.102
yathāhaṃ nābhivāñchāmi bhogān ārādhya keśavam
tena satyena viṣṇur me sarvadoṣān vyapohatu 072.103
yathā na mātā na pitā nātmā na suhṛdaḥ sutāḥ
kṛṣṇālāpāt priyatarās tathā māṃ pātu keśavaḥ 072.104
yathā viṣṇumayaṃ sarvam etat paśyāmy ahaṃ jagat
tathā mama manodoṣān aśeṣān sa vyapohatu 072.105
jātā viṣṇuvilomeṣu bhavatsv api dayā mama
yathā tenādya satyena bhavantaḥ santu tanmayāḥ 072.106
yathā nāhaṃ bhavaddveṣān na saṃharṣād bravīmy aham
kṛpayaiva tathā sarve bhavantaḥ santu tanmayāḥ 072.107
yo yo na bhakto govinde tatra tatra kṛpā yathā
mamārivarge 'pi tathā bhaktir vo 'stu janārdane 072.108
evam uccārite teṣāṃ daityānāṃ tatkṣaṇāt tathā
tasmin rājany abhūn maitrī tathānyeṣu ca jantuṣu 072.109
devadeve 'py abhūd bhaktir bhāvo naṣṭas tathāsuraḥ
svarūpadhāriṇaś cainaṃ praṇamyāsurapuṅgavāḥ
pratyūcuḥ pārthivaṃ viṣṇu- bhaktaṃ sadbrahmacāriṇam 072.110
cedibhūpāla bhadraṃ te bhavato 'tulavikrama
saṃsāre tvatsamaiḥ saṅgaḥ puṇyabhājāṃ pravartate 072.111
vayaṃ svajātidoṣeṇa devapakṣavirodhinaḥ
bhavantam āgatā hantuṃ devaprīṇanatatparam 072.112
yadā na śaktito hantum asmābhis tvaṃ nirāyudhaḥ
viṣṇudhyānamahārakṣā- kakṣāntaragataḥ prabho 072.113
tyājayadbhis tathā bhaktiṃ keśavād iti darśitam
vaiphalyam atipuṇyeṣu viṣṇuśuśrūṣaṇā nṛṇām 072.114
sa tvaṃ devātidevasya viṣṇor amitatejasaḥ
anugrāhyo yathā teyam acyute niścalā matiḥ 072.115
diṣṭyā krodhābhibhūtānām asmākaṃ tvannivarhaṇe
matir jātā yataḥ prāptā tvatsaṅgād durlabhā matiḥ 072.116
kuruṣva ca prasādaṃ tvaṃ praṇatānāṃ nareśvara
śatrāv api kṛpāśīlaṃ yan no duṣṭam abhūn manaḥ 072.117
diśāṃ vaimalyaṃ vimalaṃ cakṣuṣaś copapāditam
bhavatā duṣṭatāṃ etām āsurīm apamārjatā 072.118
duṣṭāḥ sma varṣapūgāni yad yātāni vṛthaiva naḥ
viṣayākṣiptacittānāṃ kṛṣṇe bhaktim akurvatām 072.119
karmabhūmau manuṣyāṇāṃ tad eva viphalaṃ dinam
yad acyutakathālāpa- dhyānārcārahitaṃ gatam 072.120
ity uktvā te 'surā bhūyaḥ prasādya ca tathā vasum
viṣṇau bhaktiparā yātās tīvrasaṃyogino 'layan 072.121
sa cāpi cedirāṭ tasmād devadevena cakriṇā
pātālād uddhṛtaḥ paścāt saṃsāragahanād api 072.122
ity etat sarvam ākhyātaṃ yan māṃ tvaṃ paripṛcchasi
yathāvasīdanti narā bhaktimanto 'pi keśave 072.123
dṛḍhā janārdane bhaktir yadaivāvyabhicāriṇī
tadā kiyat svargasukhaṃ saiva nirvāṇahetukī 072.124
ity etad asuraiḥ sārdhaṃ saṃvādaṃ yaḥ purā vasoḥ
paṭhiṣyaty akhilaṃ bhaktyā sa tallokam upaiṣyati 072.125
jagatprabhuṃ devadevam aśeṣeśam janārdanam
praṇipatyāham etaṃ tvāṃ yat pṛcchāmi tad ucyatām 073.001
yair upāyaiḥ pradānair vā narāṇām amarārcitaḥ
prītimān puṇḍarīkākṣo bhavaty ācakṣva tan mama 073.002
ye svadharme sthitā varṇā viprādyāḥ kurunandana
vidharmeṣu na vartante prītimāṃs teṣu keśavaḥ 073.003
brahmacārigṛhasthādyā na cyavanty āśramāc ca ye
svadharmato haris teṣāṃ prītimān eva sarvadā 073.004
ye na dambhena vartante narā bhūteṣv alolupāḥ
tyaktagrāmyādisaṃgāś ca teṣu prītiḥ parā hareḥ 073.005
dātāro nāpahartāraḥ parasvānām amāyinaḥ
ye narās teṣu govindaḥ putreṣv iva sadā hitaḥ 073.006
yeṣāṃ narāṇāṃ na matir jihvā vāsatyam ujjhati
te priyā vāsudevasya ye ca dvijaparāyaṇāḥ 073.007
karmaṇā manasā vācā ye na hiṃsānuvartinaḥ
te narā vāsudevasya priyāḥ pāṇḍukulodvaha 073.008
sarvadeveṣu ye viṣṇuṃ sarvabhūteṣv avasthitam
manyante vāsudevasya te priyāḥ putravat sadā 073.009
brahmādyaṃ sthāvarāntaṃ ca bhūtagrāmaṃ janārdanāt
ye ca paśyanty abhedena te viṣṇoḥ satataṃ priyāḥ 073.010
devavedadvijātīnāṃ nindāyāṃ ye na mānavāḥ
prītibhājo bhavantīṣṭās te sadā śārṅgadhanvinaḥ 073.011
priyāṇām atha sarveṣāṃ devadevasya sa priyaḥ
āpatsv api sadā yasya bhaktir avyabhicāriṇī 073.012
tasmāt priyatvaṃ kṛṣṇasya vāñchatā nijadharmajaiḥ
guṇair ātmā sadā yojyo na dūre guṇino hariḥ 073.013
yeṣāṃ na gṛddhiḥ pārakye dāre dravye ca cetasaḥ
hiṃsāyāṃ ca manuṣyāṇāṃ te kṛṣṇenāvalokitāḥ 073.014
vedāḥ pramāṇaṃ smṛtayo yeṣāṃ sanmārgasevinām
paropakārasaktānāṃ te kṛṣṇenāvalokitāḥ 073.015
kalikalmaṣadoṣeṇa yeṣāṃ nopahatā matiḥ
pāṣaṇḍānugatā naiva te kṛṣṇenāvalokitāḥ 073.016
yeṣāṃ kleśo guror arthe devaviprodbhavo 'pi vā
na vivitsāsamudbhūtas te kṛṣṇenāvalokitāḥ 073.017
svapantaḥ saṃsthitā yāntas tiṣṭhantaś ca janārdanam
ye cintayanty avirataṃ te kṛṣṇenāvalokitāḥ 073.018
yathātmani tathāpatye yeṣāṃ adrohiṇī matiḥ
samastasattvajāteṣu te kṛṣṇenāvalokitāḥ 073.019
devapūjām anudinaṃ guruviprārthasatkriyām
ye kurvanti narā viddhi te kṛṣṇenāvalokitāḥ 073.020
suvarṇaṃ ratnam athavā pārakyaṃ vijane vane
vilokya naiti yo lobhaṃ taṃ avaihi hareḥ priyam 073.021
devān pitR̥ṃs tathāpannān atithīñ jāmayo 'dhvagān
yo bibharti vijānīhi taṃ naraṃ bhagavatpriyam 073.022
na krodham eti kruddhebhyaḥ sahate yo nirākriyām
taṃ vijānīhi bhartavyaṃ devadevasya śārṅginaḥ 073.023
paralokapratīkāra- karaṇāya sadodyamam
kurvann ālakṣyatām eti keśavenāvalokitaḥ 073.024
nātmasaṃstavam anyeṣāṃ na nindāṃ cārthalipsayā
karoti puruṣavyāghra yasya nārāyaṇo hṛdi 073.025
sarvabhūtadayāṃ satyam akrodhaṃ dharmaśīlatām
bhajante puruṣā deve govinde hṛdaye sthite 073.026
na kalau na paradravye paradārāśritā matiḥ
narāṇāṃ jāyate rājan govinde hṛdayasthite 073.027
kṣamāṃ karoti kruddheṣu dayāṃ mūḍheṣu mānavaḥ
mudaṃ ca dharmaśīleṣu govinde hṛdaye sthite 073.028
yadā bibhety adharmāder dharmādīṃś ca yadecchati
tadā kuruvaraśreṣṭha naraḥ kṛṣṇena vīkṣitaḥ 073.029
putradāragṛhakṣetra- dravyāder mamatāṃ naraḥ
nāyāsyati jagannāthe hṛṣīkeśe parāṅmukhe 073.030
kalau kṛtayugaṃ teṣāṃ kleśās teṣāṃ sukhādhikāḥ
yeṣāṃ śarīragrahaṇe hariśuśrūṣaṇe matiḥ 073.031
yadā necchati pāpāni yadā puṇyāni vāñchati
jñeyas tadā manuṣyeṇa hṛdaye 'sya hariḥ sthitaḥ 073.032
paramārthe matiḥ puṃsām asāre tu bhavārṇave
kathaṃ bhavati rājendra viṣvaksena parāṅmukhe 073.033
śraddadhāno dayāśīlaḥ samaloṣṭāśmakāñcanaḥ
parārthe mānavaḥ kṛṣṇe prasanne nṛpa jāyate 073.034
vahato 'pi sadā kṛṣṇe bhaktim avyabhicāriṇīm
pāṇiṣv asamadṛgbuddheḥ sulabho naiva keśavaḥ 073.035
ye dāmbhikā bhinnavṛttā ye ca dharmadhvajocchrayāḥ
durlabho bhagavān devas teṣāṃ suyatatām api 073.036
kāmalobhāśritaṃ yeṣāṃ cittaṃ krodhādidūṣitam
teṣāṃ janmasahasre 'pi na matiḥ keśavāśrayā 073.037
heyāṃ kṛṣṇāśrayāṃ vṛttiṃ manyante hetusaṃśritāḥ
aviyopahatajñānā ye 'jñāne jñānamāninaḥ 073.038
vedavādavirodhena kūṭayuktim apāśritāḥ
ye keśavas taddhṛdaye na kadācit priyātithiḥ 073.039
mānuṣaṃ taṃ manuṣyatve manyamānāḥ kubuddhayaḥ
karmāṇi ye 'sya nindanti na teṣāṃ niṣkṛtir nṛṇām 073.040
kecid vadanti taṃ devaṃ manuṣyaṃ cālpamedhasaḥ
tiryaktvaṃ cāpare viṣṇuṃ māyayā tasya mohitāḥ 073.041
devatvam api kṛṣṇasya yasya nindā mahātmanaḥ
stutiṃ tasya kathaṃ śaktāḥ kartum īśasya mānavāḥ 073.042
vyāpitvaṃ śāśvatatvaṃ ca janmabhāvavivarjitam
yadāsya procyate kāsya stutir arthe tathā sthitau 073.043
sarveśvareśvaraḥ kṛṣṇaḥ procyate yadi paṇḍitaḥ
tathāpi svalpam evoktaṃ bhūtārthe katamā stutiḥ 073.044
ābrahmastambaparyante saṃsāre yasya saṃsthitiḥ
nindāpi tasya na nṛbhiḥ kartum īśasya śakyate 073.045
yadā kāṇāś ca kūṇṭhāś ca mūḍho durbuddhir āturaḥ
sarvagatvāt sa evaikas tadāsau nindyate katham 073.046
sraṣṭā pālayitā hartā jagato 'sya jagac ca saḥ
yaṣṭā yājayitā yājyaḥ sa eva bhagavān hariḥ 073.047
dātā dānaṃ tathādātā kartā kāryaṃ tathā kriyāḥ
hantā ghātayitā hiṃsyo hāryaṃ hartā ca yaḥ svayam 073.048
sarvakāraṇabhūtasya tasyeśasya mahātmanaḥ
kaḥ karoti stutiṃ viṣṇor nindāṃ vā pṛthivīpate 073.049
tasmāt sarveśvaro viṣṇur na stotuṃ na ca ninditum
śakyate sarvabhūtatvāc cokṣācokṣasvarūpiṇā 073.050
stuteḥ pādād yato nānyad utkṛṣṭam upalabhyate
tasyāpy uccāraṇeneśo na stotuṃ śakyate hariḥ 073.051
bhūtārthavādastutaye na nindāyai vidhīyate
yato 'taḥ sarvabhūtasya kā nindā tasya kā stutiḥ 073.052
yena sarvātmanā tatra hṛdayaṃ saṃniveśitam
api maunavatas tasya sulabho 'yaṃ janārdanaḥ 073.053
tasmāt tvaṃ kuruśārdūla svadharmaparipālanam
kuru viṣṇuṃ ca hṛdaye sarvavyāpinam īśvaram 073.054
tanmanā bhava tadbhaktas tadyājī taṃ namaskuru
viṣṇor evaṃ priyatvaṃ tvam āśu yāsyasi pārthiva 073.055
yaṃ stuvan stavyatām eti vandyamānaś ca vandyatām
tam īśvareśvaraṃ viṣṇuṃ hṛdaye saṃniveśaya 073.056
saṃpūjya yaṃ pūjyatamo bhavaty atra jagattraye
tam īśvareśvaraṃ viṣṇuṃ hṛdaye kuru pārthiva 073.057
svavarṇakarmābhirataḥ kuru citte janārdanam
eṣa śāstrārthasadbhāvaḥ kim uktair bahuvistaraiḥ 073.058
yasmin prasannacittas tvaṃ yasmin kopam upaiṣi ca
tāv ubhāv api tadbhūtau cintayan siddhim eṣyasi 073.059
yatra yatra sthitaṃ cetaḥ prītyā snehena vā tava
taṃ taṃ cintaya govindaṃ manasaḥ sthairyakāraṇāt 073.060
svapan vibuddhyann uttiṣṭhan sthito bhuñjan piban vrajan
sarvagaṃ sarvakartāraṃ viṣṇuṃ sarvatra cintaya 073.061
yathāgnisaṃgāt kanakam apadoṣaṃ prajāyate
saṃśliṣṭaṃ vāsudevena manuṣyāṇāṃ tathā manaḥ 073.062
yajvino yaṃ namasyanti yaṃ namasyanti devatāḥ
yogino yaṃ namasyanti taṃ namasyaṃ namāmy aham 073.063
bhūyaś ca śṛṇu rājendra yaj jagāda janārdanaḥ
nāgaparyaṅkaśayane pṛṣṭaḥ kṣīrābdhikanyayā 074.001
purā śayānaṃ govindaṃ prāvṛṭkāle mahodadhau
śeṣabhogimahābhoge vīcyambukaṇaśītale 074.002
vakṣaḥsthalasthitā devī jaganmātā jagatpatim
śrīvatsavkṣasaṃ lakṣmīḥ karasaṃvāhanādṛtā 074.003
ananyāsaktadṛṣṭiṃ ca kim apy ekāgramānasam 074.*(117)
yoganidrāvasānastham acyutaṃ jagataḥ patim
papraccha puṇḍarīkākṣaṃ puṇḍarīkakarā harim 074.004
sṛṣṭaṃ jagad idaṃ sarvaṃ bahuśaś copasaṃhṛtam
tvayā jagatpate cātra kiṃ kaścid dayitas tava 074.005
devān manuṣyān gandharvān yakṣavidyādharāsurān
sṛṣṭvā sṛṣṭān nirghṛṇatvād upasaṃharate bhavān 074.006
kaścid eteṣu bhūteṣu devādiṣu tavācyuta
dveṣo 'sti prītir athavā samaḥ sarvatra vā bhavān 074.007
samo 'smi sarvabhūteṣu na me dveṣyo 'sti na priyaḥ
tathāpi guṇagṛhyo 'haṃ pratyekahṛdayasthitaḥ 074.008
antarātmani sarvasya lokasyāham avasthitaḥ
puṇyāpuṇyakṛtau teṣu prītidveṣau śubhe mama 074.009
puṇyaṃ prītyanubhāvena sādhu buddhiṣu vartate
dveṣānubhāvenāpuṇyaṃ phaladaṃ teṣu bhāmini 074.010
śrūyatāṃ ca mahābhāge nareṣu śubhacāriṣu
satataṃ yeṣu me prītis tathāprītir varānane 074.011
pralayotpattitattvajñā ātmajñānaparāś ca ye
ete svakarmaṇā bhadre mama prītipathaṃ gatāḥ 074.012
vāṅmanaḥkāyikīṃ hiṃsāṃ ye na kurvanti kutracit
sarvamaitrā narā lakṣmi dayitās te sadā mama 074.013
svakīyadravyasaṃtuṣṭā nivṛttāś cauryakarmaṇaḥ
satyaśīladayāyuktā narā mama sadā priyāḥ 074.014
mātṛsvasṛsutātulyān paradārāṃś ca ye narāḥ
manyante te ca me lakṣmi dṛḍhaṃ priyatamāḥ sadā 074.015
na kāmān na ca saṃrambhān na dveṣād ye ca bhāmini
saṃtyajanti svakaṃ karma te 'tīva dayitā mama 074.016
viśvāsyāḥ sarvabhūtānām ahiṃsrāś ca dayālavaḥ
tyaktānṛtakathā devi manuṣyā dayitā mama 074.017
dharmalabdhāṃs tu ye bhogān bhuñjate nātikīkaṭāḥ
paralokāvirodhena te mamātipriyā narāḥ 074.018
na lobhe na ca kārpaṇye na steye na ca matsare
yeṣāṃ matir manuṣyāṇāṃ te 'tīva dayitā mama 074.019
dharmalabdheṣu dāreṣu ṛtukālābhigāminaḥ
gṛhasthakarmābhiratā narās te dayitā mama 074.020
pararandhreṣu jātyandhāḥ paradāreṣv apuṃsakāḥ
parāpavāde ye mūkā dayitās te narā mama 074.021
parāpavādaṃ nindāṃ ca paramarmāvaghaṭṭanam
ye na kurvanti puruṣās te devi mama vallabhāḥ 074.022
satyāṃ ślakṣṇāṃ nirābādhāṃ madhurāṃ prītidāyinīm
ye vācam īrayanti sma te manuṣyā mama priyāḥ 074.023
ye brāhmaṇārthe saṃtyajya sadyaḥ svam api jīvitam
yatante parayā bhaktyā te devi dayitā mama 074.024
sākṣād devam ivāyāntaṃ yā patiṃ nityam arcati
pādaśaucādibhir nārī tasyā nāhaṃ sudurlabhaḥ 074.025
pūrṇacandram ivodyataṃ bhartāraṃ yā gṛhāgatam
hṛṣṭā paśyati tāṃ viddhi dayitāṃ yoṣitaṃ mama 074.026
te bhaktā ye sadā viprān pūjayanty abdhisaṃbhave
yathāvibhavato bhaktyā svakarmābhiratā narāḥ 074.027
śrutismṛtyuditaṃ dharmaṃ manasāpi na ye narāḥ
samullaṅghya pravartante te bhaktā mama bhāmini 074.028
brahmarūpadharasyāsyān mama vedā viniḥsṛtāḥ
manvādirūpiṇaś caiva samastāḥ smṛtayaḥ smṛtāḥ 074.029
śrutiḥ smṛtir mamaivājñā tām ullaṅghya yajec chubhe
sarvasvenāpi māṃ devi nāpnoty ājñāvighātakṛt 074.030
yaḥ svadharmān na calati hiṃsādhau yo na sajyate
vahatas tasya madbhaktiṃ sadaivāhaṃ na durlabhaḥ 074.031
etad devi mayākhyātaṃ yat pṛṣṭo 'ham iha tvayā
priyāṇāṃ mama sarveṣāṃ śṛṇu yo 'titaraṃ priyaḥ 074.032
brāhmaṇaḥ kṣatriyo vaiśyaḥ śūdraś ca varavarṇini
svadharmād acalan devi dayāvān sarvajantuṣu 074.033
satyavāc chaucasaṃpanno na drohī na ca matsarī
vāṅmanaḥkarmabhiḥ śānto dayitaḥ satataṃ mama 074.034
evaṃ śrīr devadevena prāg uktā harimedhasā
tavāpi hi naraśreṣṭha yathāvat kathitaṃ mayā 074.035
saṃvādam etad devasya saha lakṣmyā jagatpateḥ
yaḥ śṛṇoti sa pāpebhyaḥ samastebhyaḥ pramucyate 074.036
bhūyo 'khilaṃ jagaddhātur vāsudevasya bhārgava
samyagārādhanāyālaṃ kriyāyogaṃ bravīhi me 075.001
yat phalaṃ keśavasyārcāṃ pratiṣṭhāpya labhen naraḥ
yac ca devakulaṃ viṣṇoḥ kārayitvā phalaṃ labhet 075.002
yad dīpadhūpapuṣpāṇāṃ gandhānāṃ ca nivedane
dhvajādidāne yat puṇyaṃ yat puṇyaṃ gītavādite 075.003
tathā pavitrapaṭhane jayaśabdādyudīraṇe
saṃmārjanādau yat puṇyaṃ namaskāre pradakṣiṇe 075.004
śīrṇasphuṭitasaṃskāra- karaṇe cāpi yat phalam
tan me vistarataḥ sarvaṃ bhagavan vaktum arhasi 075.005
yaiś copavāsair bhagavān narair ārādhyate hariḥ
teṣāṃ phalaṃ ca yat kṛtsnaṃ tan mamācakṣva vistarāt 075.006
saṃkṣepāt pūrvam evaitad bhavataḥ kathitaṃ mayā
vistareṇa mahārāja śrūyatāṃ bruvato mama 075.007
aditir nāma devānāṃ mātā paramaduścaram
tapaś cacāra varṣāṇāṃ sahasraṃ pṛthivīpate 075.008
ārādhanāya kṛṣṇasya vāgyatā vāyubhojanā
daityair nirākṛtān dṛṣṭvā tanayān kurunandana 075.009
vṛthāputrāham asmīti nirvedāt praṇatā harim
tuṣṭāva vāgbhir iṣṭābhiḥ paramārthāvabodhinī
devadaityanṛpaśvāpa- vyomavāyvādirūpiṇam 075.010
śaraṇyaṃ śaraṇaṃ viṣṇuṃ praṇatā bhaktavatsalam 075.*(118)
namaḥ smṛtārtināśāya namaḥ puṣkaramāline
namaḥ paramakalyāṇa- kalyāṇāyādivedhase 075.011
namaḥ paṅkajanetrāya namaḥ paṅkajanābhaye
namaḥ paṅkajasaṃbhūti- saṃbhavāyātmayonaye 075.012
śriyaḥ kāntāya dāntāya dāntadṛśyāya cakriṇe
namaḥ śaṅkhāsihastāya namaḥ kanakaretase 075.013
tathātmajñānavijñāna- yogacittātmayogine
nirguṇāya viśeṣāya haraye brahmarūpiṇe 075.014
jagat pratiṣṭhitaṃ yatra jagatā yo na dṛśyate
namaḥ sthūlātisūkṣmāya tasmai devāya śaṅkhine 075.015
yaṃ na paśyanti paśyanto jagad apy akhilaṃ narāḥ
apaśyadbhir jagad yac ca dṛśyate svahṛdi sthitaḥ 075.016
bahirjyotiṣi lakṣyo yo lakṣyate jyotiṣaḥ paraḥ 075.*(119)
yasminn etad yataś caitad yaś caitad akhilaṃ jagat
tasmai samastajagatām ādhārāya namo namaḥ 075.017
ādyaḥ prajāpatipatir yaḥ pitR̥ṇāṃ paraḥ patiḥ
patiḥ surāṇāṃ yas tasmai namaḥ kṛṣṇāya vedhase 075.018
yaḥ pravṛttair nivṛttaiś ca karmabhir vibhur ijyate
svargāpavargaphalado namas tasmai gadādhṛte 075.019
yaś cintyamāno manasā sadyaḥ pāpaṃ vyapohati
namas tasmai viśuddhāya parasmai harimedhase 075.020
yaṃ praviśyākhilādhāram īśānam ajam avyayam
na punar janmamaraṇe prāpnuvanti namāmi tam 075.021
yo yajñe yajñaparamair ijyate yajñasaṃsthitiḥ
taṃ yajñapuruṣaṃ viṣṇuṃ namāmi prabhum īśvaram 075.022
gīyate sarvavedeṣu vedavidbhir vidāṃ gatiḥ
yas tasmai vedavedyāya viṣṇave jiṣṇave namaḥ 075.023
yato viśvaṃ samudbhūtaṃ yasmiṃś ca layam eṣyati
viśvodbhavapratiṣṭhāya namas tasmai mahātmane 075.024
brahmādistambaparyantaṃ vinā yena tatām imām
māyāṃ nālaṃ samuttartuṃ tam upendraṃ namāmy aham 075.025
yam ārādhya viśuddhena manasā karmaṇā girā
haraty avidyām akhilāṃ tam upendraṃ namāmy aham
viṣādatoṣaroṣādyair yo 'jasraṃ sukhaduḥkhajaiḥ
nṛtyaty akhilabhūtasthas tam upendraṃ namāmy aham 075.*(120)
yo 'nnatoyasvarūpastho bibharty akhilam īśvaraḥ
viśvaṃ viśvapatiṃ viṣṇuṃ taṃ namāmi prajāpatim 075.026
mūrtaṃ tamo 'suramayaṃ tadvadhād vinihanti yaḥ
rātrijaṃ sūryarūpī ca tam upendraṃ namāmy aham 075.027
kapilādisvarūpastho yaś cājñānamayaṃ tamaḥ
hanti jñānapradānena tam upendraṃ namāmy aham 075.028
yasyākṣiṇī candrasūryau sarvalokaśubhāśubham
paśyete karma satataṃ tam upendraṃ namāmy aham 075.029
yasmin sarveśvare sarvaṃ satyam etan mayoditam
nānṛtaṃ tam ajaṃ viṣṇuṃ namāmi prabhavāvyayam 075.030
yathaitat satyam uktaṃ me bhūyaś cāto janārdanaḥ
satyena tena sakalāḥ pūryantāṃ me manorathāḥ 075.031
evaṃ stuto 'tha bhagavān vāsudeva uvāca tām
adṛśyaḥ sarvabhūtānāṃ tasyāḥ saṃdarśane sthitaḥ 075.032
manorathāṃs tvam adite yān icchasy abhipūritān
tāṃs tān prāpsyasi dharmajñe matprasādād asaṃśayam 075.033
śṛṇuṣva ca mahābhāge varaṃ yas te hṛdi sthitaḥ
maddarśanaṃ hi viphalaṃ na kadācid bhaviṣyati 075.034
taṃ prayacchāmi niyataṃ mātra kāryā vicāraṇā 075.*(122)
yadi deva prasannas tvaṃ bhaktāyā bhaktavatsala
trailokyādhipatiḥ putras tad astu mama vāsavaḥ 075.035
hṛtarājyo hṛtaś cāsya yajñabhāgo mahāsuraiḥ
tvayi prasanne varada taṃ prāpnotu suto mama 075.036
hṛtaṃ rājyaṃ na duḥkhāya mama putrasya keśava
sapatnād āyatibhraṃśo bādhāṃ naḥ kurute hṛdi 075.037
kṛtaḥ prasādo hi mayā tava devi yathepsitaḥ
svāṃśena caiva te garbhe saṃbhaviṣyāmi kaśyapāt 075.038
tava garbhasamudbhūtaḥ sutas te ye surārayaḥ
tān ahaṃ nihaniṣyāmi nirvṛtā bhava nandini 075.039
prasīda devadeveśa namas te viśvabhāvana
nāhaṃ tvām udareṇeśa voḍhuṃ śakṣyāmi keśava 075.040
yasmin pratiṣṭhitaṃ viśvaṃ yo viśvaṃ svayam īśvara
tad ahaṃ nodareṇa tvāṃ voḍhuṃ śakṣyāmi durdharam 075.041
satyam āttha mahābhāge mayi sarvam idaṃ jagat
pratiṣṭhitaṃ na māṃ śaktā voḍhuṃ sendrā divaukasaḥ 075.042
kintv ahaṃ sakalāṃl lokān sadevāsuramānuṣān
jaṅgamājaṅgamaṃ sarvaṃ tvāṃ ca devi sakāśyapām
dhārayiṣyāmi bhadraṃ te tava garbhaśayo 'dite 075.043
na te glānir na te khedo garbhasthe bhavitā mayi
dākṣāyaṇi prasādaṃ te karomy anyaiḥ sudurlabham 075.044
garbhasthe mayi putrāṇāṃ tava yo 'rir bhaviṣyati
tejasas tasya hāniṃ ca kariṣye mā vyathāṃ kṛtāḥ 075.045
evam uktvā tataḥ sadyo gato 'ntardhānam īśvaraḥ
sāpi kālena taṃ garbham avāpa kurusattama 075.046
garbhasthite tataḥ kṛṣṇe cacāla sakalā kṣitiḥ
cakampire mahāśailā jagmuḥ kṣobham athābdhayaḥ 075.047
yato yato 'ditir yāntī dadāti lalitaṃ padam
tatas tataḥ kṣitiḥ khedān nanāma vasudhādhipa 075.048
daityānām api sarveṣāṃ garbhasthe madhusūdane
babhūva tejaso hānir yathoktaṃ parameṣṭhinā 075.049
nistejaso 'surān dṛṣṭvā samastān asureśvaraḥ
prahrādam atha papraccha balir ātmapitāmaham 076.001
tāta nistejaso daityā nirdagdhā iva vahninā
kim ete sahasaivādya brahmadaṇḍahatā iva 076.002
duriṣṭaṃ kiṃ nu daityānāṃ kiṃ kṛtyā vairinirmitā
nāśāyaiṣāṃ samudbhūtā yena nistejaso 'surāḥ 076.003
ity āsuravaras tena pṛṣṭaḥ pautreṇa pārthiva
ciraṃ dhyātvā jagādedam asurendraṃ tadā balim 076.004
calanti girayo bhūmir jahāti sahajāṃ dhṛtim
sadyaḥ samudrāḥ kṣubhitā daityā nistejasaḥ kṛtāḥ 076.005
sūryādayo yathā pūrvaṃ tathā gacchanti na grahāḥ
devānāṃ ca parā lakṣmīḥ kāraṇair anumīyate 076.006
mahad etan mahābāho kāraṇaṃ dānaveśvara
na hy alpam iti mantavyaṃ tvayā kāryaṃ surārdana 076.007
ity uktvā dānavapatiṃ prahrādaḥ so 'surottamaḥ
atyantabhakto deveśaṃ jagāma manasā harim 076.008
sa dhyānapathagaṃ kṛtvā prahrādaḥ svaṃ mano 'suraḥ
vicārayām āsa tato yato devo janārdanaḥ 076.009
sa dadarśodare 'dityāḥ prahrādo vāmanākṛtim
antaḥsthān bibhrataṃ sapta lokān ādiprajāpatim 076.010
tad antaś ca vasūn rudrān aśvinau marutas tathā
sādhyān viśve tathādityān gandharvoragarākṣasān 076.011
virocanaṃ satanayaṃ baliṃ cāsuranāyakam
jambhaṃ kujambhaṃ narakaṃ bāṇam anyāṃs tathāsurān 076.012
ātmānam urvīgaganaṃ vāyum ambho hutāśanam
samudrādridrumasarit- sarāṃsi paśavo mṛgān 076.013
vayomanuṣyān akhilāṃs tathaiva ca sarīsṛpān
samastalokasraṣṭāraṃ brahmāṇaṃ bhavam eva ca 076.014
grahanakṣatratārāś ca dakṣādyāṃś ca prajāpatīn
saṃpaśyan vismayāviṣṭaḥ prakṛtisthaḥ kṣaṇāt punaḥ 076.015
prahrādaḥ prāha daityendraṃ baliṃ vairocaniṃ tadā 076.016
vatsa jñātaṃ mayā sarvaṃ yadarthaṃ bhavatām iyam
tejaso hānir utpannā tac chṛṇu tvam aśeṣataḥ 076.017
devadevo jagadyonir ayonir jagadādikṛt
anādir ādir viśvasya vareṇyo varado hariḥ 076.018
parāparāṇāṃ paramaḥ paraḥ paravatām api
prabhuḥ pramāṇaṃ mānānāṃ saptalokaguror guruḥ 076.019
sthitiṃ kartuṃ jagannāthaḥ so 'dityā garbhatāṃ gataḥ 076.*(123)
prabhuḥ prabhūṇām paramaḥ parāṇām anādimadhyo bhagavān anantaḥ
trailokyam aṃśena sanātham eṣa kartuṃ mahātmāditijo 'vatīrṇaḥ 076.020
na yasya rudro na ca padmayonir nendro na sūryendumarīcimiśrāḥ
jānanti daityādhipa yat svarūpaṃ sa vāsudevaḥ kalayāvatīrṇaḥ 076.021
yo 'sau kalāṃśena nṛsiṃharūpī jaghāna pūrvaṃ pitaram aśeṣaḥ
yaḥ sarvayogīśamanonivāsaḥ sa vāsudevaḥ kalayāvatīrṇaḥ 076.022
yam akṣaraṃ vedavido viditvā viśanti taṃ jñānavidhūtapāpāḥ
yasmin praviṣṭā na punar bhavanti taṃ vāsudevaṃ praṇamāmi devam 076.023
bhūtāny aśeṣāṇi yato bhavanti yathormayas toyanidher ajasram
layaṃ ca yasmin pralaye prayānti taṃ vāsudevaṃ praṇamāmy acintyam 076.024
na yasya rūpaṃ na balaṃ prabhāvo na ca svabhāvaḥ paramasya puṃsaḥ
vijñāyate sarvapitāmahādyais taṃ vāsudevaṃ praṇamāmy acintyam 076.025
rūpasya cakṣur grahaṇe tvag eṣā sparśagrahītrī rasanā rasasya
śrotraṃ ca śabdagrahaṇe narāṇāṃ ghrāṇaṃ ca gandhagrahaṇe niyuktam 076.026
na ghrāṇacakṣuḥśravaṇādibhir yaḥ sarveśvaro veditum avyayātmā
śakyas tam īḍyaṃ manasaiva devaṃ grāhyaṃ nato 'haṃ harim īśitāram 076.027
yenaikadaṃṣṭrāgrasamuddhṛteyaṃ dharācalā dhārayatīha sarvam
grastvā sa śete sakalaṃ jagad yas tam īḍyam īśaṃ praṇato 'smi viṣṇum 076.028
aṃśāvatīrṇena ca yena garbhe hṛtāni tejāṃsi mahāsurāṇām
namāmi taṃ devam anantam īśam aśeṣasaṃsārataroḥ kuṭhāram 076.029
devo jagadyonir ayaṃ mahātmā sa ṣoḍaśāṃśena mahāsurendra
surendramātur jaṭharaṃ praviṣṭo hṛtāni vas tena bale vapūṃṣi 076.030
tāta ko 'yaṃ harir nāma yato na bhayam āgatam
santi me śataśo daityā vāsudevabalādhikāḥ 076.031
vipracittiḥ śibiḥ śaṅkur ayaḥśaṅkus tathaiva ca
ayaḥśirā aśvaśirā bhaṅgakāro mahāhanuḥ 076.032
pratāpī praghasaḥ śaṃbhuḥ kurkurākṣaś ca durjayaḥ
ete cānye ca me santi daiteyā dānavās tathā 076.033
mahābalā mahāvīryā bhūbhāradharaṇakṣamāḥ
yeṣām ekaikaśaḥ kṛṣṇo na vīryārdhena saṃmitaḥ 076.034
pautrasyaitad vacaḥ śrutvā prahrādo daityapuṅgavaḥ
dhig dhig ity āha sa baliṃ vaikuṇṭhākṣepavādinam 076.035
vināśam upayāsyanti manye daiteyadānavāḥ
yeṣāṃ tvam īdṛśo rājā durbuddhir avivekavān 076.036
devadevaṃ mahābhāgaṃ vāsudevam ajaṃ vibhum
tvām ṛte pāpasaṃkalpaṃ ko 'nya evaṃ vadiṣyati 076.037
ya ete bhavatā proktāḥ samastā daityadānavāḥ
sabrahmakās tathā devāḥ sthāvarāntāś ca bhūtayaḥ 076.038
tvaṃ cāhaṃ ca jagac cedaṃ sādridrumanadīnadam
samudradvīpalokāś ca yac ceṅgaṃ yac ca neṅgati 076.039
yasyātivandyavandyasya vyāpinaḥ paramātmanaḥ
ekāṃśāṃśakalājanma kas tam evaṃ pravakṣyati 076.040
ṛte vināśābhimukhaṃ tvām ekam avivekinam
durbuddhim ajitātmānaṃ vṛddhānāṃ śāsanātigam 076.041
śocyo 'haṃ yasya vai gehe jātas tava pitādhamaḥ
yasya tvam īdṛśaḥ putro devadevāvamanyakaḥ 076.042
tiṣṭhatv anekasaṃsāra- saṃhṛtāghavināśanī
kṛṣṇe bhaktir ahaṃ tāvad avekṣyo bhavato na kim 076.043
na me priyataraḥ kṛṣṇād api deho 'yam ātmanaḥ
iti jānāty ayaṃ loko bhavāṃś ca ditijādhamaḥ 076.044
jānann api priyataraṃ prāṇebhyo 'pi hariṃ mama
nindāṃ karoṣi ca katham akurvan gauravaṃ mama 076.045
virocanas tava gurur gurus tasyāpy ahaṃ bale
mamāpi sarvajagatāṃ gurur nārāyaṇo guruḥ 076.046
nindāṃ karoṣi tasmiṃs tvaṃ kṛṣṇe guruguror gurau
yasmāt tasmād ihaiśvaryād acirād bhraṃśam eṣyasi 076.047
mā devo mā jagannātho bale māsau janārdanaḥ
bhavatv aham avekṣyas te prītimān atra me guruḥ 076.048
etāvanmātram apy atra nindatā jagato gurum
nāpekṣitā vayaṃ yasmāt tasmāc chāpaṃ dadāmi te 076.049
yathā me śirasaś chedād idaṃ gurutaraṃ bale
tvayoktam acyutākṣepi rājyabhraṣṭas tathā pata 076.050
yathā na kṛṣṇād aparaṃ paritrāṇaṃ bhavārṇave
tathācireṇa paśyeyaṃ bhavantaṃ rājyavicyutam 076.051
iti daityapatiḥ śrutvā guror vacanam apriyam
prasādayām āsa guruṃ praṇipatya puṇaḥ punaḥ 076.052
prasīda tāta mā kopaṃ kuru mohahate mayi
balāvalepamattena mayaitad vākyam īritam 076.053
mohopahatavijñānaḥ pāpo 'haṃ ditijottama
yac chapto 'smi durācāras tat sādhu bhavatā kṛtam 076.054
rājyabhraṃśaṃ vasubhraṃśaṃ saṃprāpsyāmīti na tv aham
viṣaṇṇo 'smi yathā tāta tavaivāvinaye kṛte 076.055
trailokyarājyam aiśvaryam anyad vā nātidurlabham
saṃsāre durlabhās tāta guravo ye bhavadvidhāḥ 076.056
tat prasīda na me kopaṃ kartum arhasi daityapa
tvatkopahetuduṣṭo 'haṃ paritapye na śāpataḥ 076.057
vatsa kopena moho me janitas tena te mayā
śāpo datto vivekaś ca mohenāpahṛto mama 076.058
yadi mohena me jñānaṃ nākṣiptaṃ syān mahāsura
tat kathaṃ sarvagaṃ jñānan hariṃ kaṃcic chāpāmy aham 076.059
yo 'yaṃ śāpo mayā datto bhavato 'surapuṅgava
bhāvyam etena nūnaṃ te tasmāt tvaṃ mā viṣīdathāḥ 076.060
adyaprabhṛti deveśe bhagavaty acyute harau
bhavethā bhaktimān īśaḥ sa te trātā bhaviṣyati 076.061
śāpaṃ prāpya ca māṃ vīra saṃsmarethāḥ smṛtas tvayā
tathā tathā yatiṣyāmi śreyasā yokṣyate yathā 076.062
evam uktvā sa daityendro virarāma mahāmatiḥ
ajāyata sa govindo bhagavān vāmanākṛtiḥ 076.063
avatīrṇe jagannāthe tasmin sarvam aśīśamat
yad āsuram abhūd duḥkhaṃ devānām adites tathā 076.064
vavur vātāḥ sukhasparśā nīrajaskam abhūn nabhaḥ
dharme ca sarvabhūtānāṃ tadā matir ajāyata 076.065
nodvegaś cāpy abhūd dehe manujānāṃ janeśvara
tathā hi sarvabhūtānāṃ bhūmyambaradivaukasām 076.066
taṃ jātamātraṃ bhagavān brahmā lokapitāmahaḥ
jātakarmādikāḥ kṛtvā kriyās tuṣṭāva pārthiva 076.067
jayādyeśa jayājeya jaya sarvātmakātmaka
jaya janmajarāpeta jayānanta jayācyuta 076.068
jayājita jayāśeṣa jayāvyakta sthite jaya
paramārthārtha sarvajña jñāna jñeyātmaniḥsṛta 076.069
jayāśeṣajagatsākṣiñ jaya kartar jagadguroḥ
jagato jagadante 'nta sthitau pālayitā jaya 076.070
jayākhila jayāśeṣa jayākhilahṛdi sthita
jayādimadhyāntamaya sarvajñānamayottama 076.071
mumukṣubhir anirdeśya svayaṃdṛṣṭa jayeśvara
yogibhir muktiphalada damādiguṇabhūṣaṇaiḥ 076.072
jayātisūkṣma durjñeya jagat sthūla jaganmaya
jaya sthūlātisūkṣma tvaṃ jayātīndriya sendriya 076.073
jaya svamāyāyogastha śeṣabhogaśayākṣara
samuddhṛtavasuṃdhara 076.074
jayaikadaṃṣṭrāprāntānta nṛkesariñ jayārāti-
vakṣaḥsthalavidāraṇa sāṃprataṃ jaya viśvātman
māyāvāmana keśava 076.075
nijamāyāpaṭacchanna jagaddhātar janārdana
jayācintya jayāneka- svarūpaikavidha prabho 076.076
vardhasva vardhitāneka- vikāraprakṛte hare
tvayy eṣā jagatām īśa saṃsthitā dharmapaddhatiḥ 076.077
na tvām ahaṃ na ceśāno nendrādyās tridaśā hare
jñātum īśā na munayaḥ sanakādyā na yoginaḥ 076.078
tvanmāyāpaṭasaṃvīte jagaty atra jagatpate
kas tvāṃ vetsyati sarveśaṃ tvatprasādaṃ vinā naraḥ 076.079
tvam evārādhito yasya prasādasumukhaḥ prabho
sa eva kevalaṃ deva vetti tvāṃ netaro janaḥ 076.080
tad īśvareśvareśāna vibho vardhasva bhāvana
prabhāvāyāsya viśvasya viśvātman pṛthulocana 076.081
evaṃ stuto hṛṣīkeśaḥ sa tadā vāmanākṛtiḥ
prahasya bhāvagambhīram uvācābjasamudbhavam 076.082
stuto 'haṃ bhavatā pūrvam indrādyaiḥ kaśyapena ca
mayā ca vaḥ pratijñātam indrasya bhuvanatrayam 076.083
bhūyaś cāhaṃ stuto 'dityā tasyāś cāpi pratiśrutam
yathā śakrāya dāsyāmi trailokyaṃ hatakaṇṭakam 076.084
so 'haṃ tathā kariṣyāmi yathendro jagataḥ patiḥ
bhaviṣyati sahasrākṣaḥ satyam etad bravīmi te 076.085
tataḥ kṛṣṇājinaṃ brahmā hṛṣīkeśāya dattavān
yajñopavītaṃ bhagavān dadau tasmai bṛhaspatiḥ 076.086
āṣāḍham adadad daṇḍaṃ marīcir brahmaṇaḥ sutaḥ
kamaṇḍaluṃ vasiṣṭhaś ca kauśyaṃ vedam athāṅgirāḥ
akṣasūtraṃ ca pulahaḥ pulastyaḥ sitavāsasī 076.087
upatasthuś ca taṃ vedāḥ praṇavasvarabhūṣaṇāḥ
śāstrāṇy aśeṣāṇi tathā sāṃkhyayogoktayaś ca yāḥ 076.088
sa vāmano jaṭī daṇḍī chattrī dhṛtakamaṇḍaluḥ
sarvadevamayo bhūpa baler adhvaram abhyayāt 076.089
yatra yatra padaṃ bhūpa bhūbhāge vāmano dadau
dadāti bhūmir vivaraṃ tatra tatrātipīḍitā 076.090
sa vāmano jaḍagatir mṛdu gacchan saparvatām
sābdhidvīpavatīṃ sarvāṃ cālayām āsa medinīm 076.091
tataḥ saṃśayam āpannāḥ sarve daiteyadānavāḥ 076.*(124)
saparvatavanām urvīṃ dṛṣṭvā saṃkṣubhitāṃ baliḥ
papracchośanasaṃ śukraṃ praṇipatya kṛtāñjaliḥ 077.001
ācārya kṣobham āyāti sābdhibhūbhṛddharā mahī
kasmāc ca nāsurān bhāgān pratigṛhṇanti vahnayaḥ 077.002
iti pṛṣṭo 'tha balinā kāvyo vedavidāṃ varaḥ
uvāca daityādhipatiṃ ciraṃ dhyātvā mahāmatiḥ 077.003
avatīrṇo jagadyoniḥ kaśyapasya gṛhe hariḥ
vāmaneneha rūpeṇa paramātmā sanātanaḥ 077.004
sa nūnaṃ yajñam āyāti tava dānavapuṅgava
tatpadanyāsavikṣobhād iyaṃ pracalitā mahī 077.005
kampante girayaś cāmī kṣubhitā makarālayāḥ
nainaṃ bhūtapatiṃ bhūmiḥ samarthā voḍhum īśvaram 077.006
sadevāsuragandharva- yakṣarākṣasapannagā
anenaiva dhṛtā bhūmir āpo 'gniḥ pavano nabhaḥ
dhārayaty akhilān deva- manuṣyādīn mahāsura 077.007
iyam asya jagaddhātur māyā kṛṣṇasya gahvarī
dhāryadhārakabhāvena yayā saṃpiṇḍitaṃ jagat 077.008
tatsaṃnidhānād asurā na bhāgārhāḥ suradviṣaḥ
bhuñjate cāsurān bhāgān amī te na tavāgnayaḥ 077.009
śukrasya vacanaṃ śrutvā hṛṣṭaromābravīd baliḥ 077.*(125)
dhanyo 'haṃ kṛtapuṇyaś ca yan me yajñapatiḥ svayam
yajñam abhyāgato brahman mattaḥ ko 'nyo 'dhikaḥ pumān 077.010
yaṃ yoginaḥ sadodyuktāḥ paramātmānam avyayam
draṣṭum icchanti devo 'sau madadhvaram upaiṣyati 077.011
hotā bhāgaprado yasya yam udgātā ca gāyati
tam adhvareśvaraṃ viṣṇuṃ mattaḥ ko 'nya upaiṣyati 077.012
sarveśvareśvare viṣṇau mamādhvaram upāgate
yan mayā cārya kartavyaṃ tan mamādeṣṭum arhasi 077.013
yajñabhāgabhujo devā vedaprāmāṇyato 'sura
tvayā tu dānavā daityā yajñabhāgabhujaḥ kṛtāḥ 077.014
ayaṃ ca devaḥ sattvasthaḥ karoti sthitipālanam
nisṛṣṭeś cāyam ante ca svayam atti prajāḥ prabhuḥ 077.015
tvayānubandhī bhavitā nūnaṃ viṣṇuḥ sthitau sthitaḥ
viditvaitan mahābhāga kuru yat te manogatam 077.016
tvayāsya daityādhipate svalpake 'pi hi vastuni
pratijñā naiva voḍhavyā vācyaṃ sāma tathāphalam 077.017
kṛtakṛtyasya devasya devārthaṃ caiva kurvataḥ 077.*(126)
nālaṃ dātuṃ dhanaṃ devety evaṃ vācyaṃ tu yācataḥ
kṛṣṇasya devabhūtyarthaṃ pravṛttasya mahāsura 077.018
brahman katham ahaṃ brūyām anyenāpi hi yācitaḥ
nāstīti kimu devena saṃsārāghaughahāriṇā 077.019
vratopavāsair vividhair yaḥ pratigrāhyate hariḥ
sa ced vakṣyati dehīti govindaḥ kim ato 'dhikam 077.020
yadartham upahārāḍhyā damaśaucaguṇānvitaiḥ
yajñāḥ kriyante deveśaḥ sa māṃ dehīti vakṣyati 077.021
tat sādhu sukṛtaṃ karma tapaḥ sucaritaṃ ca naḥ
yan mayā dattam īśeśaḥ svayam ādāsyate hariḥ 077.022
nāstīty ahaṃ guro vakṣye tam apy āgatam īśvaram
yadi tad vañcyate prāpte nūnam asmadvidhaḥ phalaiḥ 077.023
yajñe 'smin yadi yajñeśo yācate māṃ janārdanaḥ
nijamūrdhānam apy adya tad dāsyāmy avicāritam 077.024
nāstīti yan mayā noktam anyeṣām api yācatām
vakṣyāmi katham āyāte tad anabhyastam acyute 077.025
ślāghya eva hi dhīrāṇāṃ dānād āpatsamāgamaḥ
nābādhākāri yad dānaṃ tad aṅgamalavat katham 077.026
madrājye nāsukhī kaścin na daridro na cāturaḥ
nātṛṣito na codvigno na sragādivivarjitaḥ 077.027
hṛṣṭatuṣṭaḥ sugandhī ca tṛptaḥ sarvasukhānvitaḥ
janaḥ sarvo mahābhāga kimutāhaṃ sadā sukhī 077.028
etad viśiṣṭapātrotthaṃ dānabījaphalaṃ mama
viditaṃ bhṛguśārdūla mayaitat tvatprasādataḥ 077.029
etad vijānato dāna- bījaṃ patati ced guro
janārdane mahāpātre kiṃ na prāptaṃ tato mayā 077.030
matto dānam avāpyeśo yadi puṣṇāti devatāḥ
upabhogānvayaguṇaṃ dānaṃ ślāghyataraṃ tataḥ 077.031
matprasādaparo nūnaṃ yajñenārādhito hariḥ
tenābhyeti na saṃdeho darśanād upakārakṛt 077.032
atha kopena vābhyeti devabhāgoparodhinam
māṃ nihantum ato 'pi syād vadhaḥ ślāghyataro 'cyutāt 077.033
yanmayaṃ sarvam evedaṃ nāprāpya yasya vidyate
sa māṃ yācitum abhyeti nānugraham ṛte hariḥ 077.034
yaḥ sṛjaty ātmabhūḥ sarvaṃ cetasaivāpahanti ca
sa māṃ hantuṃ hṛṣīkeśaḥ kathaṃ yatnaṃ kariṣyati 077.035
etad viditvā tu guro dānavighnapareṇa me
naiva bhāvyaṃ jagannāthe govinde samupasthite 077.036
ity evaṃ vadatas tasya prāptas tatra jagapatiḥ
sarvadevamayo 'cintyo māyāvāmanarūpadhṛk 077.037
taṃ dṛṣṭvā yajñavāṭāntaḥ- praviṣṭam asurāḥ prabhum
jagmuḥ prabhāvataḥ kṣobhaṃ tejasā tasya niṣprabhāḥ 077.038
jepuś ca munayas tatra ye sametā mahādhvare
baliś caivākhilaṃ janma mene saphalam ātmanaḥ 077.039
tataḥ saṃkṣobham āpanno na kaścit kiṃcid uktavān
pratyeko devadeveśaṃ pūjayām āsa cetasā 077.040
athāsurapatiṃ prahvaṃ dṛṣṭvā munivarāṃś ca tān
devadevapatiḥ sākṣād viṣṇur vāmanarūpadhṛk 077.041
tuṣṭāva yajñaṃ vahniṃś ca yajamānam atha rtvijaḥ
yajñakarādhikārasthān sadasyān dravyasaṃpadam 077.042
tataḥ prasannam akhilaṃ vāmanaṃ prati tatkṣaṇāt
yajñavāṭasthitaṃ vīraṃ sādhu sādhv ity udīrayan 077.043
sa cārgham ādāya baliḥ prodbhūtapulakas tadā
pūjayām āsa govindaṃ prāha cedaṃ vaco 'suraḥ 077.044
suvarṇaratnasaṃghātaṃ gajāśvam amitaṃ tathā
striyo vastrāṇy alaṃkārān gāvo grāmāṃś ca puṣkalān 077.045
sarvasvaṃ sakalām urvīṃ bhavato vā yad īpsitam
tad dadāmi vṛṇuṣva tvaṃ mamārthī satataṃ priyaḥ 077.046
ity ukto daityapatinā prītigarvānvitaṃ vacaḥ
prāha sasmitagambhīraṃ bhagavān vāmanākṛtiḥ 077.047
mamāgniśaraṇārthāya dehi rājan padatrayam
suvarṇagrāmaratnādi tad arthibhyaḥ pradīyatām 077.048
tribhiḥ prayojanaṃ kiṃ te padaiḥ padavatāṃ vara
śataṃ śatasahasraṃ vā padānāṃ mārgatāṃ bhavān 077.049
etāvatā daityapate kṛtakṛtyo 'smi mārgatām
anyeṣām arthināṃ vittam icchayā dāsyate bhavān 077.050
etac chrutvā tu gaditaṃ vāmanasya mahātmanaḥ
vācayām āsa tat tasmai vāmanāya padatrayam 077.051
pāṇau tu patite toye vāmano bhūtabhāvanaḥ
sarvadevamayaṃ rūpaṃ darśayām āsa tatkṣaṇāt 077.052
candrasūryau ca nayane dyauḥ śiraś caraṇau kṣitiḥ
pādāṅgulyaḥ piśācāś ca hastāṅgulyaś ca guhyakāḥ 077.053
viśvedevāś ca jānusthā jaṅghe sādhyāḥ surottamāḥ
yakṣā nakheṣu saṃbhūtā rekhāsv apsarasaḥ sthitāḥ 077.054
dṛṣṭir dhiṣṇāny aśeṣāṇi keśāḥ sūryāṃśavaḥ prabho
tārakā romakūpāṇi romāṇi ca maharṣayaḥ 077.055
bāhavo vidiśas tasya diśaḥ śrotraṃ mahātmanaḥ
aśvinau śravaṇau tasya nāsā vāyur mahābalaḥ 077.056
prasādaś candramā devo mano dharmaḥ samāśritaḥ
satyam asyābhavad vāṇī jihvā devī sarasvatī 077.057
grīvāditir devamātā vidyās tadvalayas tathā
svargadvāram abhūn maitraṃ tvaṣṭā pūṣā ca vai bhruvau 077.058
mukhaṃ vaiśvānaraś cāsya vṛṣaṇau tu prajāpatiḥ
hṛdayaṃ ca paraṃ brahma puṃstvaṃ vai kaśyapo muniḥ 077.059
pṛṣṭhe 'sya vasavo devā marutaḥ sarvasaṃdhiṣu
sarvasūktāni daśanā jyotīṃṣi vimalaprabhāḥ 077.060
vakṣaḥsthale tathā rudro dhairye cāsya mahārṇavaḥ
udare cāsya gandharvā marutaś ca mahābalāḥ
lakṣmīr medhā dhṛtiḥ kāntiḥ sarvavidyāś ca vai kaṭiḥ 077.061
sarvajyotīṃṣi yānīha tapaś ca paramaṃ mahat
tasya devātidevasya tejaḥ prodbhūtam uttamam 077.062
stanau kukṣau ca vedāś ca jānū cāsya mahāmakhāḥ
iṣṭayaḥ paśubandhāś ca dvijānāṃ ceṣṭitāni ca 077.063
tasya devamayaṃ rūpaṃ dṛṣṭvā viṣṇor mahābalāḥ
upasarpanti daiteyāḥ pataṃgā iva pāvakam 077.064
pramathya sarvān asurān pādahastatalair vibhuḥ
kṛtvā rūpaṃ mahākāyaṃ sa jahārāśu medinīm 077.065
tasya vikramato bhumiṃ candrādityau stanāntare
nabho vikramamāṇasya sakthideśe sthitāv ubhau 077.066
paraṃ vikramamāṇasya jānumūle prabhākarau
viṣṇor āstām mahīpāla devapālanakarmaṇi 077.067
jitvā lokatrayaṃ kṛtsnaṃ hatvā cāsurapuṅgavān
puraṃdarāya trailokyaṃ dadau viṣṇur urukramaḥ 077.068
sutalaṃ nāma pātālam adhastād vasudhātalāt
baler dattaṃ bhagavatā viṣṇunā prabhaviṣṇunā 077.069
atha daityeśvaraṃ prāha viṣṇuḥ sarveśvareśvaraḥ 077.070
yat tvayā salilaṃ dattaṃ gṛhītaṃ pāṇinā mayā
kalpapramāṇaṃ tasmāt te bhaviṣyaty āyur uttamam 077.071
vaivasvate tathātīte bale manvantare tataḥ
sāvarṇake ca saṃprāpte bhavān indro bhaviṣyati 077.072
sāṃprataṃ devarājāya trailokyam akhilaṃ mayā
dattaṃ caturyugānāṃ vai sādhikā hy ekasaptatiḥ 077.073
niyantavyā mayā sarve ye tasya paripanthinaḥ
tenāhaṃ parayā bhaktyā pūrvam ārādhito bale 077.074
sutalaṃ nāma pātālaṃ tam āsādya manoramam
vasāsura mamādeśaṃ yathāvat paripālayan 077.075
tatra divyavanopete prāsādaśatasaṃkule
protphullapadmasarasi sravacchuddhasaridvare 077.076
sugandhidhūpasaṃbādhe varābharaṇabhūṣitaḥ
srakcandanādidigdhāṅgo nṛtyagītamanoramaiḥ 077.077
upabhuñjan mahābhogān vividhān dānaveśvara
mamājñayā kālam imaṃ tiṣṭha strīśatasaṃvṛtaḥ 077.078
yāvat suraiś ca vipraiś ca na virodhaṃ kariṣyasi
tāvad etān mahābhogān avāpsyasy asurottama 077.079
yadā ca devaviprāṇāṃ viruddhāny ācariṣyasi
bandhiṣyanti tathā pāśā vāruṇās tvām asaṃśayam 077.080
etad viditvā bhavatā mayājñaptam aśeṣataḥ
na virodhaḥ suraiḥ kāryo viprair vā daityasattama 077.081
ity evam ukto devena viṣṇunā prabhaviṣṇunā
baliḥ prāha mahārāja praṇipatya kṛtāñjaliḥ 077.082
tatrāsato me pātāle bhagavan bhavadājñayā
kiṃ bhaviṣyaty upādānam upabhogopapādakam 077.083
āpyāyito yena deva smareyaṃ tvām ahaṃ sadā 077.*(127)
dānāny avidhidattāni śrāddhāny aśrotriyāṇi ca
hutāny aśraddhayā yāni tāni dāsyanti te phalam 077.084
adakṣiṇās tathā yajñāḥ kriyāś cāvidhinā kṛtāḥ
phalāni tava dāsyanti adhītāny avratāni ca 077.085
baler varam idaṃ dattvā śakrāya trividaṃ tathā
vyāpinā tena rūpeṇa jagāmādarśanaṃ hariḥ 077.086
śaśāsa ca yathā pūrvam indras trailokyam ūrjitam
siṣeva ca parān kāmān baliḥ pātālam āśritaḥ 077.087
ity etad devadevasya viṣṇor māhātmyam uttamam
vāmanasya paṭhed yas tu sarvapāpaiḥ pramucyate 077.088
baliprahrādasaṃvādaṃ mantritaṃ baliśukrayoḥ
baliviṣṇvoś ca kathitaṃ yaḥ smariṣyati mānavaḥ 077.089
nādhayo vyādhayo vāsya na ca mohākulaṃ manaḥ
bhaviṣyati kuruśreṣṭha puṃsas tasya kadācana 077.090
cyutarājyo nijaṃ rājyam iṣṭaprāptiṃ viyogavān
avāpnoti mahābhāga naraḥ śrutvā kathām imām 077.091
pātāle nivasan vīras tadā vairocanir baliḥ
kāmopabhogasaṃprāptyā mudaṃ prāpa parāṃ vibhuḥ 078.001
alaṃbuṣā miśrakeśī puṇḍarīkātha vāmanā
ghṛtācī menakā rambhā nanṛtus tasya saṃnidhau 078.002
prajagur devagandharvā viśvāvasupurogamāḥ
tuṣṭuvuś ca mahābhāga baliṃ siddhāḥ sacāraṇāḥ 078.003
tasmin saṃgītagītā tu vīṇāveṇuravākule
sragādibhūṣito daityaḥ papau pānam anuttamam 078.004
śarkārasavamādhvikāṃ puṣpāsavaphalāsavam
divyāḥ prasannāś ca surās tadarhāṇi madhūni ca 078.005
parāvadaṃśān madhurāṃl lavaṇāṃs tiktakāṇ kaṭūn
kaṣāyāṃś ca mahārāja sumṛṣṭāny aparāṇi ca 078.006
suhṛṭsujanasaṃbandhi- bhṛtyavargasamanvitaḥ
bubhuje pātālagatas tadā vairocanir baliḥ 078.007
prāsādāḥ kāñcanāḥ sarve suvarṇamaṇimaṇḍitāḥ
sphāṭikāmalasopānā muktāhāraśatojjvalāḥ 078.008
teṣu sarveṣu daiteyā baleḥ saṃbandhibāndhavāḥ
nṛtyavādyādimuditā bubhujur viṣayān priyān 078.009
baliś ca bhagavān daityo daityoragaśatair vṛtaḥ
upagīyamāno bubhuje yatheṣṭaṃ viṣayān priyān 078.010
patnī vindhyāvalī nāma tasya daityapater abhūt
sarvalakṣaṇasaṃpūrṇā śrīr ivābjaṃ vināparā 078.011
na devī nāpi gandharvī nāpsarā na ca mānuṣī
tasyā rūpeṇa sadṛśī babhūva manujeśvara 078.012
sā tu pīnāyataśroṇī mṛdvaṅgī madhurasvarā
ghanonnatakucā subhrūḥ sasmitāyatalocanā 078.013
mṛdvalpapāṇipādābjā sumadhyā gajagāminī
sukeśī sumukhī śyāmā sarvair yoṣidguṇair yutā 078.014
tanayā merusāvarṇer dauhitrī mṛgamokinaḥ
patnī sahasradvitaye pradhānā tasya sābhavat 078.015
vapuṣā rūpasaṃpadā pautanā mṛgalocanā 078.*(128)
tayā tu ramatas tasya ramaṇīye rasātale
śaktir āsīd anudinaṃ vivekapratilominī 078.016
kadācid ramatas tasya daityarājasya pārthiva
tīkṣṇāṃśur madhyamāṃ vīthīṃ yayau vaiṣuvatīṃ raviḥ 078.017
yadā yadā ca viṣuvaṃ bhāskaraḥ pratipadyate
tadā tadā hareś cakraṃ pātāle parivartate 078.018
sravanti yoṣitāṃ garbhās tasya dhārāṃśutāpitāḥ
sahasā daityapatnīnāṃ yāsu puṃsāṃ samudbhavaḥ
nistejaso daityabhaṭā bhavanti ca mahīpate 078.019
tad dṛṣṭvā sahasāyāntam ādityaśatatejasam
jvālāmālāsuduḥprekṣyaṃ viṣṇucakraṃ sudarśanam
hāhākṛtam abhūt sarvaṃ pātālam arisūdana 078.020
jepur ye munayas tatra sārghapātrā mahoragāḥ
babhūvuḥ praṇatāś cānye siddhagandharvacāraṇāḥ
vaiklavyaṃ cāgatāḥ sarvāḥ striyaḥ parapuraṃjaya 078.021
tad dṛṣṭvā vyākulībhūtaṃ pātālam asurās tataḥ
ye tasthuḥ pauruṣaparās te hatāḥ śataneminā 078.022
bhrāmyatā tena cakreṇa saptalokavicāriṇā
samastajagadādhāra- karamuktena veginā 078.023
tan niṣūditadaityaughaṃ daityastrīgarbhahānidam
śrutvā cakraṃ mahācakro niścakrāma gṛhād baliḥ 078.024
āḥ kim etad itīty uktvā sa tu madyamahoddhataḥ
vimalaṃ khaḍgam ādāya śatacandraṃ ca bhānumat 078.025
niryāntam atha vegena tam udāraparākramam
vidhyāvalī nāma śubhā dadhāra dayitaṃ patim 078.026
uvāca ca pariṣvajya krodhatāmrekṣaṇaṃ balim
kalyāṇī guṇadoṣajñā praṇayān mṛdubhāṣiṇī 078.027
daityarāja na kopasya vaśam āgantum arhasi
vimṛśya tajjñaḥ sāmādīn prayuñjīta balābalam 078.028
kim etat kasya vā kutra kiṃnimittam ihāgatam
cakram itthaṃ vicārya tvaṃ krodhaṃ yāhi praśāmya vā 078.029
etat kila jagaddhātuś cakraṃ viṣṇoḥ sudarśanam
pratiṣaṇmāsam abhyeti daityagarbhavināśanam 078.030
puṅgarbhān nikhilān etad dānavānāṃ mahāsura
vināśayaty anantarāṃ sarvaduṣṭanibarhaṇam 078.031
karoti duḥkham atulaṃ ghātanāt pratipakṣajam
puruṣāṇāṃ na sarvatra saṃsthitā jagataḥ pateḥ 078.032
mayi tvayi tathānyatra yathā viṣṇur vyavasthitaḥ
tasyaitac cakram āyāntaṃ puruṣaḥ ko na pūjayet 078.033
yasyādhikṣepajā rājaṃs tava trailokyavicyutiḥ
tasya cakraṃ jaganmūrteḥ samupaiṣi ruṣā katham 078.034
sadṛśe puruṣe krodhaṃ naraḥ kurvīta daityapa
na tu sarveśvare viṣṇau yatra sarvaṃ pratiṣṭhitam 078.035
tat prasīda mahābhāga samupaihi jagatpatim
śaraṇyaṃ śaraṇaṃ viṣṇuṃ yaṃ praṇamya na sīdati 078.036
yasmin prasanne trailokyaṃ tvattaḥ prāptaḥ śacīpatiḥ
bhraṣṭaś ca yadadhikṣepāt taṃ tvaṃ śaraṇam āvraja 078.037
yatra sarveśvare sarvaṃ sarvabhūte jagat sthitam
tasya cakram upaihi tvaṃ vinayād asurādhipa 078.038
sarvakāraṇabhūtasya devadevasya cakriṇaḥ
kaś cakram ativarteta martyadharmā mahāsura 078.039
cakram atra jagaddhātuḥ karoti sthitipālanam
vipakṣāsurasaṃbhūti- garbhavisraṃsanāt prabho 078.040
prasādya cakranāmānaṃ govindaṃ jagato gurum
śreyase sarvadharmajña śaraṇaṃ vraja keśavam 078.041
saṃsmarasva ca daityendra prahrādaṃ svapitāmaham
bhraṣṭarājyena bhavatā smartavyo 'ham iti prabho 078.042
sa vyājahāra bhagavāṃs tavānugrahakāmyayā
saṃsmaryatāṃ mahābhāga sarvadharmabhṛtāṃ varaḥ
viṣṇubhakto mahābāhuḥ sa te śreyo 'bhidhāsyati 078.043
etad vacanam ākarṇya tadā vairocanir baliḥ
yayau tadārgham ādāya viṣṇoś cakrasya pūjakaḥ 078.044
sa dadarśa samāyāntam anantakarasaṅginam
cakram akṣayacakrasya viśvasya paripālakam 078.045
sasmāra ca baliḥ sarvaṃ prahrādavacanaṃ nṛpa
jagāda yac ca govindaḥ prasādasumukhaḥ prabhuḥ 078.046
bhaktinamras tato bhūtvā bhūtabhavyabhavatprabhoḥ
tuṣṭāva vāsudevasya cakram avyaktamūrtinaḥ 078.047
jvālāmālākarālāntam udyadindusamaprabham
madhyāhnārkasamābhāsaṃ tejasaḥ piṇḍasaṃsthitam 078.048
taṃ dṛṣṭvā tejasā rāśim upasaṃgamya cā vibhum
uvāca daityaśārdūlaḥ praṇipatya kṛtāñjaliḥ 078.049
anantasyāprameyasya viśvamūrter mahātmanaḥ
namāmi cakriṇaś cakraṃ karasaṅgi sudarśanam
kālāgnim iva yac cakraṃ 078.050
sahasram iva sūryāṇāṃ saṃghātaṃ vidyutām iva
tad viṣṇoḥ praṇamāmy aham 078.051
duṣṭarāhugalaccheda- śoṇitāruṇatārakam
tan namāmi hareś cakraṃ śatanemi sudarśanam 078.052
yasyārakeṣu śakrādyā lokapālā vyavasthitāḥ
tadantar vasavo rudrās tathaiva marutāṃ gaṇāḥ 078.053
dhārāyāṃ dvādaśādityāḥ samastāś ca hutāśanāḥ
dhārājāle 'bdhayaḥ sarve nābhimadhye prajāpatiḥ 078.054
samastanemiṣv akhilā yasya vidyāḥ pratiṣṭhitāḥ
yasya rūpam anirdeśyam api yogibhir uttamaiḥ 078.055
yad bhramat surasaṅghānāṃ tejasaḥ paribṛṃhaṇam
daityaujasāṃ ca nāśāya tan namāmi sudarśanam 078.056
bhraman matamahāvega- vibhrāntākhilakhecaram
tan namāmi hareś cakram anantāraṃ sudarśanam 078.*(129)
nakṣatravadvahnikaṇa- vyāptaṃ kṛtsnaṃ nabhastalam
tan namāmi hareś cakraṃ karasaṅgi sudarśanam 078.*(130)
svabhāvatejasā yuktaṃ yad arkāgnimayaṃ mahat
viśeṣato harer gatvā sarvadevamayaṃ karam 078.057
durvṛttadaityamathanaṃ jagataḥ paripālakam
tan namāmi hareś cakraṃ daityacakraharaṃ param 078.058
karotu me sadā śarma dharmatāṃ ca prayātu me
prasādasumukhe kṛṣṇe tasya cakraṃ sudarśanam 078.059
svabhāvatejasā yuktaṃ madhyāhnārkasamaprabham 078.*(131)
prasīda saṃyuge 'riṇāṃ sudarśanasudarśanam
vidyujjvālāmahākakṣaṃ dahāntar mama yat tamaḥ 078.060
jahi no viṣayagrāhi mano grahaviceṣṭitam
visphoṭayākhilāṃ māyāṃ kuruṣva vimalāṃ matim 078.061
evaṃ saṃsthūyamānaṃ tad vahnipiṇḍopamaṃ mahat
babhūva prakaṭaṃ cakraṃ daityacakrpates tadā 078.062
dadarśa sa mahābāhuḥ prabhāmaṇḍaladurdṛśam
agnijvālāgataṃ tāmraṃ taptacakram ivāparam 078.063
bhramatas tasya cakrasya nābhimadhye mahīpate
trailokyam akhilaṃ daityo dṛṣṭavān bhūrbhuvādikam 078.064
mervādīn akhilāñ śailān gaṅgādyāḥ saritas tathā
kṣīrābdhipramukhāṃś cābdhīn dvīpāñ jambvādisaṃjñitān 078.065
vaimānikān sagandharvān sūryādīṃś ca tathā grahān
nakṣatratārakākāśaṃ śakrādīṃś ca divaukasaḥ 078.066
rudrādityāṃś ca marutāṃ sādhyānāṃ ca mahīpate
saṃnidhānaṃ nirīkṣyāsau daityānāṃ vismito 'bhavat 078.067
tataḥ praṇamyārtiharaṃ surāṇām apārasāraṃ paramāyudhaṃ hareḥ
namo namas te 'stv iti daityarājaḥ provāca bhūyo 'pi namo namas te 078.068
yan no 'śubhaṃ cetasi vāyuvega yan no 'śubhaṃ vāci hutāśanottha
yac cāśubhaṃ kāyakṛtaṃ hares tad varāyudhaṃ tvaṃ praśamaṃ nayāśu 078.069
prasīda satkārakṛtaṃ mamāghaṃ prayātu te nāśam anantavīrya
satāṃ ca sanmārgavatāṃ manāṃsi sthirībhavantv acyutapādayugme 078.070
evaṃ stute tatas tasmin viṣṇucakre sudarśane
puṣpavṛṣṭir baler mūrdhni nipapātāntarikṣataḥ
parihṛtya ca daityendraṃ yayau cakraṃ yathecchayā 079.001
bhramad eva ca daityānāṃ yayau tadbhayam āvahat 079.*(132)
tatas tad adbhutaṃ dṛṣṭvā cakrasyāgamanaṃ hareḥ
pūrvavatsmaraṇaṃ prāpya sasmāra svapitāmaham 079.002
gacchatā pūrvam āryeṇa smartavyo 'ham itīritam
taṃ smariṣyāmi daityendraṃ sa naḥ śreyo 'bhidhāsyati 079.003
ity etad adhisaṃsmṛtya balir ātmapitāmaham
sasmāra daityādhipatiṃ prahrādaṃ bhagavatpriyam 079.004
saṃsmṛtaś ca sa pātālam ājagāma mahāmatiḥ
cakrodyatakaraḥ sākṣād bhagavān iva keśavaḥ 079.005
tam āgatam athotthāya yathāvat sa mahāmatiḥ
abhivādya balir bhaktyā nivedyārgham abhāṣata 079.006
tātāṃhridarśanād adya pāvito 'smy apakalmaṣaḥ
divaś cyuto 'py ahaṃ manye śakrād ātmānam uttamam 079.007
trailokyaharaṇād ugraṃ yad duḥkhaṃ hṛdaye mama
tac chāntaṃ pādasaṃparkam upetya bhavato mama 079.008
iti saṃstūya dattvā ca varāsanam udāradhīḥ
paryupāsata rājendro daityānāṃ svapitāmaham 079.009
tam upāsīnam anaghaḥ prahrādo daityapuṅgavaḥ
pratyuvāca mahātmānaṃ baliṃ vairocaniṃ nṛpa 079.010
bale brūhi yadarthaṃ te smṛto 'ham arisūdana
tavopakāraṇe viddhi dharme māṃ satatodyatam 079.011
tātenāhaṃ purā jñapto bhraṣṭarājyena te bale
saṃsmartavyo 'smy asaṃdigdhaṃ śreyo vakṣyāmy ahaṃ tadā 079.012
so 'haṃ rājyaparibhraṣṭo viṣayāsaktihṛṣitaḥ
indriyair avaśas tāta yat kāryaṃ tat praśādhi mām 079.013
yadi mad-vacanaṃ tāta śraddhadhāsi hitaṃ bale
taṃ devadevam anaghaṃ prayāhi śaraṇaṃ harim 079.014
śabdādiṣv anuraktāni tavākṣāṇy asurādhipa
śabdādayaś ca govinde santy eva vyavahārataḥ 079.015
gītakair gīyatāṃ viṣṇur manohāribhir ātmanaḥ
anyālambanataś cittam ākṛṣyādhatsva keśave 079.016
gandhān udārān bhakṣāṃś ca srajo vāsāṃsi cāsura
prayaccha devadevāya taccheṣāṇy upayuñja ca 079.017
yatra yatra ca te prītir viṣaye ditijeśvara
tat tam acyutam uddiśya viprebhyaḥ pratipādaya 079.018
sarvabhūteṣu govindo bahurūpo vyavasthitaḥ
iti matvā mahābāho sarvabhūtahito bhava 079.019
ātmānam acyutaṃ viddhi śatruṃ ca ripum ātmanaḥ
itijñānavataḥ kopas tava kutra bhaviṣyati 079.020
śabdādayo ye viṣayā viṣayī yaś ca puruṣaḥ
tad aśeṣaṃ vijānīhi svarūpaṃ paramātmanaḥ 079.021
paramātmā ca bhagavān viṣvakseno janārdanaḥ
tadbhaktimān bhāgavato nālpapuṇyo hi jāyate 079.022
bhagavacchāsanālambī bhagavacchāsanapriyaḥ
bhagavadbhaktim āsthāya vatsa bhāgavato bhava 079.023
bhagavān bhūtakṛd bhavyo bhūtānāṃ prabhavo hi yaḥ
bhāvena taṃ bhajasveśaṃ bhavabhaṅgakaraṃ harim 079.024
bhajasva bhāvena vibhuṃ bhagavantaṃ maheśvaram
tato bhāgavato bhūtvā bhavabandhād vimokṣyase 079.025
sarvabhūte manas tasmin samādhāya mahāmate
prāpsyase paramāhlāda- kāriṇīṃ paramāṃ gatim 079.026
yatrānandaparaṃ jñānaṃ sarvaduḥkhavivarjitam 079.*(133)
tatra cittaṃ samāveṣṭuṃ na śaknoti bhavān yadi
tadabhyāsaparas tasmin kuru yogaṃ divāniśam 079.027
tatrāpy asāmarthyavataḥ kriyāyogo mahātmanā
brahmaṇā yaḥ samākhyātas tanmanāḥ satataṃ bhava 079.028
karoṣi yāni karmāṇi tāni deve jagatpatau
samarpayasva bhadraṃ te tataḥ karma prahāsyasi 079.029
kṣīṇakarmā mahābāho śubhāśubhavivarjitaḥ
layam abhyeti govinde tad brahma paramaṃ mahat 079.030
bhoktum icchasi daityendra karmaṇām atha cet phalam
tatas tam arcayeśeśaṃ tataḥ karmaphalodayaḥ 079.031
yo 'rtham icchati daityendra sa samārādhya keśavam
niḥsaṃśayam avāpnoti dhundhumāro yathā nṛpaḥ 079.032
atrigehasamudbhūtaṃ dattātreyasvarūpiṇam
rājyam ārādhya govindaṃ kārtavīryas tathāptavān 079.033
dharmaṃ kṛṣṇaprasādena mudgalo jājaliḥ kuṇiḥ
prāpur anye tathā kāmān narendrā nahuṣādayaḥ 079.034
janakaḥ sudhvajo nāma janakaḥ samitidhvajaḥ
dharmadhvajas tathā muktiṃ keśavārādhanād gataḥ 079.035
tathānye munayo daitya rājānaś ca sahasraśaḥ
prāpur muktiṃ mahābhāgāḥ kṛtvā bhaktiṃ janārdane 079.036
yathā hi jvalito vahnis tamohāniṃ tadarthinām
śītahāniṃ tathānyeṣāṃ svedaṃ svedābhilāṣiṇām 079.037
karoti kṣudhitānāṃ ca bhojyapākaṃ tathotkaṭam
tathaiva kāmān bhūteśaḥ sa dadāti yathepsitān 079.038
tad etad akhilaṃ jñātvā yat taveṣṭaṃ śṛṇuṣva tat
kalpadrumād iva harer yat te manasi vartate 079.039
etat prahrādavacanaṃ niśāmya ditijeśvaraḥ
pratyuvāca mahābhāgaṃ praṇipatya pitāmaham 079.040
saṃprāptasyāmṛtasyeva tava vākyasya nāsti me
tṛptir etad ahaṃ tāta śrotum icchāmi vistarāt 079.041
akṣīṇakarmā puruṣo maraṇe samupasthite
kīdṛśaṃ lokam āyāti yaḥ saṃsmarati keśavam 079.042
yathā ca vāsudevasya smaraṇaṃ tāta mānavaiḥ
mumūrṣubhiḥ prakartavyaṃ tan mamācakṣva vistarāt 079.043
kiṃ japyaṃ kīdṛśaṃ rūpaṃ smartavyaṃ ca hares tadā
kathaṃ dhyeyaṃ ca vidvadbhis tad ācakṣva yathātatham 079.044
sādhu vatsa tvayā praśnaḥ suguhyo 'yam udāhṛtaḥ
tapasāṃ tāta sarveṣāṃ tapo nānaśanāt param 079.045
kathyate ca mahābāho saṃvādo 'yaṃ purātanaḥ
bhagīrathasya rājarṣer brahmaṇaś ca prajāpateḥ 079.046
atītyāmaralokaṃ ca gavāṃ lokaṃ ca mānada
ṛṣilokaṃ ca yo 'gacchad bhagīratha iti śrutaḥ 079.047
taṃ dṛṣṭvā sa vacaḥ prāha brahmā lokapitāmahaḥ
kathaṃ bhagīrathāgās tvam imaṃ deśaṃ durāsadam 079.048
na hi devā na gandharvā na manuṣyā bhagīratha
āyānty ataptatapasaḥ kathaṃ vai tvam ihāgataḥ 079.049
niḥśaṅkam annam adadaṃ brāhmaṇebhyaḥ śataṃ sahasrāṇi sadaiva dāyam
brāhmaṇaṃ vrataṃ nityam āsthāya vidvan na tv evāhaṃ tasya phalād ihāgām 079.050
daśaikarātrān daśa pañcarātrān ekādaśaikādaśakāṃs tathaiva
jyotiṣṭomānāṃ ca śataṃ yad iṣṭaṃ phalena tenāpi na cāgato 'ham 079.051
yac cāvasaṃ jāhnavītīranityaḥ śataṃ samās tapyamānas tapo 'ham
pradāya tatrāśvatarīsahasraṃ phalena tasyāpi na cāgato 'ham 079.052
daśa dhenusahasrāṇi maṇiratnavibhūṣitāḥ
daśārbudāni cāśvānām ayutāni ca viṃśatiḥ
puṣkareṣu dvijātibhyaḥ prādāṃ gāś ca sahasraśaḥ 079.053
suvarṇacandrottamadhāriṇīnāṃ kanyottamānām adadaṃ sragviṇīnām
ṣaṣṭiṃ sahasrāṇi vibhūṣitānāṃ jāmbūnadair ābharaṇair na tena 079.054
daśārbudāny adadaṃ gosave yās tv ekaikaśo daśa gā lokanātha
samānavatsāḥ payasā samanvitāḥ suvarṇakāṃsyopaduhā na tena 079.055
ahany ahani vipreṣu ekaikaṃ triṃśato 'dadam
gṛṣṭīnāṃ kṣīradātrīṇāṃ rohiṇīnāṃ śatāni ca 079.056
dogdhrīṇāṃ vai gavāṃ caiva prayutāni daśaiva tu
prādāṃ daśaguṇaṃ brahman na ca tenāham āgataḥ 079.057
koṭīś ca kāñcanasyāṣṭau prādāṃ brahman daśa tv aham
ekaikasmin kratau tena phalenāhaṃ na cāgataḥ 079.058
vājināṃ śyāmakarṇānāṃ haritānāṃ pitāmaha
prādāṃ hemasrajāṃ brahman koṭīr daśa ca sapta ca 079.059
īṣādantān mahākāyān kāñcanasragvibhūṣitān
patnīvataḥ sahasrāṇi prāyacchaṃ daśa sapta ca 079.060
alaṃkṛtānāṃ deveśa divyaiḥ kanakabhūṣaṇaiḥ
rathānāṃ kāñcanāṅgānāṃ sahasrāṇy adadaṃ daśa
sapta cānyāni yuktānāṃ vājibhiḥ samalaṃkṛtaiḥ 079.061
dakṣiṇāvayavāḥ kecid devair ye saṃprakīrtitāḥ
vājapeyeṣu daśasu prādāṃ tenāpi nāgataḥ 079.062
śakratulyaprabhāvānām ījyayā vikrameṇa ca
sahasraṃ niṣkakaṇṭhānāṃ pradadan dakṣiṇām aham 079.063
vijitya nṛpatīn sarvān makhair iṣṭvā pitāmaha
aṣṭābhyo rājasūyebhyo na ca tenāham āgataḥ 079.064
srotaś ca yāvad gaṅgāyāṃ chinnam āsīj jagatpate
dakṣiṇābhiḥ pravṛttābhir mama nāgaṃ ca tatkṛte 079.065
vājināṃ ca sahasre dve suvarṇamaṇibhūṣite
vāraṇānāṃ śataṃ cāham ekaikasya tridhādadam
varaṃ grāmaśataṃ cāham ekaikasya tridhādadam 079.066
tapasvī niyatāhāraḥ śamam āsthāya vāgyataḥ
dīrghakālaṃ himavati gaṅgāyāś ca durutsahām 079.067
mūrdhnā dhārāṃ mahādevaḥ śirasā yām adhārayat
na tenāpy aham āgacchaṃ phaleneha pitāmaha 079.068
śamyākṣepair ayajaṃ devadeva tathā kratūnām ayutaiś cāpi yattaḥ
trayodaśadvādaśāhaiś ca deva sapuṇḍarīkair na ca teṣāṃ phalena 079.069
aṣṭau sahasrāṇi kakudminām ahaṃ śuklarṣabhāṇām adaṃ brāhmaṇebhyaḥ
patnīś caiṣām adadaṃ niṣkakaṇṭhīs teṣāṃ phaleneha na cāgato 'smi 079.070
hiraṇyaratnaracitān adadaṃ ratnaparvatān
dhanadhānyasahasrāṃś ca grāmāñ śatasahasraśaḥ 079.071
śataṃ śatānāṃ gṛṣṭīnām adadaṃ cāpy atandritaḥ
iṣṭvānekair mahāyajñair brāhmaṇebhyo dhanena ca 079.072
ekādaśāhair ayajaṃ sudakṣiṇair dvir dvādaśāhair aśvamedhaiś ca deva
arkāyaṇaiḥ ṣoḍaśabhiś ca brahmaṃs teṣāṃ phaleneha na cāgato 'smi 079.073
bṛhadbhir dvādaśāhaiś ca aśvamedhaiḥ pitāmaha 079.*(135)
niṣkrāmakaṃ cāpy adadaṃ yojanānāṃ dvir vistīrṇaṃ kāñcanapādapānām
vanaṃ cūtānāṃ ratnavibhūṣitānām na caiva teṣām āgato 'haṃ phalena 079.074
turāyaṇaṃ tu vratam apradhṛṣyam akrodhano 'karavaṃ triṃśato 'bdān
śataṃ gavām aṣṭa śatāni cāhaṃ dine dine prādadaṃ brāhmaṇebhyaḥ 079.075
payasvinīnāṃ atha rohiṇīnāṃ tathaiva cāpy anaḍuhāṃ lokanātha
prādām nityaṃ brāhmaṇebhyaḥ sureśa nehāgatas tena phalena cāham 079.076
triṃśataṃ vidhivad vahnīn ayajaṃ yac ca nityaśaḥ
aṣṭābhiḥ sarvamedhaiś ca nṛmedhair dviguṇais tathā 079.077
daśabhir viśvajidbhiś ca stobhair aṣṭādaśottaraiḥ
na caiva teṣāṃ deveśa phalenāham ihāgamam 079.078
saravyāṃ bāhudāyāṃ ca gayāyām atha naimiṣe
gavāṃ śatānām ayutam adadaṃ na ca tena vai 079.079
utkrāntikāle govindaṃ smarann anaśanasthitaḥ
tyaktavān asmi yad dehaṃ tenedṛk prāptavān phalam 079.080
evam etad itīty āha brahmā lokapitāmahaḥ
bhagīrathaṃ mahīpālaṃ puṇyalokanivāsinam 079.081
tad etad uktaṃ tapasāṃ samastānāṃ mahāmate
guṇair anaśanaṃ brahmā pradhānataram abravīt 079.082
tyajaty anaśanastho hi prāṇān yaḥ saṃsmaran harim
sa yāti viṣṇusālokyaṃ yāvad indrāś caturdaśa 079.083
atītānāgatānīha kulāni puruṣarṣabha
punāty anaśanaṃ kurvan sapta sapta ca sapta ca 079.084
ślokāś cātra mahābāho śrūyante yān bhagīrathaḥ
jagāda brahmaṇo lokam upetaḥ pṛthivīpatiḥ 079.085
brahma brahmamayaṃ viṣṇor yaḥ padaṃ paramātmanaḥ
saṃsmaraṃs tyajati prāṇān sa viṣṇuṃ praviśaty ajam 079.086
yaḥ kṣīṇakarmā bhogena tapasā vāpi saṃsmaran
karoti kālaṃ kālena na paricchedyate hi saḥ 079.087
akṣīṇakarmā maraṇe saṃsmaran devam acyutam
yathā tvam eva devānāṃ loke bhogān upāśnute 079.088
kṣutite 'pi kule kaścij jāyeyaṃ karmaṇaḥ kṣaye
manuṣyo yena sarveśaṃ cintayeyaṃ sadā harim 079.089
taccintayādhunāśeṣa- puṇyapāpavivarjitaḥ
maraṇe tanmanas tatra layam etya tam āpnuyāt 079.090
karmabhūmau samastānāṃ karmaṇām uttamottamam
yad antakāle puruṣaiḥ smaryate puruṣottamaḥ 079.091
ity etān āha rājarṣiḥ ślokān ādyo bhagīrathaḥ
viṣṇusaṃsmaraṇāt prāpya lokān anaśane mṛtaḥ 079.092
evam atyantaśastānāṃ karmaṇām asureśvara
nānyad utkṛṣṭam uddiṣṭaṃ tajjñair anaśanāt param 079.093
tasyāhaṃ lakṣaṇaṃ vakṣye yac ca japyaṃ mumūrṣubhiḥ
yādṛgrūpaś ca bhagavāṃś cintanīyo janārdanaḥ 079.094
āsannam ātmanaḥ kālaṃ jñātvā prājño mahāsura
nirdhūtamaladoṣaś ca snāto niyatamānasaḥ 079.095
samabhyarcya hṛṣīkeśaṃ puṣpadhūpādibhis tataḥ
praṇipātaiḥ stavaiḥ puṇyair dhyānayogaiś ca pūjayet 079.096
dattvā dānaṃ ca viprebhyo vikalādibhya eva ca
sabhāprapābrāhmaṇauka- devaukādyupayogi ca 079.097
bandhuputrakalatrauka- kṣetradhānyadhanādiṣu
mitravarge ca daityendra mamatvaṃ vinivartayet 079.098
mitrān amitrān madhyasthān parān svāṃś ca punaḥ punaḥ
abhyarthanopacāreṇa kṣāmayet kukṛtaṃ svakam 079.099
tataś ca prayataḥ kuryād utsargaṃ sarvakarmaṇām
śubhāśubhānāṃ daityendra vākyaṃ cedam udāharet 079.100
parityajāmy ahaṃ bhogāṃs tyajāmi suhṛdo 'khilān
bhojanādi mayotsṛṣṭam utsṛṣṭam anulepanam 079.101
sragbhūṣaṇādikaṃ geyaṃ dānam ādānam eva ca
homādayaḥ padārthā ye yāś ca nityakriyā mama 079.102
naimittikās tathā kāmyā varṇadharmās tathojjhitāḥ
guṇadharmādayo dharmā yāś ca kāścin mama kriyāḥ 079.103
padbhyāṃ karābhyāṃ viharan kurvan vā karma na tv aham
kariṣye prāṇināṃ pīḍāṃ prāṇinaḥ santu nirbhayāḥ 079.104
nabhasi prāṇino ye tu ye jale ye ca bhūtale
kṣiter antaragā ye ca ye ca pāṣāṇasaṃpuṭe 079.105
ye dhānyādiṣu vastreṣu śayaneṣv āsaneṣu ca
te svapantu vibudhyantu sukhaṃ matto bhayaṃ vinā 079.106
na me 'sti bāndhavaḥ kaścid viṣṇuṃ muktvā jagadgurum
mitrapakṣe ca me viṣṇur adhaś cordhvaṃ tathāgrataḥ 079.107
pārśvato mūrdhni pṛṣṭhe ca hṛdaye vāci cakṣuṣi
śrotrādiṣu ca sarveṣu mama viṣṇuḥ pratiṣṭhitaḥ 079.108
iti sarvaṃ samutsṛjya dhyātvā sarvatra cācyutam
vāsudevety avirataṃ nāma devasya kīrtayan 079.109
dakṣiṇāgreṣu darbheṣu śayīta prācchirās tataḥ
udacchirā vā daityendra cintayañ jagataḥ patim 079.110
viṣṇuṃ jiṣṇuṃ hṛṣīkeśaṃ keśavaṃ madhusūdanam
nārāyaṇaṃ naraṃ kṛṣṇaṃ vāsudevaṃ janārdanam 079.111
vārāhaṃ yajñapuruṣaṃ puṇḍarīkākṣam acyutam
vāmanaṃ śrīdharaṃ śrīśaṃ nṛsiṃham aparājitam 079.112
padmanābham ajaṃ śaurim dāmodaram adhokṣajam
sarveśvareśvaraṃ śuddham anantaṃ rāmam īśvaram 079.113
cakriṇaṃ gadinaṃ śārṅgiṃ śaṅkhinaṃ garuḍadhvajam
kirīṭakaustubhadharaṃ praṇamāmy aham avyayam 079.114
aham atra jagannāthe mayi cāstu janārdanaḥ
āvayor antaraṃ māstu samīranabhasor iva 079.115
ayaṃ viṣṇur ayaṃ śaurir ayaṃ kṛṣṇaḥ puro mama
nīlotpaladalaśyāmaḥ padmapattropamekṣaṇaḥ 079.116
eṣa paśyatu mām īśaḥ paśyāmy aham adhokṣajam
yato na vyatirikto 'haṃ yanmayo 'haṃ yadāśrayaḥ 079.117
itthaṃ japann ekamanāḥ smaran sarveśvaraṃ harim
āsīnaḥ sukhaduḥkheṣu samo mitrāhiteṣu ca 079.118
oṃ namo vāsudevāyety etad vā satataṃ vadan
yad vodīrayituṃ nāma samarthas tad udīrayan
dhyāyeta devadevasya rūpaṃ viṣṇor manoramam 079.119
praśāntanetrabhrūvaktraṃ śaṅkhacakragadādharam
śrīvatsavakṣasaṃ caiva caturbāhuṃ kirīṭinam 079.120
pītāmbaradharaṃ viṣṇuṃ cārukeyūradhāriṇam
cintayec ca tadā rūpaṃ manaḥ kṛtvaikaniścayam 079.121
yādṛśe vā manaḥ sthairyaṃ rūpe badhnāti cakriṇaḥ
tad eva cintayan nāma vāsudeveti kīrtayet 079.122
ittaṃ japan smaran vetthaṃ svarūpaṃ paramātmanaḥ
ā prāṇoparamād vīras taccittas tatparāyaṇaḥ 079.123
nirvikalpena manasā yaḥ smaret puruṣottamam
sarvapātakayukto 'pi puruṣaḥ puruṣarṣabha
prayāti devadeveśe layam īḍyatame 'cyute 079.124
yathāgnis tṛṇajālāni dahaty anilasaṃgataḥ
tathānaśanasaṃkalpaḥ puṃsāṃ pāpam asaṃśayam 079.125
viṣṇoḥ saṃsmaraṇe prāpya lokam anaśane mṛtaḥ
evam atyantaśastānāṃ karmaṇām asureśvara 079.*(136)
nāsti satyāt paro dharmo nāsty adharma tathānṛtāt
nāsti vidyāsamaṃ cakṣus tapo nānaśanāt param 079.126
nāsti jñānasamaṃ dānaṃ na saṃtoṣasamaṃ sukham
na caiverṣyāsamaṃ duḥkhaṃ tapo nānaśanāt param 079.127
nāsty arogasamaṃ dhanyaṃ nāsti gaṅgāsamā sarit
nāsti viṣṇusamaṃ dhyeyaṃ tapo nānaśanāt param 079.128
utkrāntikāle bhūtānāṃ muhyante cittavṛttayaḥ
jarāvyādhividhīnānāṃ kimu vyādhyādidoṣataḥ 079.129
atyantavayasā vṛddhyā vyādhinā cātipīḍitaḥ
yadi sthātuṃ na śaknoti kṣitisthe darbhasaṃstare 079.130
tat kim anyo 'py upāyo 'sti na vānaśanakarmaṇi
viphalyaṃ yena nāpnoti tan me brūhi pitāmaha 079.131
nātra bhūmir na ca kuśāḥ saṃstaraś ca na kāraṇam
cittasyālambanībhūto viṣṇur evātra kāraṇam 079.132
bhuñjann abhuñjan gacchaṃś ca svapaṃs tiṣṭhann athāpi vā
utkrāntikāle govindaṃ saṃsmaraṃs tanmayo bhavet 079.133
kiṃ japaiḥ kiṃ bhuvā kṛtyaṃ kiṃ kuśair daityasattama
tathāpi kurvato yasya hṛdaye na janārdanaḥ 079.134
tasmāt pradhānamantroktaṃ vāsudevasya kīrtanam
tanmayatvena daityendra tasyopāyaś ca vistaraḥ 079.135
ity etat kathitaṃ sarvaṃ pṛṣṭo 'haṃ yat tvayā bale
utkrāntikāle smaraṇaṃ kiṃ bhūyaḥ kathayāmi te 079.136
kriyāyogas tvayā pūrvaṃ mamokto yaḥ pitāmaha
tam ahaṃ śrotum icchāmi phalaṃ cāsya yathātatham 080.001
devārcāṃ devatāgāre tanmayatvena pūjayam
yathāvac cetaso bhūmiṃ karoti niyato hi saḥ 080.002
tapasā brahmacaryeṇa puṇyasvādhyāyasaṃstavaiḥ
kriyāyogaḥ sa vidvadbhir yogināṃ samudāhṛtaḥ 080.003
tatrāhaṃ śrotum icchāmi kriyāyogasthito naraḥ
yat phalaṃ samavāpnoti kārayitvā harer gṛham 080.004
devārcāṃ kārayitvā vā yat puṇyaṃ puruṣo 'śnute
saṃpūjayitvā vidhivad anulipya ca yat phalam 080.005
kāni mālyāni śastāni kāni nārhanti keśave
ke dhūpāḥ kṛṣṇadayitāḥ ke varjyāś ca jagatpateḥ 080.006
upahāre phalaṃ kīm syāt kiṃ phalaṃ gītavādite
ghṛtakṣīrādinā yac ca snāpite keśave phalam 080.007
yac copalepane tāta phalam abhyukṣite ca yat
vāsudevagṛhe sarvaṃ tad aśeṣaṃ vadasva me 080.008
sādhu vatsa yad etat tvaṃ vāsudevasya pṛcchasi
śuśrūṣaṇavidhau puṇyaṃ tad ihaikamanāḥ śṛṇu 080.009
brahmaṇā kila devānām ṛṣīṇāṃ ca mahātmanām
śuśrūṣaṇaphalaṃ viṣṇoḥ proktaṃ daityapate purā 080.010
tebhyaḥ sakāśān manunā prāptaṃ svārociṣeṇa tu
svārociṣaḥ svaputrāya dattavān ṛtacakṣuṣe 080.011
ṛtacakṣuś ca bhargave śukras tasmād avāpa ca
mamākhyātaṃ ca śukreṇa yathāvat sumahātmanā 080.012
śuśrūṣave mahābhāga daityācāryeṇa dhīmatā
tad etac chrūyatāṃ tāta kriyāyogāśritaṃ phalam 080.013
jñānayogas tu saṃyogaś cittasyaivātmanā tu yaḥ
yas tu bāhyārthasāpekṣaḥ sa kriyāyoga ucyate 080.014
paramaṃ kāraṇaṃ yogo vimukter ditikeśvara
kriyāyogaś ca yogasya paramaṃ tāta sādhanam 080.015
yat tv etad bhavatā pṛṣṭaṃ phalam anvicchatā phalam
devālayādikaraṇe tad ihaikamanāḥ śṛṇu 080.016
yas tu devālayaṃ viṣṇor dārvaṃ śailamayaṃ tathā
kārayen mṛnmayaṃ vāpi śṛṇu tasya bale phalaṃ 080.017
ahany ahani yajñena yajato yan mahāphalam
prāpnoti tat phalaṃ viṣṇor yaḥ kārayati mandiram 080.018
kulānāṃ śatam āgāmi samatītaṃ tathā śatam
kārayan bhagavaddhāma nayaty acyutalokatām 080.019
saptajanmakṛtaṃ pāpaṃ svalpaṃ vā yadi vā bahu
viṣṇor ālayavinyāsa- prārambhād eva naśyati 080.020
saptalokamayo viṣṇus tasya yaḥ kurute gṛham
pratiṣṭhāṃ samavāpnoti sa naraḥ saptalaukikīm 080.021
praśastadeśabhūbhāge yaḥ śastaṃ bhavanaṃ hareḥ
kārayaty akṣayāṃl lokān sa naraḥ pratipadyate 080.022
iṣṭakācayavinyāso yāvanty ṛkṣāṇi tiṣṭhati
tāvadvarṣasahasrāṇi tatkartur divi saṃsthitiḥ 080.023
pratimāṃ lakṣaṇavatīṃ yaḥ kārayati mānavaḥ
keśavasya sa tallokam akṣayaṃ pratipadyate 080.024
ṣaṣṭiṃ varṣasahasrāṇāṃ sahasrāṇi sa modate
svargaukasāṃ nivāseṣu pratyekam arisūdana 080.025
pratiṣṭhāpya harer arcāṃ supraśaste niveśane
puruṣaḥ kṛtakṛtyatvān nainaṃ śvomaraṇaṃ tapet 080.026
ye bhaviṣyanti ye 'tītā ākalpāt puruṣāḥ kule
tāṃs tārayati saṃsthāpya devasya pratimāṃ hareḥ 080.027
anuśastāḥ kila purā yamena yamakiṃkarāḥ
pāśodyatāyudhā daitya prajāsaṃyamane ratāḥ 080.028
viharadhvaṃ yathānyāyaṃ niyogo me 'nupālyatām
nājñābhaṅgaṃ kariṣyanti bhavatāṃ jantavaḥ kvacit 080.029
kevalaṃ ye jagaddhātum anantaṃ samupāśritāḥ
bhavadbhiḥ parihartavyās teṣāṃ nāsty atra saṃsthitiḥ 080.030
ye tu bhāgavatā loke taccittās tatparāyaṇāḥ
pūjayanti sadā viṣṇuṃ te vas tyājyāḥ sudūrataḥ 080.031
yas tiṣṭhan prasvapan gacchaṃs tattiṣṭhan skhalite kṣute
saṃkīrtayati govindaṃ te vas tyājyāḥ sudūrataḥ 080.032
nityanaimittikair devaṃ ye yajanti janārdanam
nāvalokya bhavadbhis te tattejo hanti vo gatim 080.033
ye dhūpapuṣpavāsobhir bhūṣaṇaiś cāpi vallabhaiḥ
arcayanti na te grāhyā narāḥ kṛṣṇāśrayoddhatāḥ 080.034
upalepanakartāraḥ saṃmārjanaparāś ca ye
kṛṣṇālaye parityājyaṃ teṣāṃ tripuruṣaṃ kulam 080.035
yena cāyatanaṃ viṣṇoḥ kāritaṃ tatkulodbhavam
puṃsāṃ śataṃ nāvalokyaṃ bhavadbhir duṣṭacakṣuṣā 080.036
yenārcā bhagavadbhaktyā vāsudevasya kāritā
narāyutaṃ tatkulajaṃ bhavatāṃ śāsanātigam 080.037
bhavatāṃ bhramatām atra viṣṇusaṃśrayamudrayā
vinājñābhaṅgakṛn naiva bhaviṣyati naraḥ kvacit 080.038
vatsa vaivasvatasyaitāḥ śrutvā gāthā marīcinā
purukutsāya kathitāḥ pārthivendrāya dhīmate 080.039
etāṃ mahāphalāṃ yo 'rcāṃ viṣṇoh kārayate naraḥ
tavākhyātaṃ mahābāho gṛhakārayituś ca yat 080.040
yajñā narāṇāṃ pāpaugha- kṣālakāḥ sarvakāmadāḥ
tathaivejyo jagaddhātuḥ sarvayajñamayo hariḥ 080.041
sthāpitāṃ pratimāṃ viṣṇoḥ samyak saṃpūjya mānavaḥ
yaṃ yaṃ prārthayate kāmaṃ taṃ tam āpnoty asaṃśayam 081.001
yaḥ snāpayati devasya ghṛtena pratimāṃ hareḥ
prasthe prasthe dvijāgryāṇāṃ sa dadāti gavāṃ śatam 081.002
gavāṃ śatasya viprāṇāṃ yad dattasya bhavet phalam
ghṛtaprasthena tad viṣṇor labhet snānopayoginā 081.003
bhūridyumnena saṃprāptā saptadvīpā vasuṃdharā
ghṛtāḍhakena govinda- pratimāsnāpanāt kila 081.004
pratimāsaṃ sitāṣṭamyāṃ ghṛtena jagataḥ patim
snāpayitvā samastebhyaḥ pāpebhyo vipramucyate 081.005
dvādaśyāṃ pañcadaśyāṃ ca gavyena haviṣā hareḥ
snāpanaṃ daityaśārdūla mahāpātakanāśanam 081.006
jñānato 'jñānato vāpi yat pāpaṃ kurute naraḥ
tat kṣālayati saṃdhyāyāṃ ghṛtena snāpayan harim 081.007
sarvayajñamayo viṣṇur havyānāṃ paramaṃ ghṛtam
tayor aśeṣapāpānāṃ kṣālakaḥ saṃgamo 'sura 081.008
yeṣu kṣīravahā nadyo hradāḥ pāyasakardamāḥ
tāṃl lokān puruṣā yānti kṣīrasnānakarā hareḥ 081.009
āhlādaṃ nirvṛtiṃ svāsthyam ārogyaṃ cārurūpatām
sapta janmāny avāpnoti kṣīrasnānakaro hareḥ 081.010
dadhyādīnāṃ vikārāṇāṃ kṣīrataḥ saṃbhavo yathā
tathaivāśeṣakāmānāṃ kṣīrasnāpanato hareḥ 081.011
yathā ca vimalaṃ jñānaṃ yathā nirvṛtikārakam
tathāsya nirmalaṃ jñānaṃ bhavaty atiphalapradam 081.012
grahānukūlatāṃ puṣṭiṃ priyatvaṃ cākhile jane
karoti bhagavān viṣṇuḥ kṣīrasnāpanatoṣitaḥ 081.013
sarvo 'sya snigdhatām eti dṛṣṭamātraḥ prasīdati
ghṛtakṣīreṇa deveśe snāpite madhusūdane 081.014
atrāpy udāharantīmaṃ saṃvādaṃ keśavāśritam
śāṇḍilyā saha kaikeyyāḥ sumanāyāḥ surālaye 081.015
svarge 'tiśobhanāṃ dṛṣṭvā kaikeyīṃ patinā saha
brāhmaṇī śāṇḍilī nāma paryapṛcchata vismitā 081.016
śataśaḥ santi kaikeyi devāḥ svarganivāsinaḥ
devapatnyas tathaivaitāḥ siddhāḥ siddhāṅganās tathā 081.017
na teṣām īdṛśo gandho na kāntir na surūpatā
na vāsasāṃ ca śobheyaṃ yathā te patinā saha 081.018
naivābharaṇajātāni teṣāṃ bhrājanti vai tathā
yathā tava yathā patyus tava svarganivāsinaḥ 081.019
svasthatā cetasaś ceyaṃ yuvayor atiricyate
śakrādyānām apīsānāṃ kṣayātiśayavarjitaḥ 081.020
tapaḥprabhāvo dānaṃ vā karma vā homasaṃjñitam
yuvayor yan mamācakṣva tat sarvaṃ varavarṇini 081.021
yajñair yajñeśvaro viṣṇur āvābhyāṃ yat tu toṣitaḥ
svargaprāptir iyaṃ tasya karmaṇaḥ phalam uttamam 081.022
surūpatāṃ manaḥprīti paśyatāṃ cāruveṣatām
yat pṛcchasi mahābhāge tad apy eṣā vadāmi te 081.023
tīrthodakais tathā snānaiḥ snāpito 'yaṃ janārdanaḥ
tena kāntir atītyaitān devāṃs tribhuvaneśvarān 081.024
manaḥprasādaḥ saumyatvaṃ śārīrā yā ca nirvṛtiḥ
yat priyatvaṃ ca sarvasya tad ghṛtasnānajaṃ phalam 081.025
yāny abhīṣṭāni vāsāṃsi yac cābhīṣṭaṃ vibhūṣaṇam
ratnāni yāny abhīṣṭāni yat priyaṃ cānulepanam 081.026
ye dhūpā yāni mālyāni dayitāny abhavaṃs tadā
mama bhartus tathaivāsya mama rājyaṃ praśāsataḥ 081.027
tāni sarvāṇi sarvajñe sarvakartari keśave
dattāni tatsamuttho 'yaṃ gandhabhūṣātmako guṇaḥ 081.028
āhārā dayitā ye ca pavitrāś ca niveditāḥ
te lokakartre kṣṛṇāya tṛptis tadguṇasaṃbhavā 081.029
svargakāmena me bhartrā mayā ca śubhadarśane
kṛtam etad ato nābhūd āvayor bhavasaṃkṣayaḥ 081.030
ye tv akāmāṃ narāḥ samyag etat kurvanti śobhane
teṣāṃ dadāti viśveśo bhagavān muktim acyutaḥ 081.031
evam abhyarcya govindaṃ sarvabhūteśvareśvaram
prāpnoty abhimatān kāmān daityāha sumanā yathā 081.032
candanāgarukarpūra- kuṅkumośīrapadmakaiḥ
anulipto harir bhaktyā varān bhogān prayacchati 081.033
kāleyakaṃ tuṅgakaṃ ca padmacandanam eva ca
nR̥ṇāṃ bhavanti rogāya dattāni puruṣottame 081.034
tasmād ebhir na govindaḥ pūjanīyo mahāsura
yāny ātmanaḥ sadeṣṭāni tāni śastāny upākuru 081.035
tathaiva śubhagandhā ye dhūpās te jagataḥ pateḥ
vāsudevasya dharmajñair nivedyā dānaveśvara 081.036
na śallakījaṃ nākṣaulaṃ na śuktāsavasaṃbhṛtam
dadyāt kṛṣṇāya dharmajño dhūpān ārādhanodyataḥ 081.037
mālatī mallikā caiva yūthikāthātimuktakā
pāṭalā karavīraś ca javā pārantir eva ca 081.038
kubjakas tagaraś caiva karṇikāraḥ kuraṇṭakaḥ
campako rotakaḥ kundo bāṇo varvaramālikāḥ 081.039
aśokatilakā rodhrās tathā caivāṭarūṣakaḥ
amī puṣpaprakārās tu śastāḥ keśavapūjane 081.040
bilvapatraṃ śamīpatraṃ patraṃ bhṛṅgārakasya ca
tamālapatraṃ ca bale sadaiva bhagavatpriyam 081.041
tulasīkālatulasī- patraṃ bhṛṅgarajasya ca
ketakīpatrapuṣpaṃ ca sadyas tuṣṭikaraṃ hareḥ 081.042
padmāny ambusamutthānāṃ raktanīle tathotpale
sitotpalaṃ ca kṛṣṇasya dayitāni sadāsura 081.043
nārkaṃ nonmattakaṃ kāṃcit tathaiva girikarṇikām
na kaṇṭakārikāpuṣpam acyutāya nivedayet 081.044
kauṭajaṃ śālmalīpuṣpaṃ śairīṣaṃ ca janārdane
nivedite bhayaṃ rogaṃ niḥsvatāṃ ca prayacchati 081.045
yeṣāṃ na pratiṣedho 'sti gandhavarṇānvitāni ca
tāni puṣpāṇi deyāni viṣṇave prabhaviṣṇave 081.046
sugandhaiś ca surāmāṃsī- karpūrāgarucandanaiḥ
tathānyaiś ca śubhair dravyair arcayej jagataḥ patim 081.047
dukūlapaṭukauśeya- vārkṣakarpāsikādibhiḥ
vāsobhiḥ pūjayed viṣṇuṃ daiteyendrātmanaḥ priyaiḥ 081.048
bhakṣyāṇi yāny abhīṣṭāni bhojyāny abhimatāni ca
phalaṃ ca vallabhaṃ yat syāt tat tad deyaṃ janārdane 081.049
suvarṇamaṇimuktādi yac cānyad ativallabham
tat tad devātidevāya keśavāya nivedayet 081.050
ātmānaṃ keśavaṃ matvā yad yat tasyaiva rocate
tat tad avyaktarūpāya keśavāya nivedayet 081.051
cakravartī mahāvīryo māndhātā yuvanāśvajaḥ
śaśāsa sa mahābāhuḥ saptadvīpāṃ vasuṃdharām 082.001
agāyanta ca yā gāthā ye purāṇavido janāḥ
māndhātari mahābāho yauvanāśve samāśritāḥ 082.002
yāvat sūrya udeti sma yāvac ca pratitiṣṭhati
sarvaṃ tad yauvanāśvasya māndhātuḥ kṣetram ucyate 082.003
sa yauvanagataḥ saṃrāṭ saptadvīpavatīṃ mahīm
śaśāsa dharmeṇa purā cakravartī mahābalaḥ 082.004
nānyāyakṛn na cāśakto na daridro na kīkaṭaḥ
tasyābhūt puruṣo rājye samyagdharmānuśāsinaḥ 082.005
catasro gatayas tasya yauvanāśvasya dhīmataḥ
babhūvur apratihatā hatārātibalasya vai 082.006
tasya bhaktir atīvābhūn nisargād eva bhūpateḥ
vāsudeve jagaddhāmni sarvakāraṇakāraṇe 082.007
tasya rddhiṃ mahimānaṃ ca vilokya pṛthivīpateḥ
na kevalaṃ janasyābhūt tasyāpy atyantavismayaḥ 082.008
sa cintayām āsa nṛpaḥ samṛddhyā vismitas tayā
kathaṃ syāt sampad eṣā me punar apy anyajanmani 082.009
evaṃ subahuśo rājā daityendra sumahābalaḥ
cintayann api tanmūlaṃ na cāsīn niścayānvitaḥ 082.010
yadā na niścayaṃ rājā sa yayau yuvanāśvajaḥ
tadā papraccha dharmajñān sa viprān samupāgatān 082.011
vasiṣṭhapramukhān vatsa viviktāntaḥpurasthitaḥ
praṇipatya mahābāhur gṛhītāsanasatkriyān 082.012
yadi sānugrahā buddhir bhavatāṃ mayi sattamāḥ
tad ahaṃ praṣṭum icchāmi kiṃcit tad vaktum arhatha 082.013
sametyākhilavijñānaṃ samyagdhautāntarātmabhiḥ
bhavadbhir yady ahaṃ na syāṃ vimalas tan mahādbhutam 082.014
yad yathā tan mayā pṛṣṭā bhavanto matprasādhitāḥ
vaktum arhanti vidvāṃsaḥ sarvasyaivopakāriṇaḥ 082.015
yas te manasi saṃdehas taṃ pṛcchādya mahīpate
gadiṣyāmo yathānyāyaṃ yat te sāṃśayikaṃ hṛdi 082.016
vayaṃ hi naraśārdūla bhavatā paritoṣitāḥ
samyak prajāḥ pālayatā saptadvīpe mahītale 082.017
sutuṣṭo brāhmaṇo 'śnīyāc chindyād vā dharmasaṃśayam
hitaṃ vopadiśed dharmam ahitād vā nivartayet 082.018
vivakṣum atha bhūpālaṃ bhāryā tasyaiva dhīmataḥ
praṇāmapūrvam āhedaṃ vinayāt praṇayānvitam 082.019
na strīṇām avanīpāla vaktum īdṛg iheśyate
tathāpi bhūpate vakṣye saṃpad īdṛk sudurlabhā 082.020
bhūyo 'pi saṃśayaṃ praṣṭum alam īśa bhavān ṛṣīn
na tv ahaṃ puruṣavyāghra sadāntaḥpuracāriṇī 082.021
sa prasādaṃ yadi bhavān karoti mama pārthiva
tan madīyam ṛṣīn praṣṭuṃ saṃśayaṃ pārthivārhasi 082.022
brūhi subhru mataṃ yat te praṣṭavyā yan mayā dvijāḥ
bhūyo 'ham ātmasaṃdehaṃ prakṣyāmy etān dvijottamān 082.023
śrūyante pṛthivīpāla nṛpa ye ca purātanāḥ
teṣāṃ na saṃpad bhūpāla yathā tava kilābhavat 082.024
tad īdṛksaṃpadāṃ dhāma tvam aśeṣakṣitīśvaraḥ
yena karmavipākena tad vadantu maharṣayaḥ 082.025
ahaṃ ca bhavato bhāryā sarvasīmantinī bhuvi
vidhinā kena tapasā niyuktā bhavato gṛhe
atīva karmaṇā yena tadvijñāne kutūhalam 082.026
tāratamyatayeśitvam anyeṣv api hi vidyate
nirastātiśayatvena nūnaṃ nālpena karmaṇā 082.027
tad anyajanmacaritaṃ naranātha nijaṃ bhavān
munīn pṛcchatu yā cāhaṃ yan mayā ca purā kṛtam 082.028
sa tathoktas tayā rājā patnyā vismitamānasaḥ
munīnāṃ purato bhāryāṃ praśaṃsan vākyam abravīt 082.029
sādhu devi mataṃ yan me tvayā tad idam īritam
satyaṃ munivacaḥ puṃsām ardhaṃ vai gṛhiṇī yathā 082.030
mamāpy etad abhipretam imān praṣṭuṃ mahāmunīn
yat tvayābhihitaṃ bhadre matsvabhāvānuyātayā 082.031
so 'ham etan mahābhāge prakṣyāmy etān mahāmunīn
naiṣām aviditaṃ kiṃcit triṣu lokeṣu vidyate 082.032
evam uktvā priyāṃ bhāryāṃ praṇipatya ca tān ṛṣīn
yathāvad etad akhilaṃ papracchāsurasattama 082.033
bhagavanto mamāśeṣaṃ prasādāhṛtacetasaḥ
kathayantu yathāvṛttaṃ yan mayā sukṛtaṃ kṛtam 082.034
ko 'ham āsaṃ purā viprāḥ kiṃ ca karma mayā kṛtam
kiṃ vānayā sucārvaṅgyā mama patnyā kṛtaṃ dvijāḥ 082.035
yenāvayor iyaṃ sphītir martyaloke sudurlabhā
catvāraś cāpratihatā gatayo mama gacchataḥ 082.036
aśeṣā bhūbhṛto vaśyāḥ kośasyānto na vidyate
balaṃ caivāpratihataṃ śarīrārogyam uttamam 082.037
atibhāti ca me kāntyā bhāryeyam akhilaṃ jagat
mamāpi vapuṣas tejo na kaścit sahate dvijāḥ 082.038
so 'ham icchāmi vijñātuṃ tathaiveyam aninditā
nijānuṣṭhānam akhilaṃ yasyāśeṣam idaṃ phalam 082.039
iti praṣṭā narendreṇa samastās te tapodhanāḥ
vasiṣṭhaṃ codayām āsuḥ kathyatām iti bhūbhṛtaḥ 082.040
coditaḥ so 'pi dharmajñair maitrāvaruṇir ātmavān
yogam āsthāya suciraṃ yathāvad yatamānasaḥ
jñātavān nṛpates tasya pūrvadehaviceṣṭitam 082.041
sa tam āha munir bhūpaṃ viditārtho mahāsura
māndhātāraṃ mahābuddhiṃ sapatnīkam idaṃ vacaḥ 082.042
śṛṇu bhūpāla sakalaṃ yasyedaṃ karmaṇaḥ phalam
tava rājyādikaṃ subhrūr yeyaṃ cāsīn mahīpate 082.043
tvam āsīḥ śūdrajātīyaḥ parahiṃsāparāyaṇaḥ
vākkrūro daṇḍapāruṣyo niḥsnehaḥ sarvajantuṣu 082.044
tatheyaṃ bhavato bhāryā pūrvam apy āyatekṣaṇā
dveṣyā babhūva taccittā tava śuśrūṣaṇe ratā 082.045
pativratā mahābhāgā bhartsyamānāpy aniṣṭhurā
tvadvākyād anu sarveṣu vīrakarmasu codyatā 082.046
naiṣṭhuryād asahāyasya tyajyamānasya bandhubhiḥ
kṣayaṃ jagāma yo 'rtho 'bhūt saṃcitaḥ prapitāmahaiḥ 082.047
tasmin kṣīṇe kṛṣiparas tvam āsīḥ pṛthivīpate
sāpi karmavipākena kṛṣir viphalatāṃ gatā 082.048
tato niḥsvaṃ parikṣīṇaṃ pareṣāṃ bhṛtyatāṃ gatam
tatyāja sādhvī veyaṃ tvāṃ tyajyamānāpi pārthiva 082.049
anayā ca samaṃ sādhvyā viṣṇor āvasathe tvayā
kṛtaṃ śuśrūṣaṇaṃ vīra parivrāḍbrahmacāriṇām 082.050
bhagnehaḥ sarvakāmebhyas tanmayas tvaṃ tadarpaṇaḥ
ananyagatir ekasthas tasminn āyatane hareḥ 082.051
tadvṛttilipsuḥ śuśrūṣāṃ janarañjanahetukaḥ
kṛtavān yogināṃ vīra kṛṣṇasya jagataḥ pateḥ 082.052
vāsudevājire nityaṃ kṛtaṃ saṃmārjanaṃ tvayā
tathaivābhyukṣaṇaṃ vīra nityaṃ caivānulepanam
patnyānayā ca dharmajña yaṣmaccittānuvṛttayā 082.053
ahany ahani tat karma yuvayor nṛpa kurvatoḥ
tatra caitanmayatvena pāpahānir ajāyata 082.054
viṣṇoḥ kāryaṃ mayā kāryaṃ yogiśuśrūṣaṇaṃ tathā
na prabhātaṃ prabhātaṃ tu cinteyam abhavan niśi 082.055
evam āyatanaṃ ramyam ity evaṃ ca sukhāvaham
sthairyaṃ na caivam etat syād ity āsīt te manaḥ sadā 082.056
yogināṃ sukhadaṃ tv evaṃ karmaivaṃ naivam ity api
tava cittam abhūt tatra yogikarmaṇy aharniśam 082.057
evaṃ tanmanasas tatra kṛtodyogasya pārthiva
bhṛtyāvasāyinaḥ samyag yathoktādhikakāriṇaḥ 082.058
smarataḥ puṇḍarīkākṣaṃ kāryeṇātidṛḍhātmanaḥ
niḥśeṣam upaśāntaṃ tat pāpaṃ yoginiṣevaṇāt 082.059
tato 'dhikaṃ puras tasmād ādarād anulepanam
saṃmārjanaṃ ca bahuśaḥ sapatnikena te kṛtam 082.060
tatrāgataś ca sauvīraḥ purujin nāma bhūpatiḥ
mahāsainyaparīvāraḥ prabhūtagajavāhanaḥ 082.061
sarvasaṃpadupetaṃ taṃ sarvābharaṇabhūṣitam
vṛtaṃ bhāryāsahasreṇa dṛṣṭvā srakcandanojjvalam
spṛhā kṛtā tvayā tatra cārumaulini pārthive 082.062
sarvakāmapradaṃ karma devadevasya kurvatā
tenaitad akhilaṃ rājyam aśeṣadvīpavat tava 082.063
tejaś caivādhikaṃ yat te tathaitac chṛṇu pārthiva
yogaprabhāvopalabdhaṃ kathayāmy akhilaṃ tava 082.064
tatraivāvasathe dīpaḥ praśāntaḥ snehasaṃkṣayāt
nijabhojanatailena punaḥ prajvālitas tvayā 082.065
anayā cottarīyānta- cīravartyupavṛṃhitaḥ
tava patnyā sa jajvāla kāntir asyās tato 'dhikā 082.066
tavāpy akhilabhūpāla- manaḥkṣobhakaraṃ tataḥ
tejo narendra na syāc ca kim ārādhya janārdanam 082.067
evaṃ narendra śūdratvād viṣṇukarmaparāyaṇaḥ
tanmayatvena saṃprāpto mahimānam anuttamam 082.068
kiṃ punar yo naro bhaktyā viṣṇuśuśrūṣaṇādṛtaḥ
karoti satataṃ pūjāṃ niṣkāmo nānyamānasaḥ 082.069
sa tvam ṛddhim imāṃ labdhvā sarvalokeśvareśvaram
pūjayācyutam īśeśaṃ tam ārādhya na sīdati 082.070
puṣpair dhūpais tathā gandhair dīpavastrānulepanaiḥ
ārādhayācyutaṃ tadvad veśmasaṃmārjanādibhiḥ 082.071
yad yad iṣṭatamaṃ kiṃcid yad yad atyantadurlabham
tat tad dāttvā jagaddhātre vaikuṇṭhāya na sīdati 082.072
sugandhāgarukarpūra- candanākṣodakuṃkumaiḥ
vāsobhir vividhair dhūpaiḥ puṣpasragcāmarair dhvajaiḥ 082.073
annopahārair vividhair ghṛtakṣīrābhiṣecanaiḥ
gītavāditanṛtyādyais toṣayasvācyutaṃ nṛpa 082.074
puṇyarātriṣu govindaṃ nṛtyagītaravojjvalaiḥ
bhūpa jāgaraṇair bhaktyā toṣayācyutam avyayam 082.075
evaṃ saṃtoṣyate bhaktyā bhagavān bhavabhaṅgakṛt
bhūpa bhāgavatair bhūta- bhavyakṛt keśavo naraiḥ 082.076
yeṣāṃ na vittaṃ tair bhaktyā mārjanādyupalepanaiḥ
toṣito bhagavān viṣṇur dadāty abhimataṃ phalam 082.077
devakarmāsamarthāṇāṃ prāṇināṃ smṛtisaṃstavaiḥ
toṣito 'bhimatān kāmān prayacchati janārdanaḥ 082.078
naiṣa vittair na ratnaughaiḥ puṣpadhūpānulepanaiḥ
sadbhāvenaiva govindas toṣam āyāti saṃsmṛtaḥ 082.079
tvayaikāgramanaskena gṛhasaṃmārjanādikam
kṛtvālpam īdṛśaṃ prāptaṃ rājyam atyantadurlabham 082.080
prāptopakaraṇo yas tvam ekāgramatir acyutam
toṣayiṣyasi nendro 'pi bhavitā tena te samaḥ 082.081
tasmāt tvam anayā devyā sahātyantavinītayā
keśavārādhane yatnaṃ kuru dharmabhṛtāṃ vara 082.082
tataḥ prāpsyasi bhaktyaiva yat tapobhiḥ sudurlabham 082.*(137)
etan muner vasiṣṭhasya niśāmya vacanaṃ nṛpaḥ
bhāryāsahāyaḥ sa tadā saṃprahṛṣṭatanūruhaḥ 083.001
kṛtakāryam ivātmānaṃ manyamāno 'surottama
uvāca praṇato bhūtvā māndhātā vāruṇiṃ vacaḥ 083.002
yathāmaratvaṃ saṃprāpya yathā vā brahma śāśvatam
paraṃ nirvāṇam āpnoti tathāhaṃ vacasā tava 083.003
kṛtakṛtyaḥ sukhī cāsmi nirvṛtiṃ paramāṃ gataḥ
ajñānatamasāchanne yat pradīpas tvayaidhitaḥ 083.004
aham eṣā ca tanvaṅgī vibhūtibhraṃsabhīrukau
āḍhyāv āpāditau brahmann ihādya vacasā tava 083.005
saṃpadāṃ kathitaṃ bījam āvayor bhavatā mune
taduptāv udyatāv āvāṃ vijānīhi dvijottama 083.006
na ratnair na ca vittaughair na ca puṣpānulepanaiḥ
ārādhyate jagannātho bhāvaśūnyair janārdanaḥ 083.007
bāhyārthanirapekṣaiś ca manasaiva manogatiḥ
niḥsvair ārādhyate devo viṣṇuḥ sarveśvareśvaraḥ 083.008
sarvam etan mayā jñātaṃ yat tvam āttha mahāmune
yat tvāṃ pṛcchāmi tan me tvaṃ prasādasumukho vada 083.009
kāni vratāni yair devo naraiḥ strībhiś ca keśavaḥ
toṣam ārādhito 'bhyeti kaiś ca dānair mahāmune 083.010
rahasyāni ca devasya prītaye yāni cakriṇaḥ
tāny aśeṣāṇi me brūhi kṛṣṇārādhanakāṅkṣiṇaḥ 083.011
śṛṇu bhūpāla yair viṣṇur narair ārādhyate vrataiḥ
nārībhiś cātighore 'smin patitābhir bhavārṇave 083.012
samabhyarcya jagannāthaṃ vāsudevaṃ samādhinā
ekam aśnāti yo bhaktaṃ dvitīyaṃ brāhmaṇātmakam
karoti keśavaprītyai kārttikaṃ māsam ātmavān 083.013
pūrve vayasi yat tena jñānato 'jñānato 'pi vā
pāpam ācaritaṃ tasmān mucyate nātra saṃśayaḥ 083.014
anenaiva vidhānena mārgaśīrṣe 'pi mādhavam
samabhyarcyaikabhaktaṃ vai varṇibhyo yaḥ prayacchati
bhagavatprīṇanārthāya phalaṃ tasya śṛṇuṣva me 083.015
madhye vayasi yat pāpaṃ yoṣitā puruṣeṇa vā
kṛtaṃ tasmāc ca tenokto vimokṣaḥ paramātmanā 083.016
tathā caivaikabhaktaṃ vai varṇāgrebhyaḥ prayacchati
puṇḍarīkākṣam abhyarcya pauṣamāse mahīpate 083.017
tatprīṇanāya yat pāpaṃ vārddhike tena vai kṛtam
sa tasmān mucyate rājan pumān yoṣid athāpi vā 083.018
traimāsikavratam idaṃ yaḥ karoti nareśvara
sa viṣṇuprīṇanāt pāpair laghubhir vipramucyate 083.019
dvitīye vatsare rājan mucyate copapātakaiḥ
tadvat tṛtīye 'pi kṛtaṃ mahāpātakanāśanam 083.020
vratam etan naraiḥ strībhis tribhir māsair anuṣṭhitam
tribhiḥ saṃvatsarair eva pradadāti phalaṃ nṛṇām 083.021
tribhir māsais trir avasthās trividhāt pātakān nṛpa
trīṇi nāmāni devasya mocayanti trivārṣikaiḥ 083.022
yatas tato vratam idaṃ trikramaṃ samudāhṛtam
sarvapāpapraśamanaṃ keśavārādhanaṃ param 083.023
śṛṇuṣva ca mahīpāla vrataṃ viṣṇupadatrayam
sarvapāpapraśamanaṃ yaj jagāda purā hariḥ 084.001
prācetasāya dakṣāya dakṣaś cāha vivasvate
vivasvān alasidhrāya alasidhro 'sitāya ca 084.002
asitena samākhyātam alpāyāsaṃ mahāphalam
tad idaṃ śrūyatāṃ samyag vrataṃ viṣṇupadatrayam 084.003
dakṣaḥ prajāpatiḥ pūrvaṃ viṣṇum ārādhya pṛṣṭavān
bahuśas tu vipannāyāṃ sṛṣṭāv arinisūdana 084.004
bhagavan sarvakaṛtvaṃ mamādiṣṭaṃ svayaṃbhuvā
brahmaṇā devadeveśa tavādeśena keśava 084.005
vipannā ca jagannātha mama sṛṣṭiḥ kṛtā kṛtā
pūrvakarmavipākena vyākulaś cāsmi cetasā 084.006
yathā ca deva mucyeya asmāt saṃsārasaṃkaṭāt
viṣayāsaṅgaviṣamāt tan mamājñāpayācyuta 084.007
ity evam ukto dakṣeṇa devadevo janārdanaḥ
ācaṣṭa duḥkhakṣayadaṃ vrataṃ viṣṇupadatrayam 084.008
sarvārambhaviniṣpatti- kārakaṃ pāpanāśanam
saṃsārocchedakaṃ dhīrair ācīrṇaṃ sthirabuddhibhiḥ 084.009
tad ahaṃ tava rājendra vratānām uttamottamam
kathayāmi samācaṣṭa yathā pūrvaṃ mamāsitaḥ 084.010
āṣāḍhe māsi pūrvāsu tathāṣāḍhāsu pārthiva
samabhyarcya jagannātham acyutaṃ niyataḥ śuciḥ 084.011
puṣpair hṛdyais tathā dhūpair gandhaiḥ sāgarucandanaiḥ
yathāvibhavataś cānyair annair vāsobhir eva ca 084.012
kṣīrasnehasthitaṃ tadvat paiṣṭaṃ viṣṇupadadvayam
samabhyarcya yathānyāyaṃ keśavasyāgrato nyaset 084.013
yavāṃś ca dadyād viprāya bhūgatiḥ prīyatām iti
naktaṃ bhuñjīta rājendra haviṣyānnaṃ susaṃskṛtam 084.014
tathottarāsv āṣāḍhāsu śrāvaṇe māsi mānavaḥ
tathaivābhyarcya govindaṃ tadvad viṣṇupadadvayam 084.015
viprāya ca yavān dadyāt prīṇayitvā ca bhūgatim
naktaṃ bhūñjīta rājendra naro yoṣid athāpi vā 084.016
prāpte bhādrapade māsi pūrvabhadrapadāsu ca
tathaivābhyarcya govindaṃ tadvad viṣṇupadadvayam 084.017
viprāya ca yavān dattvā prīṇayitvā bhuvogatim
bhuñjīta gorasaprāyaṃ naro yoṣid athāpi vā 084.018
tadvad āśvayuje dānaṃ tadvad govindapūjanam
padadvayasya pūjāṃ ca prīṇanaṃ ca bhuvogateḥ 084.019
tathaiva naktaṃ bhuñjīta gorasaṃ maunam āsthitaḥ
strī vā rājendra pūrvāsu tathā bhadrapadāsu vai 084.020
phālgune phalgunī pūrvā bhavatī ha yadā nṛpa
trivikramaṃ tadā devaṃ pūrvoktavidhinārcayet 084.021
padadvayaṃ ca devasya samyag abhyarcya pārthiva
hiraṇyaṃ dakṣiṇāṃ dattvā svargatiḥ prīyatām iti 084.022
naktaṃ bhuñjīta rājendra vahnipākavivarjitam
eṣa evottarāyoge caitre māse vidhiḥ smṛtaḥ 084.023
etaj jagāda govindaḥ purā dakṣāya pṛcchate
sarvapāpaharaṃ puṇyaṃ vrataṃ viṣṇupadatrayam 084.024
yathoktam etad yo bhakto karoti nṛpasattama
sarvakāmān avāpnoti keśavasya vaco yathā 084.025
aputro labhate putram apatir labhate patim
samāgamaṃ proṣitaiś ca tathā prāpnoti bāndhavaiḥ 084.026
dravyam aiśvaryam ārogyaṃ saubhāgyaṃ cārurūpatām
prāpnuvanty akhilān etān pūjayitvā padatrayam 084.027
yān yān kāmān naraḥ strī vā hṛdayenābhivāñchanti
tāṃs tāṃś cāpnoti niṣkāmo viṣṇulokaṃ ca gacchati 084.028
pūrvaṃ kṛtvāpi pāpāni naraḥ strī vā narādhipa
padatrayavrataṃ cīrtvā mucyate sarvakilbiṣaiḥ 084.029
viṣṇor ārādhanārthāya yāni dānāni sattama
deyāni tāny aśeṣāṇi mamācakṣva dvijottama 085.001
yena caiva vidhānena dānaṃ puṃsaḥ sukhāvaham
prīṇanāya ca kṛṣṇasya tan mamākhyāhi vistarāt 085.002
kṛtopavāsaḥ saṃprāśya pañcagavyaṃ nareśvara
ghṛtakṣīrābhiṣekaṃ ca kṛtvā viṣṇoḥ samāhitaḥ 085.003
samabhyarcya ca govindaṃ puṣpādibhir ariṃdama
udaṅmukhīm arcayitvā tathā gṛṣṭiṃ payasvinīm 085.004
saputrāṃ vastrasaṃvītāṃ sitayajñopavītinīm
svarṇaśṛṅgīṃ śubhākārāṃ hiraṇyoparisaṃsthitām 085.005
hiraṇyaṃ vācayitvāgre brāhmaṇāyopapādayet
imāṃ tvaṃ pratigṛhṇīṣva govindaḥ prīyatām iti 085.006
samyag uccārya taṃ vipraṃ govindaṃ nṛpa kalpayet
anuvrajec ca gacchantaṃ padāny aṣṭau narādhipa 085.007
anena vidhinā dhenuṃ yo viprāya prayacchati
govindaprīṇanād rājan viṣṇulokaṃ ca gacchati 085.008
saptāvarāṃs tathā pūrvān saptātmānaṃ ca mānavaḥ
saptajanmakṛtāt pāpān mocayaty avanīpate 085.009
pade pade ca yajñasya gosavasya sa mānavaḥ
phalam āpnoti rājendra dakṣāyaivaṃ jagau hariḥ 085.010
sarvakāmasamṛddhasya sarvakāleṣu pārthiva
bhavaty aghaughāpaharā yāvad indrāś caturdaśa 085.011
sarveṣām eva pāpānāṃ kṛtānām avijānatā
prāyaścittam idaṃ śastam anutāpopavṛṃhitam 085.012
ikṣvākunaiṣā rājendra pūrvaṃ dattā mahātmanā
tataḥ sa lokān amalān prāptavān avanīpatiḥ 085.013
tathaivānyair mahīpālair dvijavaiśyādibhis tathā
lokāḥ kāmadughāḥ prāptā dattvedṛgvidhinā nṛpa 085.014
tiladhenuṃ pravakṣyāmi keśavaprīṇanāya yā
dattā bhavati yaś cāsyā narendra vidhir uttamaḥ 086.001
phalam āpnoti rājendra tadvad vā vidhivat tadā 086.*(139)
yāṃ dattvā brahmahā goghnaḥ pitṛghno gurutalpagaḥ
āgāradāhī garadaḥ sarvapāparato 'pi vā 086.002
mahāpātakayukto yo yukto yaś copapātakaiḥ
sa mucyate 'khilaiḥ pāpair viṣṇulokaṃ sa gacchati 086.003
svanulipte mahīpṛṣṭe vastrājinasamāvṛte
dhenuṃ tilamayīṃ kṛtvā sarvaratnaiḥ samanvitām 086.004
suvarṇaśṛṅgīṃ raupyakhurāṃ gandhaghrāṇavatīṃ śubhām
mṛṣṭānnajihvāṃ kurvīta guḍāsyāṃ sūtrakambalām 086.005
ikṣupādāṃ tāmrapṛṣṭhāṃ kuryān muktāphalekṣaṇām
praśastapatraśravaṇāṃ phaladantavatīṃ śubhām 086.006
sragdāmapucchāṃ kurvīta navanītastanānvitām
phalair manoharair bhakṣair maṇimuktāphalānvitām
tiladroṇena kurvīta āḍhakena tu vatsakam 086.007
śubhavastrayugacchannāṃ cārucchattrasamanvitām
īdṛksaṃsthānasaṃpannāṃ kṛtvā śrāddhasamanvitaḥ
kāṃsyopadohanāṃ dadyāt keśavaḥ prīyatām iti 086.008
samyag uccārya vidhinā dattvaitena narādhipa
sarvapāpavinirmuktaḥ pitaraṃ sapitāmaham 086.009
prapitāmahaṃ tathā pūrvaṃ puruṣāṇāṃ catuṣṭayam
ātmānaṃ tanayaṃ pautraṃ tadadhas tu catuṣṭayam
tārayaty avanīpāla tiladhenuprado naraḥ 086.010
yaś ca gṛhṇāti vidhivat tasyāpy evaṃvidhān kulān
caturdaśa tathā caiva dadataś cānumodakāḥ 086.011
dīyamānāṃ prapaśyanti tiladhenuṃ ca ye narāḥ
te 'py aśeṣāghanirmuktāḥ prayānti paramāṃ gatim 086.012
praśāntāya suśīlāya tathāmatsariṇe budhaḥ
tiladhenuṃ naro dadyād vedasnātāya dharmiṇe 086.013
trirātraṃ yas tilāhāras tiladhenuṃ prayacchati
dattvaikarātraṃ ca punas tilān atti nareśvara 086.014
dātur viśuddhapāpasya tasya puṇyavato nṛpa
cāndrāyaṇād abhyadhikaṃ śastaṃ tat tilabhakṣaṇam 086.015
tilābhāve tathā dadyād ghṛtadhenuṃ yatavrataḥ
kalpayitvā yathānyāyaṃ tiladhenvā yatavrataḥ
yena bhūpa vidhānena tad ihaikamanāḥ śṛṇu 087.001
vāsudevaṃ jagannāthaṃ puruṣeśam ajaṃ vidhum
sarvapāpanihantāraṃ ghṛtakṣīrābhiṣecanāt
saṃpūjya pūrvavat puṣpa- gandhadhūpādibhir naraḥ 087.002
ahorātroṣito bhūtvā tatparaḥ prayataḥ śuciḥ
parameśam atho nāmnā abhiṣṭūya ghṛtārciṣā 087.003
gavyasya sarpiṣaḥ kumbhaṃ puṣpamālyādibhūṣitam
kāṃsyopadhānasaṃyuktaṃ sitavastrayugena ca
hiraṇyagarbhasahitaṃ maṇividrumamuktikaiḥ 087.004
ikṣuyaṣṭimayān pādān khurān raupyamayāṃs tathā
sauvarṇe cākṣiṇī kuryāc śṛṅge cāgarukāṣṭhaje 087.005
saptadhānyamaye pārśve pattrorṇāni ca kambalam
kuryāt turuṣkakarpūrau ghrāṇaṃ phalamayān stanān 087.006
maṇiratnasuvarṇānāṃ samyakkalpanayā kṛtām 087.*(140)
tadvac charkarayā jihvāṃ guḍakṣīramayaṃ mukham
kṣaumasūtreṇa lāṅgūlaṃ romāṇi sitasarṣapaiḥ
tāmrapātramayaṃ pṛṣṭhaṃ kuryāc chraddhāsamanvitaḥ 087.007
īdṛksvarūpāṃ saṃkalpya ghṛtadhenuṃ narādhipa
tadvatkalpanayā dhenvā ghṛtavatsaṃ prakalpayet 087.008
taṃ ca vipraṃ mahābhāga manasaiva ghṛtārciṣam
kalpayitvā tatas tasmai prayataḥ pratipādayet 087.009
etāṃ mamopakārāya ghṛhṇīṣva tvaṃ dvijottama
prīyatāṃ mama deveśo ghṛtāṛciḥ puruṣottamaḥ
ity udāhṛtya viprāya dadyād dhenuṃ narottama 087.010
maṇimuktāsuvarṇānāṃ samyakkalpanayā kṛtām 087.*(141)
dattvaikarātraṃ sthitvā ca ghṛtāhāro narādhipa
mucyate sarvapāpebhyas tathā dānaphalaṃ śṛṇu 087.011
ghṛtakṣīravahā nadyo yatra pāyasakardamāḥ
teṣu lokeṣu lokeśa sa puṇyeṣūpajāyate 087.012
pitur ūrdhvena ye sapta puruṣāḥ sapta ye 'py adhaḥ
tāṃs teṣu nṛpa lokeṣu sa nayaty astakalmaṣaḥ 087.013
sakāmānām iyaṃ vyuṣṭiḥ kathitā nṛpasattama
viṣṇulokaṃ narā yānti niṣkāmā ghṛtadhenudāḥ 087.014
ghṛtam agnir ghṛtaṃ somas tanmayāḥ sarvadevatāḥ
ghṛtaṃ prayacchatā dattā bhavanty akhiladevatāḥ 087.015
jaladhenuṃ pravakṣyāmi prīyate dattayā yayā
devadevo hṛṣīkeśaḥ sarveśaḥ sarvabhāvanaḥ 088.001
jalakumbhaṃ naravyāghra suvarṇarajatānvitam
ratnagarbham aśeṣais tu grāmyair dhānyaiḥ samanvitam 088.002
sitavastrayugacchannaṃ dūrvāpallavaśobhitam
kuṣṭhaṃ māṃsīm uśīraṃ ca vālakāmalakair yutam 088.003
priyaṅgupātrasahitaṃ sitayajñopavītinam
sacchattraṃ saupānatkaṃ darbhavistarasaṃsthitam 088.004
caturbhiḥ saṃvṛtaṃ bhūpa tilapātraiś caturdiśam
sthagitaṃ dadhipātreṇa ghṛtakṣaudravatā mukhe 088.005
upoṣitaḥ samabhyarcya vāsudevaṃ janeśvaram
puṣpadhūpopahārais tu yathāvibhavam ādṛtaḥ 088.006
saṃkalpya jaladhenuṃ ca kumbhaṃ samabhipūjya ca
pūjayed vatsakaṃ tadvat kṛtaṃ jalamayaṃ budhaḥ 088.007
evaṃ saṃpūjya govindaṃ jaladhenuṃ savatsakām
sitavastradharaḥ śānto vītarāgo vimatsaraḥ 088.008
dadyād viprāya rājendra prītyarthaṃ jalaśāyinaḥ
jalaśāyī jagadyoniḥ prīyatāṃ mama keśavaḥ 088.009
iti coccārya bhūnātha viprāya pratipādyatām
apakvānnāśinā stheyam ahorātram ataḥparam 088.010
anena vidhinā dattvā jaladhenuṃ janādhipa
sarvāhlādān avāpnoti ye divyā ye ca mānuṣāḥ 088.011
śarīrārogyam ābādhā- praśamaḥ sārvakāmikaḥ
nṛṇāṃ bhavati dattāyāṃ jaladhenvāṃ na saṃśayaḥ 088.012
atrāpi śrūyate bhūpa pudgalena mahātmanā
jātismareṇa yad gītam ihābhyetya purā kila 088.013
sa pudgalaḥ purā vipro yamalokagato muniḥ
dadarśa yātanā ghorāḥ pāpakarmakṛtāṃ kila 088.014
dīptāgnitīkṣṇaśastrotthāḥ kvāthatailagatās tathā
uṣṇakṣāranadīpātā bhairavāḥ puruṣarṣabha 088.015
vraṇāḥ kṣāranipātogrāḥ kumbhīpākamahābhayāḥ
tā dṛṣṭvā yātanā vipraś cakāra paramāṃ kṛpām 088.016
āhlādaṃ te tadā jagmuḥ pāpās tadanukampitāḥ
taṃ dṛṣṭvā nārakāḥ kecit kecit tadavalokinaḥ 088.017
tadā svasthaṃ vilokyaiva munir nārakamaṇḍalam
dharmarājaṃ sa papraccha teṣāṃ praśamakāraṇam 088.018
tasmai cācaṣṭa rājendra tadā vaivasvato yamaḥ
āhlādahetuṃ viprāya pṛcchate pṛthivīpate 088.019
tavānubhāvād eteṣāṃ nārakāṇāṃ dvijottam
saṃpravṛtto 'yam āhlādaḥ kāraṇaṃ yac chṛṇuṣva tat 088.020
tvayābhyarcya jagannāthaṃ sarveśaṃ jalaśāyinam
jaladhenuḥ purā dattā vidhivan munipuṅgava 088.021
asmāt tu janmano 'tīte tṛtīye dvija janmani
tasya dānasya te vyuṣṭir iyam āhlādadāyinī 088.022
yena tvaṃ tapasā yukto mānavānām agocaram
saṃprāpto 'si mahāprajña sarvaśāstraviśārada 088.023
ye tvāṃ paśyanti śṛṇvanti ye ca dhyāyanti pāpinaḥ
śṛṇoṣi yāṃs tvaṃ viprendra yāṃś ca dhyāyasi paśyasi 088.024
nirvṛtiḥ paramā teṣāṃ sarvāhlādapradāyinī
sadyo bhavati mātra tvaṃ dvijendra kuru vismayam 088.025
āhlādahetujananaṃ nāsti viprendra tādṛśam
jaladhenur yathā nR̥ṇāṃ janmāny ekonasaptatiḥ 088.026
na dāgho na klamo nārtir na moho vipra jāyate
api janmasahasreṣu jaladhenupradāyinām 088.027
ekajanmakṛtaṃ vāñchā trijanmotthaṃ samāhṛtā
saptajanmakṛtaṃ pāpaṃ hanti dattāmbugaur nṛṇām 088.028
sa tvaṃ gaccha gṛhītvārgham asmatto dvijasattama
yeṣāṃ samāśrayaḥ kṛṣṇo na niyamyā hi te mayā 088.029
kṛṣṇaḥ saṃpūjito yais tu ye kṛṣṇārtham upoṣitāḥ
yaiś ca nityaṃ smṛtaḥ kṛṣṇo na te madviṣayopagāḥ 088.030
namaḥ kṛṣṇācyutānanta vāsudevety udīritam
yair bhāvabhāvitair vipra na te madviṣayopagāḥ 088.031
dānaṃ dadadbhir yair uktam acyutaḥ prīyatām iti
śraddhāpuraḥsarair vipra na te madviṣayopagāḥ 088.032
uttiṣṭhadbhiḥ svapadbhiś ca vrajadbhiś ca janārdanaḥ
yaiḥ saṃsmṛto dvijaśreṣṭha na te madviṣayopagāḥ 088.033
kṣutaskhalitabhītyādāv asahadbhiś ca vedanām
kṛṣṇety udīritaṃ yaiś ca na te madviṣayopagāḥ 088.034
sarvābādhāsu ye kṛṣṇaṃ smaranty uccārayanti ca
tadbhāvabhāvitā vipra na te madviṣayopagāḥ 088.035
sa eva dhātā sarvasya tanniyogakarā vayam
janasaṃyamanodyuktāḥ so 'smatsaṃyamano hariḥ 088.036
itthaṃ niśāmya vacanaṃ yamasya vadato munim
ūcus te nārakāḥ sarve vahniśastrāstrabhīravaḥ 088.037
namaḥ kṛṣṇāya haraye viṣṇave jiṣṇave namaḥ
hṛṣīkeśāya devāya jagaddhātre 'cyutāya ca 088.038
namaḥ paṅkajanetrāya namaḥ paṅkajanābhaye
janārdanāya śrīśāya śrīpate pītavāsase 088.039
govindāya namo nityaṃ namaś codadhiśāyine
namaḥ karālavaktrāya nṛsiṃhāyātinādine 088.040
śārṅgiṇe sitakhaḍgāya śaṅkhacakragadādhṛte
namo vāmanarūpāya krāntalokatrayāya ca 088.041
varāharūpāya tathā namo yajñāṅgadhāriṇe
vyāptāśeṣadigantāya śāntāya paramātmane 088.042
vāsudeva namas tubhyaṃ namaḥ kaiṭabhasūdana
keśavāya namo vyāpin namas te 'stu mahīdhara 088.043
namo 'stu vāsudevāyety evam uccārite tataḥ
śastrāṇi kuṇṭhatāṃ jagmur analaś cāpy aśīśamat 088.044
abhajyanta ca yantrāṇi samutpetur ayomukhāḥ
saṃśuṣkāḥ kṣārasaritaḥ patitaḥ kūṭaśālmaliḥ 088.045
prakāśatāmasītattvaṃ narakaś cāgatas tu saḥ
vivān babhañja pavano 'py asipatravanaṃ tataḥ 088.046
nirutsāhā jaḍadhiyo babhūvur yamakiṃkarāḥ
āsan gandhāmbuvāhinyaḥ pūyaśoṇitanimnagāḥ 088.047
vavau sugandhī pavano manaḥprītikaras tataḥ
veṇuvīṇāsvanayutān gītaśabdāṃś ca śuśruvuḥ 088.048
taṃ tādṛśam athālakṣya nṛpa vaivasvato yamaḥ
narakasya viparyāsaṃ saṃkṣuddhahṛdayas tataḥ 088.049
dadarśa nārakān sadyo divyasraganulepanān
jājvalyamānāṃs tejobhir amalāmbaravāsasaḥ 088.050
namo namo 'stu kṛṣṇāya govindāyāvyayātmane
vāsudevāya devāya viṣṇave prabhaviṣṇave 088.051
ity evaṃ vādinas tatra prajāsaṃyamano yamaḥ
kṣīṇapāpacayāṃs tāṃs tu pādyārghyādibhir arcayan 088.052
pūjayitvā ca tān āha sa kṛṣṇāya kṛtāñjaliḥ
samāhitamanā bhūtvā dharmarājo nareśvara 088.053
viṣṇor devātidevasya jagaddhātuḥ prajāpateḥ
praṇāmaṃ ye 'pi kurvanti teṣām api namo namaḥ 088.054
sarvasya sarvasaṃsthasya sarvādhārasya yoginaḥ
ye viṣṇoḥ praṇatās tebhyo namaḥ sadyaḥ punaḥ punaḥ 088.055
tasya yajñavarāhasya viṣṇor amitatejasaḥ
praṇāmaṃ ye 'pi kurvanti teṣām api namo namaḥ 088.056
evaṃ te saṃstutās tena dharmarājena nārakāḥ
vimānāni samārūḍhā nṛttagāndharvavanti vai 088.057
pudgalo 'pi mahābuddhir dṛṣṭvaitad akhilaṃ nṛpa
jātismaro 'bhavad bhūpa kaṇvagotre mahāmuniḥ 088.058
saṃsmṛtya yamavākyāni viṣṇor māhātmyam eva ca
jaladhenvāś ca māhātmyaṃ saṃsmṛtyaitad agāyata 088.059
aho duruttarā viṣṇor māyeyam atigahvarī
yayā mohitacittas taṃ na vetti parameśvaram 088.060
jīvo vāñchati kīṭatvaṃ yūkāmatkuṇayonitaḥ
tasmāc ca śalabhādīnāṃ yoniṃ tasmāc ca pakṣiṇām 088.061
tataś ca paśutāṃ prāpya naratvam abhivāñchati
vimuktihetukī dhanyā narayoniḥ kṛtātmanām 088.062
na prāpnuvanti saṃsāre vibhrāntamanaso gatim
jīvā mānuṣyatām anye janmanām ayutair api 088.063
viṣṇumāyāparītās te prāpyāpi na taranti ye 088.*(142)
tad īdṛgdurlabhaṃ prāpya muktidvāram acetasaḥ
patanti bhūyaḥ saṃsāre viṣṇumāyāvimohitāḥ 088.064
dustarāpi tu sādhyāsau māyā kṛṣṇasya mohanī
chidyate yāmanonyaste mudhaiva hi janārdane 088.065
asaṃtyajya ca gārhasthyam ataptvaiva tathā tapaḥ
chindanti vaiṣṇavīṃ māyāṃ keśavārpitamānasāḥ 088.066
avirodhena viṣayām bhuñjan viṣṇuvyapāśrayaḥ
kṛtvā manas taraty etāṃ viṣṇor māyāṃ sudustarām 088.067
īdṛgbahuphalāṃ bhaktiṃ sarvadhātari keśave
māyayā tasya devasya na kurvanti vimohitāḥ 088.068
mudhaivoktaṃ mudhāyātaṃ mudhā tad vidhiceṣṭitam
mudhaiva janma tan naṣṭaṃ yatra nārādhito hariḥ 088.069
ārādhito hi yaḥ puṃsām aihikāmuṣmikaṃ phalam
dadāti bhagavān devaḥ kas taṃ na pratipūjayet 088.070
saṃvatsarās tathā māsā viphalā divasāś ca te
narāṇāṃ viṣayāndhānāṃ yeṣu nārādhito hariḥ 088.071
yo na vittarddhivibhavair na vasobhir na bhūṣaṇaiḥ
tuṣyate hṛdayenaiva kas tam īśaṃ na pūjayet 088.072
jaladhenvāś ca māhātmyaṃ niśāmyāpīdṛśaṃ narāḥ
tāṃ na yacchanti ye teṣāṃ vivekaḥ kutra tiṣṭhati 088.073
karmabhūmau hi mānuṣyaṃ janmanām ayutair api
svargāpavargaphaladaṃ kadācit prāpyate naraiḥ 088.074
saṃprāpya tan na yair viṣṇus toṣito nāmbudhenukā
dattā ca samyak te muṣṭā janmani subahūni bhoḥ 088.075
ūrdhvabāhur viraumy eṣa dṛṣṭalokadvayo 'smi bhoḥ
ārādhayata govindaṃ jaladhenuṃ prayacchata 088.076
duḥsaho nārako vahnir aviṣahyāś ca yātanāḥ
jñānaṃ mamaitad ālambya kṛṣṇe bhavata susthirāḥ 088.077
adeśike deśiko 'ham atra mārge mayoditam
vimṛṣya satyam ity etan manaḥ kṛṣṇe niveśyatām 088.078
prātaḥ kṛṣṇeti deveti govindeti ca jalpatām
madhyāhne cāparāhne ca yo 'vasādaḥ sa ucyatām 088.079
anekaviṣayālambi yac cittaṃ taj janārdane
kurudhvam ālambanavat saṃsmṛtaḥ puṇyado hi saḥ 088.080
mudhaiva jihvā kṛṣṇeti keśaveti ca vakṣyati
mudhā ca cittaṃ tadgāmi yadi syāt kim ato 'dhikam 088.081
mayoktam etad bahuśo vinaṣṭe tu śarīrake
manuṣyatvaṃ vinā viṣṇur durlabho vo bhaviṣyati 088.082
etāḥ pudgalagāthās te yamavākyaṃ tavoditam
jaladhenvāś ca māhātmyaṃ viṣṇusaṃpūjanasya ca 088.083
vratāni sopavāsāni sarvakāmapradāni te
vratam anyan mahābhāga sarvakāmapradaṃ śṛṇu 088.084
bhaviṣyaṃ cāparaṃ bhūpa mamaitac chrotum arhasi
yat prakṣyati mahīpālaḥ parikṣit svapurohitam 089.001
parīkṣitaḥ purodhās tu dvijo gauramukho nṛpa
bhaviṣyati śamīkasya śiṣyaḥ paramasaṃmataḥ 089.002
sa ca rājā jagaddhātur devadevasya śārṅginaḥ
sadaivārādhane yatnaṃ bhaktiyuktaḥ kariṣyati 089.003
purodhasaṃ gauramukhaṃ praṇipatya sa pārthivaḥ
prakṣyaty ārādhanārthāya devadevasya cakriṇaḥ 089.004
bhagavan bhavabhīto 'ham abhavāya tato bhavān
ārādhayitum icchāmi sarvecchāpūrakaṃ hariṃ 089.005
saṃkuruṣva mahābhāga prasādaṃ mama suvrata
kṛṣṇārādhanakāmasya manaso deśiko bhava 089.006
ārādhanena yeneśo jagatām īśvareśvaraḥ
viṣṇur ārādhyate puṃbhiḥ saṃsārābdhiparikṣataiḥ 089.007
tan mamopadiśa brahman prasādapravaṇaṃ manaḥ
kṛtvā sadaivārtimatāṃ śaraṇyaṃ śaraṇaṃ guruḥ 089.008
evaṃ sa tena bhūpāla bhūpālena rṣipuṅgavaḥ
keśavārādhanārthāya samyak pṛṣṭaḥ pravakṣyati 089.009
namaskṛtya jagaddhātre devadevāya śārṅgine
parameśasureśāya hṛṣīkeśāya vedhase 089.010
varārthinām amoghāya parasmai harimedhase
sarvakalyāṇabhūtāya śaṅkhacakragadādhṛte 089.011
varāsicarmāvitate krūraśāntātmamūrtaye
yadyadbhūtopakārāya tattadrūpavikāriṇe 089.012
paramāṇvantaparyanta- sahasrāṃśāṇumūrtaye
jaṭharāntāyutāśānta- sthitabrahmāṇḍadhāriṇe 089.013
śvetādidīrghahrasvādi- kaṭhinādivikalpanā
yogicintye jagaddhāmni yatra nāsty akhilātmani 089.014
tam ajaṃ śāśvataṃ nityaṃ pariṇāmavivarjitam
yogibhiś cintyate mūrtir yatra tatrākhilātmani 089.015
tatra tatrātmano nityaṃ pariṇāmavivarjitam
praṇamya jagatām īśam anantaṃ parataḥ param 089.016
paraṃ parāṇāṃ sraṣṭāraṃ purāṇaṃ puruṣaṃ prabhum
varaṃ vareṇyaṃ varadaṃ sthūlasūkṣmasvarūpiṇam 089.017
aśeṣajagatāṃ mūlam anādinidhanasthitim
parāparasvarūpastham avikārasvarūpiṇam 089.018
yasyopacārataḥ svargaṃ svarūpaṃ vyatiricyate
jñānajñeyasya munibhir jñānavidbhir mahātmabhiḥ 089.019
tasmai pārthivamukhyāya raghuvaryamahātmane
śrūyatāṃ sa muniśreṣṭho yad vakṣyati parīkṣite 089.020
devakī nāma rājendra devakasyābhavat sutā
anapatyā tapas tepe putrārthaṃ kila bhāminī 089.021
bhāryā sā vasudevasya satyadharmaparāyaṇā
na cātuṣyata govindas tatas tām āha bhārgavaḥ 089.022
kimarthaṃ tapyate bhadre tapaḥ paramaduścaram
ko 'rthas tavābhilaṣito gantuṃ kutra tavepsitam 089.023
aputrāhaṃ dvijaśreṣṭha patyur me nāsti saṃtatiḥ
sāham ārādhya govindaṃ putram icchāmi śobhanam 089.024
tapas tāvat kariṣyāmi parameṇa samādhinā
yāvad ārādhito viṣṇur dāsyaty abhimataṃ mama 089.025
govindārādhane yatno yadi te kulanandini
tad idaṃ vratam āsthāya toṣayāśu janārdanam 089.026
prathame kārttikasyāhni saṃprāpte devakātmaje
pañcagavyajalasnātaḥ pañcagavyakṛtāśanaḥ 089.027
bāṇapuṣpaiḥ samabhyarcya vāsudevam ajaṃ vibhum
dattvā ca candanaṃ dhūpaṃ paramānnaṃ nivedayet
ghṛtena vācayed vipraṃ gṛhṇīyāc ca tato vratam 089.028
adyaprabhṛty ahaṃ māsaṃ virataḥ prāṇināṃ vadhāt
asatyavacanāt stainyān madhumāṃsādibhakṣaṇāt 089.029
svapan vibudhyan gacchaṃś ca smariṣyāmy aham acyutam
parāpavādapaiśūnyaṃ parapīḍākaraṃ tathā 089.030
sacchāstradevatāyajvi- nindām anyasya vā bhuvi
na vakṣyāmi jagaty asmin paśyan sarvagata harim 089.031
ity anyac cāpi śaknoti yan nirvoḍhuṃ yaśasvini
kurvīta niyamaṃ tasya tyāgo dharmāya yasya ca 089.032
kṛtvaivaṃ purato viṣṇor nivṛttiṃ pāpataḥ śubhe
naivedyaṃ svayam aśnīyān maunī nityam udaṅmukhaḥ 089.033
mārgaśīrṣe tathā māsi jātipuṣpair janārdanam
samabhyarcya śubhe dhūpaṃ candanaṃ saṃnivedya ca 089.034
paramānnaṃ ca devāya viprāya ca punar ghṛtam
dattvā tathaiva gṛhṇīyān niyamaṃ cāsya rocate 089.035
tathaiva naktaṃ bhuñjīta naivedyaṃ kulanandini
sarveṣv eva tu māseṣu pañcagavyādikaṃ samam 089.036
puṣpadhūpopahāreṣu viśeṣo dakṣiṇāsu ca
snānaprāśanayoḥ sāmyaṃ tathā vai naktabhojane 089.037
arcayet pratimāsaṃ ca yaiḥ puṣpais tāni me śṛṇu
ye ca dhūpāḥ pradātavyā naivedyānnaṃ ca yad yadā 089.038
bāṇasya jātikusumais tathaiva ca kuruṇṭhakaiḥ
kundātimuktakai rakta- karavīraiś ca devaki 089.039
śvetais tato mālikayā tathā mallikayā tataḥ
dadhipiṇḍyātha ketakyā padmaraktotpalena ca
krameṇābhyarcito viṣṇur dadāti manasepsitam 089.040
kārttike mārgaśīrṣe ca dhūpaḥ pauṣe ca candanam
māghaphālgunacaitreṣu dadyād viṣṇos tathāgarum 089.041
vaiśākhādiṣu māseṣu triṣu devaki bhaktitaḥ
karpūraṃ devadevāya guggulaṃ śrāvaṇādiṣu 089.042
kārttikādiṣu māseṣu paramānnaṃ śubhe triṣu
kāsāraṃ māghapūrveṣu yavānnaṃ ca tatas triṣu 089.043
ghṛtaṃ tilāñ jalaghaṭān hiraṇyam athavājinam
pratimāsaṃ tathā dadyād brāhmaṇāya śubhavrate 089.044
yathoktaṃ niyamānāṃ ca grahaṇaṃ pratimāsikam
kurvañ jagatpatir viṣṇuḥ prīyatām iti mānavaḥ 089.045
yoṣid apy amalaprajñe vratam etad yathāvidhi
karoti yā sā sakalān avāpnoti manorathān 089.046
vratenārādhito viṣṇur anena jagataḥ patiḥ
dadāty abhimatān kāmān alpakālena bhāmini 089.047
dhanyaṃ yaśasyam āyuṣyaṃ saubhāgyārogyadaṃ tathā
vratam etat priyatamaṃ vratebhyo 'vyaktajanmanaḥ 089.048
vratenānena śuddhānām abdenaikena keśavaḥ
sukhadṛśyo na saṃdeho dīpenaivāgrataḥ sthitaḥ 089.049
kāyavāṅmanaso śuddhiṃ karoty etan mahāvratam
śuddhānāṃ cāmalo devo dṛśya eva janārdanaḥ 089.050
tasminn ekāgracittānāṃ prāṇināṃ varavarṇini
viprā eva prayatnena muktibhājo vibhūtayaḥ 089.051
yathā kalpataruṃ prāpya yad yad icchati cetasā
tat tat phalam avāpnoti tathā saṃprāpya taṃ vibhum 089.052
śuddhivratam idaṃ tasmān mahāpātakanāśanam
ārādhanāya kṛṣṇasya kuru devaki pāvanam 089.053
tasmiṃś cīrṇe hṛṣīkeśas tubhyaṃ dāsyati darśanam
dṛṣṭe cābhimataṃ yat te tad aśeṣaṃ bhaviṣyati 089.054
devakī bhārgavasyaitac śrutvā vākyaṃ narādhipa
śuddhikāmā cacārātha sarvakāmapradaṃ vratam 090.001
vratenārādhitas tena tadā devyā janārdanaḥ
dadau darśanam īśeśaḥ śaṅkhacakragadādharaḥ 090.002
dṛṣṭe tasminn aśeṣeśe jagaddhātari keśave
kṛtvā praṇāmam āhedaṃ bhaktinamrātha devakī 090.003
jagatām īśvareśeśa jñāna jñeya bhavāvyaya
samastadevatādeva vāsudeva namo 'stu te 090.004
pradhānapuṃsor ajayor yaḥ kāraṇam akāraṇam
aviśeṣyam ajaṃ rūpaṃ tava tasmai namo 'stu te 090.005
tvaṃ pradhānaṃ pumāṃś caiva kāraṇākāraṇātmakaḥ
sad asac cākhilaṃ deva kenoktena tava stavaḥ 090.006
prasīda deva devānām ariśātana vāmana
lobhābhibhūtā yad ahaṃ varayāmi prayaccha tat 090.007
aditis tvaṃ mahābhāge bhuvaṃ prāptā surāraṇi
bhartā ca te kaśyapo 'yaṃ deyas tava varo mayā 090.008
aputrāsmi na me bhartur asti keśava saṃtatiḥ
prasīda dehi me putram aridurdhārapauruṣam 090.009
bhaviṣyaty acirād devi madaṃśena sutas tava
hantavyā dānavās tena saddharmaparipanthinaḥ 090.010
tvām ahaṃ jagaddhātāram udāroruparākramam
dhārayiṣyāmi garbheṇa katham acyuta śaṃsa me 090.011
tavodare 'vatāraṃ vai purāpi balibandhane
kurvatā vidhṛtāḥ sapta lokās tvaṃ cātmamāyayā 090.012
tathā sāṃpratam apy etāṃl lokān sasthāṇujaṅgamān
dhārayiṣyāmy athātmānaṃ tvāṃ ca devaki līlayā 090.013
ity evam uktvā tāṃ devīṃ devakīṃ bhagavān prabhuḥ
tirobabhūva govindo bhūrbhuvaḥprabhavo vibhuḥ 090.014
avāpa ca tato garbhaṃ ajāyata ca viśveśaḥ
svenāṅgena janārdanaḥ 090.015
devakī vasudevataḥ pratimāsaṃ ca te pūjām
aṣṭamyāṃ yaḥ kariṣyati mama caivākhilān kāmān
saṃprāpnoty apakalmaṣaḥ 090.051
nīlotpaladalaśyāmaṃ tāmrāyatavilocanam
caturbāhum udārāṅgaṃ śrīvatsāṅkitavakṣasam 090.016
taṃ jātaṃ devakī devaṃ nidhānaṃ sarvatejasām
praṇipatyābhituṣṭāva saṃprastutapayodharā 090.017
abālo bālarūpeṇa yeneśa tvam ihāsthitaḥ
tvadrūpaṃ praṇipatyāhaṃ yad bravīmi nibodha tat 090.018
namas te sarvabhūteśa namas te madhusūdana
namas te puṇḍarīkākṣa namas te 'stu janārdana 090.019
namas te śārṅgacakrāsi- gadāparighapāṇaye
upendrāyāprameyāya hṛṣīkeśāya vai namaḥ 090.020
namo 'stu te 'ṇurūpāya bṛhadrūpāya vai namaḥ
aśeṣabhūtarūpāya tathārūpāya te namaḥ 090.021
anirdeśyaviśeṣāya tubhyaṃ sarvātmane namaḥ
sarveśvarāya sarvāya sarvabhūtāya te namaḥ 090.022
namo 'stu te vāsudeva namo 'stu kamalekṣaṇa
namo 'stu te sadācintya yogicintya jagatpate 090.023
aśeṣabhūtarūpāya tathābhūtāya te namaḥ
namo 'stu te 'śvarūpāya tathārūpāya te namaḥ
anirdeśyaviśeṣāya tubhyaṃ sarvātmane namaḥ
namo 'stu te vāsudeva namas te puṣkarekṣaṇa 090.*(144)
viṣṇo namo 'stu te kṛṣṇa namas te puruṣottama
namo nārāyaṇa hare namas te 'stu sadācyuta 090.024
namo namas te govinda namas te garuḍadhvaja
śrīśa śrīvatsa yogīśa śrīkānteśa namo 'stu te 090.025
nīlotpaladalaśyāma daṃṣṭroddhṛtavasuṃdhara
hiraṇyākṣaripo deva namas te yajñasūkara 090.026
nṛsiṃha jaya viśvātman daityoraḥsthaladāraka
namo namas te 'stu sadā vikṣepadhvastatāraka 090.027
māyāvāmanarūpāya tubhyaṃ deva namo namaḥ
trivikrama namas tubhyaṃ trailokyakrānti durjaya 090.028
ṛgyajuḥsāmabhūtāya vedāharaṇakarmaṇe
praṇavodgītavacase mahāśvaśirase namaḥ 090.029
niḥkṣatriyorvīkaraṇa vikarālaparākrama
jāmadagnya namas tubhyaṃ kārtavīryāsutaskara 090.030
paulastyakulanāśāya sādhumārgavicāriṇe
nalasetukṛte tubhyaṃ namo rāghavarūpiṇe 090.031
sāṃprataṃ matprasannāya saṃbhūtāya mamodare
svamāyābālarūpāya namaḥ kṛṣṇāya vai hare 090.032
yāvanti tava rūpāṇi yāvatyaś ca vibhūtayaḥ
namāmi kṛṣṇa sarvebhyas tebhyas tābhyaś ca sarvadā 090.033
svarūpaceṣṭitaṃ yat te yad devatve viceṣṭitam
yac ca tiryaṅmanuṣyatve ceṣṭitaṃ tan namāmy aham 090.034
parameśa pareśeśa tiryagīśa nareśvara
sarveśvareśvareśeśa namas te puruṣottama 090.035
evaṃ stutas tayā devyā devakyā madhusūdanaḥ
bālarūpī jagādaivaṃ vasudevasya śṛṇvataḥ 090.036
samyag ārādhitenoktaṃ yat prasannena vai śubhe
tat kṛtaṃ sakalaṃ bhūyo yad vṛṇoṣi dadāmi tat 090.037
avatāre tathaivāsmin varṣāṇām adhikaṃ śatam
sthāsyāmi naratāṃ prāpto duṣṭadaityanibarhaṇaḥ 090.038
tat tvaṃ varaya bhadraṃ te varaṃ yan manasecchasi
dāsyāmy aham asaṃdigdhaṃ yady api syāt sudurlabham 090.039
yadi deva prasannas tvaṃ pradadāsi mamepsitam
vṛṇomi tad ahaṃ nityaṃ tava keśava darśanam 090.040
tavedṛgrūpam ālokya hārdaprasrutalocanā
nālaṃ viyogaṃ saṃsoḍhuṃ tavāhaṃ madhusūdana 090.041
dākṣāyaṇī tvam aditiḥ saṃbhūtā vasudhātale
nityam eva jagaddhātri prasādaṃ te karomy aham 090.042
ṣaṣṭhe ṣaṣṭhe tadā pakṣe dine 'sminn eva bhāmini
tvaṃ māṃ drakṣyasy asaṃdigdhaṃ prasādas te kṛto mayā 090.043
anenaiva mahābhāge bālarūpeṇa saṃvṛtaḥ
tava darśanam eṣyāmi yatra te snehavan manaḥ 090.044
tasmin kāle ca lokās tvāṃ pūjayiṣyanti devaki
māṃ ca puṣpādibhir devi tavotsaṅgavyavasthitam 090.045
saṃpūjito 'haṃ lokānāṃ tasmin kāle sutoṣitaḥ
pradāsyāmi jagaddhātri yathābhilaṣitaṃ varam 090.046
aputrāṇāṃ varān putrān adhanānāṃ tathā dhanam
śubhān dārān adārāṇāṃ sarogāṇām arogatām 090.047
sugatiṃ gatikāmānāṃ vidyāṃ vidyārthinām api
pradāsyasi mahābhāge matprasādopavṛṃhitā 090.048
prasāditā hi martyānāṃ yat tvaṃ dāsyasi śobhane
tat teṣāṃ matprasādena bhaviṣyati na durlabham 090.049
tvām abhyarcyopacāreṇa snāpayitvā ghṛtena mām
sarvakāmān avāpsyanti kāle ṣaṭpakṣasaṃjñite 090.050
tvadaṅkasthaṃ ca māṃ bālaṃ saṃsmariṣyanti bhaktitaḥ 090.*(145)
evaṃ pūrvaṃ hṛṣīkeśo devakyāḥ pradadau varam
tasmāt kṛṣṇāṣṭamī puṃsām aśeṣāghaughahāriṇī 090.052
tasyāṃ hi pūjitaḥ kṛṣṇo devakī ca samādhinā
pāpāpanodaṃ kurute dadāti ca manorathān 090.053
tad eṣa puṣṭikāmānāṃ nR̥ṇāṃ puṇyārthinām api
upavāso mahīpāla śastaḥ keśavatoṣadaḥ 090.054
śrāvaṇe śuklapakṣe tu dvādaśyāṃ prīyate nṛpa
gopradānena govindo yat pūrvaṃ kathitaṃ tava 091.001
pauṣaśukle tu tadvac ca dvādaśyāṃ ghṛtadhenukām
ghṛtārciḥ prīṇanāyālaṃ pradadyāt phaladāyinīm 091.002
tathaiva māghadvādaśyāṃ pradattā tilagaur nṛpa
keśavaṃ prīṇayaty āśu sarvakāmān prayacchati 091.003
jyaiṣṭhe māsi site pakṣe dvādaśyāṃ jaladhenukā
dattā yathāvad vidhinā prīṇayaty ambuśāyinam 091.004
lavaṇaṃ mārgaśīrṣe tu kṛṣṇam abhyarcya yo naraḥ
prayacchati dvijāgryāya sa sarvarasadāyakaḥ 091.005
sarvabhogamahābhogān bhrājiṣmanto manoramān
lokān avāpnoti nṛpa prasanne garuḍadhvaje 091.006
pauṣamāse tu yo dadyād ghṛtaṃ viprāya pārthiva
samabhyarcyācyutaṃ so 'pi sarvakāmān avāpnuyāt 091.007
māghamāse tu saṃpūjya mādhavaṃ brāhmaṇāya yaḥ
prayacchati tilāṃl lokān saṃprāpnoty abhivāñchitān 091.008
phālgune puṇḍarīkākṣaṃ yaḥ samabhyarcya yacchati
saptadhānyaṃ naraśreṣṭha sa sarvasyeśvaro bhavet 091.009
caitre citrāṇi vastrāṇi yaḥ prayacchati keśavam
pūjayitvā sa vai bhogān vicitrāṃl labhate naraḥ 091.010
vaiśākhe viṣṇum abhyarcya yavagodhūmado naraḥ
lokān aindrān samāsādya modate vigatajvaraḥ 091.011
durnivartyam ahaṃ manye cañcalaṃ hi mano yataḥ 091.*(146)
jyaiṣṭhe 'bhyarcya hṛṣīkeśam udakumbhaprado hi yaḥ
sa parāṃ nirvṛtiṃ yāti sapta janmāntarāṇi vai 091.012
āṣāḍhamāse ca hariṃ yaḥ samabhyarcya yacchati
viprāya candanaṃ so 'pi paramāhlādabhājanam 091.013
yo nṛsiṃhaṃ samabhyarcya brāhmaṇāya prayacchati
śrāvaṇe navanītaṃ tu sa svargaṃ sukṛtī vrajet 091.014
chattraṃ ca yo bhādrapade vāsudevābhipūjakaḥ
prayacchati dvijāgryāya sa cchattrādhipatir bhavet 091.015
guḍaśarkarayā yuktaṃ modakaṃ ca prayacchati
tathaivāśvayuje 'bhyarcya yo 'nantaṃ so 'maro bhavet 091.016
nārāyaṇaṃ samabhyarcya yaḥ prayacchati kārttike
dīpakaṃ viprageheṣu vimānaṃ so 'dhirohati 091.017
kāmyāny etāny aśeṣāṇi yaḥ saṃpūjya jagatpatim
dānāni yacchati naraḥ sa saṃpūrṇamanorathaḥ
sarvaśreṣṭhaḥ samastānāṃ bandhūnām āśrayo bhavet 091.018
evaṃ sarvāṇi dānāni prīṇanāyācyutasya yaḥ
prayacchati sa sarveṣāṃ phalānāṃ bhuvi bhājanam 091.019
tasmān narendra viprebhyaḥ prīṇanāya jagadguroḥ
prayacchaitāni dānāni yac cānyad dayitaṃ tava 091.020
yadīcchasi punaḥ prāptuṃ bhūtim abhraṃśanīṃ nṛpa
tadārādhaya govindaṃ nānyathā syur vibhūtayaḥ 091.021
evaṃ vasiṣṭhena tadā māndhātā nṛpa bodhitaḥ
saha patnyā mahīpālaḥ paritoṣaṃ paraṃ yayau 091.022
jagāda ca mudā yuktaḥ praṇipatya purohitam
saha patnyā naraśreṣṭhaḥ samutthāya varāsanāt 091.023
dhig dhig vṛthaiva yātāni mamaitāni dināny aho
anāsajya manaḥ kṛṣṇe viṣayāsaktacetasaḥ 091.024
tā niśās te ca divasās te rtavas te ca vatsarāḥ
narāṇāṃ saphalā yeṣu cintito bhagavān hariḥ 091.025
cintyamānaḥ samastānāṃ pāpānāṃ hāṇido hi saḥ
samutsṛjyākhilaṃ cintyaṃ so 'cyutaḥ kiṃ na cintyate 091.026
kaṣṭaṃ muṣṭo 'smi śiṣṭeṣu vidyamāneṣu mantriṣu
parāṅmukhānāṃ govinde yat prāptaṃ paramaṃ vayaḥ 091.027
evaṃ vinindya so 'tmānāṃ māndhātā pṛthivīpatiḥ
cakārārādhane yatnaṃ devadevasya śārṅgitiṇaḥ 091.028
tam ārādhya ca viśveśam upendram asureśvara
prāpa siddhiṃ parāṃ pūrvaṃ dakṣaḥ prācetaso yathā 091.029
tathā tvam api rājendra sarvabhāvena keśavam
samārādhaya govindaṃ tam ārādhya na sīdati 091.030
evaṃ sa daityarājendraḥ prahrādenāvabodhitaḥ
balir ārādhane yatnaṃ cakre cakrabhṛtas tadā 091.031
puṣpopahārair dhūpaiś ca tathā caivānulepanaiḥ
vāsobhir bhūṣaṇaiḥ samyag brāhmaṇānāṃ ca tarpaṇaiḥ 091.032
japair homair vrataiś caiva yathoktaṃ puruṣarṣabha
saha patnyā tathaiva tvaṃ samārādhaya keśavam 091.033
bhagavaṃś cañcalaṃ cittaṃ manuṣyāṇām aharniśam
viṣayāsaṅgadurduṣṭaṃ pāpāyaiva pravartate 092.001
maunena vācikaṃ pāpaṃ puṃbhir brahman nivartyate
śārīram apy akaraṇāt sunivartyaṃ mataṃ mama 092.002
yat tv etan mānasaṃ pāpaṃ manuṣyais tan mahāmate
durnivartyam ahaṃ manye cañcalaṃ hi mano yataḥ 092.003
tad ahaṃ śrotum icchāmi manuṣyair durvicintitaiḥ
yat smartavyaṃ ca japyaṃ ca mānasāghapraśāntaye 092.004
tvadyukto 'yam anupraśnaḥ sādhv etad bhavatoditam
cañcalatvād dhi cittānāṃ mānasaṃ bahu pātakam 092.005
bhūmau tṛṇam asaṃkhyātaṃ yathā ca divi tārakāḥ
tathā pāpam asaṃkhyeyaṃ cetasā kriyate tu yat 092.006
paradāraparadravya- parahiṃsāsu mānasam
aharniśaṃ manuṣyāṇāṃ sātatyena pravartate 092.007
yady asyopaśamo rājan bhuvi na kriyate nṛbhiḥ
tan nāsti narakottāro varṣakoṭīśatair api 092.008
tad asya praśamāyālaṃ prāyaścittaṃ narādhipa
śṛṇuṣva yena cittotthaṃ sadyaḥ pāpaṃ vyapohati 092.009
oṃ namo vāsudevāya puruṣāya mahātmane
hiraṇyaretase 'cintya- svarūpāyātivedhase 092.010
viṣṇave jiṣṇave nityaṃ śāntāyānagharūpiṇe
sarvasthityantakaraṇa- vratine pītavāsase 092.011
nārāyaṇāya viśvāya viśveśāyeśvarāya ca
namaḥ kamalakiñjalka- suvarṇamukuṭāya ca 092.012
keśavāyātisūkṣmāya brahmamūrtimate namaḥ
namaḥ paramakalyāṇa- kalyāṇāyātmayonaye 092.013
janārdanāya devāya śrīdharāya sumedhase
mahātmane vareṇyāya namaḥ paṅkajanābhaye 092.014
smṛtamātrāghaghātāya kṛṣṇāyākliṣṭakarmaṇe
namo natāya namreśair aśeṣair vāsavādibhiḥ 092.015
namo māyāvine tubhyaṃ haraye harimedhase
hiraṇyagarbhagarbhāya jagataḥ kāraṇātmane 092.016
govindāyādibhūtāya śrādīnāṃ mahātmane
namo bhūtātmabhūtāya ātmane paramātmane 092.017
acyutāya namo nityam anantāya namo namaḥ
dāmodarāya śucaye yajñeśāya namo namaḥ 092.018
namo māyāpaṭacchanna- jagaddhāmne mahātmane
hṛṣīkeśāya ceśāya sarvabhūtātmarūpiṇe 092.019
dayālave namo nityaṃ kapilāya sumedhase
saṃsārasāgarottāra- jñānapotapradāyine 092.020
akuṇṭhamataye dhātre sargasthityantakarmaṇi
karālasaumyarūpāya vaikuṇṭhāya namo namaḥ 092.021
yathā hi vāsudeveti prokte naśyati pātakam
tathā vilayam abhyetu mamaitad durvicintitam 092.022
yathā na viṣṇubhakteṣu pāpam āpnoti saṃsthitim
tathā vināśam abhyetu mamaitad durvicintitam 092.023
smṛtamātro yathā viṣṇuḥ sarvaṃ pāpaṃ vyapohati
tathā praṇāśam abhyetu mamaitad durvicintitam 092.024
yathā sarvatrago viṣṇus tatra sarvaṃ ca saṃsthitam
upayātu tathā nāśaṃ mamāghaṃ cittasaṃbhavam 092.025
pāpaṃ praṇāśaṃ mama saṃprayātu yan mānasaṃ yac ca karomi vācā
śārīram apy ācaritaṃ ca yan me smṛte jagaddhātari vāsudeve 092.026
prayāntu doṣā mama nāśam āśu rāgādayaḥ kāraṇakāraṇeśe
vijñānadīpāmalamārgadṛśye smṛte jagaddhātari vāsudeve 092.027
bhavantu bhadrāṇi samastadoṣāḥ prayāntu nāśaṃ jagato 'khilasya
mayādya bhaktyā parameśvareśe smṛte jagaddhātari vāsudeve 092.028
ye bhūtale ye divi ye 'ntarikṣe rasātale prāṇigaṇāś ca kecit
bhavantu te siddhiyujo mayādya smṛte jagaddhātari vāsudeve 092.029
puṣyantu maitrīṃ viramantu rāgād ujjhantu lobhaṃ kṣamiṇo bhavantu
ābrahmavṛkṣāntaragā mayādya smṛte jagaddhātari vāsudeve 092.030
ye prāṇinaḥ kutracid atra santi brahmāṇḍamadhye parataś ca kecit
te yāntu siddhiṃ paramāṃ mayādya smṛte jagaddhātari vāsudeve 092.031
ajñānino jñānavido bhavantu praśāntibhājaḥ satatogracittāḥ
kurvantu bhaktiṃ paramām anante matstotratuṣṭasya hareḥ prasādāt 092.032
śṛṇvanti ye me paṭhatas tathānye paśyanti ye mām idam īrayantam
devāsurādyā manujās tiraśco bhavantu te 'py acyutayogabhājaḥ 092.033
ye cāpi mūkā vikalendriyatvāc śṛṇvanti no naiva vilokayanti
paśvādayaḥ kīṭapipīlikāś ca bhavantu te 'py acyutayogabhājaḥ 092.034
nāmasv anantasya ca kīrtiteṣu yad atra puṇyaṃ jagataḥ prasūteḥ
tenāvivekopahatātmabodhā bhavantu puṃsāṃ matayaḥ suśīlāḥ 092.035
ye duḥkhitās te sukhino bhavantu dveṣānvitā maitraguṇopapannāḥ
satyārjavādyās tv anṛtā vimāyā matsaṃstavārādhitakṛṣṇadṛṣṭāḥ 092.036
naśyantu duḥkhāni jagaty apaitu lobhādiko doṣaguṇaḥ prajābhyaḥ
yathātmani bhrātari cātmaje ca tathā janasyāstu jane 'pi hārdam 092.037
saṃsāravaidye 'khiladoṣahāni- vicakṣaṇe nirvṛtihetubhūte
saṃsārabandhāḥ śithilībhavantu hṛdi sthite sarvajanasya viṣṇau 092.038
etat paṭhan pārthiva sarvapāpair vimucyate viṣṇuparaḥ sadaiva
prāpnoti siddhiṃ vipulaṃ maharddhim na cāpy anartheṣu matiṃ karoti 092.039
uddiśya sattvāni ca yāni yāni stotraṃ paṭhante kṛpayā manuṣyāḥ
sarvāṇi tāny apratighā bhavanti prayānti siddhiṃ bhagavatprasādāt 092.040
tasmāt tvayaitat satataṃ niśāsu dineṣu caiveśvara mādhavasya
saṃkīrtanaṃ kāryam aśeṣapāpa- vimokṣahetor abhavāya caiva 092.041
iti sakalajanopakārakārī haricaraṇābjaviniṣṭaśuddhabuddhiḥ
paṭhati khalu mahīpa yo manuṣyaḥ sa layam upaiti harau hṛtākhilāghaḥ 092.042
idaṃ ca śṛṇu bhūpāla naśyate durvicintitam
yenopāyena vai puṃsāṃ yoṣitāṃ vāpy asaṃśayam 093.001
paradāraparadravya- jīvahiṃsādike sadā
pravartate nṛṇāṃ cittaṃ tad etad abhisaṃsmaret 093.002
viṣṇave viṣṇave nityaṃ viṣṇave viṣṇave namaḥ
jiṣṇave jiṣṇave sarvaṃ jiṣṇave jiṣṇave namaḥ 093.003
namāmi viṣṇuṃ buddhistham ahaṃkāra-gataṃ harim
cittastham īśam avyaktam anantam aparājitam
viṣṇum īḍyam aśeṣeśam anādinidhanaṃ vibhum 093.004
viṣṇuś cittagato yan me viṣṇur buddhigataś ca yat
yac cāhaṃkārago viṣṇur yad viṣṇur mayi saṃsthitaḥ 093.005
karoti kartṛbhūto 'sau sthāvarasya carasya ca
tat pāpaṃ nāśam āyātu tasminn eva vicintite 093.006
dhyāto harati yaḥ pāpaṃ svapne dṛṣṭaḥ śubhāvahaḥ
tam upendram ahaṃ viṣṇuṃ praṇato 'rtiharaṃ harim 093.007
jagaty asmin nirādhāre majjamāne tamasy adhaḥ
hastāvalambadaṃ viṣṇuṃ praṇato 'smi parātparam 093.008
sarveśvareśvara vibho paramātmann adhokṣaja
hṛṣīkeśa hṛṣīkeśa hṛṣīkeśa namo 'stu te 093.009
nṛsiṃhānanta govinda bhūtabhāvana keśava
duruktaṃ duṣkṛtaṃ dhyātaṃ praśamāgrya namo 'stu te 093.010
yan mayā cintitaṃ duṣṭaṃ svacittavaśavartinā
narakāvaham atyugraṃ tac chamaṃ naya keśava 093.011
brahmaṇyadeva govinda paramārtha parāyaṇa
jagannātha jagaddhātaḥ pāpaṃ praśamayācyuta 093.012
yac cāparāhne pūrvāhne madhyāhne ca tathā niśi
kāyena manasā vācā kṛtaṃ pāpam ajānatā 093.013
jānatā vā hṛṣīkeśa puṇḍarīkākṣa mādhava
nāmatrayoccāraṇatas tat prayātu mama kṣayam 093.014
śārīraṃ me hṛṣīkeśa puṇḍarīkākṣa mānasam
pāpaṃ praśamayādya tvaṃ vākkṛtaṃ mama mādhava 093.015
yad vrajan yat svapan bhuñjan yad uttiṣṭhan yad āsthitaḥ
kṛtavāṃś cāpi yac cāhaṃ kāyena manasā girā 093.016
mahat svalpam atisthūlaṃ kuyoninarakāvaham
tad yātu praśamaṃ sarvaṃ vāsudevasya kīrtanāt 093.017
paraṃ brahma paraṃ dhāma pavitraṃ paramaṃ ca yat
tasmin saṃkīrtite viṣṇoḥ pade pāpaṃ praṇaśyatu 093.018
sūrayo yat pravekṣyanti hy apunarbhavakāṅkṣiṇaḥ
mamākhilaṃ daha tvaṃ hi tad viṣṇoḥ paramaṃ padam 093.019
yat prāpya na ninvartante gandhasparśādivarjitam
pāpaṃ praṇāśayatv adya tad viṣṇoḥ paramaṃ padam 093.020
sadasad yat tathā vyaktā- vyaktarūpam ajājaram
praṇamāmi jagaddhāma tad viṣṇoḥ paramaṃ padam 093.021
śārīre mānase caiva pāpe vāgje ca pārthiva
kṛte samyaṅ naro bhaktyā paṭhec chraddhāsamanvitaḥ
mucyate sarvapāpebhyaḥ kṛṣṇanāmaprakīrtanāt 093.022
uccāryamāne caitasmin devadevasya saṃstave
vilayaṃ pāpam āyāti bhāṇḍam āmam ivāmbhasi 093.023
tasmāt saṃcintite pāpe samanantaram eva te
japtavyam etat pāpasya praśamāya mahīpate 093.024
saṃsārārṇavamagnena puruṣeṇa mahāmune
viṣayāsaktacittena yat kāryaṃ tad vadasva me 094.001
bhrāmyatāṃ saṃkaṭe durge saṃsāre viṣayaiṣiṇām
svakarmabhir manuṣyāṇām upakārakam ucyatām 094.002
kṣīpte manasy anāyatte vṛddhe lobhādike gaṇe
śaraṇaṃ yan manuṣyāṇāṃ tad ācakṣva mahāmune 094.003
saṃsārāṇavapotāya haraye harimedhase
namaskṛtya pravakṣyāmi narāṇām upakārakam 094.004
samyag ārādhito bhaktyā vedabhāraguror guruḥ
kṛṣṇadvaipāyanaḥ prāha yac chiṣyāya sumantave 094.005
purā kila durācāro durbuddhir ajitendriyaḥ
kṣatrabandhur abhūt pāpaḥ paramarmāvaghaṭṭakaḥ 094.006
mātāpitror aśuśrūṣur drogdhā bandhujanasya ca
gurudevadvijātīnāṃ nindāsu satatodyataḥ 094.007
moṣṭā viśvasatāṃ nityam aprītiḥ prītim icchatām
ṛjūnām anṛjuḥ kṣudraḥ parahiṃsāparāyaṇaḥ 094.008
sa bāndhavaiḥ parityaktas tathānyaiḥ sādhuvṛttibhiḥ
avṛttimān aviśvāsyo mṛgayājīvano 'bhavat 094.009
ahany ahani cakrāṅgān eṇakādīṃs tathā mṛgān
hatvātmapoṣaṇaṃ cakre vyādhavṛttirato 'dhamaḥ 094.010
etayā tasya duṣṭasya kuvṛttyā pāpacetasaḥ
jagāma sumahān kālaḥ kurvato dārapoṣaṇam 094.011
ekadā tu munis tena nidāghe vijane vane
mṛgayām aṭatā dṛṣṭo vartmanaḥ pracyutaḥ pathi 094.012
kṣutkṣāmakaṇṭhaḥ suśrāntaḥ śuṣkajihvāsyatālukaḥ
tṛṭparīto 'tivibhrāntaḥ kāṃdigbhūto 'lpacetanaḥ 094.013
śvāsāyāsaślathair aṅgaiḥ kṛcchrād ātmānam udvahan
sūryāṃśutāpāt pragalat- svedārdracaraṇo nṛpa 094.014
tasmin dṛṣṭe tatas tasya kṣatrabandhor ajāyata
kāruṇyaṃ dāruṇasyāpi vyādhavṛttiparigrahāt 094.015
tam upetya ca bhūpāla kṣatrabandhuḥ sa tāpasam
uvāca viprapravaraṃ vimārge vartate bhavān 094.016
naiṣa panthā dvijaśreṣṭha vipino 'yaṃ mahāṭaviḥ
mām anvehi tvarāyukto mā vipattiṃ sameṣyasi 094.017
niśāmya tad vacaḥ śrāntaḥ kṣatrabandhor mahānuniḥ
anuvavrāja rājendra jalāśājanitodyamaḥ 094.018
kiṃcid bhūbhāgam āsādya dadarśa ca mahāmuniḥ
haṃsakāraṇḍavākīrṇaṃ protphullanalinaṃ saraḥ 094.019
sārasābhirutaṃ ramyaṃ sūpatīrtham akardamam
padmotpalayutaṃ cāru pūrṇaṃ svacchena vāriṇā 094.020
suśītavanaṣaṇḍaiś ca samantāt pariveṣṭitam
tatkṣaṇāt tṛṭparītānāṃ cakṣuṣo hlādakāriṇam 094.021
dṛṣṭvaiva sa munis tatra tadāmalajalaṃ saraḥ
sūryāṃśutapto gharmārto nipapāta tadambhasi 094.022
tatrāśvāsya kṛtāhlādaḥ papau vāri narādhipa
ujjīvayan munivaro jihvātālu śanaiḥ śanaiḥ 094.023
so 'pi kṣatriyadāyādo munitrāṇaparāyaṇaḥ
vihāya saśaraṃ cāpam ujjahāra bisāny atha 094.024
dadau ca tasmai rājendra kṣudhitāya tapasvine
yayau ca tṛptiṃ vipro 'pi bisanālāmbubhakṣaṇāt 094.025
tam āśvastaṃ kṛtāhāram upaviṣṭaṃ suśītale
nyagrodhaśākhāsaṃchanne niṣpaṅke sarasas taṭe
saṃvāhayām āsa ca taṃ kṣatrabandhuḥ śanaiḥ śanaiḥ 094.026
pādajaṅghorupṛṣṭeṣu tena saṃvāhito muniḥ
jahau śramam amitraghna vākyaṃ cedam uvāca ha 094.027
kas tvaṃ bhadramukhādyeha mama prāṇaparikṣaye
hastāvalambado dhātrā janito vipine vane 094.028
vibhraṣṭamārgo mūḍho 'haṃ kṣutpipāsāśramāturaḥ
trātas tvayā mahābhāga kas tvam atra vane 'jane 094.029
kṣutpipāsāśramārtasya yas trāṇaṃ vipine vane
karoti puruṣavyāghra tasya lokā madhuścyutaḥ 094.030
sa tvaṃ brūhi mahābhāga mamābhyuddhārakārakaḥ
yeṣāṃ prakhyātayaśasāṃ samutpannaḥ kule bhavān 094.031
haryaśvasya kule jātaḥ putraś citrarathasya ca
vimatir nāma nāmnāhaṃ hantum abhyāgato mṛgān 094.032
pitrarthaṃ mṛgayeyaṃ te lakṣyārthaṃ vā mahāmate
āhārārtham utāho 'tra mṛgayā vyasanaṃ tu te 094.033
vṛttir eṣā mama brahman parityaktasya bāndhavaiḥ
bhṛtyair anyaiś ca naṣṭe 'rthe nirdhanasyāmiṣāśinaḥ 094.034
kimarthaṃ tvaṃ parityakto bhṛtyasvajanabandhubhiḥ
pātakī kīkaṭaḥ kṣudrair upajaptaḥ pareṇa vā 094.035
ity uktaḥ so 'bhavan maunī paśyan doṣaṃ nṛpātmani
aduṣṭāṃś cātmano bhṛtyān vicintyātīva durmanāḥ 094.036
avekṣya taṃ sādhvasinaṃ kṣatrabandhuṃ mahāmuniḥ
dhyātvā ciram athāpaśyat kṣatrabandhuṃ svadoṣiṇam 094.037
saṃtyaktabandhuloke ca tasmin durvṛttacetasi
kṛpāṃ cakāra sa muniḥ kṣatrabandhau dayāparaḥ 094.038
uvāca ca munir bhūyaḥ kṣatrabandhuṃ kṛpālukaḥ
upakāriṇam ugreṇa karmaṇā taṃ vidūṣitam 094.039
api śaknoṣi saṃyantum akāryaprasṛtaṃ manaḥ
prāṇi pīḍānivṛttiṃ ca kartuṃ krodhādisaṃyamam 094.040
api maitrīṃ jane kartuṃ śaknoṣi tvaṃ mudhaiva yā
aihikāmuṣmikī vīra kriyamāṇā mahāphalā 094.041
na śaknomi kṣamāṃ kartuṃ na maitrīṃ mama cetasi
prāṇinām avadhād brahman nāsti dārādipoṣaṇam 094.042
anāyattaṃ ca me cittaṃ viṣayān eva dhāvati
tadaprāptau ca sarveṣāṃ krodhādīnāṃ samudbhavaḥ 094.043
so 'haṃ na maitrīṃ na kṣāntiṃ na hiṃsādivivarjanam
kartuṃ śaknomi yat kāryaṃ tadanyad upadiśyatām 094.044
tenaivam ukto vipro 'sau tam upekṣyam amanyata
tathāpy atikṛpālutvāt kṣatrabandhum abhāṣata 094.045
yady etad akhilaṃ kartuṃ na śaknoṣi bravīhi me
svalpam anyan mayoktaṃ hi kariṣyati bhavān yadi 094.046
aśakyam uktaṃ bhavatā cañcalatvād dhi cetasaḥ
vākśarīraviniṣpādyaṃ yac chakyaṃ tad udīraya 094.047
uttiṣṭhatā prasvapatā prasthitena gamiṣyatā
govindeti sadā vācyaṃ kṣutapraskhalitādiṣu 094.048
kāryaṃ vartmani mūḍhānāṃ kṣemamārge 'vatāraṇam
hitaṃ ca vācyaṃ pṛṣṭena śatrūṇām api jānatā 094.049
etat tavopakārāya bhaviṣyaty anupālitam
yady anyad upasaṃhartuṃ na śaknoṣi mahīpate 094.050
ity uktvā prayayau vipras tena vartmani darśite
so 'pi tac chāsanaṃ sarvaṃ kṣatrabandhuś cakāra ha 094.051
govindeti kṣute gacchan prasthānaskhalitādiṣu
udīrayann avāpāgryāṃ ratiṃ tatra śanaiḥ śanaiḥ 094.052
tataḥ kālena mahatā kṣatrabandhur mamāra vai
ajāyata ca viprasya kule jātismaro nṛpa 094.053
tasya saṃsmarato jātīḥ śataśo 'tha sahasraśaḥ
nirvedaḥ sumahāñ jajñe saṃsāre 'trātiduḥkhade
sa cintayām āsa jagat sarvam etad acetanam 094.054
aham eko 'tra saṃjñāvān govindodīritaṃ hi yat
yac cādhvani vimūḍhānāṃ kṛtaṃ vartmāvatāraṇam
hitam uktaṃ ca pṛṣṭena tasya jātismṛtiḥ phalam 094.055
so 'haṃ jātismaro bhūyaḥ kariṣyāmy atisaṃkaṭe
tadā saṃsāracakre 'smin yena prāpsyāmi nirvṛtim 094.056
yasyoccāraṇamātreṇa jātā jātismṛtir mama
tam evārādhayiṣyāmi jagatām īśvaraṃ harim 094.057
yanmayaṃ paramaṃ brahma tad avyaktaṃ ca yanmayam
yanmayaṃ vyaktam apy etad bhaviṣyāmi hi tanmayaḥ 094.058
yady anārādhite viṣṇau mamaitaj janma yāsyati
dhruvaṃ bandhavato muktir naiva jātūpapadyate 094.059
aho duḥkham aho duḥkham aho duḥkham atīva hi
svarūpam atighorasya saṃsārasyātidurlabham 094.060
viṇmūtrapūyakalile garbhavāse 'tipīḍanāt
aśucāv atibībhatse duḥkham atyantaduḥsaham 094.061
duḥkhaṃ ca jāyamānānāṃ gātrabhaṅgādipīḍanāt
vātena preryamāṇānāṃ mūrchākāry atibhītidam 094.062
bālatve nirvivekānāṃ bhūtadevātmasaṃbhavam
yauvane vārddhake caiva maraṇe cātidāruṇam 094.063
śītoṣṇatṛṣṇākṣudroga- jvarādiparivāritaḥ
sarvadaiva pumān āste yāvaj janmāntasaṃsthitiḥ 094.064
duḥkhātiśayabhūtaṃ hi yad ante vāsukhaṃ nṛṇām
tasyānumānaṃ naivāsti kāryeṇaivānumīyate 094.065
kṛṣyamāṇasya puruṣair yad yamasyātiduḥsaham
duḥkhaṃ tatsaṃsmṛtiprāptaṃ karoti mama vepathum 094.066
kumbhīpāke taptakumbhe mahārauravaraurave
kālasūtre mahāyantre śūkare kūṭaśālmalau 094.067
asipatravane duḥkham apratiṣṭhe ca yan mahat
viḍālavaktre ca tathā tamasy ugre ca duḥsaham 094.068
śastrāgniyantravegeṣu śītoṣṇādiṣu dāruṇam
tataś ca muktasya punar yonisaṃkramaṇeṣu yat 094.069
garbhasthasya ca yad duḥkham atiduḥsaham ulvaṇam
punaś ca jāyamānasya janma yauvanajaṃ ca yat 094.070
duḥkhāny etāny asahyāni saṃsārāntarvivartibhiḥ
puruṣair anubhūyante sukhabhrāntivimohitaiḥ 094.071
na vai sukhakalā kācit tatrāsty atyantaduḥkhade
saṃsārasaṃkaṭe tīvre upetānāṃ kadācana 094.072
viṣayāsaktacittānāṃ manuṣyāṇāṃ kadā matiḥ
saṃsārottāraṇe vāñchāṃ kariṣyati hi cañcalā 094.073
govindanāmnā satataṃ samuccāraṇasaṃbhavam
jātismaratvam etan naḥ kiṃ vṛthaiva prayāsyati 094.074
so 'haṃ muktipradānārtham anantam ajam avyayam
taccittas tanmayo bhūtvā toṣayiṣyāmi keśavam 094.075
ātmānam ātmanaivaṃ sa proktvā jātismaro dvijaḥ
tuṣṭāva vāgbhir iṣṭābhiḥ praṇataḥ puruṣottamam 094.076
praṇipatyākṣaraṃ viśvaṃ viśvahetuṃ nirañjanam
yat prārthayāmy avikalaṃ sakalaṃ tat prayacchatu 094.077
kartāram akṛtaṃ viṣṇuṃ sarvakāraṇakāraṇam
aṇor aṇīyāṃsam ajaṃ sarvavyāpinam īśvaram 094.078
parāt parataraṃ yasmān nāsti sarveśvarāt param
taṃ praṇamyācyutaṃ devaṃ prārthayāmi yad astu tat 094.079
sarveśvarācyutānanta paramātmañ janārdana
saṃsārābdhimahāpota samuddhara mahārṇavāt 094.080
vyomānilāgnyambudharāsvarūpa tanmātrasarvendriyabuddhirūpa
antaḥsthitātman paramātmarūpa prasīda sarveśvara viśvarūpa 094.081
tam ādir anto jagato 'sya madhyam ādes tvam ādiḥ pralayasya cāntaḥ
tvatto bhavaty etad aśeṣam īśa tvayy eva cānte layam abhyupaiti 094.082
pradīpavartyantagato 'gnir alpo yathātikakṣe vitataṃ prayāti
tadvad visṛṣṭer amarādibhinnair vikāśam āyāsi vibhūtibhedaiḥ 094.083
yathā nadīnāṃ bahavo 'mbuvegāḥ samantato 'bdhiṃ bhagavan viśanti
tvayy antakāle jagad acyutedaṃ tathā layaṃ gacchati sarvabhūte 094.084
tvaṃ sarvam etad bahudhaika eva jagatpate kāryam ivābhyupetam
yad asti yan nāsti ca tat tvam eva hare tvadanyad bhagavan kim asti 094.085
kiṃtv īśa māyā bhavato nijeyam āviṣkṛtāviṣkṛtalokasṛṣṭe
yayāham eṣo 'nyatamo mameti madīyam asyābhivadanti mūḍhāḥ 094.086
tayā vimūḍhena mayābhanābha na yat kṛtaṃ tat kvacid asti kiṃcit
bhūmyambarāgnisalileṣu deva jāgratsuṣuptādiṣu duḥkhitena 094.087
na santi tāvanti jalāny apīḍya sarveṣu nāthābdhiṣu sarvakālam
stanyāni yāvanti mayātighore pītāni saṃsāramahāsamudre 094.088
saṃpac chilānāṃ himavanmahendra- kailāsamervādiṣu naiva tādṛk
dehāny anekāny anugṛhṇato me prāptāsthisaṃpan mahati yatheśa 094.089
tvayy arpitaṃ nātha punaḥ punar me manaḥ samākṣipya sudurdharo 'pi
rāgo hi vaśyaṃ kurute tato 'nu lobhādayaḥ kiṃ bhagavan karomi 094.090
ekāgratāmūlyabalena labhyaṃ bhavauṣadhaṃ tvaṃ bhagavan kilaikaḥ
manaḥ parāyattam idaṃ bhave 'smin saṃsāraduḥkhāt kim ahaṃ karomi 094.091
na santi te deva bhuvi pradeśā na yeṣu jāto 'smi tathā vinaṣṭaḥ
attā mayā yeṣu na jantavaś ca saṃbhakṣito yaiś ca na jantusaṃghaiḥ 094.092
siṃhena bhūtvā bahavo mayāttā vyāghreṇa bhūtvā bahavo mayāttāḥ
tathānyarūpair bahavo mayāttāḥ saṃbhakṣito 'haṃ bahubhis tataś ca 094.093
utkrāntiduḥkhāny atiduḥsahāni sahasraśo yāny anusaṃsmarāmi
taiḥ saṃsmṛtais tat kṣaṇam eva deva taḍid yathā me hṛdayaṃ prayāti 094.094
tataś ca duḥkhāny anivāraṇāni yantrāgniśastraughasamudbhavāni
bhavanti yāny acyuta nārakānāṃ tāny eva teṣām upamānamātram 094.095
duḥkhāny asahyāni ca garbhavāse viṇmūtramadhye 'tinipīḍitasya
bhavanti yāni cyavataś ca garbhāt teṣāṃ svarūpaṃ gadituṃ na śakyam 094.096
duḥkhāni bāleṣu mahanti nātha kaumārake yauvaninaś ca puṃsaḥ
jvarātisārākṣirugādikāni samastaduḥkhālaya eva vṛddhaḥ 094.097
karoti karmācyuta tatkṣaṇena pāpaṃ naraḥ kāyamanovacobhiḥ
yasyābdalakṣair api nāntam eti śastrādiyantrāgninipīḍaneṣu 094.098
duḥkhāni yānīṣṭaviyogajāni bhavanti saṃsāravihārabhājām
pratyekaśas teṣu narā vināśam icchanty asūnāṃ mamatābhibhūtāḥ 094.099
śokābhibhūtasya mamāśru deva yāvatpramāṇaṃ na jalaṃ payodā
tāvatpramāṇaṃ na jalaṃ payodā muñcanty anekair api varṣalakṣaiḥ 094.100
manye dharitrī paramāṇusaṃkhyām upaiti pitror gaṇanāmaśeṣam
mitrāṇy amitrāṇy anujīvibandhūn saṃkhyātam īśo 'smi na devadeva 094.101
so 'haṃ bhṛśārtaḥ karuṇāṃ kuru tvaṃ saṃsāragātre patitasya viṣṇo
mahātmanāṃ saṃśrayam abhyupeto naivāvasīdaty atidurgato 'pi 094.102
parāyaṇaṃ rogavatāṃ hi vaidyo mahābdhimagnasya ca naur narasya
bālasya mātāpitarau sughora- saṃsārakhinnasya hare tvam ekaḥ 094.103
prasīda sarveśvara sarvabhūta sarvasya heto paramārthasāra
mām uddharāsmād uruduḥkhapaṅkāt saṃsāragartāt svaparigraheṇa 094.104
dharmātmanām avikalāṃ tvayi nātha bhaktiṃ śraddhāvatāṃ satatam udvahatāṃ vareṇya
kāryaṃ kiyan mama vimūḍhadhiyo 'dhamasya bhūtvā kṛpālur amalām aja dehi buddhim 094.105
jñātvā yayākhilam asāram asāram eva bhūtendriyādikam apāram amuktimūlam
māyāntareyam acalāṃ tava viśvarūpa saṃmohitaṃ sakalam eva jagad yayaitat 094.106
brahmendrarudramarudaśvidivākarādyā jñātuṃ na yaṃ paramaguhyatamaṃ samarthāḥ
na tvām alaṃ stutipatheṣv aham īśitāraṃ stoṣyāmi mohakaluṣālpamatir manuṣyaḥ 094.107
yasmād idaṃ bhavati yatra jagat tathedaṃ yasmiṃl layaṃ vrajati yaś ca jagatsvarūpaḥ
taṃ sargasaṃsthitivināśanimittabhūtaṃ stotuṃ bhavantam alam īśa na kaścid asti 094.108
mūḍho 'yam alpamatir alpasuceṣṭito 'yaṃ kliṣṭaṃ mano 'sya viṣayair na mayi prasaṅgi
itthaṃ kṛpāṃ kuru mayi praṇate kileśa tvāṃ stotum ambujabhavo 'pi hi deva neśaḥ 094.109
yasyodare sakala eva mahīdhracandra- devendrarudramarudaśvidivākarāgni-
bhūmyambuvāyugaganaṃ jagatāṃ samuhāṃ stoṣyāmi taṃ stutipadaiḥ katamair bhavantam 094.110
yasyāgnirudrakamalodbhavavāsavādyaiḥ svāṃśāvatārakaraṇeṣu sadāṅghriyugmam
abhyarcyate vada hare sa kathaṃ mayādya saṃpūjitaḥ param upaiṣyasi toṣam īśa 094.111
na stotum acyuta bhavantam ahaṃ samartho naivārcanair alam ahaṃ tava deva yogyaḥ
cittaṃ ca na tvayi samāhitam īśa doṣair ākṣipyate kathaya kiṃ nu karomi pāpaḥ 094.112
tat tvaṃ prasīda bhagavan kuru mayy anāthe viṣṇo kṛpāṃ paramakāruṇikaḥ kila tvam
saṃsārasāgaranimagnam ananta dīnam uddhartum arhasi hare puruṣottamo 'si 094.113
itthaṃ tena naravyāghra stuto bhaktimatā tataḥ
saṃsārabandhabhītena kṛṣṇaḥ pratyakṣatāṃ yayau 094.114
sa taṃ pratyakṣam īśānam anantam aparājitam
devadevam uvācedam anādinidhanaṃ harim 094.115
śirasā dharaṇīṃ gatvā yatavākkāyamānasaḥ
parāpareśvaraṃ viṣṇuṃ jiṣṇum ādyam anopamam 094.116
divyākṣarapadānanta prasanno bhagavān yadi
tad deva dehi dīnāya mahyam ekam imaṃ varam 094.117
varaṃ varaya mattas tvaṃ yat te manasi vartate
varārthināṃ dvijaśreṣṭha nāphalaṃ mama darśanam 094.118
janmasaṃpaccitā deva pāpasaṃpan mamākhilā
prayātu nāśam īśeśa tvatprasādād adhokṣaja 094.119
bhaktibhāvapareṇādya manmayena dvijottama
yaḥ stuto 'smi kṣayaṃ pāpaṃ tenaivākhilam āgatam 094.120
asmatto varayehādya dvijavaryāparaṃ varam
mayi bhaktimatām atra loke kiṃcin na durlabham 094.121
dhanyo 'smi sarvanāthena yatkṛto mayy anugrahaḥ
tad ekam eva tvatto 'haṃ varam icchāmi keśava 094.122
nirdhūtasarvapāpebhyo nātha puṇyakṣayān mama
tvatparasyāstu govinda mā punar dehasaṃbhavaḥ 094.123
yad akṣaraṃ yad acalaṃ vyāpi sūkṣmaṃ ca yat param
viśeṣāir aviśeṣaṃ ca gaccheyaṃ tat padaṃ tava 094.124
evaṃ bhaviṣyatīty uktvā prasādasumukhas tataḥ
bhūpāla taṃ dvijaśreṣṭhaṃ gato 'ntardhānam īśvaraḥ 094.125
tatprasādād dvijaḥ so 'pi tanmayas tadvyapāśrayaḥ
prakṣīṇakarmabandhas tu prayātaḥ paramaṃ padam 094.126
evam akṣīṇapāpo 'pi jagatām īśvareśvaram
vyapāśrito hariṃ yāti pāpamuktaḥ paraṃ padam 094.127
etat tvayā nāvratine na cāśuśrūṣave param
ākhyeyaṃ rājaśārdūla yaś ca nārcayate harim 094.128
viṣṇubhaktāya dāntāya vratine puṇyaśīline
kathanīyam idaṃ bhūpa rahasyaṃ paramaṃ hareḥ 094.129
bahuśo bhavatā proktaṃ sāṃprataṃ ca yad īritam
śrotum icchāmi viprendra tad viṣṇoḥ paramaṃ padam 095.001
yatsvarūpaṃ yadādhāraṃ yatpramāṇaṃ yadātmakam
sarvadhātuḥ padaṃ tan me śrotum icchā pravartate 095.002
sādhv etad bhavatā pṛṣṭaṃ pṛṣṭam ātmajñānasamāśritam
tat kathyamānam ekāgraḥ śṛṇu viṣṇoḥ paraṃ padam 095.003
yat tad brahma yataḥ sarvaṃ yad sarvaṃ sarvasaṃsthitiḥ
agrāhyakam anirdeśyaṃ tad eva bhagavatpadam 095.004
tatsvarūpaṃ ca rājendra śṛṇuṣveha samāhitaḥ
viṣṇoḥ padasyāvyayasya brahmaṇo gadato mama 095.005
pradhānādiviśeṣāntaṃ yad etat paṭhyate jagat
carācarasya tasyādyaṃ paraṃ brahma vilakṣaṇam 095.006
janmasvapnādirūpādi- duḥkhādirahitaṃ ca yat
nopacaryam anirdeśyaṃ svapratiṣṭhaṃ ca tat param 095.007
kṣīṇakleśās tu saṃsāra- vimuktipatham āśritāḥ
yoginas tat prapaśyanti samarthā naiva coditum 095.008
tat sarvaṃ sarvabhāvasthaṃ viśeṣeṇa vivarjitam
paśyatām apy anirdeśyaṃ yato vāgviṣaye na tat 095.009
kurvanty ālambanatvena yatprāptyarthaṃ ca devatāḥ
brahma prakāśate teṣāṃ tad vareṇaiva sarvagam 095.010
pradhānādiviśeṣāntaṃ yatraitad akhilaṃ jagat
tasyānantasya kaḥ śaktaḥ pramāṇaṃ gadituṃ naraḥ 095.011
sūkṣmāṇāṃ tat paraṃ sūkṣmaṃ sthūlānāṃ tan mahattaram
sarvavyāpy api rājendra dūrasthaṃ cāntike ca tat 095.012
parāṅmukhānāṃ govinde viṣayākrāntacetasām
teṣāṃ tat paramaṃ brahma dūrād dūratare sthitam 095.013
na prāpnuvanti gacchanto yato janmāyutair api
saṃsārādhvani rājendra tato dūratare hi tat 095.014
tanmayatvena govinde ya narā nyastacetasaḥ
viṣayatyāginas teṣāṃ vijñeyaṃ ca tadantike 095.015
sarvataḥ pāṇipādāntaṃ sarvato 'kṣiśiromukham
sarvataḥ śrutimal loke sarvam āvṛtya tiṣṭhati 095.016
sarvendriyagunābhāsaṃ sarvendriyavivarjitam
asaktaṃ sarvabhṛc cainan nirguṇaṃ guṇabhoktṛ ca 095.017
avibhaktaṃ ca bhūteṣu vibhaktam iva ca sthitam
bhūtabhartṛ ca taj jñeyaṃ grasiṣṇu prabhaviṣṇu ca 095.018
jyotiṣām api taj jyotis tamasaḥ param ucyate
jñānaṃ jñeyaṃ jñānagamyaṃ hṛdi sarvasy adhiṣṭhitam 095.019
tac cādyo jagatām īśaḥ pareśaḥ parameśvaraḥ
parāparasvarūpeṇa viṣṇuḥ sarvahṛdi sthitaḥ 095.020
yajñeśaṃ yajñapuruṣaṃ kecid icchanti tatparam
kecid viṣṇuṃ hariṃ kecit kecit keśavasaṃjñitam 095.021
kecid govindanāmānaṃ puṇḍarīkākṣam acyutam
kecij janārdanaṃ tv anye vadanti puruṣottamam 095.022
kecid viriñciṃ brāhmaṇam abjayoniṃ tathāpare
śarvam īśam ajaṃ rudraṃ śūlinaṃ cāpare nṛpa 095.023
varuṇaṃ kecid ādityam indram agnim athāpare
yamaṃ dhaneśam apare somam anye prajāpatim 095.024
hiraṇyagarbhaṃ kapilaṃ kṣetrajñaṃ kālam īśvaram
svabhāvam antarātmānam ātmānaṃ buddhirūpiṇam
vadanti nāmabhiś cānyair anāmānam arūpiṇam 095.025
śrūyatāṃ tu naravyāghra vedavedāntaniścayaḥ
yajñeśo yajñapuruṣo puṇḍarīkākṣasaṃjñitaḥ 095.026
tad viṣṇoḥ paramaṃ brahma yato nāvartate punaḥ
sa eva rudraś candro 'gniḥ sūryo vaiśravaṇo yamaḥ 095.027
brahmā prajāpatiḥ kālaḥ svabhāvo buddhir eva ca
kṣetrajñākhyas tathaivānyāḥ saṃjñābhiḥ procyate budhaiḥ 095.028
saṃjñā tu tasya naivāsti na rūpaṃ nāpi kalpanā
sa sarvabhūtānugataḥ paramātmā sanātanaḥ 095.029
ākhyātaṃ bhavatā brahmann etad brahma sanātanam
yasmād utpadyate kṛtsnaṃ jagad etac carācaram 096.001
kiṃtu kautukam atrāsti mama bhārgavanandana
tad ahaṃ śrotum icchāmi tvattaḥ saṃdeham uttamam 096.002
yad etad bhavatākhyātaṃ brahma brahmavidāṃ vara
pariṇāmo na tasyāsti nirguṇaṃ sarvagaṃ yataḥ 096.003
sanātanāt sarvagatāt pariṇāmavivarjitāt
kathaṃ saṃjāyate kṛtsnaṃ tasmād apaguṇād api 096.004
dvividhaṃ kāraṇaṃ bhūpa nibodha gadato mama
nimittakāraṇaṃ pūrvaṃ dvitīyaṃ pariṇāmi ca 096.005
yathā kumbhasya karaṇe kulālaḥ prathamaṃ nṛpa
kāraṇaṃ pariṇāmākhyaṃ mṛddravyam aparaṃ smṛtam 096.006
dharmādharmādayas tadvaj jagatsṛṣṭer mahīpate
kāraṇaṃ pariṇāmākhyaṃ nimittākhyaṃ tu tat param 096.007
kāraṇaṃ kālagagane yathā saṃnidhimātrataḥ
avikāritayā brahma tathā sṛṣṭer nareśvara 096.008
ajñānapaṭalācchanair ekadeśātmavṛttibhiḥ
anātmavedibhir jīvair nijakarmanibandhanaiḥ 096.009
kurvadbhir nṛpate karma kartṛtvam upacārataḥ
kriyate sarvabhūtasya sarvagasyāvyayātmanaḥ 096.010
yataḥ saṃbandhavān ebhir aśeṣaiḥ prāṇibhiḥ prabhuḥ
kartṛtvam upacāreṇa tatas tasyāpi bhūpate 096.011
bhedābhedasvarūpeṇa tatra brahma vyavasthitam
tayoḥ svarūpaṃ nṛpate śrūyatām ubhayor api 096.012
anādisaṃbandhavatyā kṣetrajñaḥ kṣetravidyayā
vyāptaḥ paśyaty abhedena brahma tad dhy ātmani sthitam 096.013
paśyatv ātmānam anyatra yāvad vai paramātmanaḥ
tāvat saṃbhrāmyate jantur mohito nijakarmaṇā 096.014
saṃkṣīnāśeṣakarmā tu paraṃ brahma prapaśyati
abhedenātmanaḥ śuddhaṃ śuddhatvād akṣayo 'kṣayam 096.015
bhedaś ca karmajanitaḥ kṣetrajñaparamātmanoḥ
saṃkṣīṇakarmabandhasya na bhedo brahmaṇā saha 096.016
upāsyopāsyakatayā bhedo yair api kathyate
tau hi śuddhyartham icchanti malānāṃ tad upāsanam
paro 'sāv apareṇātmā saṃtyaktamamatena tu
upāsyate tadā so 'pi tadbhāvaṃ pratipadyate 096.*(147)
karmiṇāṃ karmabhedena bhedād evādayo yataḥ
karmakṣayād aśeṣāṇāṃ bhedānāṃ saṃkṣayas tataḥ 096.017
avidyā tu kriyā sarvā vidyā jñānaṃ pracakṣate
karmaṇā jāyate jantur vidyayā tu vimucyate 096.018
advaitaṃ paramārtho hi dvaitaṃ tadbheda ucyate
ubhayaṃ brahmaṇo rūpaṃ dvaitādvaitavibhedataḥ
tayoḥ svarūpaṃ vadato nibodha mama pārthiva 096.019
devatiryaṅmanuṣyākhyas tathaiva nṛpa tārakaḥ
caturvidho hi bhedo yo mithyājñānanibandhanaḥ 096.020
aham anyo 'paraś cāyam amī cātra tathāpare
vijñānam etat tad dvaitaṃ yad anyac chrūyatāṃ param 096.021
mametyahamitiprajñā- viyuktam avikalpavat
avikāram anākhyeyam advaitam api bhūpate 096.022
abhedena tavākhyātaṃ yad etad brahma śāśvatam
jñānajñeyaikyasadbhāvaṃ tad evādvaitasaṃjñitam 096.023
yaś ca dvaite prapañcaḥ syān nivartyobhayacetasaḥ
manovṛttimayaṃ dvaitam advaitaṃ paramārthataḥ 096.024
manaso vṛttayas tasmād dharmādharmanimittajāḥ
nirodhavyās tannirodhād dvaitaṃ naivopapadyate 096.025
manodṛśyam idaṃ dvaitaṃ yat kiṃcit sacarācaram
manaso hy amatībhāve dvaitābhāvāt tad āpnuyāt 096.026
mano hi viṣayaṃ yadvad ādatte tadvad eva tat
bhavaty apāstaviṣayaṃ grāhidharme ca jāyate 096.027
agrāhi tac ca vidhṛtaṃ yogināṃ viṣayaṃ prati
nirodhe yogasāmarthyād brahmagrāhy eva jāyate 096.028
grāhyaṃ ca paramaṃ brahma yogicittasya pārthiva
samujjhitagrāhyavṛttir amalasya malaṃ mahat 096.029
kṣīṇakleśās tu saṃsāra- vimuktipatham āśritāḥ
yoginas taṃ prapaśyanti samarthā naiva coditum 096.030
ye 'pi karmāṇi kurvanti bhagavantam apāśritāḥ
kriyāyogaparā rājan kāmākāṅkṣāvivarjitāḥ
brahmaniṣṭhā dhyānaparā brahmaṇy eva vyavasthitāḥ
te 'pi tadbhāvam āyānti vimuktipatham āśritāḥ 096.*(148)
karmaṇo bhāvanā yeyaṃ sā brahmaparipanthinī
karmabhāvanayā tulyaṃ vijñānam upapadyate 096.031
tādṛg bhavato vijñaptir yādṛśī karmabhāvanā
kṣaye tasyāḥ paraṃ brahma svayam eva prakāśate 096.032
evam etan mayā bhūpa yathāvat kathitaṃ tava
dvaitādvaitasvarūpeṇa yathā brahma vyavasthitam 096.033
yathāvat karmaniṣṭhānāṃ tatprāptiḥ kathitaṃ tathā 096.*(149)
svarūpaṃ brahmaṇaś coktam ubhayatrāpi te pṛthak
vāsudevamayasyānyat kiṃ bhūyaḥ kathayāmi te 096.034
ākhyātaṃ bhagavan samyak paraṃ brahma tvayā mama
viṣṇur eva jagaddhātā yogināṃ vartate yataḥ 097.001
upāyas tasya yaḥ prāpto viṣṇor īśasya bhārgava
advaitadvaitarūpasya tan me vistarato vada 097.002
yena janmajarāmṛtyu- mahāgrāhabhavārṇavam
tvadvākyanāvam āruhya muktitīram avāpnuyām 097.003
tan mama brūhi tattvena prāpnuyāṃ yena tat padam 097.*(150)
bandhaḥ karmamayo hy atra yathāmuktivighātakṛt
tasyāpagamane yatnaḥ kāryaḥ saṃsārabhīruṇā 097.004
suvarṇādimahādāna- puṇyatīrthāvagāhanaiḥ
śārīraiś ca tathā kleśaiḥ śāstroktais tacchamo bhavet 097.005
devatāstutisacchāstra- śravaṇaiḥ puṇyadarśanaiḥ
guruśuśrūṣaṇāc caiva pāpabandhaḥ praṇaśyati 097.006
prapākūpataḍāgāni devatāyatanāni ca
kārayan puruṣavyāghra pāpabandhāt pramucyate 097.007
yoginām atha śuśrūṣāṃ tathaivāvasathān nṛpa
kurvan pūrtāśritaṃ cānyat pāpabandhāt pramucyate 097.008
viṣṇuḥ kṛṣṇo vāsudevo govindaḥ puṣkarekṣaṇaḥ
ityādi vyāharan nityaṃ pāpabandhāt pramucyate 097.009
viśvo viśveśvaro viśva- vidhātā dhāma śāśvatam
viṣṇur ityādi ca japan pāpabandhāt pramucyate 097.010
padmanābho hṛṣīkeśaḥ keśavo madhusūdanaḥ
ityādi vyāharan nityaṃ pāpabandhāt pramucyate 097.011
nārāyaṇaś cakradharo viśvarūpas trivikramaḥ
ityādi vyāharan nityaṃ pāpabandhāt pramucyate 097.012
viṣṇau pratiṣṭhitaṃ viśvaṃ viṣṇur viśve pratiṣṭhitaḥ
viṣṇur viśveśvaro viśvam iti bhāvāt pramucyate 097.013
evaṃ saṃśāntapāpasya puṇyavṛddhimato nṛpa
icchā pravartate pūṃso muktidāyiṣu karmasu 097.014
muktidāyīni karmāṇi niṣkāmena kṛtāni tu
bhavanti doṣakṣayakāḥ puṇyabandhāt pramucyate 097.*(151)
nityanaimittikānīha karmāṇy uktāni yāni vai
teṣāṃ niṣkāmakāraṇāt puṇyabandhaḥ praśāmyati 097.015
anekajanmasaṃsāra- citasyāpi dṛḍhātmanaḥ
karmabandhasya śaithilya- kāraṇaṃ cāparaṃ śṛṇu 097.016
ahiṃsā nātimānitvam adambhitvam amatsaram
titikṣā samadarśitvaṃ maitryādau daṇḍasaṃyamaḥ 097.017
ṛjutvam indriyajayaḥ śaucam ācāryapūjanam
puṇyastavādipaṭhanam apaiśunyam akatthanam 097.018
viṣayān prati vairāgyam anahaṃkāram eva ca
akāmitvaṃ manaḥsthairyam adrohaḥ sarvajantuṣu 097.019
avivādas tathā mūḍhair amūḍhaiḥ praśnasatkathā
viviktadeśe 'bhiratir mahājanavivarjanam 097.020
sadbhiḥ sahāsya satataṃ yogābhyāso mitoktitā
strībhartsotsavasaṃlāpa- vivarjanam avekṣaṇam 097.021
parayoṣidvilāsānāṃ kāvyālāpavivarjanam
gītavāditanṛtteṣu mṛdaṅgeṣv apareṣu ca 097.022
asaktir manaso maunam ātmatattvāvalokanam
tapaḥ saṃtoṣaḥ satyeṣu sthitir lobhavivarjanam 097.023
tathā parigraho rājan māyāvyājavivarjanam
asṛṅmāṃsādibhūtatvān nijadehajugupsanam 097.024
sarvāṇy etāni bhūtāni viṣṇur ity acalā matiḥ
tatraivāśeṣabhūteśe bhaktir avyabhicāriṇī 097.025
ete guṇā mayākhyātā manonirvṛtikārakāḥ
śaithilyahetavaś caite karmabandhasya pūrthiva 097.026
ebhiḥ śāntiṃ gate citte dhyānākṛṣṭaḥ sthito hariḥ
śamaṃ nayati karmāṇi sitamiśrāsitāni vai 097.027
bhūyaś ca śṛṇu śāstrārthaṃ saṃkṣepād vadato mama
yathā saṃprāpyate muktir manujendra mumukṣubhiḥ 097.028
nityanaimittikānāṃ tu niṣkāmasya hi yā kriyā
nisiddhānāṃ sakāmānāṃ tathaivākaraṇaṃ nṛpa 097.029
sarveśvare ca govinde bhaktir avyabhicāriṇī
prayacchati nṛṇāṃ muktiṃ mā te bhūd atra saṃśayaḥ 097.030
ākhyātam etad akhilaṃ yat pṛṣṭo 'si mayā dvija
jāyate śamakāmānāṃ praśamaḥ karmaṇāṃ yathā 098.001
kiṃtv atra bhavatā proktā praśāntiḥ sarvakarmaṇām
nātyantanāśaḥ śāntānām udbhavo bhavitā punaḥ
nijakāraṇam āsādya stokasyāgner yathā tṛṇam 098.002
tad ācakṣva mahābhāga prasādasumukho mama
saṃkṣayo yena bhavati mūlodvartena karmaṇām 098.003
na karmaṇāṃ kṣayo bhūpa janmanām ayutair api
karmakṣayam ṛte yogād yogāgniḥ kṣapayet param 098.004
taṃ yogaṃ mama viprarṣe praṇatasyābhiyācataḥ
tvam ācakṣva kṣayo yena jāyate 'khilakarmaṇām 098.005
hiraṇyagarbho bhagavān anādir munibhiḥ purā
pṛṣṭaḥ provāca yaṃ yogaṃ taṃ samāsena me śṛṇu 098.006
anādikālaprasṛtā yathā vidyā mahīpate
tathā tatkṣayahetutvād yogo vidyāmayo 'vyayaḥ 098.007
taṃ paraṃparayā śrutvā munayo 'tra dayālavaḥ
prakāśayanti bhūtānām upakāracikīrṣavaḥ 098.008
devā maharṣayo rājaṃs tathā rājarṣayo 'khilāḥ
śreyo'rthinaḥ purā jagmuḥ śaraṇaṃ kapilaṃ kila 098.009
te tam ūcur bhavān nityaṃ dayāluḥ sarvajantuṣu
so 'smān uddhara saṃmagnān itaḥ saṃsārakardamāt 098.010
yac chreyaḥ sarvavarṇānāṃ strīṇām apy upakārakam
yasmāt parataraṃ nānyac śreyas tad brūhi naḥ prabho 098.011
ādāv ante ca madhye ca nR̥ṇāṃ yad upakārakam
api kīṭapataṃgānāṃ tan naḥ śreyaḥ paraṃ vada 098.012
ity uktaḥ kapilaḥ sarvair devair devarṣibhis tathā
nāsti yogāt paraṃ śreyaḥ kiṃcid ity uktavān purā 098.013
yathā janmāyutaiḥ kleśāḥ sthairyaṃ cetasy upāgatāḥ
tacchāntaye tathā yogo bahujanmārjito bhavet 098.014
sa evābhyasatāṃ nR̥ṇāṃ tīvrasaṃvegicetasām
āsannatāṃ prayāty āśu viṣṇuḥ saṃnyastakarmaṇām 098.015
brāhmaṇakṣatriyaviśāṃ strīśūdrasya ca pāvanam
śāntaye karmaṇāṃ nānyad yogād asti hi muktaye 098.016
abhyastaṃ janmabhir naikaiḥ śubhajātibhaveṣu yat
yogasvarūpaṃ tat teṣāṃ strīśūdratve vyavasthitam 098.017
yogābhyāso nṛṇāṃ yeṣāṃ nāsti janmāntarāhṛtaḥ
yogasya prāptaye teṣāṃ śūdravaiśyādikaḥ kramaḥ 098.018
strītvāc chūdratvam abhyeti tato vaiśyatvam āpnuyāt
tataś ca kṣatriyo vipraḥ kriyāhīnas tato bhavet 098.019
anūcānas tathā yajvī karmanyāsī tataḥ param
tato jñānitvam abhyetya yogī muktiṃ kramāl labhet 098.020
yeṣāṃ tu jātimātreṇa yogābhyāsas tirohitaḥ
āste tatraiva mucyante jātihetau kṣayaṃgate 098.021
asatkarma kṛtaṃ pūrvam asajjātipradāyi yat
tasmin yogāgninā dagdhe tasya jāter balaṃ kutaḥ 098.022
yathā vāteritaḥ kakṣaṃ dahaty ūrdhvaśikho 'nalaḥ
sarvakarmāṇi yogāgnir bhasmasāt kurute tathā 098.023
yathā dagdhatuṣaṃ bījam abījatvān na jāyate
yogadagdhais tathā kleśair nātmā saṃjāyate punaḥ 098.024
adṛṣṭā dṛṣṭatattvānāṃ yogināṃ yogavicyutiḥ
yeṣāṃ bhavati yogitvaṃ prāpnuvantīha te punaḥ 098.025
sajjātiprāpakaṃ karma kṛtaṃ tena tadātmanā
jātiṃ prayānti viprādyā yogakarmānurañjitāḥ 098.026
tatrāpy anekajanmottha- yogābhyāsānurañjitāḥ
tenaivābhyāsayogena hriyante tattvavidyayā 098.027
jaigīṣavyo yathā vipro yathā caivāsitādayaḥ
hiraṇyanābho rājanyas tathā vai janakādayaḥ 098.028
pūrvābhyastena yogena tulādhārādayo viśaḥ
saṃprāptāḥ paramāṃ siddhiṃ śūdrāḥ pailavakādayaḥ 098.029
maitreyī sulabhā gārgī śāṇḍilī ca tapasvinī
strītve prāptāḥ parāṃ siddhim anyajanmasamādhitaḥ 098.030
dharmavyādhādayo 'py anye pūrvābhyāsāj jugupsite
varṇāvaratve saṃprāptāḥ saṃsiddhiṃ śravaṇī tathā 098.031
pūrvābhyastaṃ ca tat teṣāṃ yogajñānaṃ mahātmanām
suptotthitapratyayavad upadeśādinā vinā 098.032
tasmād yogaḥ paraṃ śreyo vimuktiphalado hi yaḥ
vimuktau sukham atyantaṃ saṃmohas tv itarat sukham 098.033
etat te sarvam ākhyātaṃ mayā manujakuñjara
śreyaḥ parataraṃ yogāt kiṃcid anyan na vidyate 098.034
kathitaṃ yogamāhātmyaṃ bhavatā munisattama
svarūpaṃ tu na me proktaṃ śrotum icchāmi tad dhy aham 099.001
dvaividhyaṃ nṛpa yogasya paraṃ cāparam eva ca
tac chṛṇuṣva vadāmy eṣa vācyaṃ śuśrūṣatāṃ satām 099.002
yo dadyād bhagavajjñānaṃ kuryād vā dharmadeśanām
kṛtsnāṃ vā pṛthivīṃ dadyān na tattulyaṃ kathaṃcana 099.003
kṣayiṣṇūny aparāṇīha dānāni manujādhipa
ekam evākṣayaṃ śastaṃ jñānadānam anuttamam 099.004
dānāny ekaphalānīha trailokye dadatā satām
jñānaṃ prayacchatā samyak kiṃ na dattaṃ bhaven nṛpa 099.005
jñānāny anyāny asārāṇi śilpinīva nareśvara
ekam eva paraṃ jñānaṃ yad yogaprāptikārakam 099.006
ahaṃ vaktā bhavāñ śrotā vācyo yogo vimuktidaḥ
prāṇinām upakārāya saṃpad eṣā guṇādhikā 099.007
pareṇa brahmaṇā sārdham ekatvaṃ yan nṛpātmanaḥ
sa eva yogo vikhyātaḥ kim anyad yogalakṣaṇam 099.008
aparaṃ ca paraṃ caiva dvau yogau pṛthivīpate
tayoḥ svarūpaṃ vakṣyāmi tad ihaikamanāḥ śṛṇu 099.009
sattāmātraṃ paraṃ brahma viṣṇvākhyam aviśeṣaṇam
durvicintyaṃ yataḥ pūrvaṃ tatprāptyartham athocyate 099.010
vātālīcañcalaṃ cittam anālambanam asthiti
sūkṣmatvād brahmaṇo rājann agrāhy agrāhyadharmiṇaḥ 099.011
samyag abhyasyato 'jasram upavṛṃhitaśaktimat
janmāntaraśatair vāpi brahmagrāhy abhijāyate 099.012
yady antarāya doṣeṇa nāpakarṣo narādhipa
yogino yogarūḍhasya tālāgrāt patanaṃ yathā 099.013
jñānaṃ prayacchatāṃ samyak kiṃ vadatu bhaven nṛpa 099.*(152)
tad āpnoti paraṃ brahma kleśena mahatā nṛpa
janmābhyāsāntarotthena vijñānena samedhitaḥ 099.014
viṣṇvākhyaṃ brahma duṣprāpaṃ viṣayākṛṣṭacetasā
manuṣyeṇeti tatprāptāv upāyam aparaṃ śṛṇu 099.015
surūpāṃ pratimāṃ viṣṇoḥ prasannavadanekṣaṇām
kṛtvātmanaḥ prītikarīṃ suvarṇarajatādibhiḥ 099.016
tasyāś ca lakṣaṇaṃ bhūpa śṛṇuṣva gadato mama
yaddravyā yatsvarūpā ca kartavyā dhyānakarmaṇi 099.017
suvarṇarūpyatāmrais tu ārakūṭamayīṃ tathā
śailadārumṛdā vāpi lekhyajāṃ vāpi kārayet 099.018
kāryas tu viṣṇur bhagavān saumyarūpaś caturbhujaḥ
salilādhmātameghābhaḥ śrīmāñ śrīvatsabhūṣitaḥ 099.019
ābaddhamakuṭaḥ sragvī hārabhārārpitodaraḥ
svakṣeṇa cārucipukaḥ sulalāṭena subhruṇā 099.020
svoṣṭhena sukapolena vadanena virājatā
kaṇṭhena śubhalekhena varābharaṇadhāriṇā 099.021
nānāratnānatārtābhyāṃ śravaṇābhyām alaṃkṛtaḥ
puṣṭaśliṣṭāyatabhujas tanutāmranakhāṅguliḥ 099.022
madhyena trivalībhaṅga- bhūṣitena ca cāruṇā
supādaḥ sūruyugalaḥ sukaṭīgulphajānukaḥ 099.023
vāmapārśve gadādevī cakraṃ devasya dakṣiṇe
śaṅkho vāmakare deyo dakṣiṇe padma suprabham 099.024
ūrdhvadṛṣṭim adhodṛṣṭiṃ tiryagdṛṣṭiṃ na kārayet
nimīlitākṣo bhagavān na praśasto janārdanaḥ
saumyā tu dṛṣṭiḥ kartavyā kiṃcit prahasiteva ca 099.025
kāryaś caraṇavinyāsaḥ sarvataḥ supratiṣṭhitaḥ
caraṇāntarasaṃsthā ca bibhratī rūpam uttamam
kāryā vasuṃdharā devī tatpādataladhāriṇī 099.026
yādṛgvidhā vā manasaḥ sthairyalambhopapādikā
nṛsiṃhavāmanādīnāṃ tādṛśīṃ kārayed budhaḥ 099.027
brahma tasyāṃ samāropya manasā tanmayo bhavet
tām ārcayet tāṃ praṇamet tāṃ smaret tāṃ vicintayet 099.028
tām arcayaṃs tāṃ praṇamaṃs tāṃ smaraṃs tāṃ ca cintayan
viśaty apāstadoṣas tu tām eva brahmarūpiṇīm 099.029
saṃkalpanakriyārūḍhaḥ svarūpeṇa nṛpātmanaḥ
kurvīta bhāvanāṃ tatra tadbhāvotpattikāraṇāt
nānyatra manasāneyā buddhir īṣad api kvacit 099.030
yamaiś ca niyamaiś caiva pūtātmā pṛthivīśvara
mūrtiṃ bhagavataḥ saṃyak pūjayet tanmayaḥ sadā 099.031
yamāṃś ca niyamāṃś caiva śrotum icchāmi bhārgava
yair dhūtakalmaṣo yogī muktibhāg upajāyate 100.001
ahiṃsā satyam asteyaṃ brahmacaryāparigrahau
yamās tavaite kathitā niyamān api me śṛṇu 100.002
saṃtoṣaśaucasvādhyāyās tapaś ceśvarabhāvanā
niyamāḥ kauravaśreṣṭha yogasaṃsiddhihetavaḥ 100.003
ebhir mūlaguṇaiḥ sadbhir viṣṇor bhaktimatas tathā
śraddadhānasya cānyāni yogāṅgāni nibodha me 100.004
madhyamaprāṇam acalaṃ sukhadāyi śubhaṃ śuci
yogasaṃsiddhaye bhūpa yoginām āsanaṃ smṛtam 100.005
prāṇāyāmas tridhā vāyoḥ prāṇasya hṛdi dhāraṇam
kumbharecakapūrākhyās tasya bhedās trayo nṛpa 100.006
ete nibodha mātrās tu nālambanaguṇānvitāḥ
sālambanaś caturtho 'nyo bāhyāntarviṣayaḥ smṛtaḥ 100.007
indriyāṇāṃ svaviṣayād buddhiḥ pratyekaśas tu yat
karoty āharaṇaṃ jñeyaḥ pratyāhāraḥ sa paṇḍitaiḥ 100.008
śubhe hy ekatra viṣaye cetaso yac ca dhāraṇam
niścalatvāt tu sā sadbhir dhāraṇety abhidhīyate 100.009
paunaḥpunyena tatraiva viṣaye saiva dhāraṇā
dhyānākhyā labhate rājan samādhim api me śṛṇu 100.010
arthamātraṃ ca yad grāhye cittam ādāya pārthiva
arthasvarūpavad bhāti samādhiḥ so 'bhidhīyate 100.011
kathitāni tavaitāni yogāṅgāni kṛtais tu yaiḥ
utkarṣo jāyate vyastaiḥ samastair heyasaṃkṣayaḥ 100.012
yogāṅgāny aṅgabhūtāni dhyānasyaitāny aśeṣataḥ
dhyānam apy avanīpāla yogasyāṅgatvam archati 100.013
dhyānam ekavratānāṃ tu kuśalākuśaleṣu tat
artheṣv āśaktim abhyeti sarvadaiva nareśvara 100.014
śubhāvyāvartitaṃ dhyānam avivekasya jāyate
saṃsāraduḥkhadaṃ rājann aśubhālambi tad yataḥ 100.015
tad evākṛṣya duṣṭebhyo viṣayebhyaḥ śubhāśubham
sarvasaṃsārakāntāra- pāram abhyeti mānavaḥ 100.016
duḥkhadāghapraśamane yā cintāharniśaṃ nṛṇām
taddhyānam aviśuddhārthaṃ sukhadānām apālane 100.017
kathaṃ saṃsārabandho 'yam asmān muktiḥ kathaṃ tv iti
manovṛttir manuṣyāṇāṃ dhyānam etac chubhaṃ dvidhā 100.018
śuddham apy etad akhilaṃ lobhakāryatayānayā
sukhābhilāṣo yanmuktau bandhuduḥkhādipīḍanāt 100.019
avāñchitaphalaṃ lobham alobhāṃśavivarjitam
śubhāśubhaphalaṃ dhyānam araktaṃ dviṣṭam iṣyate 100.020
dṛṣṭānumānāgamikaṃ dhyānasyālambanaṃ tridhā
na hi nirviṣayaṃ dhyānaṃ mūḍhavṛttir iveṣyate 100.021
prāk sthūleṣu padārtheṣu tataḥ sūkṣmeṣu paṇḍitaḥ
dhyānaṃ kurvīta tatpaścāt paramāṇau mahīpate 100.022
dhyānābhyāsaparasyaivaṃ heyālambanabādhane
tacchāntaye tadvipakṣa- bhāvanām eva bhāvayet 100.023
taccittas tanmayo jñānī bhavaty asmān na doṣavat
kurvītālambanaṃ kāle kasmiṃścid api pārthiva 100.024
ābrahmastambaparyanta- jagadantarvyavasthitāḥ
prāṇinaḥ karmajanita- saṃskāravaśavartinaḥ 100.025
yatas tato na te dhyāne dhyāninām upakārakāḥ
avidyāntargatāḥ sarve te hi saṃsāragocarāḥ 100.026
paścād udbhūtabodhāś ca dhyātā naivopakārakāḥ
naisargiko na vai bodhas teṣām apy anyato yataḥ 100.027
tasmāt tad amalaṃ brahma nisargād eva bodhavat
dhyeyaṃ dhyānavidāṃ samyag yad viṣṇoḥ paramaṃ padam 100.028
na tad yajñair na dānena na tapobhir na tad vrataiḥ
paśyanty ekāgramanaso dhyānenaiva sanātanam 100.029
tac ca viṣṇoḥ paraṃ rūpam anirdeśyam ajaṃ sthiram
yataḥ pravartate sarvaṃ layam abhyeti yatra ca 100.030
anidram ajam asvapnam arūpānāma śāśvatam
yoginas taṃ prapaśyanti jñānadṛśyaṃ sanātanam 100.031
nirdhūtapuṇyapāpā ye te viśanty evam īśvaram 100.*(153)
tac ca sarvagataṃ brahma viṣṇuḥ sarveśvareśvaraḥ
paramātmā paraḥ proktaḥ sarvakāraṇakāraṇam 100.032
anantaśaktim īśeśaṃ svapratiṣṭham anopamam
yoginas taṃ prapaśyanti bhagavantaṃ sanātanam 100.033
yatra sarvaṃ yataḥ sarvaṃ yaḥ sarvaṃ sarvataś ca yaḥ
yoginas taṃ prapaśyanti bhagavantaṃ sanātanam 100.034
sargādikāraṇaṃ yasya svabhāvād eva śaktayaḥ
yoginas taṃ prapaśyanti bhagavantaṃ sanātanam 100.035
nirdhūtapuṇyapāpā yaṃ viśanty avyayam īśvaram
yoginas taṃ prapaśyanti bhagavantaṃ sanātanam 100.036
tatra yogavataḥ samyak puruṣasya nareśvara
yad uktaṃ lakṣaṇaṃ tan me gadataḥ śrotum arhasi 100.037
brahmaṇy eva sthitaṃ cittaṃ sarvataḥ saṃnivartitam
nānyālambanasāpekṣaṃ yoginaḥ siddhikārakam 100.038
saṃsthānam avikāreṇa cetaso brahmasaṃsthitau
nivāta iva dīpasya yoginaḥ siddhilakṣaṇam 100.039
evam ekāgracittasya puṇyāpuṇyam aśeṣataḥ
prayāti saṃkṣayam ṛte dehārambhakare nṛpa 100.040
dehārambhakarasyāpi karmaṇaḥ saṃkṣayāvahaḥ
yo yogaḥ pṛthivīpāla śṛṇu tasyāpi lakṣaṇam 100.041
yat tad brahma paraṃ proktaṃ viṣṇvākhyam ajam avyayam
cetasaḥ pralayas tatra yoga ity abhidhīyate 100.042
yogasevānirodhena pralīne tatra cetasi
puruṣaḥ kāranābhāvād bhedaṃ naivānupaśyati 100.043
parātmanor manuṣyendra vibhāgo jñānakalpitaḥ
kṣaye tasyātmaparayor vibhāgābhāga eva hi 100.044
paramātmātmanor yo 'yam avibhāgaḥ paraṃtapa
sa eva paramo yogaḥ samāsāt kathitas tava 100.045
yathā kamaṇḍalau bhinne tattoyaṃ salile gatam
vrajaty aikyaṃ tathaivaitad ubhayaṃ kāraṇakṣayāt 100.046
yathāgnir agnau saṃkṣiptaḥ samānatvam anuvrajet
tadākhyas tanmayo bhūtvā gṛhyate na viśeṣataḥ 100.047
evaṃ brahmātmanor yogād akatvam upapannayoḥ
na bhedaḥ kalaśākāśa- nabhasor iva jāyate 100.048
prakṣīṇāśeṣakarmā tu yadā brahmamayaḥ pumān
tadā svarūpam asyokter gocare nopapadyate 100.049
ghaṭadhvaṃse ghaṭākāśaṃ na bhinnaṃ nabhaso yathā
brahmaṇā heyavidhvaṃse viṣṇvākhyena pumāṃs tathā 100.050
bhinne dṛtau yathā vāyur naivānyaḥ saha vāyunā
kṣīṇapuṇyāghabandhas tu tathātmā brahmaṇā saha 100.051
tataḥ samastakalyāṇa- samastasukhasaṃpadām
āhlādam anyam atulaṃ kam apy āpnoti śāśvatam 100.052
brahmasvarūpasya tadā hy ātmano nityadaiva saḥ
vyuttānakāle rājendra āste heyatirohitaḥ 100.053
ādarśasya malābhāvād vaimalyaṃ kāśate yathā
jñānāgnidagdhaheyasya so 'hlādo hy ātmanas tathā 100.054
yathā na kriyate jyotsnā malaprakṣālanādinā
doṣaprahāṇaṃ na jñānam ātmanaḥ kriyate tathā 100.055
yathodupānakaraṇāt kriyate na jalāmbaram
sadaiva nīyate vyaktim asataḥ saṃbhavaḥ kutaḥ 100.056
yathā heyagaṇadhvaṃsād avabodhādayo guṇāḥ
prakāśyante na janyante nityā evātmano hite 100.057
jñānavairāgyam aiśvaryaṃ dharmaś ca manujeśvara
ātmano brahmabhūtasya nityam eva catuṣṭayam 100.058
etad advaitam ākhyātam eṣa yogas tavoditaḥ
ayaṃ viṣṇur idaṃ brahma tathaitat satyam uttamam 100.059
punaś ca śrūyatām eṣa saṃkṣepād gadato mama
nānādvaikatvavijñāna- svarūpam avanīpate 100.060
ātmā kṣetrajñasaṃjño 'yaṃ saṃyuktaḥ prākṛtair guṇaiḥ
tair eva vigataiḥ śuddhaḥ paramātmā nigadyate 100.061
dhyeyaṃ brahma pumān dhyātā upāyo dhyānasaṃjñitaḥ
yas tv etat karaṇeṣv āste tadvarge kā vibhāgatā 100.062
saṃkṣepād api bhūpāla saṃkṣepan aparaṃ śṛṇu
putrāya yat pitā brūyāt svaśiṣyāyāthavā guruḥ 100.063
na vāsudevāt param asti kiṃcin na vāsudevād gaditaṃ paraṃ ca
satyaṃ paraṃ vāsudevo 'mitātmā namo namo vāsudevāya nityam 100.064
tasmāt tam ārādhaya cintayeśam abhyarcayānantam atandritātmā
saṃsārapāraṃ param īpsamānair ārādhanīyo harir eka eva 100.065
ārādhito 'rthān dhanakāṅkṣakānāṃ dharmārthināṃ dharmam aśeṣadharmī
dadāti kāmāṃś ca manoniviṣṭān mokṣārthināṃ muktida eva viṣṇuḥ 100.066
mamaitat kathitaṃ samyag ātmavidyāśritaṃ mune
yat tv anyac chrotum icchāmi tat prasanno vadasva me 101.001
yeyaṃ muktir bhagavatā proktā varṇakramān mama
tatrecchāmi mune śrotuṃ varṇād varṇottarocchrayam 101.002
śūdro vaiśyatvam abhyeti kathaṃ vaiśyaś ca bhārgava
kṣatriyatvaṃ dvijaśreṣṭha brāhmaṇatvaṃ kathaṃ tataḥ 101.003
vipratvān muktiyogyatvaṃ yathā yāti mahāmune
tad ahaṃ śrotum icchāmi tvatto bhārgavanandana 101.004
tvadyukto 'yam anupraśnaḥ kuruvarya śṛṇuṣva tam
mayocyamānam akhilaṃ varṇānām upakārakam 101.005
śūdradharmān aśeṣeṇa kurvañ śūdro yathāvidhi
vaiśyatvam eti vaiśyaś ca kṣatriyatvaṃ svakarmakṛt 101.006
vipratvaṃ kṣatriyaḥ samyag dvijadharmaparo nṛpa
vipraś ca muktilābhena yujyate satkriyāparaḥ 101.007
sarveṣām eva varṇānāṃ svadharmam anuvartatām
sadocchritir nyūnakṛto hāniś cotkṛṣṭakarmaṇaḥ 101.008
teṣāṃ ca brāhmaṇādīnāṃ varṇadharmān anukramāt
samucchritipradān rājan gadato me niśāmaya 101.009
anasūyā dayā kṣāntiḥ śaucaṃ maṅgalam aspṛhā
akārpaṇyam anāyāsas tathānyaḥ sārvavarṇikaḥ 101.010
aṣṭāv ete guṇāḥ puṃsāṃ paratreha ca bhūtaye
bhavanti kuruśārdūla pṛthagdharmāṃś ca me śṛṇu 101.011
yajñādhyayanadānāni brahmakṣatraviśāṃ nṛpa
sādhāraṇāni teṣāṃ tu jīvikākarma kathyate 101.012
yājanādhyāpanair vipras tathā śastapratigrahaiḥ
bhṛtyādibharaṇaṃ kuryād yajñāṃś ca vibhave sati 101.013
bhṛtyādibharaṇe nālaṃ svavṛttyā hi yadā dvijaḥ
tadā jīvet samālambya vṛttiṃ kṣatriyavaiśyayoḥ 101.014
saṃtyajeta samastāṃs tān na kuryād vṛttisaṃkaram
āpatkāle 'pi viprasya śūdrakarma na śasyate 101.015
prajānāṃ pālanaṃ samyag vidhiḥ prathamakalpitaḥ
rājanyasya mahīpāla śastrājīvena vā bhṛtiḥ 101.016
tadutpannair dhanaiḥ kuryāt samastāḥ kṣatriyakriyāḥ
tasyāpy āpadi vaiśyasya yā vṛttiḥ sā vidhīyate 101.017
vāṇijyaṃ vaiśyajātasya paśūnāṃ pālanaṃ kṛṣiḥ
dadyād yajec ca vidhivat tadutpannadhanena saḥ 101.018
dvijātijanaśuśrūṣāṃ krayavikrayajair dhanaiḥ
śūdro yajet pākayajñair dadyād iṣṭāni cārthinām 101.019
tasmai śuśrūṣave deyaṃ jīrṇavastram upānahau
chattrādikaṃ tathā kuryāt samyagdharmopapādanam 101.020
caturṇām api varṇānāṃ dharmas te kathito mayā
śṛṇuṣva ca mahīpāla dharmam āśramiṇām ataḥ 101.021
kṛtopanayanaḥ pūrvaṃ brahmacārī guror gṛhe
guruśuśrūṣaṇaṃ kuryād bhaikṣānnakṛtabhojanaḥ 101.022
nivedya gurave bhaikṣam attavyaṃ tadanujñayā
guror bhuktavataḥ paścān nātisvādumudāvatā 101.023
vahniśuśrūṣaṇaṃ kruyād vedāharaṇam eva ca
guror arthe sadā toyaṃ samidāharaṇaṃ tathā 101.024
puṣpādīnāṃ ca kurvīta supte tasmiñ śayīta ca
śayane ca samuttiṣṭhet taṃ vrajantam anuvrajet 101.025
āhūtaś ca paṭhet tena tanmanā nānyatomukhaḥ
vratāni caratā saṃyag grāhyo vedo yatātmanā
daṇḍavatplavanaṃ snāne śastaṃ nāsyāṅgaśodhanam 101.026
adhītya vedān vedau vā vedaṃ vāpi yathākramam
aviplutabrahmacaryo gṛhasthāśramam āvaset 101.027
yatheṣṭāṃ dakṣiṇāṃ dattvā gurave kurunandana
tato 'nujñāṃ samāsādya gṛhasthāśramam āvaset 101.028
tenaivāntaṃ vrajet prājñas tacchuśrūṣaṇatatparaḥ
vānaprasthāśramaṃ tasmāc caturthaṃ vāpi saṃśrayet
yathākramaṃ vā kurvīta vidhivad dārasaṃgraham 101.029
tatas tv arogikulajāṃ tulyāṃ patnīṃ samudvahet
gṛhasthāśramavṛttyartham avyaṅgāṃ vidhinā nṛpa 101.030
ākhyātavarṇadharmeṇa dhanaṃ labdhvā mahīpate
kurvīta śraddhayā yukto nityanaimittikīḥ kriyāḥ 101.031
abhyāgatātithīn bandhūn bhṛtyādīn āturāṃs tathā
toṣayec chaktito 'nnena vayāṃsy antyapaśūn api 101.032
ṛtāv upagamaś caiva gṛhasthasyāpi śabditaḥ
dharmo dharmabhṛtāṃ śreṣṭha yajñocchiṣṭaṃ ca bhojanam 101.033
havyena prīṇayed devān pitṛn kavyena śaktitaḥ
manuṣyān annapānena svādhyāyena rṣitarpaṇam 101.034
kuryāc ca prīṇanaṃ nityaṃ bhūtānāṃ balikarmaṇā
prajāpatiṃ sutotpattyā hārdena sakalaṃ janam 101.035
śubhena karmaṇātmānam upadeśena cātmajān
anujīvijanaṃ vṛtyā gṛhasthas toṣayet sadā 101.036
tathaivāparamānebhyaḥ pradeyaṃ gṛhamedhinā
annaṃ bhikṣārthino ye ca parivrāḍbrahmacāriṇaḥ 101.037
evaṃ gṛhāśrame devāḥ pitaro munayas tathā
sarvakāmān prayacchanti manuṣyāś ca supūjitāḥ 101.038
gṛhasthas tu yadā paśyed valīpalitam ātmanaḥ
apatyasya tathāpatyaṃ tadāraṇyaṃ samāśrayet 101.039
pitṛdevātithīnāṃ tu smṛtaṃ tatrāpi pūjanam
tathaivāraṇyabhogaś ca tapobhiś cātmakarṣaṇam 101.040
brahmacaryaṃ mahīśayyā homas triṣavaṇāplutiḥ
maunādikaraṇaṃ śastaṃ jaṭāvalkaladhāraṇam 101.041
grīṣme pañcatapobhiś ca varṣāsv abhrāvakāśikaiḥ
jalaśayyā ca hemante bhāvyaṃ vananiketanaiḥ 101.042
iṅgudairaṇḍatailena gātrābhyaṅgāni ceṣyate
śyāmākanīvāramayaṃ phalamūlaiś ca bhojanam 101.043
apraveśas tathā grāme vānaprasthavidhiḥ smṛtaḥ
vānaprasthasya te proktaṃ dharmalakṣaṇam āditaḥ 101.044
āśramaṇaṃ tv aparaṃ bhikṣoḥ śṛṇuṣva gadato mama
grāmaikarātrir vasatir nagare pañcarātrikā 101.045
sarvasaṅgaparityāgaḥ kṣāntir indriyasaṃyamaḥ
vikālabhaikṣacaraṇam anārambhas tathā nṛpa 101.046
ātmajñānāvabodhecchā ātmāvalokanaṃ caiva
bhikṣoḥ śastāni pārthiva 101.047
brahmacaryaṃ samādhinā yasyāṅghripadmagalitāmbhasi deva daitya-
yakṣādibhiḥ sakalapāpam apohya siddhiḥ saṃprāpyate maraṇajanmajarāpahantrī
viṣṇor ajāt kathaya ko 'bhyadhikas tato 'sti 101.057
caturthaś caiṣa kathitas tava bhikṣor mayāśramaḥ
kramād vimuktikāmānāṃ puruṣāṇām ayaṃ vidhiḥ 101.048
evaṃ tu varṇadharmeṇa tathā cāśramakarmanā
nijena saṃpūjya hariṃ siddhim āpnoti mānavaḥ 101.049
brahmacārī gṛhasthaś ca bhikṣur vaikhānasas tathā
kurvanto nijakarmāṇi viṣṇum eva yajanti te 101.050
yato hi devatāḥ sarvā brahmādyāḥ kurunandana
aṃśabhūtā jagaddhātur viṣṇor avyaktajanmanaḥ 101.051
viśve devā yato viṣṇur viṣṇuḥ pitṛgaṇo yataḥ
devā yajñabhujaś ceśo yataḥ pāpaharo hariḥ 101.052
viśve bhūtāni bhūtāni yato viṣṇus tatharṣayaḥ
tataḥ sarvāśramāṇāṃ hi pūjya eko janārdanaḥ 101.053
sarveśvaraṃ sarvamayaṃ samasta- saṃsārahetukṣayakāraṇeśam
varaṃ vareṇyaṃ varadaṃ variṣṭhaṃ viṣṇuṃ kriyāvān yajate manuṣyaḥ 101.054
yasyodare jagad idaṃ paramāṇubhūtaṃ candrendrarudramarudaśvivasuprajeśaiḥ
sarvaiḥ sametam amitātmatanos tam ekam abhyarcya viṣṇum abhivāñchitam asty alabhyam 101.055
ārādhya yaṃ bhuvanabhāvanam acyutākhyam aiśvaryam īpsitam avāpa patiḥ surāṇām
trailokyasāram amarārcitapādapadmam ekaṃ tam eva harim arcayatārcanīyam 101.056
kamalajaharasūryacandraśakraiḥ satatam abhiṣṭutam ādyam īśitāram
sakalabhuvanakāryakāraneśaṃ puruṣatanuṃ praṇato 'smi vāsudevam 101.058
śrutaṃ bhagavato rūpam advaite yat tvayoditam
viṣṇor bhṛgukulaśreṣṭha yac ca dvaite mahātmanaḥ 102.001
avidyābhinnadṛgbuddhiḥ puruṣo munipuṅgava
dvaitabhūte jagaty asminn advaitaṃ bhāvayet katham 102.002
krodhalobhādayo doṣā ye mukteḥ paripanthinaḥ
vinivṛttirūpā yena teṣāṃ yena vader ha tam 102.003
sarveśvareśvareśasya yac ca rūpaṃ hareḥ param
tac cāhaṃ śrotum icchāmi tvatto bhṛgukulodvaha 102.004
samyak pṛṣṭam idaṃ bhūpa bhavatā guhyam uttamam
dvaitādvaitakathālāpa- saṃbandhād upakārakam 102.005
purā dharmagṛhe jajñe caturmūrtir nareśvara
devadevo jagaddhātā paramātmā janārdanaḥ 102.006
jagataḥ pālanārthāya durvṛttanidhanāya ca
svecchayā bhagavān viṣṇuḥ saṃbhavaty eva bhūtale 102.007
svarge vāpi bhūloke vā bhuvarloke 'thavā vibhuḥ
yatra vā rocate tatra cikīrṣur jagato hitam 102.008
turīyāṃśena dharmasya bhagavān bhūtabhāvanaḥ
yadāvatāraṃ kṛtavāṃs tadā taccaritaṃ śṛṇu 102.009
naro nārāyaṇaś caiva hariḥ kṛṣṇas tathaiva ca
viṣṇor aṃśāṃśakā hy ete catvāro dharmasūnavaḥ 102.010
teṣāṃ nārāyaṇanarau gandhamādanaparvate
ātmany ātmānam ādhāya tepate paramaṃ tapaḥ 102.011
dhyāyamānāv anaupamyaṃ svakāraṇam akāraṇam
vāsudevam anirdeśyam apratarkyam ajaṃ param
yogayuktau mahāmaunam āsthitau gurutejasau 102.012
tayos tapaḥprabhāveṇa na tatāpa divākaraḥ
vavau cāśaṅkito vāyuḥ sukhasparśo hy asarkaraḥ 102.013
śiśiro 'bhavad atyarthaṃ jvalann api vibhāvasuḥ
siṃhavyāghrādayaḥ saumyāś ceruḥ saha mṛgair girau 102.014
tayor gauravabhārārtā pṛthivī pṛthivīpate
cacāla bhūdharāś celuś cukṣubhuś ca mahābdhayaḥ 102.015
devāś ca sveṣu dhiṣṇyeṣu niṣprabheṣu hataprabhāḥ
babhūvur avanīpāla paramaṃ kṣobham āgatāḥ 102.016
devarājas tataḥ śakraḥ saṃtrastas tapasas tayoḥ
yuyojāpsarasaḥ śubhrās tayor vighnacikīrṣayā 102.017
rambhe tilottame kuṇṭhe ghṛtāci lalitāvati
umloce subhrupramloce saurabhe 'pi madoddhate 102.018
alambuṣe miśrakeśi puṇḍarīke varūthini
vilobhanīyaṃ bibhrāṇā vapur manmathabodhanam
gandhamādanam āsādya kurudhvaṃ vacanaṃ mama 102.019
naranārāyaṇau tatra tapodīkṣānvitau dvijau
tapyete dharmatanayau tapaḥ paramaduścaram 102.020
tāv asmākaṃ varārohāḥ kurvāṇau paramaṃ tapaḥ
karmātiśayaduḥkhārti- pradāvayatināśakau 102.021
tad gacchata na bhīḥ kāryā bhavatībhir idaṃ vacaḥ
smaraḥ sahāyo bhavitā vasantaś ca varāṅganāḥ 102.022
rūpaṃ ca vaḥ samālokya madanoddīpanaṃ param
kandarpavaśam abhyeti vivaśaḥ ko na mānavaḥ 102.023
ity uktā devarājena madanena samaṃ tadā
jagmur apsarasaḥ sarvā vasantaś ca mahīpate 102.024
gandhamādanam āsādya puṃskokilakulākulam
cakāra mādhavo ramyaṃ protphullavanapādapam 102.025
pravavau dakṣiṇaḥ sadyo malayānugato 'nilaḥ
bhṛṅgamālārutaravair ramaṇīyam abhūd vanam 102.026
gandhaś ca surabhiḥ sadyo vanarājisamudbhavaḥ
kiṃnaroragayakṣāṇāṃ babhūva ghrāṇatarpaṇaḥ 102.027
varāṅganāś ca tāḥ sarvā naranārāyaṇāv ṛṣī
vilobhayitum ārabdhā varāṅgalalitaiḥ smitaiḥ 102.028
jagur manoharaṃ kāścin nanṛtuś cātra cāparāḥ
avādayaṃs tathaivānyā manoharataraṃ nṛpa 102.029
hāvair bhāvaiḥ smitais trāsais tathānyā valgubhāṣitaiḥ
tayoḥ kṣobhāya tanvaṅgyaś cakrur udyamam aṅganāḥ 102.030
tathāpi na tayoḥ kaścin manasaḥ pṛthivīpate
vikāro 'bhavad adhyātma- pārasaṃprāptacetasoḥ 102.031
nivātasthau yathā dīpāv akampau nṛpa tiṣṭhataḥ
vāsudevārpaṇe svacche tathaiva manasī tayoḥ 102.032
pūryamāṇo 'pi cāmbhobhir bhuvam anyāṃ mahodadhiḥ
yathā na yāti na yayau tathā tanmānasaṃ kvacit 102.033
sarvabhūtahitau brahma vāsudevamayaṃ param
manyamānau na rāgasya dveṣasya ca vaśaṃgatau 102.034
smaro 'pi na śaśākātha praveṣṭuṃ hṛdayaṃ tayoḥ
vidyāmayaṃ dīpayutam andhakāram ivālayam 102.035
puṣpojjvalāṃs taruvarān vasantaṃ dakṣiṇānilam
tāś caivāpsarasaḥ sarvāḥ kandarpaṃ ca mahāmunī 102.036
yac cārabdhaṃ tapas tābhyām ātmānaṃ gandhamādanam
dadṛśāte 'khilaṃ rūpaṃ brahmaṇaḥ puruṣarṣabha 102.037
dāhāya nānalo vahner nāpaḥkledāya cāmbhasaḥ
taddravyam eva taddravya- vikārāya na vai yataḥ 102.038
tato vijñānavijñāta- parabrahmasvarūpayoḥ
madhukandarpayoṣitsu vikāro nābhavat tayoḥ 102.039
tato gurutaraṃ yatnaṃ vasantamadanau nṛpa
cakrāte tāś ca tanvaṅgyas tatkṣobhāya punaḥ punaḥ 102.040
atha nārāyaṇo dhairya- gāmbhīryodāryamānasaḥ
ūror utpādayām āsa tāṃ varorubalāṃ tadā 102.041
trailokyasundarīratnam aśeṣam avanīpate
guṇalāghavam abhyeti yasyāḥ saṃdarśanād anu 102.042
tāṃ vilokya mahīpāla cakampe mādhavānilam
vasanto vismayaṃ yātaḥ saṃyātaḥ saṃsmaraṃ smaraḥ 102.043
rambhātilottamādyāś ca vilakṣā devayoṣitaḥ
na rejur avanīpāla tallakṣahṛdayekṣaṇāḥ 102.044
tataḥ kāmo vasantaś ca pārthivāpsarasaś ca tāḥ
praṇamya bhagavantau tau tuṣṭuvur munisattamau 102.045
prasīdatu jagaddhātā yasya devasya māyayā
mohitāḥ sma vijānīmo nāntaraṃ vandyanindyayoḥ 102.046
prasīdatu sa no devo yasya rūpam idaṃ dvidhā
dhāma bhūtasya lokānām anāder atra tiṣṭhati 102.047
naranārāyaṇau devau śārṅgacakrāyudhāv ubhau
āstāṃ prasādasumukhāv asmākam aparādhinām 102.048
nidhānaṃ sarvavidyānāṃ sarvapāpendhanānalaḥ
nārāyaṇo no bhagavān sarvapāpaṃ vyapohatu 102.049
śārṅgacakrāyudhaḥ śrīmān ātmajñānamayo 'naghaḥ
naraḥ samastapāpāni hatvātmā sarvadehinām 102.050
jaṭākalāpabandho 'yam anayor akṣayātmanoḥ
saumyā ca dṛṣṭiḥ pāpāni hantu sarvāṇi naḥ śubhā 102.051
prasīdatu naro 'smākaṃ tathā nārāyaṇo 'vyayaḥ
aparādhaḥ kṛto 'smābhir yayor avyaktajanmanoḥ 102.052
kva mūrtir aiśvaryaguṇair yuktā divyair mahātmanoḥ
kva naḥ śarīrakāṇīdṛg miśrakarmacitāni vai 102.053
tathāpy avidyāduṣṭena manasā yaḥ kṛto hi vām
asmābhir aparādho 'yaṃ kṣamyatāṃ sumahādyutī 102.054
śaraṇaṃ ca prapannānāṃ tavāsmīti ca vādinām
prasādaṃ pitṛhantR̥ṇām api kurvanti sādhavaḥ 102.055
eṣa eva varo 'smākam avivekāhṛto mahān
trailokyavandyau yannāthau vilobhayitum āgatāḥ 102.056
prasīda deva vijñāna- ghanamūḍhadṛśām api
bhavanti santaḥ satataṃ saddharmanyavatārakāḥ 102.057
dṛṣṭvaitan naḥ samutpannaṃ yathā strīratnam īdṛśam
tvayi nārāyaṇotpannā śreṣṭhā pāravatī matiḥ 102.058
tena satyena satyātman paramātman sanātanam
nārāyaṇa prasīdeti sarvalokaparāyaṇa 102.059
prasannabuddhe śāntātman prasannavadanekṣaṇa
prasīda yoginām īśa nara sarvagatācyuta 102.060
namasyāmo naraṃ devaṃ tathā nārāyaṇaṃ harim
namo narāya namyāya namo nārāyaṇāya ca 102.061
prasannānām anāthānām aparādhavatāṃ prabhuḥ
śaṃ karotu naro 'smākaṃ śaṃ nārāyaṇa dehi naḥ 102.062
evam abhyarthitaḥ stutyā rāgadveṣādivarjitaḥ
prāheśaḥ sarvabhūtānāṃ sādhyo nārāyaṇo nṛpa 102.063
svāgataṃ madhave kāma bhavato 'psarasām api
yat kāryam āgatānāṃ va ihāsmābhis tad ucyatām 102.064
yūyaṃ saṃsiddhaye nūnam asmākaṃ valaśatruṇā
saṃpreṣitās tato 'smākaṃ nṛttageyādidarśitam 102.065
na vayaṃ nṛttagītena nāṅgaceṣṭādibhāṣitaiḥ
lubhyāmo viṣato manye viṣayā dāruṇātmakāḥ 102.066
śabdādisaṅgaduṣṭāni yadā nākṣāṇi naḥ śubhāḥ
tadā nṛttādayo bhāvāḥ kathaṃ lobhapradāyinaḥ 102.067
te siddhāḥ sma na vai sādhyā bhavatīnāṃ smarasya ca
mādhavasya ca śakro 'pi svāsthyaṃ yātv aviśaṅkitaḥ 102.068
yo 'sau parasmāt paramaḥ puruṣāt parameśvaraḥ
paramātmā hṛṣīkeśaḥ sthāvarasya carasya ca 102.069
utpattihetur ante ca yasmin sarvaṃ pralīyate
sa sarvavāsidevatvād vāsudevety udāhṛtaḥ 102.070
vayam aṃśāṃśakās tasya caturvyūhasya māyinaḥ
tadādeśitavartmano jagadbodhāya dehinaḥ 102.071
taṃ sarvabhūtaṃ sarveśaṃ sarvatra samadarśinaḥ
paśyantaḥ kutra rāgādīn kariṣyāmo vibhedakān 102.072
vasante mayi cendre ca bhavatīṣu tathā smare
yadā sa eva viśvātmā tadā dveṣādayaḥ katham 102.073
tanmayāny avibhaktāni yadā sarveṣu jantuṣu
pṛthivy āpas tathā tejo vāyur ākāśam eva ca 102.074
tathendriyāṇy ahaṃkāro buddhiś ca na pṛthag yataḥ
samadṛṣṭir yataḥ kutra rāgadveṣau pravartataḥ 102.075
ātmā cāyam abhedena yataḥ sarveṣu jantuṣu
sarveśvareśvaro viṣṇuḥ kutra rāgādayas tataḥ 102.076
brahmāṇam indram īśānam ādityān maruto 'khilān
viśvedevān ṛṣīn sādhyān vasūn pitṛgaṇāṃs tathā 102.077
yakṣarākṣasabhūtādīn nāgasarpasarīsṛpān
manuṣyapakṣigorūpa- gajasiṃhajalecarān 102.078
makṣikāmaśakādaṃśāñ śalabhān alasān kṛmīn
gulmavṛkṣalatāvalli- tvaksāratṛṇajātijān 102.079
yac ca kiṃcid adṛśyaṃ vā dṛśyaṃ vā tridaśāṅganāḥ
manyadhvaṃ rūpam ekasya tat sarvaṃ paramātmanaḥ 102.080
jānamānaḥ kathaṃ viṣṇum ātmānaṃ paramaṃ ca yat
rāgadveṣau tathā lobhaṃ kaḥ kuryād amarāṅganāḥ 102.081
sarvabhūtasthite viṣṇau sarvage sarvadhātari
nipātyatāṃ pṛthagbhūte kutra rāgādiko gaṇaḥ 102.082
evam asmāsu yuṣmāsu sarvabhūteṣu cābalāḥ
tanmayatvaikabhūteṣu rāgādyavasaraḥ kutaḥ 102.083
samyagdṛṣṭir iyaṃ proktā samastaikyāvalokinī
pṛthagvijñānam atraiva lokasaṃvyavahāravat 102.084
bhūtendriyāntaḥkaraṇa- pradhānapuruṣātmakam
jagad yad etad akhilaṃ tadā bhedaḥ kimātmakaḥ 102.085
bhavanti layam āyānti samudre salilormayaḥ
na vāribhedato bhinnās tathaivaikyād idaṃ jagat 102.086
yathāgner arciṣaḥ pītāḥ piṅgalāruṇadhūsarāḥ
bhavanti nāgnibhedena tathaitad brahmaṇo jagat 102.087
bhavatībhiś ca yat kṣobham asmākaṃ sa puraṃdaraḥ
kārayaty asad etac ca vivekādhāracetasām 102.088
bhavatyaḥ sa ca devendro lokāś ca sasurāsurāḥ
samudrādrivanopetā maddehāntaragocarāḥ 102.089
yatheyaṃ cārusarvāṅgī bhavatīnāṃ mayorutaḥ
darśitā darśayiṣyāmi tathātraivākhilaṃ jagat 102.090
prayātu śakro mā garvam indratvaṃ kasya susthiram
yūyaṃ ca mā smayaṃ yāta santi rūpānvitāḥ striyaḥ 102.091
kiṃ surūpaṃ kurūpaṃ vā yadā bhedo na dṛśyate
tāratamyaṃ surūpatve satataṃ bhinnadarśinām 102.092
bhavatīnāṃ smayaṃ matvā rūpaudāryaguṇodbhavam
mayeyaṃ darśitā tanvī tatas tacchamam icchatā 102.093
yasmān madūror udbhūtā iyam indīvarekṣaṇā
urvaśī nāma kalyāṇī bhaviṣyati tato 'psarāḥ 102.094
tad iyaṃ devarājāya nīyatāṃ varavarṇinī
bhavatyas tena cāsmākaṃ preṣitāḥ prītim icchatā 102.095
vaktavyaś ca sahasrākṣo nāsmākaṃ bhogakāraṇāt
tapaścaryā na cāprāpya- phalaṃ prāptum abhīpsitam 102.096
sanmārgam asya jagato darśayiṣyan karomy aham
tapo nareṇa sahito jagataḥ pālanodyataḥ 102.097
yadi kaścit tavābādhāṃ karoti tridaśeśvara
tam ahaṃ vārayiṣyāmi nirvṛto bhava vāsava 102.098
kartāsi cet tvam ābādhām aduṣṭasyeha kasyacit
tavāpi śāstaitad ahaṃ pravartiṣyāmy asaṃśayam 102.099
etaj jñātvā na saṃtāpas tvayā kāryo hi māṃ prati
upakārāya jagatām avatīrṇo 'smi vāsava 102.100
yā ceyam urvaśī mattaḥ samudbhūtā puraṃdara
tretāgnihetubhūteyam ailaṃ prāpya bhaviṣyati 102.101
ity ukte 'psarasaḥ sarvāḥ praṇipatyātivismitāḥ
ūcur nārāyaṇaṃ devaṃ taddarśanakutūhalāḥ 103.001
ukto bhagavatā yo 'yam upadeśo hitārthinām
proktaḥ sa sarvo vijñāto māhātmyaṃ viditaṃ ca te 103.002
yat tv etad bhavatā proktaṃ prasannenāvyayātmanā
darśiteyaṃ viśālākṣī darśayiṣyāmi vo jagat 103.003
tannātha sarvabhāvena prapannānāṃ jagatpate
darśayātmānam akhilaṃ darśiteyaṃ yathorvaśī 103.004
yadi devāparāddheṣu nāsmāsu kupitaṃ tava
manas taj jagatam īśa darśayātmānam ātmanā 103.005
paśyatehākhilāṃl lokān mama dehe surāṅganāḥ
madhuṃ madanam ātmānaṃ yac cānyad draṣṭum icchatha 103.006
ity uktvā bhagavān devas tadā nārāyaṇo nṛpa
uccair jahāsa svanavat tatrābhūd akhilaṃ jagat 103.007
brahmā prajāpatiḥ śakraḥ saha rudraiḥ pinākadhṛk
ādityā vasavaḥ sādhyā viśvedevā maharṣayaḥ 103.008
nāsatyadasrāv anilāḥ sarve sarve tathāgnayaḥ
yakṣagandharvasiddhāś ca piśācāḥ kiṃnaroragāḥ 103.009
samastāpsaraso vidyāḥ sāṅgā vedās taduktayaḥ
manuṣyāḥ paśavaḥ kīṭāḥ pakṣiṇaḥ pādapās tathā 103.010
sarīsṛpāś ca ye sūkṣmā yac cānyaj jīvasaṃjñitam
samudrāḥ sakalāḥ śailāḥ saritaḥ kānanāni ca 103.011
dvīpāny aśeṣāṇi tathā nadāḥ sarvasarāṃsi ca
nagaragrāmapūrṇā ca medinī medinīpate
devāṅganābhir devasya dehe dṛṣṭaṃ mahātmanaḥ 103.012
nakṣatragrahatārābhiḥ samavetaṃ nabhastalam
dadṛśus tāḥ sucārvaṅgyas tasyāntar viśvarūpiṇaḥ 103.013
nordhvaṃ na tiryaṅ nādhaś ca yadāntas tasya dṛśyate
tam anantam anādiṃ ca tatas tās tuṣṭuvuḥ prabhum 103.014
madanena samaṃ sarvā madhunā ca surāṅganāḥ
sasādhvasā bhaktimatyaḥ paraṃ vismayam āgatāḥ 103.015
paśyāma nādiṃ tava deva nāntam na madhyam avyākṛtarūpapāram
parāyaṇaṃ tvā jagatām anantam natāḥ sma nārāyaṇam ātmabhūtam 103.016
mahī divaṃ vāyujalāgnayas tvaṃ śabdādirūpaś ca parāparātman
tvatto bhavaty acyuta sarvam etad abhedarūpo 'si vibho tvam ebhiḥ 103.017
draṣṭāsi rūpasya rasasya vettā śrotā ca śabdasya hare tvam ekaḥ
spraṣṭā bhavān spraśavato 'khilasya ghrātāsi gandhasya pṛthakśarīrī 103.018
sureṣu sarveṣu na so 'sti kaścin manuṣyaloke ca na so 'sti kaścit
paśvādivarge ca na so 'sti kaścid yo nāṃśabhūtas tava devadeva 103.019
brahmādyupendrapramukhāni saumyeṣv indrāgnirūpāṇi ca vīryavatsu
rudrāntakādīni ca raudravatsu rūpeṣu rūpāṇi tavottamāni 103.020
samudrarūpaṃ tava dhairyavatsu tejasvirūpeṣu ravis tathāgniḥ
kṣamādhaneṣu kṣitirūpam agryaṃ rūpaṃ tavāgryaṃ balavatsu vāyuḥ 103.021
manuṣyarūpaṃ tava rājaseṣu mūḍheṣu sarveśvara pādapo 'si
darpānviteṣv acyuta dānavas tvaṃ sanatsujātaś ca vivekavatsu 103.022
rasasvarūpeṇa jale sthito 'si gandhasvarūpo bhavato dharitryam
dṛśyasvarūpaś ca hutāśane tvaṃ sparśasvarūpo bhagavān samīre 103.023
śabdātmakaṃ te nabhasi svarūpaṃ mantavyarūpo manasi prabho tvam
bodhavyarūpaś ca vibho tvam ekaḥ sarvatra sarveśvara sarvabhūtaḥ 103.024
paśyāma te nābhisarojamadhye brahmāṇam etaṃ ca haraṃ bhrukūṭyam
tatrāśvinau karṇagatau samastāṇ avasthitān bāhuṣu lokapālān 103.025
ghrāṇe 'nilaṃ netragatau ravīndū jihvā ca te nātha sarasvatīyam
pādau dharitrīṃ jaṭharaṃ samastāṃl lokān hṛṣīkeśa vilokayāmaḥ 103.026
jaṅghe viyat pādakarāṅgulīṣu piśācarakṣoragasiddhasaṅghān
puṃstve prajānāṃ patir oṣṭhayugme pratiṣṭhitās te kratavaḥ samastāḥ 103.027
sarveṣṭayas te daśaneṣu deva daṃṣṭṛāsu vidyā bhavataś catasraḥ
romasv aśeṣās tava devasaṅghā vidyādharā nātha karāṅghrirekhāḥ
sāṅghāḥ samastās tava deva vedāḥ samāsthitā bahuṣu saṃdhibhūtāḥ 103.028
varāharūpaṃ dharaṇīdhṛtas te nṛsiṃharūpaṃ ca saṭākarālam
paśyāma te vājiśiras tathoccais trivikrame yaś ca tavāprameyaḥ 103.029
amī samudrās tava deva dehe mervādayaḥ śailavarās tavāmī
imāś ca gaṅgāpramukhāḥ sravatyo dvīpāny aśeṣāṇi vanāni caiva 103.030
stuvanti caite munayas taveśa dehe sthitās tvanmahimānam agryam
tvām īśitāraṃ jagatām anantam yajñeśam arcanti ca yajvino 'mī 103.031
tvatto na saumyaṃ jagatīha kiṃcit tvatto na raudraṃ ca samastamūrte
tvatto na śītaṃ na ca keśavoṣṇaṃ sarvasvarūpātiśayī tvam ekaḥ 103.032
prasīda sarveśvara sarvabhūta sanātanātman parameśvareśa
tvanmāyayā mohitamānasābhir yat te 'parāddhaṃ tad idaṃ kṣamasva 103.033
kiṃ vāparāddhaṃ tava deva mūḍhair yan māyayā no hṛdayaṃ tathāpi
pāpāvaśaṃ kiṃ praṇatārtihārin mano hi no viṅkalatām upaiti 103.034
na te 'parāddhaṃ yadi vāparāddham asmābhir unmārgavivartanībhiḥ
tat kṣamyatāṃ sṛṣṭikaras tavaiva devāparādhaṃ sṛjato vivekān 103.035
namo namas te govinda nārāyaṇa janārdana
tvannāmasmaraṇāt pāpam aśeṣaṃ naḥ praṇaśyatu 103.036
tato 'nanta namas tubhyaṃ viśvātman viśvabhāvana
tvannāmasmaraṇāt pāpam aśeṣaṃ naḥ praṇaśyatu
namo namas te vaikuṇṭha śrīvatsāṅkābjalocana
vareṇya yajñapuruṣa prajāpālaka vāmana 103.*(155)
namo 'stu te 'bjanābhāya prajāpatikṛte hare
tvannāmasmaraṇāt pāpam aśeṣaṃ naḥ praṇaśyatu 103.037
saṃsārārṇavapotāya namas tubhyam adhokṣaja
tvannāmasmaraṇāt pāpam aśeṣaṃ naḥ praṇaśyatu 103.038
namaḥ parasmai śrīśāya vāsudevāya vedhase
svecchayā guṇabhoktṛtve sargāntasthitikāriṇe 103.039
upasaṃhāra viśvātman rūpam etat samantataḥ
vardhamānaṃ na no draṣṭuṃ samarthaṃ cakṣur īśvara 103.040
pralayāgnisahasrasya samā dīptis tavācyuta
pramāṇena diśo bhūmir gaganaṃ ca samāvṛtam 103.041
na vidmaḥ kva nu vartāmo bhavān naivopalakṣyate
sarvaṃ jagad ihaikasthaṃ piṇḍitaṃ lakṣayāmahe 103.042
kiṃ varṇayāmo rūpaṃ te kiṃ pramāṇam idaṃ hare
māhātmyaṃ kiṃtu te deva jihvāyā yan na gocaram 103.043
vaktrāṇām ayutenāpi buddhīnām ayutāyutaiḥ
guṇānāṃ varṇanaṃ nātha tava vaktuṃ na śakyate 103.044
tad etad darśitaṃ rūpaṃ prasādaḥ paramaḥ kṛtaḥ
chandato jagatām īśa tad etad upasaṃhara 103.045
ity evaṃ saṃstutas tābhir apsarobhir janārdanaḥ
divyajñānopapannānāṃ tāsāṃ pratyakṣam īśvaraḥ
viveśa sarvabhūtāni svair aṃśair bhūtabhāvanaḥ 103.046
taṃ dṛṣṭvā sarvabhūteṣu līyamānam adhokṣajam
vismayaṃ paramaṃ jagmuḥ samastā devayoṣitaḥ 103.047
sa ca sarveśvaraḥ śailān pādapān sāgarān bhuvam
jalam agniṃ tathā vāyum ākāśaṃ ca viveśa ha 103.048
kāle dikṣv atha sarvātmā manuṣyātmany athāpi ca
ātmarūpaḥ sthitaḥ svena mahimnā bhāvayañ jagat 103.049
devadānavarakṣāṃsi yakṣavidyādharoragān
manuṣyapaśukīṭādīn mṛgapakṣyantarikṣagān 103.050
ye 'ntarikṣe tathā bhūmau divi ye ye jalāśrayāḥ
tān praviśya sa viśvātmā punas tad rūpam āsthitaḥ
nareṇa sārchaṃ yat tābhir dṛṣṭapūrvam ariṃdama 103.051
tāḥ paraṃ vismayaṃ gatvā sarvās tridaśayoṣitaḥ
praṇemuḥ sādhyasāḥ pāṇḍu- vadanā nṛpasattama 103.052
nārāyaṇo 'pi bhagavān āha tās tridaśāṅganāḥ
nīyatām urvaśī bhadrā yatrāste tridaśeśvaraḥ 103.053
bhavatīnāṃ hitārthāya sarvabhūteṣv asāv iti
jñānam utpāditaṃ bhūyo layaṃ bhūteṣu kurvatā 103.054
tad gacchata samasto 'yaṃ bhūtagrāmo madaṃśakaḥ
aham apy ātmabhūtasya vāsudevasya yoginaḥ 103.055
yasmāt parataraṃ nāsti yo 'nantaḥ paripaṭhyate
tam ajaṃ sarvabhūteśaṃ jānīta paramaṃ padam 103.056
ahaṃ bhavatyo devāś ca manuṣyāḥ paśavaś ca ye
etat sarvam anantasya 103.057
devadevasya vistṛtiḥ etaj jñātvā samaṃ sargaṃ
sadevāsuramānuṣam sapaśvādigaṇaṃ caiva
draṣṭavyaṃ tridaśāṅganāḥ 103.058
ity uktas tena devena samastās tāḥ surastriyaḥ
praṇamya tau samadanāḥ savasantāś ca pārthiva 103.059
ādāya corvaśīṃ bhūyo devarājam upāgatāḥ
ācakhyuś ca yathāvṛttaṃ devarājāya tat tathā 103.060
tathā tvam api rājendra sarvabhūteṣu keśavam
cintayan samatāṃ gaccha samataiva hi muktaye 103.061
jānann evam aśeṣeṣu bhūteṣu parameśvaram
vāsudevaṃ kathaṃ doṣāṃl lobhādīn na prahāsyasi 103.062
sarvabhūtāni govindād yadā nānyāni bhūpate
tadā vairādayo bhāvāḥ kriyatāṃ kutra pārthiva 103.063
iha paśyañ jagat sarvaṃ vāsudevātmakaṃ nṛpa
etad eva hi kṛṣṇena rūpam āviṣkṛtaṃ tadā 103.064
paramasmād api mahad rūpaṃ yat kathitaṃ tava
janmādibhāvarahitaṃ tad viṣṇoḥ paramaṃ padam 103.065
saṃkṣepeṇa ca bhūpāla śrūyatāṃ yad vadāmi te
yan matau puruṣaḥ kṛtvā paraṃ nirvāṇam ṛcchati 103.066
sarvaṃ viṣṇuḥ samastau hi bhāvābhāvau ca tanmayau
sadasat sarvam īśeśo vāsudevaḥ paraṃ padam 103.067
bhavajaladhigatānāṃ dvandvavātāhatānāṃ sutaduhitṛkalatratrāṇabhārārditānām
viṣamaviṣayatoye majjatām aplavānāṃ bhavati śaraṇam eko viṣṇupoto narāṇām 103.068
ity uktaṃ tava dharmajña viṣṇor māhātmyam uttamam
svarūpaṃ ca jagaddhātur ārādhanaviniścayaḥ 104.001
ārādhitāt phalaṃ yac ca keśavāt prāpyate naraiḥ
kathitaś ca mahābhāga dānānāṃ vistarād vidhiḥ 104.002
yogadvaidhaṃ ca kathitam advaitaṃ dvaitam eva ca
advaitabhāvanopāyo vistarāc ca tavoditaḥ 104.003
saṃkṣepavistarābhyāṃ ca sarvam etat tavoditam
devadevasya māhātmyaṃ sarvagasyāvyayātmanaḥ 104.004
sa eṣa sarvapravaraḥ sarvabhūtaś ca mādhavaḥ
sarvam atra ca sarvasminn eṣa eva pratiṣṭhitaḥ 104.005
triyugaṃ puṇḍarīkākṣam apavargamahāhradam
samutpatya parāhlādam anantaṃ pratipadyate 104.006
śrutam etan mayā pūrvaṃ vistareṇa tvayoditam
yat tv etat triyugety uktaṃ tasya nirvacanaṃ vada 104.007
caturyugena kālasya parisaṃkhyā yadā dvija
triyugena tadā viṣṇoḥ kriyate kiṃ viśeṣaṇam 104.008
kṛtaṃ tretā dvāparaṃ ca kaliś ceti caturyugam
yadā jagati vikhyātaṃ tadā triyugatā kutaḥ 104.009
sādhu pṛṣṭo 'smi bhūpāla bhavatā triyugāśritam
viśeṣaṇam anantasya gadatas tan niśāmaya 104.010
kāṣṭhā pārthiva vijñeyā nimeṣā daśa pañca ca
kāṣṭhātriṃśat kalā jñeyā muhūrtaṃ tāvatīḥ kalāḥ 104.011
triṃśanmuhūrtā bhūpāla tathāhorātram ucyate
tatsaṃkhyātair ahorātrair māsaḥ pārthivasattama 104.012
ayanaṃ dakṣiṇaṃ māsāḥ ṣaṇ māsāś ca tathottaram
ayanadvitayākhyaś ca kālaḥ saṃvatsaraḥ smṛtaḥ 104.013
dakṣiṇaṃ tv ayanaṃ rātrir devānām uttaraṃ dinam
saṃvatsareṇa devānām ahorātram ihocyate 104.014
śatatrayeṇa varṣāṇāṃ ṣaṣṭyā ca pṛthivīpate
manuṣyasaṃkhyayā varṣaṃ devānām api gaṇyate 104.015
iti divyena mānena caturyugavikalpanām
kathyamānāṃ mayā rājan yathāvac chrotum arhasi 104.016
catvāri tu sahasrāṇi varṣāṇāṃ kṛtam ucyate
tasya tāvacchatī saṃdhyā saṃdhyāṃśaś ca tathāvidhaḥ 104.017
tretā trīṇi sahasrāṇi divyābdānāṃ nararṣabha
tasya tāvacchatī saṃdhyā saṃdhyāṃśaś ca tathāvidhaḥ 104.018
dvāparaṃ dve sahasre tu varṣāṇām abhidhīyate
tasya tāvacchatī saṃdhyā saṃdhyāṃśaś ca tathāvidhaḥ 104.019
kaliḥ sahasram ekaṃ tu divyābdānāṃ nararṣabha
tasya tāvacchatī saṃdhyā saṃdhyāṃśaś ca tathāvidhaḥ 104.020
kṛtaṃ nāmayugaṃ pūrvaṃ yatra dharmaḥ sanātanaḥ
kṛtam eva ca kartavyaṃ tasmin kāle nṛpepsitam 104.021
na tatra dharmāḥ sīdanti na ca kṣīyanti vai prajāḥ
tataḥ kṛtayugaṃ nāma guṇataḥ procyate yugam 104.022
devadānavagandharvā yakṣarākṣasapannagāḥ
nāsan kṛtayuge rājan na tadā krayavikrayaḥ 104.023
na sāmayajurṛgvarṇāḥ kriyā nāsīc ca mānavī
nābhisaṃdhāya ca phalaṃ kaścid dharme pravartate 104.024
na tasmin yugasaṃsarge vyādhayo nendriyakṣayaḥ
nāsūyā nāpi ruditaṃ na darpo nāpi paiśunam 104.025
na vigrahaḥ kutas tandrī na dveṣo nāpi dambhanam
na bhayaṃ nāpi saṃtāpo na cerṣyā nāpi matsaraḥ 104.026
tataḥ paramakaṃ brahma yā gatir yogināṃ parā
ātmā ca sarvabhūtānāṃ śuklo nārāyaṇas tadā 104.027
tasminn ātmani lokānāṃ sarvalokamaye 'cyute
svecchayā śauklyam āpanne sarvaṃ bhavati nirmalam 104.028
brāhmaṇāḥ kṣatriyā vaiśyāḥ śūdrāś ca kṛtalakṣaṇāḥ
kṛte yuge bhavantīha svakarmaniratāḥ prajāḥ 104.029
svam āśramaṃ svam ācāraṃ samyagjñānasamanvitam
jagad bhavati rājendra satyaprāyaṃ taporatam 104.030
ekavedasamāyuktā ekamantravidhikriyāḥ
pṛthagdharmās tv ekavedā dharmam ekam anuvratāḥ 104.031
caturāśramayuktena karmaṇā kālayoginā
akāmaphalasaṃyogāt prāpnuvanti parāṃ gatim 104.032
ātmayogasamāyukto dharmo 'yaṃ kṛtalakṣaṇaḥ
kṛte yuge catuṣpādaś caturvarṇyasya śāśvataḥ 104.033
etat kṛtayugaṃ nāma traiguṇyaparivarjitam
tretām api nibodha tvaṃ yādṛgrūpaṃ pravartate 104.034
pādena hrasate dharmo raktatāṃ yāti cācyutaḥ
satyapravṛttāś ca narāḥ kriyādharmaparāyaṇāḥ 104.035
tato yajñāḥ pravartante dharmāś ca vividhāḥ kriyāḥ
tretāyāṃ bhāvasaṃkalpāḥ kriyādānaphalodayāḥ 104.036
pracaranti tato varṇās tapodānaparāyaṇāḥ
svakarmasthāḥ kriyāvantaḥ samatvād rajasānvitāḥ 104.037
dvāpare 'pi yuge dharmo dvibhāgonaḥ pravartate
viṣṇuḥ pītatvam abhyeti caturdhā veda eva ca 104.038
tato 'nye ca caturvedās trivedāś ca tathāpare
dvivedāś caikavedāś ca anṛcaś ca tathāpare 104.039
evaṃ śāstreṣu bhinneṣu bahudhā nīyate kriyā
tapodānapravṛttā ca rājasī bhavati prajā 104.040
alpāyuṣo narā vedaḥ sumahāṃś ceti dustaraḥ
karoti bahudhā vedān vyāsarūpī tadā hariḥ 104.041
sattvasya cāpy avijñānāt sattve kaścid vyavasthitaḥ
sattvāt pracyavamānānāṃ vyādhayo bahavo 'bhavan 104.042
kāmāś copadravāś caiva tadā daivatakāritāḥ
yair ardyamānāḥ subhṛśaṃ tapas tapyanti mānavāḥ 104.043
dhanakāmāḥ svargakāmā yajñāṃs tanvanti cāpare
evaṃ dvāparam āsādya prajāḥ kṣīyanty adharmataḥ 104.044
pādenaikena rājendra dharmaḥ kaliyuge 'pi hi
tāmasaṃ yugam āsādya kṛṣṇo bhavati keśavaḥ 104.045
vratācārāḥ praśāmyanti dharmayajñakriyās tathā
ītayo vyādhayas tandrī doṣāḥ krodhādayas tathā
upadravāś ca vardhante manastāpāś ca saṃgatāḥ 104.046
yugeṣv āvartamāneṣu loko vyāvartate punaḥ
loke kṣīṇe kṣayaṃ yānti bhāvā lokapravartakāḥ
yugadvayakṛtān dharmān prārthanā na ca kurvate 104.047
etat kaliyugaṃ bhūpa yatra jāto 'si pārthiva
nātrāvatāraṃ kurute kṛṣṇāṃśena svarūpiṇā 104.048
kṛtādiṣu jagat pāti daityebhyo rūpadhṛd dhariḥ
kalau tv anyaṃ samāviśya pūrvotpannaṃ bibharti tam 104.049
pratyagrarūpadhṛg devo dṛśyate na kalau hariḥ
kṛtādiṣv eva tenaiṣa triyugaḥ paripaṭhyate 104.050
kaler ante ca saṃprāpte kalkinaṃ brahmavādinam
anupraviśya kurute vāsudevo jagatsthitim 104.051
pūrvotpanneṣu bhūteṣu teṣu teṣu kalau prabhuḥ
kṛtvā praveśaṃ kurute yad abhipretam acyutaḥ 104.052
svecchāśukle jagac chuklaṃ rakte raktaṃ ca jāyate
pīte ca pītatām asmin kṛṣṇe cātrāsitaṃ nṛpa 104.053
eṣa eva jagaddevo jagatsraṣṭā jagadguruḥ
yadrūpa eva devo 'yaṃ tadrūpaṃ jāyate jagat 104.054
caturyugaṃ naḥ kathitaṃ saṃkṣepād bhavatākhilam
kaliṃ vistarato brūhi yatra jāto 'smi bhārgava 105.001
bhagavaty amale viṣṇau krīḍayā kṛṣṇatāṃ gate
kimāhārāḥ kimācārā bhaviṣyanti prajās tadā 105.002
brāhmaṇāḥ kṣatriyā vaiśyāḥ śūdrāś ca dvija kīdṛśāḥ
bhaviṣyanti kalau prāpte tan mamācakṣva vistarāt 105.003
tapaḥ paraṃ kṛtayuge tretāyāṃ yajña eva hi
pradhānaṃ dvāpare dānaṃ satyam eva kalau yuge 105.004
kṛte yuge manaḥśuddhir asty evāyatnatas tapaḥ
tapo niṣpādyate bhūpa yogasaṃsādhanaṃ param 105.005
rāgādidoṣaduṣṭena manasā yat tapo nṛpa
kriyate kleśanāśāya tat tapo na vimuktaye 105.006
tretāyāṃ tu kriyāyajñān manoyajñāṃs tato narāḥ
vitanvate sthūlataraḥ panthā dharmasya sa prabho 105.007
dvāpare nātividvattā yathā tretāyuge 'bhavat
tataḥ sthūlataraḥ panthā dānātmā kriyate naraiḥ 105.008
na vidvattā na śuddhārtho na śuddhir manasaḥ kalau
yato 'taḥ satyam evaikam ekāntenopakārakam 105.009
yathā satyaṃ tathā kṣāntir ahiṃsā ca kalau yuge
paropatāpād viratir narāṇām upakārikā 105.010
tasmin ghore yuge prāpte kṛṣṇe kṛṣṇatvam āgate
yādṛgrūpaṃ jagad idaṃ bhavatīha śṛṇuṣva tat 105.011
rājāno brāhmaṇā vaiśyāḥ śūdrāś ca manujeśvara
vyājadharmaparāś caiva dharmavaitaṃsikā janāḥ 105.012
satyaṃ saṃkṣipyate loke naraiḥ paṇḍitamānibhiḥ
satyahānyā tatas teṣāṃ svalpam āyur bhaviṣyati 105.013
āyuṣaḥ prakṣayād vidyāṃ na śakṣyanty upaśikṣitum
vidyāhīnān abuddhīṃs tāṃl lobho 'py abhibhaviṣyati 105.014
lobhakrodhaparā mūḍhāḥ kāmavaśyāś ca mānavāḥ
baddhavairā bhaviṣyanti parasparavadhepsavaḥ 105.015
brāhmaṇāḥ kṣatriyā vaiśyāḥ saṃkīryantaḥ parasparam
śūdratulyā bhaviṣyanti tapaḥsatyavinākṛtāḥ 105.016
antyā madhyā bhaviṣyanti madhyāś cāntāvasāyinaḥ
īdṛśo bhavitā lokaḥ kṛṣṇe kṛṣṇatvam āgate 105.017
vastrāṇāṃ pravarā śāṇī dhānyānāṃ koradūṣakaḥ
bhāryāmitrāś ca puruṣā bhaviṣyanti kalau yuge 105.018
matsyāmiṣeṇa jīvanto duhantaś cāpy ajāvikāḥ
goṣu naṣṭāsu puruṣā bhaviṣyanti tadā nṛpa 105.019
sarittīreṣu kuddālair vāpayiṣyanti cauṣadhīḥ
tāś cāpy alpaphalās teṣāṃ bhaviṣyanti yugakṣaye 105.020
aniṣkrāntās tu saṃbandhāḥ svagotrāt puruṣarṣabha
aniṣkrāntāni śrāddhāni bhaviṣyanti ca gehataḥ 105.021
na vratāni cariṣyanti brāhmaṇā vedanindakāḥ
na yakṣyanti na hoṣyanti hetuvādavikūlinaḥ 105.022
prāyaśaḥ kṛpaṇānāṃ ca tathā bandhimatām api
vidhavānāṃ ca vittāni hariṣyanti balānvitāḥ 105.023
anyāyopāttavitteṣu kariṣyanti narāḥ spṛhām
veśyālāvaṇyabhāveṣu spṛhāṃ yoṣit kariṣyati 105.024
kanyāṃ na yācitā kaścin na ca kanyāprado naraḥ
kanyā varaś ca cchandena gṛhīṣyanti parasparam 105.025
bhāryā na patiśuśrūṣāṃ tadā kācit kariṣyati
narā devadvijāṃs tyaktvā bhaviṣyanty anyatomukhāḥ 105.026
yajñabhāgabhujo devā ye vedapaṭhitā dvijāḥ
brahmādyās tān parityajya narāḥ kālabalātkṛtāḥ
hetuvādaparā devān kariṣyanty aparāṃs tadā 105.027
ye yavānnā janapadā godhūmānnās tathaiva ca
tān deśān saṃśrayiṣyanti narāḥ kaliyuge nṛpa 105.028
na śrāddhaiś ca pitR̥ṃś cāpi tarpayiṣyanti mānavāḥ
bahu maṃsyanti te snānaṃ nāpi śaucaparā narāḥ 105.029
na viṣṇubhaktipravaṇaṃ narāṇāṃ nṛpa mānasam
bhavitā tu yuge prāpte kṛṣṇe kārṣṇyopalakṣite 105.030
vinindāṃ prathame pāde kariṣyanti harer narāḥ
yugānte tu harer nāma naiva kaścid gṛhīṣyati 105.031
dhanyās te puruṣavyāghra pāpāmbhodhāv apāpinaḥ
ye nāmāpi kalau viṣṇor gṛhīṣyanty akṣayātmanaḥ 105.032
dhyāyan hariṃ kṛtayuge tretādvāparayor yajan
yad āpnoti kalau nāmnā tad eva parikīrtayan 105.033
harir harati pāpāni nāma bhaktyā yadīritam
vāsudeveti na janas tad evoccārayiṣyati 105.034
bahupāṣaṇḍasaṃkīrṇe jagaty asmin kalau yuge
kṛṣṇāyeti namo 'stv atra sukṛtī yadi vakṣyati 105.035
hetuvādabalair mohaṃ kuhakaiś ca jane tadā
pāṣaṇḍinaḥ kariṣyanti cāturāśramyadūṣakāḥ 105.036
pāṣaṇḍabhūtam atyarthaṃ jagad etad asatkṛtam
bhaviṣyati tadā bhūpa vṛthāpravrajitotkaṭam 105.037
na tu dvijātiśuśrūṣāṃ na svadharmānupālanam
kariṣyanti tadā śūdrāḥ pravrajyāliṅgino vṛthā 105.038
utkocāḥ saugatāś caiva mahāyānaratās tathā
bhaviṣyanty atha pāṣaṇḍāḥ kāpilā bhikṣavas tathā 105.039
vṛddhāḥ śrāvakanirgranthāḥ siddhaputrās tathāpare
bhaviṣyanti durātmānaḥ śūdrāḥ kaliyuge nṛpa 105.040
niḥśaucā vakramatayaḥ parapākānnabhojanāḥ
bhaviṣyanti durātmānaḥ śūdrāḥ pravrajitās tadā 105.041
ete cānye ca bahavaḥ pāṣaṇḍāḥ puruṣarṣabha
brāhmaṇāḥ kṣatriyā vaiśyā bhaviṣyanti tathā pare 105.042
rājaśulkaharāḥ kṣudrā gṛhasthaparimoṣakāḥ
muniveṣākṛticchannā vāṇijyam upajīvikāḥ 105.043
na dvijān na kalau devān pūjayiṣyanti mānavāḥ
mlecchabhāṣānibandhais tu hetuvādair vikūlitāḥ 105.044
evaṃ teṣv atiduṣṭeṣu vimārgapathivartinaḥ
bhaviṣyanty apare duṣṭās teṣāṃ mārgānuyāyinaḥ 105.045
asaṃskṛtoktivaktāro vedaśāstravinindakāḥ
jagadunmārgakartāro bhaviṣyanti tadā narāḥ 105.046
tacchīlavartibhir bhūpa manuṣyaiḥ paripūrite
jagaty atra tadā nR̥ṇāṃ svalpam āyur bhaviṣyati 105.047
paramāyuś ca bhavitā tadā varṣāṇi ṣoḍaśa
tataḥ prāṇān prahāsyanti kṛṣṇe kṛṣṇatvam āgate 105.048
pañcame vātha ṣaṣṭhe vā varṣe kanyā prasūyate
saptavarṣāṣṭavarṣā vā prajāsyanti narās tadā 105.049
alpadravyā vṛthāliṅgā hiṃsāratiparāyaṇāḥ
hartāro na tu dātāro bhaviṣyanti kalau narāḥ 105.050
śuklādānaparāḥ kṣudrāḥ parapākāśino dvijāḥ
vaiśyās tathā tu rājāno na tu kṣatriyavaṃśajāḥ 105.051
śūdrā bhikṣavatā viprāḥ śuśrūṣāvipaṇāśritāḥ
bhaviṣyanti nṛpaśreṣṭha kṛṣṇe kṛṣṇatvam āgate 105.052
na śiṣyo na guruḥ kaścin na putro na pitā tathā
na bhāryā na patir bhūpa bhavitā tatra saṃkule 105.053
etat kālasvarūpaṃ te śatānīka mayoditam
viṣṇubhaktān naraśreṣṭha na narān bādhate kaliḥ 105.054
ye 'harniśaṃ jagaddhātur vāsudevasya kīrtanam
kurvanti tān naravyāghra na kalir bādhate narān 105.055
ye tanmanaskās tiṣṭhanti prayāntaḥ saṃsthitās tathā
svapantaś ca naravyāghra tān kalir na prabādhate 105.056
sarvatra bhagavān viṣṇur govindaḥ keśavo hariḥ
yasya bhāvo na taṃ bhūpa kadācid bādhate kaliḥ 105.057
na kalau kaliceṣṭo 'sau mūḍheṣu na sa muhyate
bhagavaty acyute nityaṃ yena bhāvaḥ samarpitaḥ 105.058
kaliprabhāvo duṣṭoktiḥ pāṣaṇḍānāṃ tathoktayaḥ
na krāmante manas tasya yasya cetasi keśavaḥ 105.059
kalau kṛtayugaṃ tasya kalis tasya kṛte yuge
yasya cetasi govindo hṛdaye yasya nācyutaḥ 105.060
aniṣṭvāpi mahāyajñair akṛtvāpi pitṛsvadhām
kṛṣṇam abhyarcya yad bhaktyā nainaṃ śvomaraṇaṃ tapet 105.061
yasyāgratas tathā pṛṣṭhe gacchatas tiṣṭhato 'pi vā
govinde niyataṃ cetaḥ kṛtakṛtyaḥ sadaiva saḥ 105.062
etad viditvā bhūpāla sarve sarveśvare harau
tanmanā bhava taccittas tanmanā nāvasīdati 105.063
paramārtham aśeṣasya jagataḥ prabhavāvyayam
śaraṇyaṃ śaraṇaṃ gacchan govindaṃ nāvasīdati 105.064
kalikalmaṣakakṣāgniṃ nirvāṇaṃ padam avyayam
sarvakāraṇam avyaktaṃ viṣṇuṃ dhyāyan na sīdati 105.065
yatra sarvamaye dhyāte dhyeyam anyan na vidyate
yatrārcite 'rcanīyaś ca jāyate taṃ namāmy aham 105.066
jagatsraṣṭāram iśeśam anādiṃ parataḥ param
sarvāspadaṃ sarvabhūtaṃ gacchan sarvātmanā harim 105.067
haraty agham aśeṣaṃ yo harir ity abhisaṃstutaḥ
aśeṣāghaharaṃ viṣṇuṃ harivarṇaṃ hariṃ namaḥ 105.068
yatkīrtanād aghaḥ śuddhaḥ smṛte yatrāśuciḥ suciḥ
tam ātmani sthitaṃ bhūpa puṇḍarīkekṣaṇaṃ namaḥ 105.069
apavitraḥ pavitro vā sarvāvasthagato 'pi vā
yaḥ smaret puṇḍarīkākṣaṃ sa bāhyābhyantaraḥ śuciḥ 105.070
yady apy upahataḥ pāpair yadi vātyantaduṣkṛtaiḥ
tathāpi saṃsmaran viṣṇuṃ sa bāhyābhyantaraḥ śuciḥ 105.071
kalāv atrātidoṣāḍhye viṣayāsaktamānasaḥ
kṛtvāpi pāpaṃ govindaṃ dhyāyan pāpair vimucyate 105.072
tad dhyānaṃ yatra govindaḥ sā kathā yatra keśavaḥ
tat karma yat tadarthīyaṃ kim anyair bahubhāṣitaiḥ 105.073
naitat pitā tanūjāya na śiṣyāya gurur nṛpa
paramārthapadaṃ brūyād yad etat te mayoditam 105.074
saṃsāre bhramatā labhyaṃ putradāradhanaṃ vasu
suhṛdaś ca tathivānye nopadeśo nṛpedṛśaḥ 105.075
kiṃ putradārair vittair vā na mitre kṣetrabāndhavaiḥ
upadeṣṭā paro bandhur īdṛśo yo vimuktaye 105.076
yo naikāgramanā viṣṇāv iti jñātvāpi pārthiva
sa nūnam acyutasyaiva nānugrāhyo 'tra pāpakṛt 105.077
dvividho bhūtasargo 'yaṃ daiva āsura eva ca
viṣṇubhaktiparo daivo viparītas tathāsuraḥ 105.078
upadeśapradānena saṃbhūtitraya āsuraḥ
naiva viṣṇuparo bhūpa bhavaty akṣīṇakalmaṣaḥ 105.079
upadeśeṣu so 'tyantaṃ saṃrambhī yuktiyojitam
hetuvādāśrito mūḍho dadāty uttaram akṣayam 105.080
snātasya devakāryeṣu tathāpatsu kathāsu ca
āsurasyāpi tanmātrā jāyate nṛpate matiḥ 105.081
iti matvātisadbhāvaṃ rahasyaṃ param īritam
tvayācyutān matir bhūpa nāpaneyā kathaṃcana 105.082
aprāpya vāñchati ratiṃ sarvadaiva nṛṇāṃ manaḥ
ihaivācyutasaṃsargi yadi tat kiṃ prahīyate 105.083
tad alaṃ tava rājyena balakośādibhis tathā
cintitair acyutaś cintyo yadbhāvi na tadanyathā 105.084
etat pavitram ārogyaṃ dhanyaṃ duḥsvapnanāśanam
sukhaprītikaraṃ nR̥ṇāṃ patatāṃ nirvṛtipradam 105.085
yeṣāṃ gṛheṣu likhitam etat sthāsyati nityadā
na tadgṛhāṇi daivotthā bādhiṣyante hy upadravāḥ 105.086
kiṃ tīrthaiḥ kiṃ pradānair vā kiṃ yajñaiḥ kim upoṣitaiḥ
ahany ahany etad eva tanmayatvena śṛṇvataḥ 105.087
yao dadāti tilaprasthaṃ suvarṇasya ca māsakam
śṛṇoti ślokam ekaṃ ca dharmasyāsya samaṃ hi tat 105.088
adhyāyapāraṇaṃ cāsya gopradānāh viśiṣyate
śṛṇvaṃś cāsya daśādhyāyān sadyaḥ pāpaiḥ pramucyate 105.089
rātryā yad enaḥ kurute divasena ca mānavaḥ
śrotuṃ vāñchā samastaṃ tat pārthivasya vyapohati 105.090
kapilānāṃ śate datte yad bhavej jyeṣṭhapuṣkare
narendra viṣṇudharmāṇāṃ tadāvāpnoti pāraṇe 105.091
pravṛttau ca nivṛttau ca dharmaṃ dharmabhṛtāṃ vara
nāsty anyad viṣṇudhamāṇāṃ sadṛśaṃ śāstram uttamam 105.092
maitrīṃ karoti bhūteṣu bhaktim atyantam acyute
śrutvā dharmān imān vetti abhedenātmano jagat 105.093
paṭhann anudinaṃ dharmān etāñ śṛṇvaṃs tathāpi vā
bhaktyā matimatāṃ śreṣṭha sarvapāpaiḥ pramucyate 105.094
nopasargo na cānartho na caurāgnibhayaṃ gṛhe
tasmin bhavati bhūpāla yatraitat pustakaṃ sthitam 105.095
na garbhahāriṇī bhītir na ca bālagrahā gṛhe
yatraitad bhūpate tatra na piśācādikād bhayam 105.096
śṛṇvan vipro vedavit syāt kṣatriyaḥ pṛthivīpatiḥ
ṛddhiṃ prayāti vaiśyaś ca śūdraś cārogyam ṛcchati 105.097
yaś caitān niyatān dharmān paṭhec chraddhāsamanvitaḥ
viṣṇau manaḥ samāveśya sarvatra samadarśanaḥ 105.098
tasya pāpaṃ tathā rogān duḥsvapnādyābhicārukān
yac cānyad duritaṃ kiṃcit tat sarvaṃ hanti keśavaḥ 105.099
hemante ya imān dharmāñ śṛṇoti vasudhādhipa
śraddhāsamanvitaḥ samyak so 'gniṣṭomaphalaṃ labhet 105.100
śiśire ca naravyāghra yaḥ śṛṇoti yathāvidhi
puṇḍarīkasya yajñasya sa prāpnoti phalaṃ naraḥ 105.101
madhumādhavasaṃjñe tu yaḥ śṛṇoti naras tv imān
so 'śvamedhakrator bhūpa prāpnoty avikalaṃ phalam 105.102
śṛṇvann etān nidāghe ca dharmān dharmabhṛtāṃ vara
vājapeyasya yajñasya phalaṃ prāpnoty asaṃśayam 105.103
varṣāsu cemān yo dharmān saṃśṛṇvan vasudhādhipa
rājasūyakratoḥ puṇyam akhilaṃ samavāpnuyāt 105.104
śaratkāle ca saṃśṛṇvan dharmān etān nararṣabha
prāpnoti gosavaphalaṃ samyak śraddhāsamanvitaḥ 105.105
ṛtuṣv eteṣv etad eva paṭhatām api pārthiva
phalaṃ bhavati duṣṭeṣu graheṣv ete śubhapradāḥ 105.106
kapilānāṃ śatasyoktaṃ yat phalaṃ jyeṣṭhapuṣkare
bhūyo bhūyas tad āpnoti pāraṇe pāraṇe gate 105.107
bhaktyā paṭhati yaś caitān devasya purato hareḥ
so 'rcayaty avanīpāla jñānayajñena keśavam 105.108
sarvābādhās tathā pāpam akhilaṃ manujeśvara
viṣṇudharmā vyapohanti saṃsmṛtāḥ paṭhitāḥ śrutāḥ 105.109
etat te sarvam ākhyātaṃ rahasyaṃ paramaṃ hareḥ
nātaḥ parataraṃ kiṃcic śrāvyaṃ śrutisukhāvaham 105.110
atroktavidhiyuktasya puruṣasya vipaścitaḥ
na durlabhaṃ naravyāghra paramaṃ brahma śāśvatam 105.111
